            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> <b class=\"calibre3\">Harry Potter is lucky to reach the age of</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">thirteen, since he has already survived the</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">murderous attacks of the feared Dark Lord</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">on more than one occasion. But his hopes</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">for a quiet term concentrating on  </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">Quidditch are dashed when a maniacal</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">mass-murderer escapes from Azkaban,</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">pursued by the soul-sucking Dementors</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">who guard the prison. It’s assumed that</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">Hogwarts is the safest place for Harry to</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">be. But is it a coincidence that he can feel</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">eyes watching him in the dark, and should</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">he be taking Professor Trelawney’s</b> <b class=\"calibre3\">ghoulish predictions seriously? </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I<b class=\"calibre3\"> </b>can honestly say I can’t remember the last time I encountered an author who has had this effect on me. For the first time in years the book lives up to the hype ... </p></div>"
        },
