            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rowling deserves all the plaudits that are being heaped upon her. For once, the word phenomenon is an understatement’ </p></div>"
        },
