            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">To Jill Prewett and Aine Kiely, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Godmothers of Swing </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER ONE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Owl Post </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter was a highly unusual boy in many ways. For one thing, he hated the summer holidays more than any other time of year. For another, he really wanted to do his homework, but was forced to do it in secret, in the dead of night. And he also happened to be a wizard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was nearly midnight, and he was lying on his front in bed, the blankets drawn right over his head like a tent, a torch in one hand and a large leather-bound book ( <i class=\"calibre4\">A History of Magic, </i> by Bathilda Bagshot) propped open against the pillow. Harry moved the tip of his eagle-feather quill down the page, frowning as he looked for something that would help him write his essay, ‘Witch-Burning in the Fourteenth Century Was Completely Pointless – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">discuss’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The quill paused at the top of a likely-looking paragraph. Harry pushed his round glasses up his nose, moved his torch closer to the book and read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Non-magic people (more commonly known as Muggles) were</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">particularly afraid of magic in medieval times, but not very</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">good at recognising it. On the rare occasion that they did catch</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">a real witch or wizard, burning had no effect whatsoever. The</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">witch or wizard would perform a basic Flame-Freezing Charm</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">and then pretend to shriek with pain while enjoying a gentle,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">tickling sensation. Indeed, Wendelin the Weird enjoyed being</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">burnt so much that she allowed herself to be caught no fewer</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">than forty-seven times in various disguises. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put his quill between his teeth and reached underneath his pillow for his ink bottle and a roll of parchment. Slowly and very </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>8 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">carefully he unscrewed the ink bottle, dipped his quill into it and began to write, pausing every now and then to listen, because if any of the Dursleys heard the scratching of his quill on their way to the bathroom, he’d probably find himself locked in the cupboard under the stairs for the rest of the summer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dursley family of number four, Privet Drive, was the reason that Harry never enjoyed his summer holidays. Uncle Vernon, Aunt Petunia and their son, Dudley, were Harry’s only living relatives. They were Muggles, and they had a very medieval attitude towards magic. Harry’s dead parents, who had been a witch and wizard themselves, were never mentioned under the Dursleys’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">roof. For years, Aunt Petunia and Uncle Vernon had hoped that if they kept Harry as downtrodden as possible, they would be able to squash the magic out of him. To their fury, they had been unsuccessful, and now lived in terror of anyone finding out that Harry had spent most of the last two years at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. The most the Dursleys could do these days was to lock away Harry’s spellbooks, wand, cauldron and broomstick at the start of the summer holidays, and forbid him to talk to the neighbours. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This separation from his spellbooks had been a real problem for Harry, because his teachers at Hogwarts had given him a lot of holiday work. One of the essays, a particularly nasty one about Shrinking Potions, was for Harry’s least favourite teacher, Professor Snape, who would be delighted to have an excuse to give Harry detention for a month. Harry had therefore seized his chance in the first week of the holidays. While Uncle Vernon, Aunt Petunia and Dudley had gone out into the front garden to admire Uncle Vernon’s new company car (in very loud voices, so that the rest of the street would notice it too), Harry had crept downstairs, picked the lock on the cupboard under the stairs, grabbed some of his books and hidden them in his bedroom. As long as he didn’t leave spots of ink on the sheets, the Dursleys need never know that he was studying magic by night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was keen to avoid trouble with his aunt and uncle at the moment, as they were already in a bad mood with him, all because he’d received a telephone call from a fellow wizard one week into the school holidays. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron Weasley, who was one of Harry’s best friends at Hogwarts, came from a whole family of wizards. This meant that he knew a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post 9 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">lot of things Harry didn’t, but had never used a telephone before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Most unluckily, it had been Uncle Vernon who had answered the call. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vernon Dursley speaking.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who happened to be in the room at the time, froze as he heard Ron’s voice answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HELLO? HELLO? CAN YOU HEAR ME? I – WANT – TO – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">TALK – TO – HARRY – POTTER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was yelling so loudly that Uncle Vernon jumped and held the receiver a foot away from his ear, staring at it with an expression of mingled fury and alarm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WHO IS THIS?’ he roared in the direction of the mouthpiece. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WHO ARE YOU?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘RON – WEASLEY!’ Ron bellowed back, as though he and Uncle Vernon were speaking from opposite ends of a football pitch. ‘I’M – A – FRIEND – OF – HARRY’S – FROM – SCHOOL –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon’s small eyes swivelled around to Harry, who was rooted to the spot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THERE IS NO HARRY POTTER HERE!’ he roared, now holding the receiver at arm’s length, as though frightened it might explode. ‘I DON’T KNOW WHAT SCHOOL YOU’RE TALKING </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ABOUT! NEVER CONTACT ME AGAIN! DON’T YOU COME </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">NEAR MY FAMILY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he threw the receiver back onto the telephone as if dropping a poisonous spider. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The row that had followed had been one of the worst ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HOW DARE YOU GIVE THIS NUMBER TO PEOPLE LIKE – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">PEOPLE LIKE  <i class=\"calibre4\">YOU! </i>’ Uncle Vernon had roared, spraying Harry with spit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron obviously realised that he’d got Harry into trouble, because he hadn’t called again. Harry’s other best friend from Hogwarts, Hermione Granger, hadn’t been in touch either. Harry suspected that Ron had warned Hermione not to call, which was a pity, because Hermione, the cleverest witch in Harry’s year, had Muggle parents, knew perfectly well how to use a telephone, and would probably have had enough sense not to say that she went to Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Harry had had no word from any of his wizarding friends for five long weeks, and this summer was turning out to be almost as bad as the last one. There was just one, very small improvement: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>10 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">after swearing that he wouldn’t use her to send letters to any of his friends, Harry had been allowed to let his owl, Hedwig, out at night. Uncle Vernon had given in because of the racket Hedwig made if she was locked in her cage all the time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry finished writing about Wendelin the Weird and paused to listen again. The silence in the dark house was broken only by the distant, grunting snores of his enormous cousin, Dudley. It must be very late. Harry’s eyes were itching with tiredness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps he’d finish this essay tomorrow night … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He replaced the top of the ink bottle, pulled an old pillowcase from under his bed, put the torch,  <i class=\"calibre4\">A History of Magic, </i> his essay, quill and ink inside it, got out of bed and hid the lot under a loose floorboard under his bed. Then he stood up, stretched, and checked the time on the luminous alarm clock on his bedside table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was one o’clock in the morning. Harry’s stomach gave a funny jolt. He had been thirteen years old, without realising it, for a whole hour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yet another unusual thing about Harry was how little he looked forward to his birthdays. He had never received a birthday card in his life. The Dursleys had completely ignored his last two birthdays, and he had no reason to suppose they would remember this one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry walked across the dark room, past Hedwig’s large, empty cage, to the open window. He leant on the sill, the cool night air pleasant on his face after a long time under the blankets. Hedwig had been absent for two nights now. Harry wasn’t worried about her – she’d been gone this long before – but he hoped she’d be back soon. She was the only living creature in this house who didn’t flinch at the sight of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, though still rather small and skinny for his age, had grown a few inches over the last year. His jet-black hair, however, was just as it always had been: stubbornly untidy, whatever he did to it. The eyes behind his glasses were bright green, and on his forehead, clearly visible through his hair, was a thin scar, shaped like a bolt of lightning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Of all the unusual things about Harry, this scar was the most extraordinary of all. It was not, as the Dursleys had pretended for ten years, a souvenir of the car crash that had killed Harry’s parents, because Lily and James Potter had not died in a car crash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had been murdered, murdered by the most feared Dark wizard </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post 11 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">for a hundred years, Lord Voldemort. Harry had escaped from the same attack with nothing more than a scar on his forehead, when Voldemort’s curse, instead of killing him, had rebounded upon its originator. Barely alive, Voldemort had fled … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry had come face to face with him since at Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Remembering their last meeting as he stood at the dark window, Harry had to admit he was lucky even to have reached his thir-teenth birthday. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He scanned the starry sky for a sign of Hedwig, perhaps soaring back to him with a dead mouse dangling from her beak, expecting praise. Gazing absently over the rooftops, it was a few seconds before Harry realised what he was seeing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silhouetted against the golden moon, and growing larger every moment, was a large, strangely lop-sided creature, and it was flapping in Harry’s direction. He stood quite still, watching it sink lower and lower. For a split second, he hesitated, his hand on the window-latch, wondering whether to slam it shut, but then the bizarre creature soared over one of the streetlamps of Privet Drive, and Harry, realising what it was, leapt aside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the window soared three owls, two of them holding up the third, which appeared to be unconscious. They landed with a soft  <i class=\"calibre4\">flump  </i> on Harry’s bed, and the middle owl, which was large and grey, keeled right over and lay motionless. There was a large package tied to its legs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry recognised the unconscious owl at once – his name was Errol, and he belonged to the Weasley family. Harry dashed to the bed at once, untied the cords around Errol’s legs, took off the parcel and then carried Errol to Hedwig’s cage. Errol opened one bleary eye, gave a feeble hoot of thanks, and began to gulp some water. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned back to the remaining owls. One of them, the large snowy female, was his own Hedwig. She, too, was carrying a parcel, and looked extremely pleased with herself. She gave Harry an affectionate nip with her beak as he removed her burden, then flew across the room to join Errol. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t recognise the third owl, a handsome tawny one, but he knew at once where it had come from, because in addition to a third parcel, it was carrying a letter bearing the Hogwarts crest. When Harry relieved this owl of its post it ruffled its feathers importantly, stretched its wings and took off through the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>12 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">window into the night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down on his bed, grabbed Errol’s package, ripped off the brown paper and discovered a present wrapped in gold, and his first ever birthday card. Fingers trembling slightly, he opened the envelope. Two pieces of paper fell out – a letter and a newspaper cutting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The cutting had clearly come out of the wizarding newspaper, the   <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet, </i> because the people in the black and white picture were moving. Harry picked up the cutting, smoothed it out and read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">MINISTRY OF MAGIC EMPLOYEE SCOOPS GRAND PRIZE </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Arthur Weasley, Head of the Misuse of Muggle Artefacts</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Office at the Ministry of Magic, has won the annual </i> Daily Prophet <i class=\"calibre4\"> Grand Prize Galleon Draw. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">A delighted Mr Weasley told the </i> Daily Prophet,  <i class=\"calibre4\"> ‘We will be</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">spending the gold on a summer holiday in Egypt, where our</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">eldest son, Bill, works as a curse breaker for Gringotts</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Wizarding Bank.’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Weasley family will be spending a month in Egypt,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">returning for the start of the new school year at Hogwarts,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">which five of the Weasley children currently attend. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry scanned the moving photograph, and a grin spread across his face as he saw all nine of the Weasleys waving furiously at him, standing in front of a large pyramid. Plump little Mrs Weasley, tall, balding Mr Weasley, six sons and one daughter, all (though the black and white picture didn’t show it) with flaming red hair. Right in the middle of the picture was Ron, tall and gan-gling, with his pet rat Scabbers on his shoulder and his arm around his little sister, Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t think of anyone who deserved to win a large pile of gold more than the Weasleys, who were very nice and extremely poor. He picked up Ron’s letter and unfolded it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Harry, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Happy birthday! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Look, I’m really sorry about that telephone call. I hope the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Muggles didn’t give you a hard time. I asked Dad, and he reckons I shouldn’t have shouted. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post 13 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">It’s brilliant here in Egypt. Bill’s taken us round all the tombs</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">and you wouldn’t believe the curses those old Egyptian wizards</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">put on them. Mum wouldn’t let Ginny come in the last one. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">There were all these mutant skeletons in there, of Muggles</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">who’d broken in and grown extra heads and stuff. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I couldn’t believe it when Dad won the </i> Daily Prophet  <i class=\"calibre4\">Draw. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Seven hundred galleons! Most of it’s gone on this holiday, but</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">they’re going to buy me a new wand for next year. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry remembered only too well the occasion when Ron’s old wand had snapped. It had happened when the car the two of them had been flying to Hogwarts had crashed into a tree in the school grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">We’ll be back about a week before term starts and we’ll be</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">going up to London to get my wand and our new books. Any</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">chance of meeting you there? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Don’t let the Muggles get you down! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Try and come to London, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">PS: Percy’s Head Boy. He got the letter last week. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced back at the photograph. Percy, who was in his seventh and final year at Hogwarts, was looking particularly smug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had pinned his Head Boy badge to the fez perched jauntily on top of his neat hair, his horn-rimmed glasses flashing in the Egyptian sun. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry now turned to his present and unwrapped it. Inside was what looked like a miniature glass spinning top. There was another note from Ron beneath it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry – this is a Pocket Sneakoscope. If there’s someone</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">untrustworthy around, it’s supposed to light up and spin. Bill</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">says it’s rubbish sold for wizard tourists and isn’t reliable,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">because it kept lighting up at dinner last night. But he didn’t</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">realise Fred and George had put beetles in his soup. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Bye – Ron</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put the Pocket Sneakoscope on his bedside table, where it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>14 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">stood quite still, balanced on its point, reflecting the luminous hands of his clock. He looked at it happily for a few seconds, then picked up the parcel Hedwig had brought. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Inside this, too, there was a wrapped present, a card and a letter, this time from Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Harry, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron wrote to me and told me about his phone call to your</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Uncle Vernon. I do hope you’re all right. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I’m on holiday in France at the moment and I didn’t know</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">how I was going to send this to you – what if they’d opened it at</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Customs? – but then Hedwig turned up! I think she wanted to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">make sure you got something for your birthday for a change. I</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">bought your present by owl-order; there was an advertisement</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">in the </i> Daily Prophet <i class=\"calibre4\"> (I’ve been getting it delivered, it’s so good</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">to keep up with what’s going on in the wizarding world). Did</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">you see that picture of Ron and his family a week ago? I bet he’s</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">learning loads, I’m really jealous – the ancient Egyptian wizards were fascinating. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">There’s some interesting local history of witchcraft here, too. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I’ve re-written my whole History of Magic essay to include some</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">of the things I’ve found out. I hope it’s not too long, it’s two rolls</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">of parchment more than Professor Binns asked for. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron  says  he’s  going  to  be  in  London  in  the  last  week  of  the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">holidays. Can you make it? Will your aunt and uncle let you</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">come? I really hope you can. If not, I’ll see you on the Hogwarts</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Express on September the first! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Love from</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hermione</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">P.S. Ron says Percy’s Head Boy. I’ll bet Percy’s really pleased. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron doesn’t seem too happy about it. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry laughed again as he put Hermione’s letter aside and picked up her present. It was very heavy. Knowing Hermione, he was sure it would be a large book full of very difficult spells – but it wasn’t. His heart gave a huge bound as he ripped back the paper and saw a sleek black leather case with silver words stamped across it:  <i class=\"calibre4\">Broomstick Servicing Kit. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wow, Hermione!’ Harry whispered, unzipping the case to look </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post 15 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a large jar of Fleetwood’s High-Finish Handle Polish, a pair of gleaming silver Tail-Twig Clippers, a tiny brass compass to clip onto your broom for long journeys, and a  <i class=\"calibre4\">Handbook of Do-it-Yourself Broomcare. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Apart from his friends, the thing that Harry missed most about Hogwarts was Quidditch, the most popular sport in the magical world – highly dangerous, very exciting and played on broomsticks. Harry happened to be a very good Quidditch player; he had been the youngest person in a century to be picked for one of the Hogwarts house teams. One of Harry’s most prized posses-sions was his Nimbus Two Thousand racing broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put the leather case aside and picked up his last parcel. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He recognised the untidy scrawl on the brown paper at once: this was from Hagrid, the Hogwarts gamekeeper. He tore off the top layer of paper and glimpsed something green and leathery, but before he could unwrap it properly, the parcel gave a strange quiver, and whatever was inside it snapped loudly – as though it had jaws. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry froze. He knew that Hagrid would never send him anything dangerous on purpose, but then, Hagrid didn’t have a normal person’s view of what was dangerous. Hagrid had been known to befriend giant spiders, buy vicious, three-headed dogs from men in pubs and sneak illegal dragon eggs into his cabin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry poked the parcel nervously. It snapped loudly again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry reached for the lamp on his bedside table, gripped it firmly in one hand and raised it over his head, ready to strike. Then he seized the rest of the wrapping paper in his other hand and pulled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And out fell – a book. Harry just had time to register its handsome green cover, emblazoned with the golden title,  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Monster</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Book of Monsters</i>, before it flipped onto its edge and scuttled sideways along the bed like some weird crab. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Uh oh,’ Harry muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The book toppled off the bed with a loud clunk and shuffled rapidly across the room. Harry followed it stealthily. The book was hiding in the dark space under his desk. Praying that the Dursleys were still fast asleep, Harry got down on his hands and knees and reached towards it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ouch!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>16 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The book snapped shut on his hand and then flapped past him, still scuttling on its covers. Harry scrambled around, threw himself forward and managed to flatten it. Uncle Vernon gave a loud, sleepy grunt in the room next door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hedwig and Errol watched interestedly as Harry clamped the struggling book tightly in his arms, hurried to his chest of drawers and pulled out a belt, which he buckled tightly around it.  <i class=\"calibre4\">The</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Monster Book </i> shuddered angrily, but could no longer flap and snap, so Harry threw it down on the bed and reached for Hagrid’s card. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Harry, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Happy Birthday! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Think you might find this useful for next year. Won’t say no</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">more here. Tell you when I see you. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hope the Muggles are treating you right. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">All the best, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hagrid</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It struck Harry as ominous that Hagrid thought a biting book would come in useful, but he put up Hagrid’s card next to Ron and Hermione’s, grinning more broadly than ever. Now there was only the letter from Hogwarts left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Noticing that it was rather thicker than usual, Harry slit open the envelope, pulled out the first page of parchment within and read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Mr Potter, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Please note that the new school year will begin on September</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the first. The Hogwarts Express will leave from King’s Cross</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Station, platform nine and three-quarters, at eleven o’clock. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Third-years are permitted to visit the village of Hogsmeade</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">at certain weekends. Please give the enclosed permission form</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">to your parent or guardian to sign. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">A list of books for next year is enclosed. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Yours sincerely, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Professor M. McGonagall</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Deputy Headmistress</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled out the Hogsmeade permission form and looked  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post 17 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">at it, no longer grinning. It would be wonderful to visit Hogsmeade at weekends; he knew it was an entirely wizarding village, and he had never set foot there. But how on earth was he going to persuade Uncle Vernon or Aunt Petunia to sign the form? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked over at the alarm clock. It was now two o’clock in the morning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Deciding that he’d worry about the Hogsmeade form when he woke up, Harry got back into bed and reached up to cross off another day on the chart he’d made for himself, counting down the days left until his return to Hogwarts. Then he took off his glasses and lay down, eyes open, facing his three birthday cards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Extremely unusual though he was, at that moment Harry Potter felt just like everyone else: glad, for the first time in his life, that it was his birthday. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWO — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went down to breakfast next morning to find the three Dursleys already sitting around the kitchen table. They were watching a brand-new television, a welcome-home-for-the-summer present for Dudley, who had been complaining loudly about the long walk between the fridge and the television in the living room. Dudley had spent most of the summer in the kitchen, his piggy little eyes fixed on the screen and his five chins wobbling as he ate continually. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down between Dudley and Uncle Vernon, a large, beefy man with very little neck and a lot of moustache. Far from wishing Harry a happy birthday, none of the Dursleys gave any sign that they had noticed Harry enter the room, but Harry was far too used to this to care. He helped himself to a piece of toast and then looked up at the newsreader on the television, who was halfway through a report on an escaped convict. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… the public is warned that Black is armed and extremely dangerous. A special hotline has been set up, and any sighting of Black should be reported immediately.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No need to tell us  <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i>’s no good,’ snorted Uncle Vernon, staring over the top of his newspaper at the prisoner. ‘Look at the state of him, the filthy layabout! Look at his hair!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He shot a nasty look sideways at Harry, whose untidy hair had always been a source of great annoyance to Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Compared to the man on the television, however, whose gaunt face was surrounded by a matted, elbow-length tangle, Harry felt very well groomed indeed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The newsreader had reappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Ministry of Agriculture and Fisheries will announce today –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on!’ barked Uncle Vernon, staring furiously at the newsreader. ‘You didn’t tell us where that maniac’s escaped from! What </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake 19 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">use is that? Lunatic could be coming up the street right now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia, who was bony and horse-faced, whipped around and peered intently out of the kitchen window. Harry knew Aunt Petunia would simply love to be the one to call the hotline number. She was the nosiest woman in the world and spent most of her life spying on her boring, law-abiding neighbours. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When will they  <i class=\"calibre4\">learn</i>,’ said Uncle Vernon, pounding the table with his large purple fist, ‘that hanging’s the only way to deal with these people?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very true,’ said Aunt Petunia, who was still squinting into next door’s runner-beans. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon drained his teacup, glanced at his watch and added, ‘I’d better be off in a minute, Petunia, Marge’s train gets in at ten.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, whose thoughts had been upstairs with the Broomstick Servicing Kit, was brought back to earth with an unpleasant bump. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aunt Marge?’ he blurted out. ‘Sh- <i class=\"calibre4\">she</i>’s not coming here, is she?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge was Uncle Vernon’s sister. Even though she was not a blood relative of Harry’s (whose mother had been Aunt Petunia’s sister), he had been forced to call her ‘Aunt’ all his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge lived in the country, in a house with a large garden, where she bred bulldogs. She didn’t often stay in Privet Drive, because she couldn’t bear to leave her precious dogs, but each of her visits stood out horribly vividly in Harry’s mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At Dudley’s fifth birthday party, Aunt Marge had whacked Harry around the shins with her walking stick to stop him beating Dudley at musical statues. A few years later, she had turned up at Christmas with a computerised robot for Dudley and a box of dog biscuits for Harry. On her last visit, the year before Harry had started at Hogwarts, Harry had accidentally trodden on the paw of her favourite dog. Ripper had chased Harry out into the garden and up a tree, and Aunt Marge had refused to call him off until past midnight. The memory of this incident still brought tears of laughter to Dudley’s eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Marge’ll be here for a week,’ Uncle Vernon snarled, ‘and while we’re on the subject,’ he pointed a fat finger threateningly at Harry, ‘we need to get a few things straight before I go and collect her.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley smirked and withdrew his gaze from the television. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>20 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Watching Harry being bullied by Uncle Vernon was Dudley’s favourite form of entertainment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Firstly,’ growled Uncle Vernon, ‘you’ll keep a civil tongue in your head when you’re talking to Marge.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ said Harry bitterly, ‘if she does when she’s talking to me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Secondly,’ said Uncle Vernon, acting as though he had not heard Harry’s reply, ‘as Marge doesn’t know anything about your <i class=\"calibre4\">abnormality</i>, I don’t want any – any  <i class=\"calibre4\">funny</i> stuff while she’s here. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You behave yourself, got me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I will if she does,’ said Harry through gritted teeth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And thirdly,’ said Uncle Vernon, his mean little eyes now slits in his great purple face, ‘we’ve told Marge you attend St Brutus’s Secure Centre for Incurably Criminal Boys.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ Harry yelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you’ll be sticking to that story, boy, or there’ll be trouble,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">spat Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat there, white-faced and furious, staring at Uncle Vernon, hardly able to believe it. Aunt Marge coming for a week-long visit – it was the worst birthday present the Dursleys had ever given him, including that pair of Uncle Vernon’s old socks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Petunia,’ said Uncle Vernon, getting heavily to his feet, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll be off to the station, then. Want to come along for the ride, Dudders?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Dudley, whose attention had returned to the television now that Uncle Vernon had finished threatening Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Duddy’s got to make himself smart for his auntie,’ said Aunt Petunia, smoothing Dudley’s thick blond hair. ‘Mummy’s bought him a lovely new bow-tie.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon clapped Dudley on his porky shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you in a bit, then,’ he said, and he left the kitchen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who had been sitting in a kind of horrified trance, had a sudden idea. Abandoning his toast, he got quickly to his feet and followed Uncle Vernon to the front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon was pulling on his car coat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not taking  <i class=\"calibre4\">you, </i>’ he snarled, as he turned to see Harry watching him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like I wanted to come,’ said Harry coldly. ‘I want to ask you something.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon eyed him suspiciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake 21 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Third-years at Hog– at my school are allowed to visit the village sometimes,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So?’ snapped Uncle Vernon, taking his car keys from a hook next to the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I need you to sign the permission form,’ said Harry in a rush. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And why should I do that?’ sneered Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Harry, choosing his words carefully, ‘it’ll be hard work, pretending to Aunt Marge I go to that St Whatsits …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘St Brutus’s Secure Centre for Incurably Criminal Boys!’ bellowed Uncle Vernon, and Harry was pleased to hear a definite note of panic in Uncle Vernon’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly,’ said Harry, looking calmly up into Uncle Vernon’s large, purple face. ‘It’s a lot to remember. I’ll have to make it sound convincing, won’t I? What if I accidentally let something slip?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You’ll get the stuffing knocked out of you, won’t you? </i>’ roared Uncle Vernon, advancing on Harry with his fist raised. But Harry stood his ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Knocking the stuffing out of me won’t make Aunt Marge forget what I could tell her,’ he said grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon stopped, his fist still raised, his face an ugly puce. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if you sign my permission form,’ Harry went on quickly, ‘I swear I’ll remember where I’m supposed to go to school, and I’ll act like a Mug– like I’m normal and everything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could tell that Uncle Vernon was thinking it over, even if his teeth were bared and a vein was throbbing in his temple. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ he snapped finally. ‘I shall monitor your behaviour carefully during Marge’s visit. If, at the end of it, you’ve toed the line and kept to the story, I’ll sign your ruddy form.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wheeled around, pulled open the front door and slammed it so hard that one of the little panes of glass at the top fell out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t return to the kitchen. He went back upstairs to his bedroom. If he was going to act like a real Muggle, he’d better start now. Slowly and sadly he gathered up all his presents and his birthday cards and hid them under the loose floorboard with his homework. Then he went to Hedwig’s cage. Errol seemed to have recovered; he and Hedwig were both asleep, heads under their wings. Harry sighed, then poked them both awake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hedwig,’ he said gloomily, ‘you’re going to have to clear off for </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>22 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a week. Go with Errol, Ron’ll look after you. I’ll write him a note, explaining. And don’t look at me like that’ – Hedwig’s large amber eyes were reproachful, ‘it’s not my fault. It’s the only way I’ll be allowed to visit Hogsmeade with Ron and Hermione.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ten minutes later, Errol and Hedwig (who had a note to Ron bound to her leg) soared out of the window and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, now feeling thoroughly miserable, put the empty cage away inside the wardrobe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry didn’t have long to brood. In next to no time, Aunt Petunia was shrieking up the stairs for Harry to come down and get ready to welcome their guest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do something about your hair!’ Aunt Petunia snapped as he reached the hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t see the point of trying to make his hair lie flat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge loved criticising him, so the untidier he looked, the happier she would be. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All too soon, there was a crunch of gravel outside as Uncle Vernon’s car pulled back into the driveway, then the clunk of the car doors, and footsteps on the garden path. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get the door!’ Aunt Petunia hissed at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A feeling of great gloom in his stomach, Harry pulled the door open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On the threshold stood Aunt Marge. She was very like Uncle Vernon; large, beefy and purple-faced, she even had a moustache, though not as bushy as his. In one hand she held an enormous suitcase, and tucked under the other was an old and evil-tempered bulldog. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s my Dudders?’ roared Aunt Marge. ‘Where’s my neffy poo?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley came waddling down the hall, his blond hair plastered flat to his fat head, a bow-tie just visible under his many chins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge thrust the suitcase into Harry’s stomach, knocking the wind out of him, seized Dudley in a tight one-armed hug and planted a large kiss on his cheek. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew perfectly well that Dudley only put up with Aunt Marge’s hugs because he was well paid for it, and sure enough, when they broke apart, Dudley had a crisp twenty-pound note clutched in his fat fist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Petunia!’ shouted Aunt Marge, striding past Harry as though he was a hat-stand. Aunt Marge and Aunt Petunia kissed, or rather, Aunt Marge bumped her large jaw against Aunt Petunia’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake 23 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bony cheekbone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon now came in, smiling jovially as he shut the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tea, Marge?’ he said. ‘And what will Ripper take?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ripper can have some tea out of my saucer,’ said Aunt Marge, as they all trooped into the kitchen, leaving Harry alone in the hall with the suitcase. But Harry wasn’t complaining; any excuse not to be with Aunt Marge was fine by him, so he began to heave the case upstairs into the spare bedroom, taking as long as he could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By the time he got back to the kitchen, Aunt Marge had been supplied with tea and fruitcake and Ripper was lapping noisily in the corner. Harry saw Aunt Petunia wince slightly as specks of tea and drool flecked her clean floor. Aunt Petunia hated animals. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s looking after the other dogs, Marge?’ Uncle Vernon asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I’ve got Colonel Fubster managing them,’ boomed Aunt Marge. ‘He’s retired now, good for him to have something to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I couldn’t leave poor old Ripper. He pines if he’s away from me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ripper began to growl again as Harry sat down. This directed Aunt Marge’s attention to Harry for the first time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So!’ she barked. ‘Still here, are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you say “yes” in that ungrateful tone,’ Aunt Marge growled. ‘It’s damn good of Vernon and Petunia to keep you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wouldn’t have done it myself. You’d have gone straight to an orphanage if you’d been dumped on  <i class=\"calibre4\">my </i> doorstep.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was bursting to say that he’d rather live in an orphanage than with the Dursleys, but the thought of the Hogsmeade form stopped him. He forced his face into a painful smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you smirk at me!’ boomed Aunt Marge. ‘I can see you haven’t improved since I last saw you. I hoped school would knock some manners into you.’ She took a large gulp of tea, wiped her moustache and said, ‘Where is it that you send him, again, Vernon?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘St Brutus’s,’ said Uncle Vernon promptly. ‘It’s a first-rate institu-tion for hopeless cases.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see,’ said Aunt Marge. ‘Do they use the cane at St Brutus’s, boy?’ she barked across the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>24 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon nodded curtly behind Aunt Marge’s back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. Then, feeling he might as well do the thing properly, he added, ‘All the time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent,’ said Aunt Marge. ‘I won’t have this namby-pamby, wishy-washy nonsense about not hitting people who deserve it. A good thrashing is what’s needed in ninety-nine cases out of a hundred. Have  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> been beaten often?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah,’ said Harry, ‘loads of times.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge narrowed her eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I still don’t like your tone, boy,’ she said. ‘If you can speak of your beatings in that casual way, they clearly aren’t hitting you hard enough. Petunia, I’d write if I were you. Make it clear that you approve the use of extreme force in this boy’s case.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps Uncle Vernon was worried that Harry might forget their bargain; in any case, he changed the subject abruptly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Heard the news this morning, Marge? What about that escaped prisoner, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Aunt Marge started to make herself at home, Harry caught himself thinking almost longingly of life at number four without her. Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia usually encouraged Harry to stay out of their way, which Harry was only too happy to do. Aunt Marge, on the other hand, wanted Harry under her eye at all times, so that she could boom out suggestions for his improvement. She delighted in comparing Harry with Dudley, and took huge pleasure in buying Dudley expensive presents while glaring at Harry, as though daring him to ask why he hadn’t got a present too. She also kept throwing out dark hints about what made Harry such an unsatisfactory person. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You mustn’t blame yourself for the way the boy’s turned out, Vernon,’ she said over lunch on the third day. ‘If there’s something rotten on the  <i class=\"calibre4\">inside, </i> there’s nothing anyone can do about it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to concentrate on his food, but his hands shook and his face was starting to burn with anger.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Remember the form, </i> he told himself.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Think about Hogsmeade. Don’t say anything. Don’t rise </i>– </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge reached for her glass of wine. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s one of the basic rules of breeding,’ she said. ‘You see it all the time with dogs. If there’s something wrong with the bitch, there’ll be something wrong with the pup –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake 25 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, the wine glass Aunt Marge was holding exploded in her hand. Shards of glass flew in every direction and Aunt Marge spluttered and blinked, her great ruddy face dripping. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Marge!’ squealed Aunt Petunia. ‘Marge, are you all right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not to worry,’ grunted Aunt Marge, mopping her face with her napkin. ‘Must have squeezed it too hard. Did the same thing at Colonel Fubster’s the other day. No need to fuss, Petunia, I have a very firm grip …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Aunt Petunia and Uncle Vernon were both looking at Harry suspiciously, so he decided he’d better skip pudding and escape from the table as soon as he could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Outside in the hall, he leant against the wall, breathing deeply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had been a long time since he’d lost control and made something explode. He couldn’t afford to let it happen again. The Hogsmeade form wasn’t the only thing at stake – if he carried on like that, he’d be in trouble with the Ministry of Magic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was still an underage wizard, and he was forbidden by wizard law to do magic outside school. His record wasn’t exactly clean, either. Only last summer he’d got an official warning which had stated quite clearly that if the Ministry got wind of any more magic in Privet Drive, Harry would face expulsion from Hogwarts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He heard the Dursleys leaving the table and hurried upstairs out of the way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got through the next three days by forcing himself to think about his  <i class=\"calibre4\">Handbook of Do-it-Yourself Broomcare</i> whenever Aunt Marge started on him. This worked quite well, though it seemed to give him a glazed look, because Aunt Marge started voicing the opinion that he was mentally subnormal. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, at long last, the final evening of Marge’s stay arrived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Petunia cooked a fancy dinner and Uncle Vernon uncorked several bottles of wine. They got all the way through the soup and the salmon without a single mention of Harry’s faults; during the lemon meringue pie, Uncle Vernon bored them all with a long talk about Grunnings, his drill-making company; then Aunt Petunia made coffee and Uncle Vernon brought out a bottle of brandy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can I tempt you, Marge?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge had already had rather a lot of wine. Her huge face was very red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>26 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just a small one, then,’ she chuckled. ‘A bit more than that … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and a bit more … that’s the boy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley was eating his fourth slice of pie. Aunt Petunia was sip-ping coffee with her little finger sticking out. Harry really wanted to disappear into his bedroom, but he met Uncle Vernon’s angry little eyes and knew he would have to sit it out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aah,’ said Aunt Marge, smacking her lips and putting the empty brandy glass back down. ‘Excellent nosh, Petunia. It’s normally just a fry-up for me of an evening, with twelve dogs to look after …’ She burped richly and patted her great tweed stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pardon me. But I do like to see a healthy-sized boy,’ she went on, winking at Dudley. ‘You’ll be a proper-sized man, Dudders, like your father. Yes, I’ll have a spot more brandy, Vernon …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, this one here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She jerked her head at Harry, who felt his stomach clench.  <i class=\"calibre4\">The</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Handbook</i>, he thought quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This one’s got a mean, runty look about him. You get that with dogs. I had Colonel Fubster drown one last year. Ratty little thing it was. Weak. Underbred.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry  was  trying  to  remember  page  twelve  of  his  book:   <i class=\"calibre4\">A</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Charm to Cure Reluctant Reversers. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It all comes down to blood, as I was saying the other day. Bad blood will out. Now, I’m saying nothing against your family, Petunia’ – she patted Aunt Petunia’s bony hand with her shovel-like one, ‘but your sister was a bad egg. They turn up in the best families. Then she ran off with a wastrel and here’s the result right in front of us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was staring at his plate, a funny ringing in his ears.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Grasp</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">your broom firmly by the tail, </i> he thought. But he couldn’t remember what came next. Aunt Marge’s voice seemed to be boring into him like one of Uncle Vernon’s drills. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This Potter,’ said Aunt Marge loudly, seizing the brandy bottle and splashing more into her glass and over the tablecloth, ‘you never told me what he did?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia were looking extremely tense. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dudley had even looked up from his pie to gape at his parents. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He – didn’t work,’ said Uncle Vernon, with half a glance at Harry. ‘Unemployed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As I expected!’ said Aunt Marge, taking a huge swig of brandy and wiping her chin on her sleeve. ‘A no-account, good-for-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Aunt Marge’s Big Mistake 27 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">nothing, lazy scrounger who –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was not,’ said Harry suddenly. The table went very quiet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was shaking all over. He had never felt so angry in his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘MORE BRANDY!’ yelled Uncle Vernon, who had gone very white. He emptied the bottle into Aunt Marge’s glass. ‘You, boy,’ he snarled at Harry. ‘Go to bed, go on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Vernon,’ hiccoughed Aunt Marge, holding up a hand, her tiny bloodshot eyes fixed on Harry’s. ‘Go on, boy, go on. Proud of your parents, are you? They go and get themselves killed in a car crash (drunk, I expect) –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They didn’t die in a car crash!’ said Harry, who found himself on his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They died in a car crash, you nasty little liar, and left you to be a burden on their decent, hardworking relatives!’ screamed Aunt Marge, swelling with fury. ‘You are an insolent, ungrateful little –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Aunt Marge suddenly stopped speaking. For a moment, it looked as though words had failed her. She seemed to be swelling with inexpressible anger – but the swelling didn’t stop. Her great red face started to expand, her tiny eyes bulged and her mouth stretched too tightly for speech. Next second, several buttons burst from her tweed jacket and pinged off the walls – she was inflating like a monstrous balloon, her stomach bursting free of her tweed waistband, each of her fingers blowing up like a salami … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘MARGE!’ yelled Uncle Vernon and Aunt Petunia together, as Aunt Marge’s whole body began to rise off her chair towards the ceiling. She was entirely round, now, like a vast life buoy with piggy eyes, and her hands and feet stuck out weirdly as she drifted up into the air, making apoplectic popping noises. Ripper came skidding into the room, barking madly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NOOOOOOO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Uncle Vernon seized one of Marge’s feet and tried to pull her down again, but was almost lifted from the floor himself. Next second, Ripper had leapt forward and sunk his teeth into Uncle Vernon’s leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tore from the dining room before anyone could stop him, heading for the cupboard under the stairs. The cupboard door burst magically open as he reached it. In seconds, he had heaved his trunk to the front door. He sprinted upstairs and threw himself under the bed, wrenched up the loose floorboard and grabbed </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>28 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the pillowcase full of his books and birthday presents. He wriggled out, seized Hedwig’s empty cage and dashed back downstairs to his trunk, just as Uncle Vernon burst out of the dining room, his trouser leg in bloody tatters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘COME  BACK  IN  HERE!’  he  bellowed.  ‘COME  BACK  AND </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">PUT HER RIGHT!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But a reckless rage had come over Harry. He kicked his trunk open, pulled out his wand and pointed it at Uncle Vernon. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She deserved it,’ Harry said, breathing very fast. ‘She deserved what she got. You keep away from me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He fumbled behind him for the catch on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going,’ Harry said. ‘I’ve had enough.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And next moment, he was out in the dark, quiet street, heaving his heavy trunk behind him, Hedwig’s cage under his arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER THREE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Knight Bus </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was several streets away before he collapsed onto a low wall in Magnolia Crescent, panting from the effort of dragging his trunk. He sat quite still, anger still surging through him, listening to the frantic thumping of his heart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But after ten minutes alone in the dark street, a new emotion overtook him: panic. Whichever way he looked at it, he had never been in a worse fix. He was stranded, quite alone, in the dark Muggle world, with absolutely nowhere to go. And the worst of it was, he had just done serious magic, which meant that he was almost certainly expelled from Hogwarts. He had broken the Decree for the Restriction of Underage Wizardry so badly, he was surprised Ministry of Magic representatives weren’t swooping down on him where he sat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shivered and looked up and down Magnolia Crescent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What was going to happen to him? Would he be arrested, or would he simply be outlawed from the wizarding world? He thought of Ron and Hermione, and his heart sank even lower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was sure that, criminal or not, Ron and Hermione would want to help him now, but they were both abroad, and with Hedwig gone, he had no means of contacting them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t have any Muggle money, either. There was a little wizard gold in the moneybag at the bottom of his trunk, but the rest of the fortune his parents had left him was stored in a vault at Gringotts Wizarding Bank in London.  He’d  never  be  able  to  drag his trunk all the way to London. Unless … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked down at his wand, which he was still clutching in his hand. If he was already expelled (his heart was now thumping painfully fast), a bit more magic couldn’t hurt. He had the Invisibility Cloak he had inherited from his father – what if he bewitched the trunk to make it feather-light, tied it to his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>30 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">broomstick, covered himself in the Cloak and flew to London? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he could get the rest of his money out of his vault and … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">begin his life as an outcast. It was a horrible prospect, but he couldn’t sit on this wall for ever or he’d find himself trying to explain to Muggle police why he was out in the dead of night with a trunkful of spellbooks and a broomstick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry opened his trunk again and pushed the contents aside, looking for the Invisibility Cloak – but before he had found it, he straightened up suddenly, looking around him once more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A funny prickling on the back of his neck had made Harry feel he was being watched, but the street appeared to be deserted, and no lights shone from any of the large square houses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bent over his trunk again, but almost immediately stood up once more, his hand clenched on his wand. He had sensed rather than heard it: someone or something was standing in the narrow gap between the garage and the fence behind him. Harry squinted at the black alleyway. If only it would move, then he’d know whether it was just a stray cat or – something else. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos, </i>’ Harry muttered, and a light appeared at the end of his wand, almost dazzling him. He held it high over his head, and the pebble-dashed walls of number two suddenly sparkled; the garage door gleamed, and between them, Harry saw, quite distinctly, the hulking outline of something very big, with wide, gleaming eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped backwards. His legs hit his trunk and he tripped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His wand flew out of his hand as he flung out an arm to break his fall, and he landed, hard, in the gutter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a deafening BANG and Harry threw up his hands to shield his eyes against a sudden blinding light … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a yell, he rolled back onto the pavement, just in time. A second later, a gigantic pair of wheels and headlights had screeched to a halt exactly where Harry had just been lying. They belonged, as Harry saw when he raised his head, to a triple-decker, violently purple bus, which had appeared out of thin air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gold lettering over the windscreen spelled  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Knight Bus. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a split second, Harry wondered if he had been knocked silly by his fall. Then a conductor in a purple uniform leapt out of the bus and began to speak loudly to the night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome to the Knight Bus, emergency transport for the stranded witch or wizard. Just stick out your wand hand, step on board and we can take you anywhere you want to go. My name is </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 31 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan Shunpike, and I will be your conductor this eve–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The conductor stopped abruptly. He had just caught sight of Harry, who was still sitting on the ground. Harry snatched up his wand again and scrambled to his feet. Close to, he saw that Stan Shunpike was only a few years older than he was; eighteen or nine-teen at most, with large, protruding ears and a fair few pimples. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What were you doin’ down there?’ said Stan, dropping his professional manner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fell over,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Choo fall over for?’ sniggered Stan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I didn’t do it on purpose,’ said Harry, annoyed. One of the knees in his jeans was torn, and the hand he had thrown out to break his fall was bleeding. He suddenly remembered why he had fallen over, and turned around quickly to stare at the alleyway between the garage and fence. The Knight Bus’s headlamps were flooding it with light, and it was empty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Choo lookin’ at?’ said Stan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There was a big black thing,’ said Harry, pointing uncertainly into the gap. ‘Like a dog … but massive …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked around at Stan, whose mouth was slightly open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a feeling of unease, Harry saw Stan’s eyes move to the scar on Harry’s forehead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Woss that on your ’ead?’ said Stan abruptly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry quickly, flattening his hair over his scar. If the Ministry of Magic was looking for him, he didn’t want to make it too easy for them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Woss your name?’ Stan persisted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Neville Longbottom,’ said Harry, saying the first name that came into his head. ‘So – so this bus,’ he went on quickly, hoping to distract Stan, ‘did you say it goes  <i class=\"calibre4\">anywhere? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yep,’ said Stan proudly, ‘anywhere you like, long’s it’s on land. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Can’t do nuffink underwater. ’Ere,’ he said, looking suspicious again, ‘you  <i class=\"calibre4\">did</i> flag us down, dincha? Stuck out your wand ’and, dincha?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry quickly. ‘Listen, how much would it be to get to London?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eleven Sickles,’ said Stan, ‘but for firteen you get ’ot chocolate, and for fifteen you get an ’ot-water bottle an’ a toofbrush in the colour of your choice.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry rummaged once more in his trunk, extracted his money </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>32 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bag and shoved some silver into Stan’s hand. He and Stan then lifted his trunk, with Hedwig’s cage balanced on top, up the steps of the bus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were no seats; instead, half-a-dozen brass bedsteads stood beside the curtained windows. Candles were burning in brackets beside each bed, illuminating the wood-panelled walls. A tiny wizard in a nightcap at the rear of the bus muttered, ‘Not now, thanks, I’m pickling some slugs,’ and rolled over in his sleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You ’ave this one,’ Stan whispered, shoving Harry’s trunk under the bed right behind the driver, who was sitting in an armchair in front of the steering wheel. ‘This is our driver, Ernie Prang. This is Neville Longbottom, Ern.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie Prang, an elderly wizard wearing very thick glasses, nodded to Harry, who nervously flattened his fringe again and sat down on his bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Take ’er away, Ern,’ said Stan, sitting down in the armchair next to Ernie’s. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was another tremendous BANG, and next moment Harry found himself flat on his bed, thrown backwards by the speed of the Knight Bus. Pulling himself up, Harry stared out of the dark window and saw that they were now bowling along a completely different street. Stan was watching Harry’s stunned face with great enjoyment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is where we was before you flagged us down,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where are we, Ern? Somewhere in Wales?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ar,’ said Ernie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How come the Muggles don’t hear the bus?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Them!’ said Stan contemptuously. ‘Don’ listen properly, do they? Don’ look properly either. Never notice nuffink, they don’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Best  go  wake  up  Madam  Marsh,  Stan,’  said  Ern.  ‘We’ll  be  in Abergavenny in a minute.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan passed Harry’s bed and disappeared up a narrow wooden staircase. Harry was still looking out of the window, feeling increasingly nervous. Ernie didn’t seem to have mastered the use of a steering wheel. The Knight Bus kept mounting the pavement, but it didn’t hit anything; lines of lamp posts, letter-boxes and bins jumped out of its way as it approached and back into position once it had passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan came back downstairs, followed by a faintly green witch wrapped in a travelling cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 33 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘’Ere you go, Madam Marsh,’ said Stan happily, as Ern stamped on the brake and the beds slid a foot or so towards the front of the bus. Madam Marsh clamped a handkerchief to her mouth and tottered down the steps. Stan threw her bag out after her and rammed the doors shut; there was another loud BANG, and they were thundering down a narrow country lane, trees leaping out of the way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wouldn’t have been able to sleep even if he had been travelling on a bus that didn’t keep banging loudly and jumping a hundred miles at a time. His stomach churned as he fell back to wondering what was going to happen to him, and whether the Dursleys had managed to get Aunt Marge off the ceiling yet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan had unfurled a copy of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> and was now reading with his tongue between his teeth. A large photograph of a sunken-faced man with long, matted hair blinked slowly at Harry from the front page. He looked strangely familiar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That man!’ Harry said, forgetting his troubles for a moment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was on the Muggle news!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stanley turned to the front page and chuckled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius Black,’ he said, nodding. ‘ ’Course ’e was on the Muggle news, Neville. Where you been?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave a superior sort of chuckle at the blank look on Harry’s face, removed the front page and handed it to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You oughta read the papers more, Neville.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry held the paper up to the candlelight and read: <i class=\"calibre4\">BLACK STILL AT LARGE </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Sirius Black, possibly the most infamous prisoner ever to be</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">held in Azkaban fortress, is still eluding capture, the Ministry of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Magic confirmed today. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘We are doing all we can to recapture Black,’ said the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Minister for Magic, Cornelius Fudge, this morning, ‘and we beg</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the magical community to remain calm.’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Fudge has been criticised by some members of the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">International Federation of Warlocks for informing the Muggle</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prime Minister of the crisis. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">‘Well, really, I had to, don’t you know,’ said an irritable</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Fudge. ‘Black is mad. He’s a danger to anyone who crosses him,</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">magic or Muggle. I have the Prime Minister’s assurance that he</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">will not breathe a word of Black’s true identity to anyone. And</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">let’s face it – who’d believe him if he did?’</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>34 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">While Muggles have been told that Black is carrying a gun</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">(a kind of metal wand which Muggles use to kill each other),</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the magical community lives in fear of a massacre like that of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">twelve years ago, when Black murdered thirteen people with a</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">single curse. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked into the shadowed eyes of Sirius Black, the only part of the sunken face that seemed alive. Harry had never met a vampire, but he had seen pictures of them in his Defence Against the Dark Arts classes, and Black, with his waxy white skin, looked just like one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scary-lookin’ fing, inee?’ said Stan, who had been watching Harry read. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He murdered  <i class=\"calibre4\">thirteen people? </i>’ said Harry, handing the page back to Stan, ‘with  <i class=\"calibre4\">one curse? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yep,’ said Stan. ‘In front of witnesses an’ all. Broad daylight. Big trouble it caused, dinnit, Ern?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ar,’ said Ern darkly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan swivelled in his armchair, his hands on the back, the better to look at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Black woz a big supporter of You-Know-’Oo,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What, Voldemort?’ said Harry, without thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even Stan’s pimples went white; Ern jerked the steering wheel so hard that a whole farmhouse had to jump aside to avoid the bus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You outta your tree?’ yelped Stan. ‘ ’Choo say ’is name for?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ said Harry hastily. ‘Sorry, I – I forgot –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Forgot!’ said Stan weakly. ‘Blimey, my ’eart’s goin’ that fast …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – so Black was a supporter of You-Know-Who?’ Harry prompted apologetically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Stan, still rubbing his chest. ‘Yeah, that’s right. Very close to You-Know-’Oo, they say … anyway, when little ’Arry Potter put paid to You-Know-’Oo’ – Harry nervously flattened his fringe down again – ‘all You-Know-’Oo’s supporters was tracked down, wasn’t they, Ern? Most of ’em knew it was all over, wiv You-Know-’Oo gone, and they came quiet. But not Sirius Black. I ’eard he thought ’e’d be second-in-command once You-Know-’Oo ’ad taken over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway, they cornered Black in the middle of a street full of Muggles an’ Black took out ’is wand and ’e blasted ’alf the street </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 35 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">apart, an’ a wizard got it, an’ so did a dozen Muggles what got in the way. ’Orrible, eh? An’ you know what Black did then?’ Stan continued in a dramatic whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Laughed, </i>’ said Stan. ‘Jus’ stood there an’ laughed. An’ when reinforcements from the Ministry of Magic got there, ’e went wiv </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">’em quiet as anyfink, still laughing ’is ’ead off. ’Cos ’e’s mad, inee, Ern? Inee mad?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If he weren’t when he went to Azkaban, he will be now,’ said Ern in his slow voice. ‘I’d blow meself up before I set foot in that place. Serves him right, mind … after what he did …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They ’ad a job coverin’ it up, din’ they, Ern?’ Stan said. ‘ ’Ole street blown up an’ all them Muggles dead. What was it they said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">’ad ’appened, Ern?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gas explosion,’ grunted Ernie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ now ’e’s out,’ said Stan, examining the newspaper picture of Black’s gaunt face again. ‘Never been a breakout from Azkaban before, ’as there, Ern? Beats me ’ow ’e did it. Frightenin’, eh? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mind, I don’t fancy ’is chances against them Azkaban guards, eh, Ern?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ernie suddenly shivered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Talk about summat else, Stan, there’s a good lad. Them Azkaban guards give me the collywobbles.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan put the paper away reluctantly and Harry leant against the window of the Knight Bus, feeling worse than ever. He couldn’t help imagining what Stan might be telling his passengers in a few nights’ time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Ear about that ’Arry Potter? Blew up ’is Aunt! We ’ad ’im ’ere on the Knight Bus, di’n’t we, Ern? ’E was tryin’ to run for it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He, Harry, had broken wizard law just like Sirius Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Was inflating Aunt Marge bad enough to land him in Azkaban? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know anything about the wizard prison, though everyone he’d ever heard speak of it did so in the same fearful tone. Hagrid the Hogwarts gamekeeper had spent two months there only last year. Harry wouldn’t soon forget the look of terror on Hagrid’s face when he had been told where he was going, and Hagrid was one of the bravest people Harry knew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus rolled through the darkness, scattering bushes and bollards, telephone boxes and trees, and Harry lay, restless </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>36 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and miserable, on his feather bed. After a while, Stan remembered that Harry had paid for hot chocolate, but poured it all over Harry’s pillow when the bus moved abruptly from Anglesey to Aberdeen. One by one, wizards and witches in dressing-gowns and slippers descended from the upper floors to leave the bus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They all looked very pleased to go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Finally, Harry was the only passenger left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then, Neville,’ said Stan, clapping his hands, ‘where-abouts in London?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Diagon Alley,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Righto,’ said Stan, ‘ ’old tight, then …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BANG! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were thundering along Charing Cross Road. Harry sat up and watched buildings and benches squeezing themselves out of the Knight Bus’s way. The sky was getting a little lighter. He would lie low for a couple of hours, go to Gringotts the moment it opened, then set off – where, he didn’t know. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ern slammed on the brakes and the Knight Bus skidded to a halt in front of a small and shabby-looking pub, the Leaky Cauldron, behind which lay the magical entrance to Diagon Alley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks,’ Harry said to Ern. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He jumped down the steps and helped Stan lower his trunk and Hedwig’s cage onto the pavement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Harry, ‘bye then!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Stan wasn’t paying attention. Still standing in the doorway to the bus, he was goggling at the shadowy entrance to the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">There</i> you are, Harry,’ said a voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Harry could turn, he felt a hand on his shoulder. At the same time, Stan shouted, ‘Blimey! Ern, come ’ere! Come ’ <i class=\"calibre4\">ere! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the owner of the hand on his shoulder and felt a bucketful of ice cascade into his stomach – he had walked right into Cornelius Fudge, the Minister for Magic himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Stan leapt onto the pavement beside them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What didja call Neville, Minister?’ he said excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge, a portly little man in a long, pinstriped cloak, looked cold and exhausted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Neville?’ he repeated, frowning. ‘This is Harry Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew it!’ Stan shouted gleefully. ‘Ern! Ern! Guess ’oo Neville </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 37 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">is, Ern! ’E’s ’Arry Potter! I can see ’is scar!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Fudge testily. ‘Well, I’m very glad the Knight Bus picked Harry up, but he and I need to step inside the Leaky Cauldron now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge increased the pressure on Harry’s shoulder, and Harry found himself being steered inside the pub. A stooping figure bearing a lantern appeared through the door behind the bar. It was Tom, the wizened, toothless landlord. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got him, Minister!’ said Tom. ‘Will you be wanting anything? Beer? Brandy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perhaps a pot of tea,’ said Fudge, who still hadn’t let go of Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud scraping and puffing from behind them, and Stan and Ern appeared, carrying Harry’s trunk and Hedwig’s cage and looking around excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Ow come you di’n’t tell us ’oo you are, eh, Neville?’ said Stan, beaming at Harry, while Ernie’s owlish face peered interestedly over Stan’s shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And a  <i class=\"calibre4\">private </i> parlour, please, Tom,’ said Fudge pointedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye,’ Harry said miserably to Stan and Ern, as Tom beckoned Fudge towards the passage that led from the bar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye, Neville!’ called Stan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge marched Harry along the narrow passage after Tom’s lantern, and then into a small parlour. Tom clicked his fingers, a fire burst into life in the grate, and he bowed himself out of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down, Harry,’ said Fudge, indicating a chair by the fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down, feeling goosebumps rising up his arms despite the glow of the fire. Fudge took off his pinstriped cloak and tossed it aside, then hitched up the trousers of his bottle-green suit and sat down opposite Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am Cornelius Fudge, Harry. The Minister for Magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry already knew this, of course; he had seen Fudge once before, but as he had been wearing his father’s Invisibility Cloak at the time, Fudge wasn’t to know that. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Tom the innkeeper reappeared, wearing an apron over his nightshirt and bearing a tray of tea and crumpets. He placed the tray on a table between Fudge and Harry, and left the parlour, closing the door behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Harry,’ said Fudge, pouring out tea, ‘you’ve had us all in a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>38 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">right flap, I don’t mind telling you. Running away from your aunt and uncle’s house like that! I’d started to think … but you’re safe, and that’s what matters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge buttered himself a crumpet and pushed the plate towards Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat, Harry, you look dead on your feet. Now then … You will be pleased to hear that we have dealt with the unfortunate blowing-up of Miss Marjorie Dursley. Two members of the Accidental Magic Reversal Squad were dispatched to Privet Drive a few hours ago. Miss Dursley has been punctured and her memory has been modified. She has no recollection of the incident at all. So that’s that, and no harm done.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge smiled at Harry over the rim of his teacup, rather like an uncle surveying a favourite nephew. Harry, who couldn’t believe his ears, opened his mouth to speak, couldn’t think of anything to say, and closed it again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, you’re worrying about the reaction of your aunt and uncle?’ said Fudge. ‘Well, I won’t deny that they are extremely angry, Harry, but they are prepared to take you back next summer as long as you stay at Hogwarts for the Christmas and Easter holidays.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry unstuck his throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I   <i class=\"calibre4\">always</i> stay at Hogwarts for the Christmas and Easter holidays,’ he said, ‘and I don’t ever want to go back to Privet Drive.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, now, I’m sure you’ll feel differently once you’ve calmed down,’ said Fudge in a worried tone. ‘They are your family, after all, and I’m sure you are fond of each other – er –  <i class=\"calibre4\">very</i> deep down.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It didn’t occur to Harry to put Fudge right. He was still waiting to hear what was going to happen to him now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So all that remains,’ said Fudge, now buttering himself a second crumpet, ‘is to decide where you’re going to spend the last three weeks of your holidays. I suggest you take a room here at the Leaky Cauldron and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on,’ blurted Harry, ‘what about my punishment?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge blinked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Punishment?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I broke the law!’ Harry said. ‘The Decree for the Restriction of Underage Wizardry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, my dear boy, we’re not going to punish you for a little </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 39 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">thing like that!’ cried Fudge, waving his crumpet impatiently. ‘It was an accident! We don’t send people to Azkaban just for blowing up their aunts!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But this didn’t tally at all with  Harry’s  past  dealings  with  the Ministry of Magic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Last year, I got an official warning just because a house-elf smashed a pudding in my uncle’s house!’ said Harry, frowning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Ministry of Magic said I’d be expelled from Hogwarts if there was any more magic there!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unless Harry’s eyes were deceiving him, Fudge was suddenly looking awkward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Circumstances change, Harry … we have to take into account </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… in the present climate … surely you don’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">want </i> to be expelled?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course I don’t,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well then, what’s all the fuss about?’ laughed Fudge airily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, have a crumpet, Harry, while I go and see if Tom’s got a room for you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge strode out of the parlour and Harry stared after him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was something extremely odd going on. Why had Fudge been waiting for him at the Leaky Cauldron, if not to punish him for what he’d done? And now Harry came to think of it, surely it wasn’t usual for the Minister for Magic  <i class=\"calibre4\">himself  </i> to get involved in matters of underage magic? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge came back, accompanied by Tom the innkeeper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Room eleven’s free, Harry,’ said Fudge. ‘I think you’ll be very comfortable. Just one thing, and I’m sure you’ll understand: I don’t want you wandering off into Muggle London, all right? Keep to  Diagon  Alley.  And  you’re  to  be  back  here  before  dark  each night. Sure you’ll understand. Tom will be keeping an eye on you for me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Harry slowly, ‘but why –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t want to lose you again, do we?’ said Fudge with a hearty laugh. ‘No, no … best we know where you are … I mean …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge cleared his throat loudly and picked up his pinstriped cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’ll be off, plenty to do, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you had any luck with Black yet?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge’s fingers slipped on the silver fastenings of his cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that? Oh, you’ve heard – well, no, not yet, but it’s only a matter of time. The Azkaban guards have never yet failed … and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>40 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they are angrier than I’ve ever seen them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge shuddered slightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, I’ll say goodbye.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He held out his hand and Harry, shaking it, had a sudden idea. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – Minister? Can I ask you something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly,’ smiled Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, third-years at Hogwarts are allowed to visit Hogsmeade, but my aunt and uncle didn’t sign the permission form. D’you think you could?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge was looking uncomfortable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ he said. ‘No. No, I’m very sorry, Harry, but as I’m not your parent or guardian –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you’re the Minister for Magic,’ said Harry eagerly. ‘If you gave me permission –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I’m sorry, Harry, but rules are rules,’ said Fudge flatly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perhaps you’ll be able to visit Hogsmeade next year. In fact, I think it best if you don’t … yes … well, I’ll be off. Enjoy your stay, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And with a last smile and shake of Harry’s hand, Fudge left the room. Tom now moved forward, beaming at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you’ll follow me, Mr Potter,’ he said. ‘I’ve already taken your things up …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry followed Tom up a handsome wooden staircase to a door with a brass number eleven on it, which Tom unlocked and opened for him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Inside was a very comfortable-looking bed, some highly polished oak furniture, a cheerfully crackling fire and, perched on top of the wardrobe – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hedwig!’ Harry gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The snowy owl clicked her beak and fluttered down onto Harry’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very smart owl you’ve got there,’ chuckled Tom. ‘Arrived about five minutes after you did. If there’s anything you need, Mr Potter, don’t hesitate to ask.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave another bow and left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat on his bed for a long time, absent-mindedly stroking Hedwig. The sky outside the window was changing rapidly from deep, velvety blue to cold, steely grey and then, slowly, to pink shot with gold. Harry could hardly believe that he’d only left Privet Drive a few hours ago, that he wasn’t expelled, and that he </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Knight Bus 41 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">was now facing three completely Dursley-free weeks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s been a very weird night, Hedwig,’ he yawned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And without even removing his glasses, he slumped back onto his pillows and fell asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FOUR — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Leaky Cauldron </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took Harry several days to get used to his strange new freedom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Never before had he been able to get up whenever he wanted or eat whatever he fancied. He could even go wherever he liked, as long as it was in Diagon Alley, and as this long cobbled street was packed with the most fascinating wizarding shops in the world, Harry felt no desire to break his word to Fudge and stray back into the Muggle world. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ate breakfast each morning in the Leaky Cauldron, where he liked watching the other guests: funny little witches from the country, up for a day’s shopping; venerable-looking wizards arguing over the latest article in  <i class=\"calibre4\">Transfiguration Today</i>; wild-looking warlocks, raucous dwarfs and, once, what looked suspiciously like a hag, who ordered a plate of raw liver from behind a thick woollen balaclava. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After breakfast Harry would go out into the back yard, take out his wand, tap the third brick from the left above the dustbin, and stand back as the archway into Diagon Alley opened in the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry spent the long sunny days exploring the shops and eating under the brightly coloured umbrellas outside cafés, where his fellow diners were showing each other their purchases (‘it’s a lunascope, old boy – no more messing around with moon charts, see?’) or else discussing the case of Sirius Black (‘personally, I won’t let any of the children out alone until he’s back in Azkaban’). Harry didn’t have to do his homework under the blankets by torchlight any more; now he could sit in the bright sun-shine outside Florean Fortescue’s Ice-Cream Parlour, finishing all his essays with occasional help from Florean Fortescue himself, who, apart from knowing a great deal about medieval witch-burnings, gave Harry free sundaes every half hour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once Harry had refilled his money bag with gold Galleons, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 43 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">silver Sickles and bronze Knuts from his vault at Gringotts, he needed to exercise a lot of self-control not to spend the whole lot at once. He had to keep reminding himself that he had five years to go at Hogwarts, and how it would feel to ask the Dursleys for money for spellbooks, to stop himself buying a handsome set of solid gold Gobstones (a wizarding game rather like marbles, in which the stones squirted a nasty-smelling liquid into the other player’s face when they lost a point). He was sorely tempted, too, by the perfect, moving model of the galaxy in a large glass ball, which would have meant he never had to take another Astronomy lesson. But the thing that tested Harry’s resolution most appeared in his favourite shop, Quality Quidditch Supplies, a week after he’d arrived at the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Curious to know what the crowd in the shop was staring at, Harry edged his way inside and squeezed in amongst the excited witches and wizards until he glimpsed a newly erected podium on which was mounted the most magnificent broom he had ever seen in his life. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just come out … prototype …’ a square-jawed wizard was telling his companion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the fastest broom in the world, isn’t it, Dad?’ squeaked a boy younger than Harry, who was swinging off his father’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Irish International Side’s just put in an order for seven of these beauties!’ the proprietor of the shop told the crowd. ‘And they’re favourites for the World Cup!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A large witch in front of Harry moved, and he was able to read the sign next to the broom: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">THE FIREBOLT</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">This state-of-the-art racing broom sports a streamlined, super-fine handle of ash, treated with a diamond-hard polish and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">hand-numbered with its own registration number. Each individ-ually selected birch twig in the broomtail has been honed to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">aerodynamic perfection, giving the Firebolt unsurpassable balance and pinpoint precision. The Firebolt has an acceleration of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">0–150 miles an hour in ten seconds and incorporates an</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">unbreakable braking charm. Price on request. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Price on request … Harry didn’t like to think how much gold the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>44 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Firebolt would cost. He had never wanted anything so much in his whole life – but he had never lost a Quidditch match on his Nimbus Two Thousand, and what was the point in emptying his Gringotts vault for the Firebolt, when he had a very good broom already? Harry didn’t ask for the price, but he returned, almost every day after that, just to look at the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were, however, things that Harry needed to buy. He went to the apothecary to replenish his store of Potions’ ingredients, and as his school robes were now several inches too short in the arm and leg, he visited Madam Malkin’s Robes for All Occasions and bought new ones. Most important of all, he had to buy his new school books, which would include those for his two new subjects, Care of Magical Creatures and Divination. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got a surprise as he looked in at the bookshop window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead of the usual display of gold-embossed spellbooks the size of paving slabs, there was a large iron cage behind the glass which held about a hundred copies of  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Monster Book of Monsters. </i>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Torn pages were flying everywhere as the books grappled with each other, locked together in furious wrestling matches and snapping aggressively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled his booklist out of his pocket and consulted it for the first time.  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Monster Book of Monsters</i> was listed as the set book for Care of Magical Creatures. Now Harry understood why Hagrid had said it would come in useful. He felt relieved; he had been wondering whether Hagrid wanted help with some terrifying new pet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry entered Flourish and Blotts, the manager came hurrying towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hogwarts?’ he said abruptly. ‘Come to get your new books?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. ‘I need –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way,’ said the manager impatiently, brushing Harry aside. He drew on a pair of very thick gloves, picked up a large, knobbly walking stick and proceeded towards the door of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Monster Books</i>’ cage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on,’ said Harry quickly, ‘I’ve already got one of those.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you?’ A look of enormous relief spread over the manager’s face. ‘Thank heavens for that, I’ve been bitten five times already this morning –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A loud ripping noise rent the air; two of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Monster Books </i> had seized a third and were pulling it apart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 45 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop it! Stop it!’ cried the manager, poking the walking stick through the bars and knocking the books apart. ‘I’m never stock-ing them again, never! It’s been bedlam! I thought we’d seen the worst when we bought two hundred copies of  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Invisible Book of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Invisibility</i> – cost a fortune, and we never found them … Well, is there anything else I can help you with?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry, looking down his booklist. ‘I need  <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Future</i>, by Cassandra Vablatsky.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, starting Divination, are you?’ said the manager, stripping off his gloves and leading Harry into the back of the shop, where there was a corner devoted to fortune-telling. A small table was stacked with volumes such as  <i class=\"calibre4\">Predicting the Unpredictable: Insulate</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Yourself against Shocks</i> and  <i class=\"calibre4\">Broken Balls: When Fortunes Turn Foul. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here you are,’ said the manager, who had climbed a set of steps to take down a thick, black-bound book. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future</i>. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Very good guide to all your basic fortune-telling methods – palmistry, crystal balls, bird entrails …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry wasn’t listening. His eyes had fallen on another book, which was among a display on a small table:  <i class=\"calibre4\">Death Omens: What to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Do When You Know the Worst Is Coming. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, I wouldn’t read that if I were you,’ said the assistant lightly, looking to see what Harry was staring at. ‘You’ll start seeing death omens everywhere, it’s enough to frighten anyone to death.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry continued to stare at the front cover of the book; it showed a black dog large as a bear, with gleaming eyes. It looked oddly familiar … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The assistant pressed  <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future </i> into Harry’s hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anything else?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry, tearing his eyes away from the dog’s and dazedly consulting his booklist. ‘Er – I need  <i class=\"calibre4\">Intermediate</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Transfiguration </i> and  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Standard Book of Spells, Grade Three. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry emerged from Flourish and Blotts ten minutes later with his new books under his arms, and made his way back to the Leaky Cauldron, hardly noticing where he was going and bumping into several people. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tramped up the stairs to his room, went inside and tipped his books onto his bed. Somebody had been in to tidy; the windows were open and sun was pouring inside. Harry could hear the buses rolling by in the unseen Muggle street behind him, and the sound of the invisible crowd below in Diagon Alley. He caught </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>46 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sight of himself in the mirror over the basin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It can’t have been a death omen,’ he told his reflection defiantly. ‘I was panicking when I saw that thing in Magnolia Crescent. It was probably just a stray dog …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised his hand automatically and tried to make his hair lie flat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re fighting a losing battle there, dear,’ said his mirror in a wheezy voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the days slipped by, Harry started looking wherever he went for a sign of Ron or Hermione. Plenty of Hogwarts students were arriving in Diagon Alley now, with the start of term so near. Harry met Seamus Finnigan and Dean Thomas, his fellow Gryffindors, in Quality Quidditch Supplies, where they, too, were ogling the Firebolt; he also ran into the real Neville Longbottom, a round-faced, forgetful boy, outside Flourish and Blotts. Harry didn’t stop to chat; Neville appeared to have mislaid his booklist, and was being told off by his very formidable-looking grandmother. Harry hoped she never found out that he’d pretended to be Neville while on the run from the Ministry of Magic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke on the last day of the holidays, thinking that he would at least meet Ron and Hermione tomorrow, on the Hogwarts Express. He got up, dressed, went for a last look at the Firebolt, and was just wondering where he’d have lunch, when someone yelled his name and he turned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! HARRY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were there, both of them, sitting outside Florean Fortescue’s Ice-Cream Parlour, Ron looking incredibly freckly, Hermione very brown, both waving frantically at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Finally!’ said Ron, grinning at Harry as he sat down. ‘We went to the Leaky Cauldron, but they said you’d left, and we went to Flourish and Blotts, and Madam Malkin’s, and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I got all my school stuff last week,’ Harry explained. ‘And how come you know I’m staying at the Leaky Cauldron?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dad,’ said Ron simply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley, who worked at the Ministry of Magic, would of course have heard the whole story of what had happened to Aunt Marge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you  <i class=\"calibre4\">really </i> blow up your aunt, Harry?’ said Hermione in a very serious voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 47 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I didn’t mean to,’ said Harry, while Ron roared with laughter. ‘I just – lost control.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not funny, Ron,’ said Hermione sharply. ‘Honestly, I’m amazed Harry wasn’t expelled.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So am I,’ admitted Harry. ‘Forget expelled, I thought I was going to be arrested.’ He looked at Ron. ‘Your dad doesn’t know why Fudge let me off, does he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably ’cause it’s you, isn’t it?’ shrugged Ron, still chuckling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Famous Harry Potter and all that. I’d hate to see what the Ministry’d do to  <i class=\"calibre4\">me</i> if I blew up an aunt. Mind you, they’d have to dig me up first, because Mum would’ve killed me. Anyway, you can ask Dad yourself this evening. We’re staying at the Leaky Cauldron tonight, too! So you can come to King’s Cross with us tomorrow! Hermione’s there as well!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione nodded, beaming. ‘Mum and Dad dropped me off this morning with all my Hogwarts things.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent!’ said Harry happily. ‘So, have you got all your new books and stuff?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at this,’ said Ron, pulling a long thin box out of a bag and opening it. ‘Brand-new wand. Fourteen inches, willow, containing one unicorn tail-hair. And we’ve got all our books’ – he pointed at a large bag under his chair. ‘What about those  <i class=\"calibre4\">Monster Books</i>, eh? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The assistant nearly cried when we said we wanted two.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s all that, Hermione?’ Harry asked, pointing at not one, but three, bulging bags in the chair next to her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I’m taking more new subjects than you, aren’t I?’  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione. ‘Those are my books for Arithmancy, Care of Magical Creatures, Divination, Study of Ancient Runes, Muggle Studies –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing Muggle Studies for?’ said Ron, rolling his eyes at Harry. ‘You’re Muggle-born! Your mum and dad are Muggles! You already know all about Muggles!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But it’ll be fascinating to study them from the wizarding point of view,’ said Hermione earnestly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you planning to eat or sleep at all this year, Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">asked Harry, while Ron sniggered. Hermione ignored them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve still got ten Galleons,’ she said, checking her purse. ‘It’s my birthday in September, and Mum and Dad gave me some money to get myself an early birthday present.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How about a nice <i class=\"calibre4\"> book? </i>’ said Ron innocently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>48 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I don’t think so,’ said Hermione composedly. ‘I really want an owl. I mean, Harry’s got Hedwig and you’ve got Errol –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I haven’t,’ said Ron. ‘Errol’s a family owl. All I’ve got is Scabbers.’ He pulled his pet rat out of his pocket. ‘And I want to get him checked over,’ he added, placing Scabbers on the table in front of them. ‘I don’t think Egypt agreed with him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scabbers was looking thinner than usual, and there was a definite droop to his whiskers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s a magical-creature shop just over there,’ said Harry, who knew Diagon Alley very well by now. ‘You can see if they’ve got anything for Scabbers, and Hermione can get her owl.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So they paid for their ice-creams and crossed the street to the Magical Menagerie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There wasn’t much room inside. Every inch of wall was hidden by cages. It was smelly and very noisy because the occupants of these cages were all squeaking, squawking, jabbering or hissing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The witch behind the counter was already advising a wizard on the care of double-ended newts, so Harry, Ron and Hermione waited, examining the cages. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pair of enormous purple toads sat gulping wetly and feasting on dead blowflies. A gigantic tortoise with a jewel-encrusted shell was glittering near the window. Poisonous orange snails were oozing slowly up the side of their glass tank, and a fat white rabbit kept changing into a silk top hat and back again with a loud popping noise. Then there were cats of every colour, a noisy cage of ravens, a basket of funny custard-coloured furballs that were humming loudly, and, on the counter, a vast cage of sleek black rats which were playing some sort of skipping game using their long bald tails. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The double-ended-newt wizard left and Ron approached the counter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s my rat,’ he told the witch. ‘He’s been a bit off-colour ever since I brought him back from Egypt.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bang him on the counter,’ said the witch, pulling a pair of heavy black spectacles out of her pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron lifted Scabbers out of his inside pocket and placed him next to the cage of his fellow rats, who stopped their skipping tricks and scuffled to the wire for a better look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Like nearly everything Ron owned, Scabbers the rat was second-hand (he had once belonged to Ron’s brother Percy) and a bit </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 49 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">battered. Next to the glossy rats in the cage, he looked especially woebegone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hm,’ said the witch, picking Scabbers up. ‘How old is this rat?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno,’ said Ron. ‘Quite old. He used to belong to my brother.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What powers does he have?’ said the witch, examining Scabbers closely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ said Ron. The truth was that Scabbers had never shown the faintest trace of interesting powers. The witch’s eyes moved from Scabbers’s tattered left ear to his front paw, which had a toe missing, and tutted loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s been through the mill, this one,’ she said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was like that when Percy gave him to me,’ said Ron defensively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An ordinary, common or garden rat like this can’t be expected to live longer than three years or so,’ said the witch. ‘Now, if you were looking for something a bit more hard-wearing, you might like one of these …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She indicated the black rats, who promptly started skipping again. Ron muttered, ‘Show-offs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, if you don’t want a replacement, you can try this Rat Tonic,’ said the witch, reaching under the counter and bringing out a small red bottle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Ron. ‘How much – OUCH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron buckled as something huge and orange came soaring from the top of the highest cage, landed on his head and then propelled itself, spitting madly, at Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NO, CROOKSHANKS, NO!’ cried the witch, but Scabbers shot from between her hands like a bar of soap, landed splay-legged on the floor and then scarpered for the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers!’ Ron shouted, haring out of the shop after him; Harry followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took them nearly ten minutes to find Scabbers, who had taken refuge under a wastepaper bin outside Quality Quidditch Supplies. Ron stuffed the trembling rat back into his pocket and straightened up, massaging his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was either a very big cat or quite a small tiger,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably getting her owl.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They made their way back up the crowded street to the Magical Menagerie. As they reached it, Hermione came out, but she wasn’t </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>50 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">carrying an owl. Her arms were clamped tightly around the enormous ginger cat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre4\">bought</i> that monster?’ said Ron, his mouth hanging open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">gorgeous, </i> isn’t he?’ said Hermione, glowing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That was a matter of opinion, thought Harry. The cat’s ginger fur was thick and fluffy, but it was definitely a bit bow-legged and its face looked grumpy and oddly squashed, as though it had run headlong into a brick wall. Now that Scabbers was out of sight, however, the cat was purring contentedly in Hermione’s arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, that thing nearly scalped me!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He didn’t mean to, did you, Crookshanks?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what about Scabbers?’ said Ron, pointing at the lump in his chest pocket. ‘He needs rest and relaxation! How’s he going to get it with that thing around?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That reminds me, you forgot your Rat Tonic,’ said Hermione, slapping the small red bottle into Ron’s hand. ‘And stop  <i class=\"calibre4\">worrying</i>, Crookshanks will be sleeping in my dormitory and Scabbers in yours. What’s the problem? Poor Crookshanks, that witch said he’d been in there for ages: no one wanted him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wonder why,’ said Ron sarcastically, as they set off towards the Leaky Cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They found Mr Weasley sitting in the bar, reading the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prophet</i>. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ he said, smiling as he looked up. ‘How are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine, thanks,’ said Harry, as he, Ron and Hermione joined Mr Weasley with all their shopping. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley put down his paper, and Harry saw the now familiar picture of Sirius Black staring up at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They still haven’t caught him, then?’ he asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Mr Weasley, looking extremely grave. ‘They’ve pulled us all off our regular jobs at the Ministry to try and find him, but no luck so far.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would we get a reward if we caught him?’ asked Ron. ‘It’d be good to get some more money –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be ridiculous, Ron,’ said Mr Weasley, who on closer inspection looked very strained. ‘Black’s not going to be caught by a thirteen-year-old wizard. It’s the Azkaban guards who’ll get him back, you mark my words.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment Mrs Weasley entered the bar, laden with shopping and followed by the twins, Fred and George, who were about </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 51 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">to start their fifth year at Hogwarts, the newly elected Head Boy, Percy, and the Weasleys’ youngest child and only girl, Ginny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny, who had always been very taken with Harry, seemed even more heartily embarrassed than usual when she saw him, perhaps because he had saved her life during their last term at Hogwarts. She went very red and muttered ‘hello’ without looking at him. Percy, however, held out his hand solemnly as though he and Harry had never met and said, ‘Harry. How nice to see you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello, Percy,’ said Harry, trying not to laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I hope you’re well?’ said Percy pompously, shaking hands. It was rather like being introduced to the mayor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well, thanks –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ said Fred, elbowing Percy out of the way and bowing deeply. ‘Simply  <i class=\"calibre4\">splendid</i> to see you, old boy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Marvellous,’ said George, pushing Fred aside and seizing Harry’s hand in turn. ‘Absolutely spiffing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy scowled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s enough, now,’ said Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mum!’ said Fred, as though he’d only just spotted her, and seized her hand, too. ‘How really corking to see you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I said, that’s enough,’ said Mrs Weasley, depositing her shopping in an empty chair. ‘Hello, Harry, dear. I suppose you’ve heard our exciting news?’ She pointed at the brand-new silver badge on Percy’s chest. ‘Second Head Boy in the family!’ she said, swelling with pride. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And last,’ Fred muttered under his breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t doubt that,’ said Mrs Weasley, frowning suddenly. ‘I notice they haven’t made you two Prefects.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do we want to be Prefects for?’ said George, looking revolted at the very idea. ‘It’d take all the fun out of life.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny giggled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to set a better example to your sister!’ snapped Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny’s got other brothers to set her an example, Mother,’ said Percy loftily. ‘I’m going up to change for dinner …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He disappeared and George heaved a sigh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We tried to shut him in a pyramid,’ he told Harry. ‘But Mum spotted us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>52 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dinner that night was a very enjoyable affair. Tom the innkeeper put three tables together in the parlour and the seven Weasleys, Harry and Hermione ate their way through five delicious courses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’re we getting to King’s Cross tomorrow, Dad?’ asked Fred, as they tucked into a sumptuous chocolate pudding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Ministry’s providing a couple of cars,’ said Mr Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone looked up at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ said Percy curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s because of you, Perce,’ said George seriously. ‘And there’ll be little flags on the bonnets, with HB on them –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– for Humungous Bighead,’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone except Percy and Mrs Weasley snorted into their pudding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why are the Ministry providing cars, Father?’ Percy asked again, in a dignified voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, as we haven’t got one any more,’ said Mr Weasley, ‘and as I work there, they’re doing me a favour …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His voice was casual, but Harry couldn’t help noticing that Mr Weasley’s ears had gone red, just like Ron’s did when he was under pressure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good job, too,’ said Mrs Weasley briskly. ‘Do you realise how much luggage you’ve all got between you? A nice sight you’d be on the Muggle Underground … You are all packed, aren’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron hasn’t put all his new things in his trunk yet,’ said Percy, in a long-suffering voice. ‘He’s dumped them on my bed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better go and pack properly, Ron, because we won’t have much time in the morning,’ Mrs Weasley called down the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron scowled at Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After dinner everyone felt very full and sleepy. One by one they made their way upstairs to their rooms to check their things for the next day. Ron and Percy were next door to Harry. He had just closed and locked his own trunk when he heard angry voices through the wall, and went to see what was going on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of number twelve was ajar and Percy was shouting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was  <i class=\"calibre4\">here</i>, on the bedside table, I took it off for polishing –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I haven’t touched it, all right?’ Ron roared back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My Head Boy badge has gone,’ said Percy, rounding on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So’s Scabbers’s Rat Tonic,’ said Ron, throwing things out of his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 53 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">trunk to look. ‘I think I might’ve left it in the bar –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re not going anywhere till you’ve found my badge!’ yelled Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll get Scabbers’s stuff, I’m packed,’ Harry said to Ron, and he went downstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was halfway along the passage to the bar, which was now very dark, when he heard another pair of angry voices coming from the parlour. A second later, he recognised them as Mr and Mrs Weasley’s. He hesitated, not wanting them to know he’d heard them rowing, when the sound of his own name made him stop, then move closer to the parlour door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… makes no sense not to tell him,’ Mr Weasley was saying heat-edly. ‘Harry’s got a right to know. I’ve tried to tell Fudge, but he insists on treating Harry like a child. He’s thirteen years old and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arthur, the truth would terrify him!’ said Mrs Weasley shrilly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you really want to send Harry back to school with that hanging over him? For heaven’s sake, he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">happy</i> not knowing!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want to make him miserable, I want to put him on his guard!’ retorted Mr Weasley. ‘You know what Harry and Ron are like, wandering off by themselves – they’ve even ended up in the Forbidden Forest! But Harry mustn’t do that this year! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When I think what could have happened to him that night he ran away from home! If the Knight Bus hadn’t picked him up, I’m prepared to bet he would have been dead before the Ministry found him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> dead, he’s fine, so what’s the point –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Molly, they say Sirius Black’s mad, and maybe he is, but he was clever enough to escape from Azkaban, and that’s supposed to be impossible. It’s been a month now, and no one’s seen hide nor hair of him, and I don’t care what Fudge keeps telling the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prophet</i>, we’re no nearer catching Black than inventing self-spelling wands. The only thing we know for sure is what Black’s after –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Harry will be perfectly safe at Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We thought Azkaban was perfectly safe. If Black can break out of Azkaban, he can break into Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But no one’s really sure that Black’s after Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a thud on wood, and Harry was sure Mr Weasley had banged his fist on the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Molly, how many times do I have to tell you? They didn’t </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>54 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">report it in the press because Fudge wanted it kept quiet, but Fudge went out to Azkaban the night Black escaped. The guards told Fudge that Black’s been talking in his sleep for a while now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Always the same words: “He’s at Hogwarts … he’s at Hogwarts.” </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black is deranged, Molly, and he wants Harry dead. If you ask me, he thinks murdering Harry will bring You-Know-Who back to power. Black lost everything the night Harry stopped You-Know-Who, and he’s had twelve years alone in Azkaban to brood on that …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a silence. Harry leant still closer to the door, desperate to hear more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Arthur, you must do what you think is right. But you’re forgetting Albus Dumbledore. I don’t think anything could hurt Harry at Hogwarts while Dumbledore’s Headmaster. I suppose he knows about all this?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course he knows. We had to ask him if he minds the Azkaban guards stationing themselves around the entrances to the school grounds. He wasn’t happy about it, but he agreed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not happy? Why shouldn’t he be happy, if they’re there to catch Black?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore isn’t fond of the Azkaban guards,’ said Mr Weasley heavily. ‘Nor am I, if it comes to that … but when you’re dealing with a wizard like Black, you sometimes have to join forces with those you’d rather avoid.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If they save Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– then I will never say another word against them,’ said Mr Weasley wearily. ‘It’s late, Molly, we’d better go up …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard chairs move. As quietly as he could, he hurried down the passage to the bar and out of sight. The parlour door opened, and a few seconds later footsteps told him that Mr and Mrs Weasley were climbing the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The bottle of Rat Tonic was lying under the table they had sat at earlier. Harry waited until he heard Mr and Mrs Weasley’s bedroom door close, then headed back upstairs with the bottle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George were crouching in the shadows on the landing, heaving with laughter as they listened to Percy dismantling his and Ron’s room in the search for his badge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got it,’ Fred whispered to Harry. ‘We’ve been improving it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The badge now read  <i class=\"calibre4\">Bighead Boy. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry forced a laugh, went to give Ron the rat tonic, then shut </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Leaky Cauldron 55 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">himself in his room and lay down on his bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So Sirius Black was after him. That explained everything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge had been lenient with him because he was so relieved to find him alive. He’d made Harry promise to stay in Diagon Alley, where there were plenty of wizards to keep an eye on him. And he was sending two Ministry cars to take them all to the station tomorrow, so that the Weasleys could look after Harry until he was on the train. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay listening to the muffled shouting next door and wondered why he didn’t feel more scared. Sirius Black had murdered thirteen people with one curse; Mr and Mrs Weasley obviously thought Harry would be panic-stricken if he knew the truth. But Harry happened to agree whole-heartedly with Mrs Weasley that the safest place on earth was wherever Albus Dumbledore happened to be. Didn’t people always say that Dumbledore was the only person Lord Voldemort had ever been afraid of? Surely Black, as Voldemort’s right-hand man, would be just as frightened of him? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then there were these Azkaban guards everyone kept talking about. They seemed to scare most people senseless, and if they were stationed all around the school, Black’s chances of getting inside seemed very remote. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No, all in all, the thing that bothered Harry most was the fact that his chances of visiting Hogsmeade now looked like zero. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody would want Harry to leave the safety of the castle until Black was caught; in fact, Harry suspected his every move would be carefully watched until the danger had passed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He scowled at the dark ceiling. Did they think he couldn’t look after himself? He’d escaped Lord Voldemort three times, he wasn’t completely useless … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Unbidden, the image of the beast in the shadows of Magnolia Crescent crossed his mind.  <i class=\"calibre4\">What to do when you know the worst is</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">coming </i>… </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m  <i class=\"calibre4\">not</i> going to be murdered,’ Harry said out loud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s the spirit, dear,’ said his mirror sleepily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FIVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Dementor </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Tom woke Harry next morning with his usual toothless grin and a cup of tea. Harry got dressed and was just persuading a dis-gruntled Hedwig to get back into her cage when Ron banged his way into the room, pulling a sweatshirt over his head and looking irritable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The sooner we get on the train, the better,’ he said. ‘At least I can get away from Percy at Hogwarts. Now he’s accusing me of dripping tea on his photo of Penelope Clearwater. You know,’ Ron grimaced, ‘his  <i class=\"calibre4\">girlfriend. </i> She’s hidden her face under the frame because her nose has gone all blotchy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got something to tell you,’ Harry began, but they were interrupted by Fred and George, who had looked in to congratulate Ron on infuriating Percy again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They headed down to breakfast, where Mr Weasley was reading the front page of the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> with a furrowed brow and Mrs Weasley was telling Hermione and Ginny about a Love Potion she’d made as a young girl. All three of them were rather giggly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What were you saying?’ Ron asked Harry, as they sat down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Later,’ Harry muttered, as Percy stormed in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had no chance to speak to Ron or Hermione in the chaos of leaving; they were too busy heaving all their trunks down the Leaky Cauldron’s narrow staircase and piling them up near the door, with Hedwig and Hermes, Percy’s screech owl, perched on top in their cages. A small wickerwork basket stood beside the heap of trunks, spitting loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all right, Crookshanks,’ Hermione cooed through the wickerwork, ‘I’ll let you out on the train.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You won’t,’ snapped Ron. ‘What about poor Scabbers, eh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pointed at his chest, where a large lump indicated that Scabbers was curled up in his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 57 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley, who had been outside waiting for the Ministry cars, stuck his head inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re here,’ he said. ‘Harry, come on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley marched Harry across the short stretch of pavement towards the first of two old-fashioned dark green cars, each of which was driven by a furtive-looking wizard, wearing a suit of emerald velvet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In you get, Harry,’ said Mr Weasley, glancing up and down the crowded street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry got into the back of the car, and was shortly joined by Hermione, Ron and, to Ron’s disgust, Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The journey to King’s Cross was very uneventful compared to Harry’s trip on the Knight Bus. The Ministry of Magic cars seemed almost ordinary, though Harry noticed that they could slide through gaps that Uncle Vernon’s new company car certainly couldn’t have managed. They reached King’s Cross with twenty minutes to spare; the Ministry drivers found them trolleys, unloaded their trunks, touched their hats to Mr Weasley and drove away, somehow managing to jump to the head of an unmoving queue for the traffic lights. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley kept close to Harry’s elbow all the way into the station. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then,’ he said, glancing around them. ‘Let’s do this in pairs, as there are so many of us. I’ll go through first with Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley strolled towards the barrier between platforms nine and ten, pushing Harry’s trolley and apparently very interested in the InterCity 125 that had just arrived at platform nine. With a meaningful look at Harry, he leant casually against the barrier. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry imitated him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next moment, they had fallen sideways through the solid metal onto platform nine and three-quarters and looked up to see the Hogwarts Express, a scarlet steam engine, puffing smoke over a platform packed with witches and wizards seeing their children onto the train. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy and Ginny suddenly appeared behind Harry. They were panting, and had apparently taken the barrier at a run. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, there’s Penelope!’ said Percy, smoothing his hair and going pink again. Ginny caught Harry’s eye and they both turned away to hide their laughter as Percy strode over to a girl with long, curly hair, walking with his chest thrown out so that she couldn’t </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>58 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">miss his shiny badge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once the remaining Weasleys and Hermione had joined them, Harry and Ron led the way to the end of the train, past packed compartments, to a carriage that looked quite empty. They loaded the trunks onto it, stowed Hedwig and Crookshanks in the luggage rack, then went back outside to say goodbye to Mr and Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mrs Weasley kissed all her children, then Hermione, and finally, Harry. He was embarrassed, but really quite pleased, when she gave him an extra hug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do take care, won’t you, Harry?’ she said as she straightened up, her eyes oddly bright. Then she opened her enormous handbag and said, ‘I’ve made you all sandwiches. Here you are, Ron … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">no, they’re not corned beef … Fred? Where’s Fred? Here you are, dear …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Mr Weasley quietly, ‘come over here a moment.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He jerked his head towards a pillar, and Harry followed him behind it, leaving the others crowded around Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s something I’ve got to tell you before you leave –’ said Mr Weasley, in a tense voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all right, Mr Weasley,’ said Harry, ‘I already know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know? How could you know?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – er – I heard you and Mrs Weasley talking last night. I couldn’t help hearing,’ Harry added quickly. ‘Sorry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s not the way I’d have chosen for you to find out,’ said Mr Weasley, looking anxious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No – honestly, it’s OK. This way, you haven’t broken your word to Fudge and I know what’s going on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, you must be very scared –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not,’ said Harry sincerely. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Really, </i>’ he added, because Mr Weasley was looking disbelieving. ‘I’m not trying to be a hero, but seriously, Sirius Black can’t be worse than Voldemort, can he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Mr Weasley flinched at the sound of the name, but overlooked it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, I knew you were, well, made of stronger stuff than Fudge seems to think, and I’m obviously pleased that you’re not scared, but –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arthur!’ called Mrs Weasley, who was now shepherding the rest onto the train. ‘Arthur, what are you doing? It’s about to go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s  coming,  Molly!’  said  Mr  Weasley,  but  he  turned  back  to </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 59 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and kept talking in a lower and more hurried voice. ‘Listen, I want you to give me your word –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– that I’ll be a good boy and stay in the castle?’ said Harry gloomily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not entirely,’ said Mr Weasley, who looked more serious than Harry had ever seen him. ‘Harry, swear to me you won’t go  <i class=\"calibre4\">looking</i> for Black.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. ‘What?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud whistle. Guards were walking along the train, slamming all the doors shut. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Promise me, Harry,’ said Mr Weasley, talking more quickly still, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘that whatever happens –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would I go looking for someone I know wants to kill me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Harry blankly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Swear to me that whatever you might hear –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arthur, quickly!’ cried Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Steam was billowing from the train; it had started to move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ran to the compartment door and Ron threw it open and stood back to let him on. They leant out of the window and waved at Mr and Mrs Weasley until the train turned a corner and blocked them from view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I need to talk to you in private,’ Harry muttered to Ron and Hermione as the train picked up speed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go away, Ginny,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, that’s nice,’ said Ginny huffily, and she stalked off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione set off down the corridor, looking for an empty compartment, but all were full except for the one at the very end of the train. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This only had one occupant, a man sitting fast asleep next to the window. Harry, Ron and Hermione checked on the threshold. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hogwarts Express was usually reserved for students and they had never seen an adult there before, except for the witch who pushed the food trolley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The stranger was wearing an extremely shabby set of wizard’s robes which had been darned in several places. He looked ill and exhausted. Though he seemed quite young, his light-brown hair was flecked with grey. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who d’you reckon he is?’ Ron hissed, as they sat down and slid the door shut, taking the seats furthest away from the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor R. J. Lupin,’ whispered Hermione at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>60 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How d’you know that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s on his case,’ replied Hermione, pointing at the luggage rack over the man’s head, where there was a small, battered case held together with a large quantity of neatly knotted string. The name  ‘Professor  R.  J.  Lupin’  was  stamped  across  one  corner  in peeling letters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder what he teaches?’ said Ron, frowning at Professor Lupin’s pallid profile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s obvious,’ whispered Hermione. ‘There’s only one vacancy, isn’t there? Defence Against the Dark Arts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione had already had two Defence Against the Dark Arts teachers, both of whom had only lasted one year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were rumours that the job was jinxed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I hope he’s up to it,’ said Ron doubtfully. ‘He looks like one good hex would finish him off, doesn’t he? Anyway …’ he turned to Harry, ‘what were you going to tell us?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry explained all about Mr and Mrs Weasley’s argument and the warning Mr Weasley had just given him. When he’d finished, Ron looked thunderstruck, and Hermione had her hands over her mouth. She finally lowered them to say, ‘Sirius Black escaped to come after  <i class=\"calibre4\">you? </i> Oh, Harry … you’ll have to be really, really careful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Don’t go looking for trouble, Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t go looking for trouble,’ said Harry, nettled. ‘Trouble usually finds  <i class=\"calibre4\">me</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How thick would Harry have to be, to go looking for a nutter who wants to kill him?’ said Ron shakily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were taking the news worse than Harry had expected. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both Ron and Hermione seemed to be much more frightened of Black than he was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one knows how he got out of Azkaban,’ said Ron uncomfortably. ‘No one’s ever done it before. And he was a top-security prisoner, too.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But they’ll catch him, won’t they?’ said Hermione earnestly. ‘I mean, they’ve got all the Muggles looking out for him, too …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that noise?’ said Ron suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A faint, tinny sort of whistle was coming from somewhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They looked all around the compartment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s coming from your trunk, Harry,’ said Ron, standing up and reaching into the luggage rack. A moment later he had pulled the Pocket Sneakoscope out from between Harry’s robes. It was spin-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 61 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ning very fast in the palm of Ron’s hand, and glowing brilliantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is that a  <i class=\"calibre4\">Sneakoscope? </i>’ said Hermione interestedly, standing up for a better look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah … mind you, it’s a very cheap one,’ Ron said. ‘It went hay-wire just as I was tying it to Errol’s leg to send it to Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Were you doing anything untrustworthy at the time?’ said Hermione shrewdly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No! Well … I wasn’t supposed to be using Errol. You know he’s not really up to long journeys … but how else was I supposed to get Harry’s present to him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stick it back in the trunk,’ Harry advised, as the Sneakoscope whistled piercingly, ‘or it’ll wake him up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He nodded towards Professor Lupin. Ron stuffed the Sneakoscope into a particularly horrible pair of Uncle Vernon’s old socks, which deadened the sound, then closed the lid of the trunk on it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We could get it checked in Hogsmeade,’ said Ron, sitting back down. ‘They sell that sort of thing in Dervish and Banges, magical instruments and stuff, Fred and George told me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you know much about Hogsmeade?’ asked Hermione keenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve read it’s the only entirely non-Muggle settlement in Britain –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I think it is,’ said Ron in an offhand sort of way, ‘but that’s not why I want to go. I just want to get inside Honeydukes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s this sweetshop,’ said Ron, a dreamy look coming over his face, ‘where they’ve got  <i class=\"calibre4\">everything  </i>… Pepper Imps – they make you smoke at the mouth – and great fat Chocoballs full of straw-berry mousse and clotted cream, and really excellent sugar quills which you can suck in class and just look like you’re thinking what to write next –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Hogsmeade’s a very interesting place, isn’t it?’ Hermione pressed on eagerly. ‘In  <i class=\"calibre4\">Sites of Historical Sorcery</i> it says the inn was the headquarters for the 1612 goblin rebellion, and the Shrieking Shack’s supposed to be the most severely haunted building in Britain –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and massive sherbet balls that make you levitate a few inches off the ground while you’re sucking them,’ said Ron, who was plainly not listening to a word Hermione was saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked around at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Won’t it be nice to get out of school for a bit and explore Hogsmeade?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>62 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Spect it will,’ said Harry heavily. ‘You’ll have to tell me when you’ve found out.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t go. The Dursleys didn’t sign my permission form, and Fudge wouldn’t, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked horrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You’re not allowed to come? </i> But – no way – McGonagall or someone will give you permission –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry gave a hollow laugh. Professor McGonagall, Head of Gryffindor house, was very strict. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– or we can ask Fred and George, they know every secret passage out of the castle –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ said Hermione sharply. ‘I don’t think Harry should be sneaking out of school with Black on the loose –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I expect that’s what McGonagall will say when I ask for permission,’ said Harry bitterly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if  <i class=\"calibre4\">we’re</i> with him,’ said Ron spiritedly to Hermione, ‘Black wouldn’t dare –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Ron, don’t talk rubbish,’ snapped Hermione. ‘Black’s already murdered a whole bunch of people in the middle of a crowded street, do you really think he’s going to worry about attacking Harry just because  <i class=\"calibre4\">we’re</i> there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She was fumbling with the straps of Crookshanks’s basket as she spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t let that thing out!’ Ron said, but too late; Crookshanks leapt lightly from the basket, stretched, yawned, and sprang onto Ron’s knees; the lump in Ron’s pocket trembled and he shoved Crookshanks angrily away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, don’t!’ said Hermione angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was about to answer back when Professor Lupin stirred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They watched him apprehensively, but he simply turned his head the other way, mouth slightly open, and slept on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hogwarts Express moved steadily north and the scenery outside the window became wilder and darker while the clouds overhead thickened. People were chasing backwards and forwards past the door of their compartment. Crookshanks had now settled in an empty seat, his squashed face turned towards Ron, his yellow eyes on Ron’s top pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At one o’clock the plump witch with the food trolley arrived at </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 63 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the compartment door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think we should wake him up?’ Ron asked awkwardly, nodding towards Professor Lupin. ‘He looks like he could do with some food.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione approached Professor Lupin cautiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – Professor?’ she said. ‘Excuse me – Professor?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry, dear,’ said the witch, as she handed Harry a large stack of Cauldron Cakes. ‘If he’s hungry when he wakes, I’ll be up front with the driver.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose he  <i class=\"calibre4\">is </i> asleep?’ said Ron quietly, as the witch slid the compartment door closed. ‘I mean – he hasn’t died, has he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, he’s breathing,’ whispered Hermione, taking the Cauldron Cake Harry passed her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He might not be very good company, but Professor Lupin’s presence in their compartment had its uses. Mid-afternoon, just as it had started to rain, blurring the rolling hills outside the window, they heard footsteps in the corridor again, and their three least favourite people appeared at the door: Draco Malfoy, flanked by his cronies, Vincent Crabbe and Gregory Goyle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Draco Malfoy and Harry had been enemies ever since they had met on their very first train journey to Hogwarts. Malfoy, who had a pale, pointed, sneering face, was in Slytherin house; he played Seeker on the Slytherin Quidditch team, the same position that Harry played on the Gryffindor team. Crabbe and Goyle seemed to exist to do Malfoy’s bidding. They were both wide and muscly; Crabbe was the taller, with a pudding-basin haircut and a very thick neck; Goyle had short, bristly hair and long, gorilla arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, look who it is,’ said Malfoy in his usual lazy drawl, pulling open the compartment door. ‘Potty and the Weasel.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle chuckled trollishly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard your father finally got his hands on some gold this summer, Weasley,’ said Malfoy. ‘Did your mother die of shock?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stood up so quickly he knocked Crookshanks’s basket to the floor. Professor Lupin gave a snort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s that?’ said Malfoy, taking an automatic step backwards as he spotted Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘New teacher,’ said Harry, who had got to his feet, too, in case he needed to hold Ron back. ‘What were you saying, Malfoy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>64 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy’s  pale  eyes  narrowed;  he  wasn’t  fool  enough  to  pick  a fight right under a teacher’s nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon,’ he muttered resentfully to Crabbe and Goyle, and they disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron sat down again, Ron massaging his knuckles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not going to take any rubbish from Malfoy this year,’ he said angrily. ‘I mean it. If he makes one more crack about my family, I’m going to get hold of his head and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron made a violent gesture in mid-air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron,’ hissed Hermione, pointing at Professor Lupin, ‘be  <i class=\"calibre4\">careful</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Professor Lupin was still fast asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rain thickened as the train sped yet further north; the windows were now a solid, shimmering grey, which gradually darkened until lanterns flickered into life all along the corridors and over the luggage racks. The train rattled, the rain hammered, the wind roared, but still, Professor Lupin slept. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We must be nearly there,’ said Ron, leaning forward to look past Professor Lupin at the now completely black window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The words had hardly left him when the train started to slow down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant,’ said Ron, getting up and walking carefully past Professor Lupin to try and see outside. ‘I’m starving, I want to get to the feast …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can’t be there yet,’ said Hermione, checking her watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So why’re we stopping?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The train was getting slower and slower. As the noise of the pistons fell away, the wind and rain sounded louder than ever against the windows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who was nearest the door, got up to look into the corridor. All along the carriage, heads were sticking curiously out of their compartments. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The train came to a stop with a jolt and distant thuds and bangs told them that luggage had fallen out of the racks. Then, without warning, all the lamps went out and they were plunged into total darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ said Ron’s voice from behind Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ouch!’ gasped Hermione. ‘Ron, that was my foot!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt his way back to his seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think we’ve broken down?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 65 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a squeaking sound, and Harry saw the dim black outline of Ron, wiping a patch clean on the window and peering out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s something moving out there,’ Ron said. ‘I think people are coming aboard …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The compartment door suddenly opened and someone fell painfully over Harry’s legs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry! D’you know what’s going on? Ouch! Sorry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello, Neville,’ said Harry, feeling around in the dark and pulling Neville up by his cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry? Is that you? What’s happening?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No idea! Sit down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud hissing and a yelp of pain; Neville had tried to sit on Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to go and ask the driver what’s going on,’ came Hermione’s voice. Harry felt her pass him, heard the door slide open again and then a thud and two loud squeals of pain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">that? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ginny?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was looking for Ron –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come in and sit down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not here!’ said Harry hurriedly. ‘I’m here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ouch!’ said Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quiet!’ said a hoarse voice suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin appeared to have woken up at last. Harry could hear movements in his corner. None of them spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a soft, crackling noise and a shivering light filled the compartment. Professor Lupin appeared to be holding a handful of flames. They illuminated his tired grey face, but his eyes looked alert and wary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stay where you are,’ he said, in the same hoarse voice, and he got slowly to his feet with his handful of fire held out in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the door slid slowly open before Lupin could reach it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Standing in the doorway, illuminated by the shivering flames in Lupin’s hand, was a cloaked figure that towered to the ceiling. Its face was completely hidden beneath its hood. Harry’s eyes darted </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>66 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">downwards, and what he saw made his stomach contract. There was a hand protruding from the cloak and it was glistening, grey-ish, slimy-looking and scabbed, like something dead that had decayed in water … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was visible only for a split second. As though the creature beneath the cloak sensed Harry’s gaze, the hand was suddenly withdrawn into the folds of the black material. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then the thing beneath the hood, whatever it was, drew a long, slow, rattling breath, as though it was trying to suck something more than air from its surroundings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">An intense cold swept over them all. Harry felt his own breath catch in his chest. The cold went deeper than his skin. It was inside his chest, it was inside his very heart … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s eyes rolled up into his head. He couldn’t see. He was drowning in cold. There was a rushing in his ears as though of water. He was being dragged downwards, the roaring growing louder … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, from far away, he heard screaming, terrible, terrified, pleading  screams.  He  wanted  to  help  whoever  it  was,  he  tried  to move his arms, but couldn’t … a thick white fog was swirling around him, inside him – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry! Are you all right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone was slapping his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘W-what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry opened his eyes. There were lanterns above him, and the floor was shaking – the Hogwarts Express was moving again and the lights had come back on. He seemed to have slid out of his seat onto the floor. Ron and Hermione were kneeling next to him, and above them he could see Neville and Professor Lupin watching. Harry felt very sick; when he put up his hand to push his glasses back on, he felt cold sweat on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione heaved him back onto his seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you OK?’ Ron asked nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Harry, looking quickly towards the door. The hooded creature had vanished. ‘What happened? Where’s that – that thing? Who screamed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one screamed,’ said Ron, more nervously still. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around the bright compartment. Ginny and Neville looked back at him, both very pale. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I heard screaming –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 67 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A loud snap made them all jump. Professor Lupin was breaking an enormous slab of chocolate into pieces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here,’ he said to Harry, handing him a particularly large piece. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat it. It’ll help.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took the chocolate but didn’t eat it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was that thing?’ he asked Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Dementor,’ said Lupin, who was now giving chocolate to everyone else. ‘One of the Dementors of Azkaban.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone stared at him. Professor Lupin crumpled up the empty chocolate wrapper and put it in his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat,’ he repeated. ‘It’ll help. I need to speak to the driver, excuse me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strolled past Harry and disappeared into the corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you sure you’re OK, Harry?’ said Hermione, watching Harry anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t get it … what happened?’ said Harry, wiping more sweat off his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – that thing – the Dementor – stood there and looked around (I mean, I think it did, I couldn’t see its face) – and you – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought you were having a fit or something,’ said Ron, who still looked scared. ‘You went sort of rigid and fell out of your seat and started twitching –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Professor Lupin stepped over you, and walked towards the Dementor, and pulled out his wand,’ said Hermione. ‘And he said, “None of us is hiding Sirius Black under our cloaks. Go.” But the Dementor didn’t move, so Lupin muttered something, and a silvery thing shot out of his wand at it, and it turned round and sort of glided away …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was horrible,’ said Neville, in a higher voice than usual. ‘Did you feel how cold it went when it came in?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I felt weird,’ said Ron, shifting his shoulders uncomfortably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like I’d never be cheerful again …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ginny, who was huddled in her corner looking nearly as bad as Harry felt, gave a small sob; Hermione went over and put a comforting arm around her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But didn’t any of you – fall off your seats?’ said Harry awkwardly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Ron, looking anxiously at Harry again. ‘Ginny was shaking like mad, though …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>68 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t understand. He felt weak and shivery, as though he was recovering from a bad bout of flu; he also felt the beginnings of shame. Why had he gone to pieces like that, when no one else had? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin had come back. He paused as he entered, looked around and said, with a small smile, ‘I haven’t poisoned that chocolate, you know …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took a bite and to his great surprise felt warmth spread suddenly to the tips of his fingers and toes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll be at Hogwarts in ten minutes,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘Are you all right, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t ask how Professor Lupin knew his name. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine,’ he muttered, embarrassed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t talk much during the remainder of the journey. At long last, the train stopped at Hogsmeade station, and there was a great scramble to get out; owls hooted, cats miaowed, and Neville’s pet toad croaked loudly from under his hat. It was freezing on the tiny platform; rain was driving down in icy sheets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Firs’-years this way!’ called a familiar voice. Harry, Ron and Hermione turned and saw the gigantic outline of Hagrid at the other end of the platform, beckoning the terrified-looking new students forward for their traditional journey across the lake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All righ’, you three?’ Hagrid yelled over the heads of the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They waved at him, but had no chance to speak to him because the mass of people around them was shunting them away along the platform. Harry, Ron and Hermione followed the rest of the school out onto a rough mud track, where at least a hundred stagecoaches awaited the remaining students, each pulled, Harry could only assume, by an invisible horse, because when they climbed inside one and shut the door, the coach set off all by itself, bumping and swaying in procession. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The coach smelled faintly of mould and straw. Harry felt better since the chocolate, but still weak. Ron and Hermione kept looking at him sideways, as though frightened he might collapse again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the carriage trundled towards a pair of magnificent wrought-iron gates, flanked with stone columns topped with winged boars, Harry saw two more towering, hooded Dementors, standing guard on either side. A wave of cold sickness threatened to engulf him again; he leant back into the lumpy seat and closed his eyes until </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 69 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they had passed through the gates. The carriage picked up speed on the long, sloping drive up to the castle; Hermione was leaning out of the tiny window, watching the many turrets and towers draw nearer. At last, the carriage swayed to a halt, and Hermione and Ron got out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry stepped down, a drawling, delighted voice sounded in his ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You   <i class=\"calibre4\">fainted</i>, Potter? Is Longbottom telling the truth? You actually  <i class=\"calibre4\">fainted? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy elbowed past Hermione to block Harry’s way up the stone steps to the castle, his face gleeful and his pale eyes glinting maliciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shove off, Malfoy,’ said Ron, whose jaw was clenched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you faint as well, Weasley?’ said Malfoy loudly. ‘Did the scary old Dementor frighten you, too, Weasley?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is there a problem?’ said a mild voice. Professor Lupin had just got out of the next carriage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy gave Professor Lupin an insolent stare, which took in the patches on his robes and the dilapidated suitcase. With a tiny hint of sarcasm in his voice, he said, ‘Oh, no – er –  <i class=\"calibre4\">Professor</i>,’ then he smirked at Crabbe and Goyle, and led them up the steps into the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione prodded Ron in the back to make him hurry, and the three of them joined the crowd swarming up the steps, through the giant oak front doors, and into the cavernous Entrance Hall, which was lit with flaming torches and housed a magnificent marble staircase which led to the upper floors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door into the Great Hall stood open at the right; Harry followed the crowd towards it, but had barely glimpsed the enchanted ceiling, which was black and cloudy tonight, when a voice called, ‘Potter! Granger! I want to see you both!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione turned around, surprised. Professor McGonagall, Transfiguration teacher and Head of Gryffindor house, was calling over the heads of the crowd. She was a stern-looking witch who wore her hair in a tight bun; her sharp eyes were framed with square spectacles. Harry fought his way over to her with a feeling of foreboding; Professor McGonagall had a way of making him feel he must have done something wrong. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s no need to look so worried – I just want a word in my office,’ she told them. ‘Move along there, Weasley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>70 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stared as Professor McGonagall ushered Harry and Hermione away from the chattering crowd; they accompanied her across the Entrance Hall, up the marble staircase and along a corridor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once they were in her office, a small room with a large, welcoming fire, Professor McGonagall motioned Harry and Hermione to sit down. She settled herself behind her desk and said abruptly, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin sent an owl ahead to say that you were taken ill on the train, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Harry could reply, there was a soft knock on the door and Madam Pomfrey, the matron, came bustling in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt himself going red in the face. It was bad enough that he’d passed out, or whatever he had done, without everyone making all this fuss. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m fine,’ he said. ‘I don’t need anything –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, it’s you, is it?’ said Madam Pomfrey, ignoring this and bending down to stare closely at him. ‘I suppose you’ve been doing something dangerous again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was a Dementor, Poppy,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They exchanged a dark look and Madam Pomfrey clucked disapprovingly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Setting Dementors around a school,’ she muttered, pushing Harry’s hair back and feeling his forehead. ‘He won’t be the last one who collapses. Yes, he’s all clammy. Terrible things, they are, and the effect they have on people who are already delicate –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not delicate!’ said Harry crossly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course you’re not,’ said Madam Pomfrey absent-mindedly, now taking his pulse. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does he need?’ said Professor McGonagall crisply. ‘Bed rest? Should he perhaps spend tonight in the hospital wing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m   <i class=\"calibre4\">fine! </i>’ said Harry, jumping up. The idea of what Draco Malfoy would say if he had to go to the hospital wing was torture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, he should have some chocolate, at the very least,’ said Madam Pomfrey, who was now trying to peer into Harry’s eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve already had some,’ said Harry. ‘Professor Lupin gave me some. He gave it to all of us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did he, now?’ said Madam Pomfrey approvingly. ‘So we’ve finally got a Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher who knows his remedies.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you sure you feel all right, Potter?’ said Professor McGonagall sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 71 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Yes, </i>’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well. Kindly wait outside while I have a quick word with Miss Granger about her timetable, then we can go down to the feast together.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went back into the corridor with Madam Pomfrey, who left for the hospital wing, muttering to herself. He only had to wait a few minutes; then Hermione emerged looking very happy about something, followed by Professor McGonagall, and the three of them made their way back down the marble staircase to the Great Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a sea of pointed black hats; each of the long house tables was lined with students, their faces glimmering by the light of thousands of candles, which were floating over the tables in mid-air. Professor Flitwick, who was a tiny little wizard with a shock of white hair, was carrying an ancient hat and a three-legged stool out of the Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Hermione softly, ‘we’ve missed the Sorting!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">New students at Hogwarts were sorted into houses by trying on the Sorting Hat, which shouted out the house they were best suit-ed to (Gryffindor, Ravenclaw, Hufflepuff or Slytherin). Professor McGonagall strode off towards her empty seat at the staff table, and Harry and Hermione set off in the other direction, as quietly as possible, towards the Gryffindor table. People looked around at them as they passed along the back of the Hall, and a few of them pointed at Harry. Had the story of him collapsing in front of the Dementor travelled that fast? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He  and  Hermione  sat  down  on  either  side  of  Ron,  who  had saved them seats. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was all that about?’ he muttered to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry started to explain in a whisper, but at that moment the Headmaster stood up to speak, and he broke off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Dumbledore, though very old, always gave an impression of great energy. He had several feet of long silver hair and beard, half-moon spectacles and an extremely crooked nose. He was often described as the greatest wizard of the age, but that wasn’t why Harry respected him. You couldn’t help trusting Albus Dumbledore, and as Harry watched him beaming around at the students, he felt really calm for the first time since the Dementor had entered the train compartment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome!’ said Dumbledore, the candlelight shimmering on </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>72 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">his beard. ‘Welcome to another year at Hogwarts! I have a few things to say to you all, and as one of them is very serious, I think it best to get it out of the way before you become befuddled by our excellent feast …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore cleared his throat and continued. ‘As you will all be aware after their search of the Hogwarts Express, our school is presently playing host to some of the Dementors of Azkaban, who are here on Ministry of Magic business.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He paused, and Harry remembered what Mr Weasley had said about Dumbledore not being happy with the Dementors guarding the school. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They are stationed at every entrance to the grounds,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore continued, ‘and while they are with us, I must make it plain that nobody is to leave school without permission. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dementors are not to be fooled by tricks or disguises – or even Invisibility Cloaks,’ he added blandly, and Harry and Ron glanced at each other. ‘It is not in the nature of a Dementor to understand pleading or excuses. I therefore warn each and every one of you to give them no reason to harm you. I look to the Prefects, and our new Head Boy and Girl, to make sure that no student runs foul of the Dementors.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy, who was sitting a few seats along from Harry, puffed out his chest again and stared around impressively. Dumbledore paused again; he looked very seriously around the Hall, and nobody moved or made a sound. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘On a happier note,’ he continued, ‘I am pleased to welcome two new teachers to our ranks this year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Firstly, Professor Lupin, who has kindly consented to fill the post of Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was some scattered, rather unenthusiastic, applause. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Only those who had been in the compartment on the train with Professor Lupin clapped hard, Harry among them. Professor Lupin looked particularly shabby next to all the other teachers in their best robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at Snape!’ Ron hissed in Harry’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Snape, the Potions master, was staring along the staff table at Professor Lupin. It was common knowledge that Snape wanted the Defence Against the Dark Arts job, but even Harry, who hated Snape, was startled at the expression twisting his thin, sallow face. It was beyond anger: it was loathing. Harry knew that </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementor 73 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">expression only too well; it was the look Snape wore every time he set eyes on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As to our second new appointment,’ Dumbledore continued, as the lukewarm applause for Professor Lupin died away, ‘well, I am sorry to tell you that Professor Kettleburn, our Care of Magical Creatures teacher, retired at the end of last year in order to enjoy more time with his remaining limbs. However, I am delighted to say that his place will be filled by none other than Rubeus Hagrid, who has agreed to take on this teaching job in addition to his gamekeeping duties.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione stared at each other, stunned. Then they joined in with the applause, which was tumultuous at the Gryffindor table in particular. Harry leant forward to see Hagrid, who was ruby red in the face and staring down at his enormous hands, his wide grin hidden in the tangle of his black beard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We should’ve known!’ Ron roared, pounding the table. ‘Who else would have set us a biting book?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione were the last to stop clapping, and as Professor Dumbledore started speaking again, they saw that Hagrid was wiping his eyes on the tablecloth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, I think that’s everything of importance,’ said Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let the feast begin!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The golden plates and goblets before them filled suddenly with food and drink. Harry, suddenly ravenous, helped himself to everything he could reach and began to eat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a delicious feast; the Hall echoed with talk, laughter and the clatter of knives and forks. Harry, Ron and Hermione, however, were eager for it to finish so that they could talk to Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They knew how much being made a teacher would mean to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid wasn’t a fully qualified wizard; he had been expelled from Hogwarts in his third year, for a crime he had not committed. It had been Harry, Ron and Hermione who had cleared Hagrid’s name last year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At long last, when the last morsels of pumpkin tart had melted from the golden platters, Dumbledore gave the word that it was time for them all to go to bed, and they got their chance. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Congratulations, Hagrid!’ Hermione squealed, as they reached the teachers’ table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All down ter you three,’ said Hagrid, wiping his shining face on his napkin as he looked up at them. ‘Can’ believe it … great man, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>74 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore  …  came  straight  down  to  me  hut  after  Professor Kettleburn said he’d had enough … it’s what I always wanted …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Overcome with emotion, he buried his face in his napkin, and Professor McGonagall shooed them away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione joined the Gryffindors streaming up the marble staircase and, very tired now, along more corridors, up more and more stairs, to the hidden entrance to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A large portrait of a fat lady in a pink dress asked them, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Password?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Coming through, coming through!’ Percy called from behind the crowd. ‘The new password’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">Fortuna Major! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh no,’ said Neville Longbottom sadly. He always had trouble remembering the passwords. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Through the portrait hole and across the common room, the girls and boys divided towards their separate staircases. Harry climbed the spiral stairs with no thought in his head except how glad he was to be back. They reached their familiar, circular dormitory with its five four-poster beds and Harry, looking around, felt he was home at last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SIX — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Talons and Tea Leaves </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry, Ron and Hermione entered the Great Hall for breakfast next day, the first thing they saw was Draco Malfoy, who seemed to be entertaining a large group of Slytherins with a very funny story. As they passed, Malfoy did a ridiculous impression of a swooning fit and there was a roar of laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ignore him,’ said Hermione, who was right behind Harry. ‘Just ignore him, it’s not worth it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, Potter!’ shrieked Pansy Parkinson, a Slytherin girl with a face like a pug. ‘Potter! The Dementors are coming, Potter! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Woooooooo! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dropped into a seat at the Gryffindor table, next to George Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘New third-year timetables,’ said George, passing them over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s up with you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy,’ said Ron, sitting down on George’s other side and glaring over at the Slytherin table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">George looked up in time to see Malfoy pretending to faint with terror again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That little git,’ he said calmly. ‘He wasn’t so cocky last night when the Dementors were down our end of the train. Came running into our compartment, didn’t he, Fred?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nearly wet himself,’ said Fred, with a contemptuous glance at Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wasn’t too happy myself,’ said George. ‘They’re horrible things, those Dementors …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sort of freeze your insides, don’t they?’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You didn’t pass out, though, did you?’ said Harry in a low voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Forget it, Harry,’ said George bracingly. ‘Dad had to go out to Azkaban one time, remember, Fred? And he said it was the worst </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>76 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">place he’d ever been. He came back all weak and shaking … They suck the happiness out of a place, Dementors. Most of the prisoners go mad in there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway, we’ll see how happy Malfoy looks after our first Quidditch match,’ said Fred. ‘Gryffindor versus Slytherin, first game of the season, remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The only time Harry and Malfoy had faced each other in a Quidditch match, Malfoy had definitely come off worse. Feeling slightly more cheerful, Harry helped himself to sausages and fried tomatoes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was examining her new timetable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ooh, good, we’re starting some new subjects today,’ she said happily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione,’ said Ron, frowning as he looked over her shoulder, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘they’ve messed up your timetable. Look – they’ve got you down for about ten subjects a day. There isn’t enough  <i class=\"calibre4\">time</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll manage. I’ve fixed it all with Professor McGonagall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But look,’ said Ron, laughing, ‘see this morning? Nine o’clock, Divination. And underneath, nine o’clock, Muggle Studies. And –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron leant closer to the timetable, disbelieving, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">look</i> – underneath that, Arithmancy,  <i class=\"calibre4\">nine o’clock</i>. I mean, I know you’re good, Hermione, but no one’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">that</i> good. How’re you supposed to be in three classes at once?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be silly,’ said Hermione shortly. ‘Of course I won’t be in three classes at once.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, then –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pass the marmalade,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Ron, what’s it to you if my timetable’s a bit full?’ Hermione snapped. ‘I told you, I’ve fixed it all with Professor McGonagall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Just then, Hagrid entered the Great Hall. He was wearing his long moleskin overcoat and was absent-mindedly swinging a dead polecat from one enormous hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All righ’?’ he said eagerly, pausing on the way to the staff table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer in my firs’ ever lesson! Right after lunch! Bin up since five gettin’ everythin’ ready … hope it’s OK … me, a teacher … hones’ly …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He grinned broadly at them and headed off to the staff table, still swinging the polecat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder what he’s been getting ready?’ said Ron, a note of anxi-ety in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 77 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hall was starting to empty as people headed off towards their first lesson. Ron checked his timetable. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better go, look, Divination’s at the top of North Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’ll take us ten minutes to get there …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They finished their breakfast hastily, said goodbye to Fred and George and walked back through the Hall. As they passed the Slytherin table, Malfoy did yet another impression of a fainting fit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The shouts of laughter followed Harry into the Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The journey through the castle to North Tower was a long one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Two years at Hogwarts hadn’t taught them everything about the castle, and they had never been inside North Tower before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s – got – to – be – a – short – cut,’ Ron panted, as they climbed their seventh long staircase and emerged on an unfamiliar landing, where there was nothing but a large painting of a bare stretch of grass hanging on the stone wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think it’s this way,’ said Hermione, peering down the empty passage to the right. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t be,’ said Ron. ‘That’s south. Look, you can see a bit of the lake out of the window …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was watching the painting. A fat, dapple-grey pony had just ambled onto the grass and was grazing nonchalantly. Harry was used to the subjects of Hogwarts paintings moving around and leaving their frames to visit each other, but he always enjoyed watching them. A moment later, a short, squat knight in a suit of armour had clanked into the picture after his pony. By the look of the grass stains on his metal knees, he had just fallen off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aha!’ he yelled, seeing Harry, Ron and Hermione. ‘What vil-lains are these that trespass upon my private lands? Come to scorn at my fall, perchance? Draw, you knaves, you dogs!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They watched in astonishment as the little knight tugged his sword out of its scabbard and began brandishing it violently, hopping up and down in rage. But the sword was too long for him; a particularly wild swing made him overbalance, and he landed face down in the grass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you all right?’ said Harry, moving closer to the picture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get back, you scurvy braggart! Back, you rogue!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The knight seized his sword again and used it to push himself back up, but the blade sank deeply into the grass and, though he pulled with all his might, he couldn’t get it out again. Finally he had to flop back down onto the grass and push up his visor to  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>78 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">mop his sweating face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen,’ said Harry, taking advantage of the knight’s exhaustion, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘we’re looking for the North Tower. You don’t know the way, do you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A quest!’ The knight’s rage seemed to vanish instantly. He clanked to his feet and shouted, ‘Come follow me, dear friends, and we shall find our goal, or else shall perish bravely in the charge!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He gave the sword another fruitless tug, tried and failed to mount the fat pony, and cried, ‘On foot then, good sirs and gentle lady! On! On!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he ran, clanking loudly, into the left-hand side of the frame and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hurried after him along the corridor, following the sound of his armour. Every now and then they spotted him running through a picture ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be of stout heart, the worst is yet to come!’ yelled the knight, and they saw him reappear in front of an alarmed group of women in crinolines, whose picture hung on the wall of a narrow spiral staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Puffing loudly, Harry, Ron and Hermione climbed the tightly spiralling steps, getting dizzier and dizzier, until at last they heard the murmur of voices above them, and knew they had reached the classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Farewell!’ cried the knight, popping his head into a painting of some sinister-looking monks. ‘Farewell, my comrades-in-arms! If ever you have need of noble heart and steely sinew, call upon Sir Cadogan!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, we’ll call you,’ muttered Ron, as the knight disappeared, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘if we ever need someone mental.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They climbed the last few steps and emerged onto a tiny landing, where most of the class was already assembled. There were no doors off this landing; Ron nudged Harry and pointed at the ceiling, where there was a circular trap door with a brass plaque on it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sybill Trelawney, Divination teacher,’ Harry read. ‘How’re we supposed to get up there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As though in answer to his question, the trap door suddenly opened, and a silvery ladder descended right at Harry’s feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone went quiet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 79 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘After you,’ said Ron, grinning, so Harry climbed the ladder first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He emerged into the strangest-looking classroom he had ever seen. In fact, it didn’t look like a classroom at all; more like a cross between someone’s attic and an old-fashioned teashop. At least twenty small, circular tables were crammed inside it, all surrounded by chintz armchairs and fat little pouffes. Everything was lit with a dim, crimson light; the curtains at the windows were all closed, and the many lamps were draped with dark red scarves. It was stiflingly warm, and the fire which was burning under the crowded mantelpiece was giving off a heavy, sickly sort of perfume as it heated a large copper kettle. The shelves running around the circular walls were crammed with dusty-looking feathers, stubs of candles, many packs of tattered playing cards, count-less silvery crystal balls and a huge array of teacups. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron appeared at Harry’s shoulder as the class assembled around them, all talking in whispers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is she?’ Ron said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A voice came suddenly out of the shadows, a soft, misty sort of voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome,’ it said. ‘How nice to see you in the physical world at last.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s immediate impression was of a large, glittering insect. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney moved into the firelight, and they saw that she was very thin; her large glasses magnified her eyes to several times their natural size, and she was draped in a gauzy spangled shawl. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Innumerable chains and beads hung around her spindly neck, and her arms and hands were encrusted with bangles and rings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit, my children, sit,’ she said, and they all climbed awkwardly into armchairs or sank onto pouffes. Harry, Ron and Hermione sat themselves around the same round table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Welcome to Divination,’ said Professor Trelawney, who had seated herself in a winged armchair in front of the fire. ‘My name is Professor Trelawney. You may not have seen me before. I find that descending too often into the hustle and bustle of the main school clouds my Inner Eye.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody said anything in answer to this extraordinary pronouncement. Professor Trelawney delicately rearranged her shawl and continued, ‘So you have chosen to study Divination, the most difficult of all magical arts. I must warn you at the outset that if </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>80 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you do not have the Sight, there is very little I will be able to teach you. Books can take you only so far in this field …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At these words, both Harry and Ron glanced, grinning, at Hermione, who looked startled at the news that books wouldn’t be much help in this subject. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Many witches and wizards, talented though they are in the area of loud bangs and smells and sudden disappearings, are yet unable to penetrate the veiled mysteries of the future,’ Professor Trelawney went on, her enormous, gleaming eyes moving from face to nervous face. ‘It is a Gift granted to few. You, boy,’ she said suddenly to Neville, who almost toppled off his pouffe, ‘is your grandmother well?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think so,’ said Neville tremulously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I  wouldn’t  be  so  sure  if  I  were  you,  dear,’  said  Professor Trelawney, the firelight glinting on her long emerald earrings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville gulped. Professor Trelawney continued placidly, ‘We will be covering the basic methods of Divination this year. The first term will be devoted to reading the tea leaves. Next term we shall progress to palmistry. By the way, my dear,’ she shot suddenly at Parvati Patil, ‘beware a red-haired man.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati gave a startled look at Ron, who was right behind her, and edged her chair away from him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In the summer term,’ Professor Trelawney went on, ‘we shall progress to the crystal ball – if we have finished with fire-omens, that is. Unfortunately, classes will be disrupted in February by a nasty bout of flu. I myself will lose my voice. And around Easter, one of our number will leave us for ever.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A very tense silence followed this pronouncement, but Professor Trelawney seemed unaware of it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wonder, dear,’ she said to Lavender Brown, who was nearest and shrank back in her chair, ‘if you could pass me the largest silver teapot?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lavender, looking relieved, stood up, took an enormous teapot from the shelf and put it down on the table in front of Professor Trelawney. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, my dear. Incidentally, that thing you are dreading – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it will happen on Friday the sixteenth of October.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lavender trembled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, I want you all to divide into pairs. Collect a teacup from the shelf, come to me and I will fill it. Then sit down and drink; </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 81 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">drink until only the dregs remain. Swill these around the cup three times with the left hand, then turn the cup upside-down on its saucer; wait for the last of the tea to drain away, then give your cup to your partner to read. You will interpret the patterns using pages five and six of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future</i>. I shall move among you, helping and instructing. Oh, and dear –’ she caught Neville by the arm as he made to stand up, ‘after you’ve broken your first cup, would you be so kind as to select one of the blue patterned ones? I’m rather attached to the pink.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sure enough, Neville had no sooner reached the shelf of teacups than there was a tinkle of breaking china. Professor Trelawney swept over to him holding a dustpan and brush and said, ‘One of the blue ones, then, dear, if you wouldn’t mind … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">thank you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry and Ron had had their teacups filled, they went back to their table and tried to drink the scalding tea quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They swilled the dregs around as Professor Trelawney had instructed, then drained the cups and swapped them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Ron, as they both opened their books at pages five and six. ‘What can you see in mine?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A load of soggy brown stuff,’ said Harry. The heavily perfumed smoke in the room was making him feel sleepy and stupid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Broaden your minds, my dears, and allow your eyes to see past the mundane!’ Professor Trelawney cried through the gloom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to pull himself together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right, you’ve got a wonky sort of cross …’ he said, consulting <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future</i>. ‘That means you’re going to have “trials and suffering” – sorry about that – but there’s a thing that could be the sun. Hang on … that means “great happiness” … so you’re going to suffer but be very happy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You need your Inner Eye testing, if you ask me,’ said Ron, and they both had to stifle their laughs as Professor Trelawney gazed in their direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My turn …’ Ron peered into Harry’s teacup, his forehead wrin-kled with effort. ‘There’s a blob a bit like a bowler hat,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe you’re going to work for the Ministry of Magic …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned the teacup the other way up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But this way it looks more like an acorn … what’s that?’ He scanned his copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future</i>. ‘ “A windfall, unexpected gold.” Excellent, you can lend me some. And there’s a thing </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>82 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">here,’ he turned the cup again, ‘that looks like an animal. Yeah, if that was its head … it looks like a hippo … no, a sheep …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney whirled around as Harry let out a snort of laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me see that, my dear,’ she said reprovingly to Ron, sweeping over and snatching Harry’s cup from him. Everyone went quiet to watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney was staring into the teacup, rotating it anti-clockwise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The falcon … my dear, you have a deadly enemy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But everyone knows  <i class=\"calibre4\">that</i>,’ said Hermione in a loud whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney stared at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, they do,’ said Hermione. ‘Everybody knows about Harry and You-Know-Who.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron stared at her with a mixture of amazement and admiration. They had never heard Hermione speak to a teacher like that before. Professor Trelawney chose not to reply. She lowered her huge eyes to Harry’s cup again and continued to turn it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The club … an attack. Dear, dear, this is not a happy cup …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought that was a bowler hat,’ said Ron sheepishly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The skull … danger in your path, my dear …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone was staring, transfixed, at Professor Trelawney, who gave the cup a final turn, gasped, and then screamed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was another tinkle of breaking china; Neville had smashed his second cup. Professor Trelawney sank into a vacant armchair, her glittering hand at her heart and her eyes closed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear boy – my poor dear boy – no – it is kinder not to say – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">no – don’t ask me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What is it, Professor?’ said Dean Thomas at once. Everyone had got to their feet, and slowly, they crowded around Harry and Ron’s table, pressing close to Professor Trelawney’s chair to get a good look at Harry’s cup. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear,’ Professor Trelawney’s huge eyes opened dramatically, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘you have the Grim.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The what?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could tell that he wasn’t the only one who didn’t understand; Dean Thomas shrugged at him and Lavender Brown looked puzzled, but nearly everybody else clapped their hands to their mouths in horror. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Grim, my dear, the Grim!’ cried Professor Trelawney, who </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 83 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">looked shocked that Harry hadn’t understood. ‘The giant, spectral dog that haunts churchyards! My dear boy, it is an omen – the worst omen – of  <i class=\"calibre4\">death! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s stomach lurched. That dog on the cover of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Death Omens</i> in Flourish and Blotts – the dog in the shadows of Magnolia Crescent … Lavender Brown clapped her hands to her mouth, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone was looking at Harry; everyone except Hermione, who had got up and moved around to the back of Professor Trelawney’s chair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I </i> don’t think it looks like a Grim,’ she said flatly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney surveyed Hermione with mounting dislike. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll forgive me for saying so, my dear, but I perceive very little aura around you. Very little receptivity to the resonances of the future.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seamus Finnigan was tilting his head from side to side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It looks like a Grim if you do this,’ he said, with his eyes almost shut, ‘but it looks more like a donkey from here,’ he said, leaning to the left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When you’ve all finished deciding whether I’m going to die or not!’ said Harry, taking even himself by surprise. Now nobody seemed to want to look at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think we will leave the lesson here for today,’ said Professor Trelawney, in her mistiest voice. ‘Yes … please pack away your things …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silently the class took their teacups back to Professor Trelawney, packed away their books and closed their bags. Even Ron was avoiding Harry’s eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Until we meet again,’ said Professor Trelawney faintly, ‘fair fortune be yours. Oh, and dear –’ she pointed at Neville, ‘you’ll be late next time, so mind you work extra hard to catch up.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione descended Professor Trelawney’s ladder and the winding staircase in silence, then set off for Professor McGonagall’s Transfiguration lesson. It took them so long to find her classroom that, early as they had left Divination, they were only just in time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry chose a seat right at the back of the room, feeling as though he was sitting in a very bright spotlight; the rest of the class kept shooting furtive glances at him, as though he was about to drop dead at any moment. He hardly heard what Professor McGonagall was telling them about Animagi (wizards who could </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>84 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">transform at will into animals), and wasn’t even watching when she transformed herself in front of their eyes into a tabby cat with spectacle markings around her eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really, what has got into you all today?’ said Professor McGonagall, turning back into herself with a faint  <i class=\"calibre4\">pop</i>, and staring around at them all. ‘Not that it matters, but that’s the first time my transformation’s not got applause from a class.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everybody’s heads turned towards Harry again, but nobody spoke. Then Hermione raised her hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, Professor, we’ve just had our first Divination class, and we were reading the tea leaves, and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, of course,’ said Professor McGonagall, suddenly frowning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There is no need to say any more, Miss Granger. Tell me, which of you will be dying this year?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone stared at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me,’ said Harry, finally. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see,’ said Professor McGonagall, fixing Harry with her beady eyes. ‘Then you should know, Potter, that Sybill Trelawney has predicted the death of one student a year since she arrived at this school. None of them has died yet. Seeing death omens is her favourite way of greeting a new class. If it were not for the fact that I never speak ill of my colleagues –’ Professor McGonagall broke off, and they saw that her nostrils had gone white. She went on, more calmly, ‘Divination is one of the most imprecise branches of magic. I shall not conceal from you that I have very little patience with it. True Seers are very rare, and Professor Trelawney …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She stopped again, and then said, in a very matter-of-fact tone, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You look in excellent health to me, Potter, so you will excuse me if I don’t let you off homework today. I assure you that if you die, you need not hand it in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione laughed. Harry felt a bit better. It was harder to feel scared of a lump of tea leaves away from the dim red light and befuddling perfume of Professor Trelawney’s classroom. Not everyone was convinced, however. Ron still looked worried, and Lavender whispered, ‘But what about Neville’s cup?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the Transfiguration class had finished, they joined the crowd thundering towards the Great Hall for lunch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, cheer up,’ said Hermione, pushing a dish of stew towards him. ‘You heard what Professor McGonagall said.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 85 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron spooned stew onto his plate and picked up his fork but didn’t start. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ he said, in a low, serious voice, ‘you  <i class=\"calibre4\">haven’t</i> seen a great black dog anywhere, have you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I have,’ said Harry. ‘I saw one the night I left the Dursleys.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron let his fork fall with a clatter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably a stray,’ said Hermione calmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked at Hermione as though she had gone mad. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, if Harry’s seen a Grim, that’s – that’s bad,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My – my Uncle Bilius saw one and – and he died twenty-four hours later!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Coincidence,’ said Hermione airily, pouring herself some pumpkin juice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t know what you’re talking about!’ said Ron, starting to get angry. ‘Grims scare the living daylights out of most wizards!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There you are, then,’ said Hermione in a superior tone. ‘They see the Grim and die of fright. The Grim’s not an omen, it’s the cause of death! And Harry’s still with us because he’s not stupid enough to see one and think, right, well, I’d better pop my clogs then!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron mouthed wordlessly at Hermione, who opened her bag, took out her new Arithmancy book and propped it open against the juice jug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think Divination seems very woolly,’ she said, searching for her page. ‘A lot of guesswork, if you ask me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There was nothing woolly about the Grim in that cup!’ said Ron hotly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You didn’t seem quite so confident when you were telling Harry it was a sheep,’ said Hermione coolly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Trelawney said you didn’t have the right aura! You just don’t like being rubbish at something for a change!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had touched a nerve. Hermione slammed her Arithmancy book down on the table so hard that bits of meat and carrot flew everywhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If being good at Divination means I have to pretend to see death omens in a lump of tea leaves, I’m not sure I’ll be studying it much longer! That lesson was absolute rubbish compared to my Arithmancy class!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>86 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She snatched up her bag and stalked away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron frowned after her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s she talking about?’ he said to Harry. ‘She hasn’t been to an Arithmancy class yet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was pleased to get out of the castle after lunch. Yesterday’s rain had cleared; the sky was a clear, pale grey and the grass was springy and damp underfoot as they set off for their first ever Care of Magical Creatures class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione weren’t speaking to each other. Harry walked beside them in silence as they went down the sloping lawns to Hagrid’s hut on the edge of the Forbidden Forest. It was only when he spotted three only-too-familiar backs ahead of them that he realised they must be having these lessons with the Slytherins. Malfoy was talking animatedly to Crabbe and Goyle, who were chortling. Harry was quite sure he knew what they were talking about. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was waiting for his class at the door of his hut. He stood in his moleskin overcoat, with Fang the boarhound at his heels, looking impatient to start. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon, now, get a move on!’ he called, as the class approached. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got a real treat for yeh today! Great lesson comin’ up! Everyone here? Right, follow me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For one nasty moment, Harry thought that Hagrid was going to lead them into the Forest; Harry had had enough unpleasant experiences in there to last him a lifetime. However, Hagrid strolled off around the edge of the trees, and five minutes later, they found themselves outside a kind of paddock. There was nothing in there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone gather round the fence here!’ he called. ‘That’s it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">make sure yeh can see. Now, firs’ thing yeh’ll want ter do is open yer books –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How?’ said the cold, drawling voice of Draco Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eh?’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do we open our books?’ Malfoy repeated. He took out his copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Monster Book of Monsters</i>, which he had bound shut with a length of rope. Other people took theirs out, too; some, like Harry, had belted their book shut; others had crammed them inside tight bags or clamped them together with bullclips. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hasn’ – hasn’ anyone bin able ter open their books?’ said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 87 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid, looking crestfallen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class all shook their heads. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’ve got ter  <i class=\"calibre4\">stroke</i> ’em,’ said Hagrid, as though this was the most obvious thing in the world. ‘Look …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took Hermione’s copy and ripped off the Spellotape that bound it. The book tried to bite, but Hagrid ran a giant forefinger down its spine, and the book shivered, and then fell open and lay quiet in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, how silly we’ve all been!’ Malfoy sneered. ‘We should have <i class=\"calibre4\">stroked</i> them! Why didn’t we guess!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I … I thought they were funny,’ Hagrid said uncertainly to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, tremendously funny!’ said Malfoy. ‘Really witty, giving us books that try and rip our hands off!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, Malfoy,’ said Harry quietly. Hagrid was looking down-cast and Harry wanted Hagrid’s first lesson to be a success. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Righ’ then,’ said Hagrid, who seemed to have lost his thread, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘so … so yeh’ve got yer books an’ … an’ … now yeh need the Magical Creatures. Yeah. So I’ll go an’ get ’em. Hang on …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strode away from them into the Forest and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘God, this place is going to the dogs,’ said Malfoy loudly. ‘That oaf teaching classes, my father’ll have a fit when I tell him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shut up, Malfoy,’ Harry repeated. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Careful, Potter, there’s a Dementor behind you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oooooooh!’ squealed Lavender Brown, pointing towards the opposite side of the paddock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Trotting towards them were a dozen of the most bizarre creatures Harry had ever seen. They had the bodies, hind legs and tails of horses, but the front legs, wings and heads of what seemed to be giant eagles, with cruel, steel-coloured beaks and large, brilliantly orange eyes. The talons on their front legs were half a foot long and deadly-looking. Each of the beasts had a thick leather collar around its neck, which was attached to a long chain, and the ends of all of these were held in the vast hands of Hagrid, who came jogging into the paddock behind the creatures. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gee up, there!’ he roared, shaking the chains and urging the creatures towards the fence where the class stood. Everyone drew back slightly as Hagrid reached them and tethered the creatures to the fence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hippogriffs!’ Hagrid roared happily, waving a hand at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>88 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Beau’iful, aren’ they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could sort of see what Hagrid meant. Once you had got over the first shock of seeing something that was half-horse, half-bird, you started to appreciate the Hippogriffs’ gleaming coats, changing smoothly from feather to hair, each of them a different colour: stormy grey, bronze, a pinkish roan, gleaming chestnut and inky black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ said Hagrid, rubbing his hands together and beaming around, ‘if yeh wan’ ter come a bit nearer …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one seemed to want to. Harry, Ron and Hermione, however, approached the fence cautiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, firs’ thing yeh gotta know abou’ Hippogriffs is they’re proud,’ said Hagrid. ‘Easily offended, Hippogriffs are. Don’t never insult one, ’cause it might be the last thing yeh do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle weren’t listening; they were talking in an undertone and Harry had a nasty feeling they were plotting how best to disrupt the lesson. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh always wait fer the Hippogriff ter make the firs’ move,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid continued. ‘It’s polite, see? Yeh walk towards him, and yeh bow, an’ yeh wait. If he bows back, yeh’re allowed ter touch him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If he doesn’ bow, then get away from him sharpish, ’cause those talons hurt.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right – who wants ter go first?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Most of the class backed further away in answer. Even Harry, Ron and Hermione had misgivings. The Hippogriffs were tossing their fierce heads and flexing their powerful wings; they didn’t seem to like being tethered like this. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one?’ said Hagrid, with a pleading look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll do it,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was an intake of breath from behind him and both Lavender and Parvati whispered, ‘Oooh, no, Harry, remember your tea leaves!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ignored them. He climbed over the paddock fence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good man, Harry!’ roared Hagrid. ‘Right then – let’s see how yeh get on with Buckbeak.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He untied one of the chains, pulled the grey Hippogriff away from his fellows and slipped off his leather collar. The class on the other side of the paddock seemed to be holding its breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy’s eyes were narrowed maliciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Easy, now, Harry,’ said Hagrid quietly. ‘Yeh’ve got eye contact, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 89 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">now try not ter blink – Hippogriffs don’ trust yeh if yeh blink too much …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s eyes immediately began to water, but he didn’t shut them. Buckbeak had turned his great, sharp head, and was staring at Harry with one fierce orange eye. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tha’s it,’ said Hagrid. ‘Tha’s it, Harry … now, bow …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t feel much like exposing the back of his neck to Buckbeak, but he did as he was told. He gave a short bow and then looked up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hippogriff was still staring haughtily at him. It didn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Hagrid, sounding worried. ‘Right – back away, now, Harry, easy does it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But then, to Harry’s enormous surprise, the Hippogriff suddenly bent his scaly front knees, and sank into what was an unmistakeable bow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done, Harry!’ said Hagrid, ecstatic. ‘Right – yeh can touch him! Pat his beak, go on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Feeling that a better reward would have been to back away, Harry moved slowly towards the Hippogriff and reached out towards him. He patted the beak several times and the Hippogriff closed his eyes lazily, as though enjoying it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class broke into applause, all except for Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle, who were looking deeply disappointed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Righ’ then, Harry,’ said Hagrid, ‘I reckon he migh’ let yeh ride him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This was more than Harry had bargained for. He was used to a broomstick; but he wasn’t sure a Hippogriff would be quite the same. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh climb up there, jus’ behind the wing joint,’ said Hagrid, ‘an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">mind yeh don’ pull any of his feathers out, he won’ like that …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put his foot on the top of Buckbeak’s wing and hoisted himself onto his back. Buckbeak stood up. Harry wasn’t sure where to hold on; everything in front of him was covered in feathers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go on, then!’ roared Hagrid, slapping the Hippogriff’s hindquarters. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Without warning, twelve-foot wings flapped open on either side of Harry; he just had time to seize the Hippogriff around the neck before he was soaring upwards. It was nothing like a broomstick, and Harry knew which one he preferred; the Hippogriff’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>90 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wings were beating uncomfortably on either side of him, catching him under his legs and making him feel he was about to be thrown off; the glossy feathers slipped under his fingers and he didn’t dare get a stronger grip; instead of the smooth action of his Nimbus Two Thousand, he now felt himself rocking backwards and forwards as the hindquarters of the Hippogriff rose and fell with his wings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak flew him once around the paddock and then headed back to the ground; this was the bit Harry had been dreading; he leant back as the smooth neck lowered, feeling he was going to slip off over the beak; then he felt a heavy thud as the four ill-assorted feet hit the ground, and just managed to hold on and push himself straight again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good work, Harry!’ roared Hagrid, as everyone except Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle cheered. ‘OK, who else wants a go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Emboldened by Harry’s success, the rest of the class climbed cautiously into the paddock. Hagrid untied the Hippogriffs one by one, and soon people were bowing nervously, all over the paddock. Neville ran repeatedly backwards from his, which didn’t seem to want to bend its knees. Ron and Hermione practised on the chestnut, while Harry watched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle had taken over Buckbeak. He had bowed to Malfoy, who was now patting his beak, looking disdainful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is very easy,’ Malfoy drawled, loud enough for Harry to hear him. ‘I knew it must have been, if Potter could do it … I bet you’re not dangerous at all, are you?’ he said to the Hippogriff. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you, you ugly great brute?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It happened in a flash of steely talons; Malfoy let out a high-pitched scream and next moment, Hagrid was wrestling Buckbeak back into his collar as he strained to get at Malfoy, who lay curled in the grass, blood blossoming over his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m dying!’ Malfoy yelled, as the class panicked. ‘I’m dying, look at me! It’s killed me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yer not dyin’!’ said Hagrid, who had gone very white. ‘Someone help me – gotta get him outta here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione ran to open the gate while Hagrid lifted Malfoy easily. As they passed, Harry saw that there was a long, deep gash in Malfoy’s arm; blood splattered the grass and Hagrid ran with him, up the slope towards the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 91 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Very shaken, the Care of Magical Creatures class followed at a walk. The Slytherins were all shouting about Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They should sack him straight away!’ said Pansy Parkinson, who was in tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was Malfoy’s fault!’ snapped Dean Thomas. Crabbe and Goyle flexed their muscles threateningly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They all climbed the stone steps into the deserted Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m  going  to  see  if  he’s  OK!’  said  Pansy,  and  they  all  watched her run up the marble staircase. The Slytherins, still muttering about Hagrid, headed away in the direction of their dungeon common room; Harry, Ron and Hermione proceeded upstairs to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you think he’ll be all right?’ said Hermione nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Course he will, Madam Pomfrey can mend cuts in about a second,’ said Harry, who had had far worse injuries mended magically by the matron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was a really bad thing to happen in Hagrid’s first class, though, wasn’t it?’ said Ron, looking worried. ‘Trust Malfoy to mess things up for him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were among the first to reach the Great Hall at dinner-time, hoping to see Hagrid, but he wasn’t there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They  <i class=\"calibre4\">wouldn’t</i> sack him, would they?’ said Hermione anxiously, not touching her steak-and-kidney pudding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’d better not,’ said Ron, who wasn’t eating either. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was watching the Slytherin table. A large group including Crabbe and Goyle were huddled together, deep in conversation. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was sure they were cooking up their own version of how Malfoy had got injured. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you can’t say it wasn’t an interesting first day back,’ said Ron gloomily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went up to the crowded Gryffindor common room after dinner and tried to do the homework Professor McGonagall had set them, but all three of them kept breaking off and glancing out of the tower window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s a light on in Hagrid’s window,’ Harry said suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron looked at his watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If we hurried, we could go down and see him, it’s still quite early …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ Hermione said slowly, and Harry saw her glance at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>92 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m allowed to walk across the  <i class=\"calibre4\">grounds</i>,’ he said pointedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius Black hasn’t got past the Dementors here, has he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So they put their things away and headed out of the portrait hole, glad not to meet anybody on their way to the front doors, as they weren’t entirely sure they were supposed to be out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The grass was still wet and looked almost black in the twilight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they reached Hagrid’s hut, they knocked, and a voice growled, ‘C’min.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was sitting in his shirt-sleeves at his scrubbed wooden table; his boarhound, Fang, had his head in Hagrid’s lap. One look told them that Hagrid had been drinking a lot; there was a pewter tankard almost as big as a bucket in front of him, and he seemed to be having difficulty in getting them into focus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Spect it’s a record,’ he said thickly, when he recognised them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’ reckon they’ve ever had a teacher who on’y lasted a day before.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You haven’t been sacked, Hagrid!’ gasped Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not yet,’ said Hagrid miserably, taking a huge gulp of whatever was in the tankard. ‘But ’s only a matter o’ time, i’n’t it, after Malfoy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How is he?’ said Ron, as they all sat down. ‘It wasn’t serious, was it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Madam Pomfrey fixed him best she could,’ said Hagrid dully, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘but he’s sayin’ it’s still agony … covered in bandages … moanin’ …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s faking it,’ said Harry at once. ‘Madam Pomfrey can mend anything. She regrew half my bones last year. Trust Malfoy to milk it for all it’s worth.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘School gov’nors have bin told, o’ course,’ said Hagrid miserably. ‘They reckon I started too big. Shoulda left Hippogriffs fer later … done Flobberworms or summat … jus’ thought it’d make a good firs’ lesson … ’s all my fault …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s all  <i class=\"calibre4\">Malfoy</i>’s fault, Hagrid!’ said Hermione earnestly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re witnesses,’ said Harry. ‘You said Hippogriffs attack if you insult them. It’s Malfoy’s problem he wasn’t listening. We’ll tell Dumbledore what really happened.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, don’t worry, Hagrid, we’ll back you up,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Tears leaked out of the crinkled corners of Hagrid’s beetle-black eyes. He grabbed both Harry and Ron and pulled them into a bone-breaking hug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think you’ve had enough to drink, Hagrid,’ said Hermione </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talons and Tea Leaves 93 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">firmly. She took the tankard from the table and went outside to empty it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ar, maybe she’s right,’ said Hagrid, letting go of Harry and Ron, who both staggered away, rubbing their ribs. Hagrid heaved himself out of his chair and followed Hermione unsteadily outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard a loud splash. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s he done?’ said Harry nervously, as Hermione came back in with the empty tankard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stuck his head in the water barrel,’ said Hermione, putting the tankard away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid came back, his long hair and beard sopping wet, wiping the water out of his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tha’s better,’ he said, shaking his head like a dog and drench-ing them all. ‘Listen, it was good of yeh ter come an’ see me, I really –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid stopped dead, staring at Harry as though he’d only just realised he was there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WHAT D’YEH THINK YOU’RE DOIN’, EH?’ he roared, so suddenly that they jumped a foot in the air. ‘YEH’RE NOT TO GO </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WANDERIN’ AROUND AFTER DARK, HARRY! AN’ YOU TWO! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">LETTIN’ HIM!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid strode over to Harry, grabbed his arm and pulled him to the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon!’ Hagrid said angrily. ‘I’m takin’ yer all back up ter school, an’ don’ let me catch yeh walkin’ down ter see me after dark again. I’m not worth that!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy didn’t reappear in classes until late on Thursday morning, when the Slytherins and Gryffindors were halfway through double Potions. He swaggered into the dungeon, his right arm covered in bandages and bound up in a sling, acting, in Harry’s opinion, as though he was the heroic survivor of some dreadful battle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How is it, Draco?’ simpered Pansy Parkinson. ‘Does it hurt much?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Malfoy, putting on a brave sort of grimace. But Harry saw him wink at Crabbe and Goyle when Pansy had looked away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Settle down, settle down,’ said Professor Snape idly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron scowled at each other; Snape wouldn’t have said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘settle down’ if  <i class=\"calibre4\">they</i>’d walked in late, he’d have given them detention. But Malfoy had always been able to get away with anything in Snape’s classes; Snape was Head of Slytherin house, and gener-ally favoured his own students before all others. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were making a new potion today, a Shrinking Solution. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy set up his cauldron right next to Harry and Ron, so that they were preparing their ingredients on the same table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir,’ Malfoy called, ‘sir, I’ll need help cutting up these daisy roots, because of my arm –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Weasley, cut up Malfoy’s roots for him,’ said Snape, without looking up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron went brick red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s nothing wrong with your arm,’ he hissed at Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy smirked across the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Weasley, you heard Professor Snape, cut up these roots.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron seized his knife, pulled Malfoy’s roots towards him and began to chop them roughly, so that they were all different sizes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor,’ drawled Malfoy, ‘Weasley’s mutilating my roots, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 95 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape approached their table, stared down his hooked nose at the roots, then gave Ron an unpleasant smile from beneath his long, greasy black hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Change roots with Malfoy, Weasley.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But sir –!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had spent the last quarter of an hour carefully shredding his own roots into exactly equal pieces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Now</i>,’ said Snape in his most dangerous voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron shoved his own beautifully cut roots across the table at Malfoy, then took up the knife again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And, sir, I’ll need this Shrivelfig skinned,’ said Malfoy, his voice full of malicious laughter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter, you can skin Malfoy’s Shrivelfig,’ said Snape, giving Harry the look of loathing he always reserved just for him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took Malfoy’s Shrivelfig as Ron set about trying to repair the damage to the roots he now had to use. Harry skinned the Shrivelfig as fast as he could and flung it back across the table at Malfoy without speaking. Malfoy was smirking more broadly than ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seen your pal Hagrid lately?’ he asked them quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘None of your business,’ said Ron jerkily, without looking up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m afraid he won’t be a teacher much longer,’ said Malfoy, in a tone of mock sorrow. ‘Father’s not very happy about my injury –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Keep talking, Malfoy, and I’ll give you a real injury,’ snarled Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– he’s complained to the school governors.  <i class=\"calibre4\">And</i> to the Ministry of Magic. Father’s got a lot of influence, you know. And a lasting injury like this –’ he gave a huge, fake sigh, ‘who knows if my arm’ll ever be the same again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So that’s why you’re putting it on,’ said Harry, accidentally beheading a dead caterpillar because his hand was shaking in anger. ‘To try and get Hagrid sacked.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Malfoy, lowering his voice to a whisper, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">partly</i>, Potter. But there are other benefits, too. Weasley, slice my caterpillars for me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few cauldrons away, Neville was in trouble. Neville regularly went to pieces in Potions lessons; it was his worst subject, and his great fear of Professor Snape made things ten times worse. His potion, which was supposed to be a bright, acid green, had turned – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>96 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Orange, Longbottom,’ said Snape, ladling some up and allow-ing it to splash back into the cauldron, so that everyone could see. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Orange. Tell me, boy, does anything penetrate that thick skull of yours? Didn’t you hear me say, quite clearly, that only one rat spleen was needed? Didn’t I state plainly that a dash of leech juice would suffice? What do I have to do to make you understand, Longbottom?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville was pink and trembling. He looked as though he was on the verge of tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, sir,’ said Hermione, ‘please, I could help Neville put it right –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t remember asking you to show off, Miss Granger,’ said Snape coldly, and Hermione went as pink as Neville. ‘Longbottom, at the end of this lesson we will feed a few drops of this potion to your toad and see what happens. Perhaps that will encourage you to do it properly.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape moved away, leaving Neville breathless with fear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Help me!’ he moaned to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hey, Harry,’ said Seamus Finnigan, leaning over to borrow Harry’s brass scales, ‘have you heard?  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> this morning – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they reckon Sirius Black’s been sighted.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where?’ said Harry and Ron quickly. On the other side of the table, Malfoy looked up, listening closely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not too far from here,’ said Seamus, who looked excited. ‘It was a Muggle who saw him. ’Course, she didn’t really understand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Muggles think he’s just an ordinary criminal, don’t they? So she ’phoned the telephone hotline. By the time the Ministry of Magic got there, he was gone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not too far from here …’ Ron repeated, looking significantly at Harry. He turned around and saw Malfoy watching closely. ‘What, Malfoy? Need something else skinning?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Malfoy’s eyes were shining malevolently, and they were fixed on Harry. He leant across the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thinking of trying to catch Black single-handed, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, that’s right,’ said Harry offhandedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy’s thin mouth was curving in a mean smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of  course,  if  it  was  me,’  he  said  quietly,  ‘I’d  have  done  something before now. I wouldn’t be staying in school like a good boy, I’d be out there looking for him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you talking about, Malfoy?’ said Ron roughly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 97 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you  <i class=\"calibre4\">know</i>, Potter?’ breathed Malfoy, his pale eyes narrowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Know what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy let out a low, sneering laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe you’d rather not risk your neck,’ he said. ‘Want to leave it to the Dementors, do you? But if it was me, I’d want revenge. I’d hunt him down myself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What are you talking about? </i>’ said Harry angrily, but at that moment Snape called, ‘You should have finished adding your ingredients  by  now.  This  potion  needs  to  stew  before  it  can  be drunk; clear away while it simmers and then we’ll test Longbottom’s …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle laughed openly, watching Neville sweat as he stirred his potion feverishly. Hermione was muttering instructions to him out of the corner of her mouth, so that Snape wouldn’t see. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron packed away their unused ingredients and went to wash their hands and ladles in the stone basin in the corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did Malfoy mean?’ Harry muttered to Ron, as he stuck his hands under the icy jet that poured from a gargoyle’s mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would I want revenge on Black? He hasn’t done anything to me – yet.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s making it up,’ said Ron, savagely, ‘he’s trying to make you do something stupid …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The end of the lesson in sight, Snape strode over to Neville, who was cowering by his cauldron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone gather round,’ said Snape, his black eyes glittering, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘and watch what happens to Longbottom’s toad. If he has managed to produce a Shrinking Solution, it will shrink to a tadpole. If, as I don’t doubt, he has done it wrong, his toad is likely to be poisoned.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindors watched fearfully. The Slytherins looked excited. Snape picked up Trevor the toad in his left hand, and dipped a small spoon into Neville’s potion, which was now green. He trickled a few drops down Trevor’s throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a moment of hushed silence, in which Trevor gulped; then there was a small  <i class=\"calibre4\">pop</i>, and Trevor the tadpole was wriggling in Snape’s palm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindors burst into applause. Snape, looking sour, pulled a small bottle from the pocket of his robe, poured a few drops on top of Trevor and he reappeared suddenly, fully grown. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>98 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Five points from Gryffindor,’ said Snape, which wiped the smiles from every face. ‘I told you not to help him, Miss Granger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Class dismissed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione climbed the steps to the Entrance Hall. Harry was still thinking about what Malfoy had said, while Ron was seething about Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Five points from Gryffindor because the potion was all right! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Why didn’t you lie, Hermione? You should’ve said Neville did it all by himself!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione didn’t answer. Ron looked around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is she?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned, too. They were at the top of the steps now, watching the rest of the class pass them, heading for the Great Hall and lunch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She was right behind us,’ said Ron, frowning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy passed them, walking between Crabbe and Goyle. He smirked at Harry and disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There she is,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was panting slightly, hurrying up the stairs; one hand was clutching her bag, the other seemed to be tucking something down the front of her robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you do that?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Hermione, joining them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One minute you were right behind us, and next moment, you were back at the bottom of the stairs again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ Hermione looked slightly confused. ‘Oh – I had to go back for something. Oh, no …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A seam had split on Hermione’s bag. Harry wasn’t surprised; he could see that it was crammed with at least a dozen large and heavy books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why are you carrying all these around with you?’ Ron asked her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know how many subjects I’m taking,’ said Hermione breathlessly. ‘Couldn’t hold these for me, could you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ Ron was turning over the books she had handed him, looking at the covers – ‘you haven’t got any of these subjects today. It’s only Defence Against the Dark Arts this afternoon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes,’ said Hermione vaguely, but she packed all the books back into her bag just the same. ‘I hope there’s something good for lunch, I’m starving,’ she added, and she marched off towards the Great Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 99 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you get the feeling Hermione’s not telling us something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron asked Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin wasn’t there when they arrived at his first Defence Against the Dark Arts lesson. They all sat down, took out their books, quills and parchment, and were talking when he finally entered the room. Lupin smiled vaguely and placed his tatty old briefcase on the teacher’s desk. He was as shabby as ever but looked healthier than he had on the train, as though he had had a few square meals. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good afternoon,’ he said. ‘Would you please put all your books back in your bags. Today’s will be a practical lesson. You will only need your wands.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few curious looks were exchanged as the class put away their books. They had never had a practical Defence Against the Dark Arts before, unless you counted the memorable class last year when their old teacher had brought a cageful of pixies to class and set them loose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then,’ said Professor Lupin, when everyone was ready, ‘if you’d follow me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Puzzled but interested, the class got to its feet and followed Professor Lupin out of the classroom. He led them along the deserted corridor and around a corner, where the first thing they saw was Peeves the poltergeist, who was floating upside-down in mid-air and stuffing the nearest keyhole with chewing gum. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves didn’t look up until Professor Lupin was two feet away, then he wiggled his curly-toed feet and broke into song. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Loony, loopy Lupin,’ Peeves sang. ‘Loony, loopy Lupin, loony, loopy Lupin –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Rude and unmanageable as he almost always was, Peeves usually showed some respect towards the teachers. Everyone looked quickly at Professor Lupin to see how he would take this; to their surprise, he was still smiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d take that gum out of the keyhole, if I were you, Peeves,’ he said pleasantly. ‘Mr Filch won’t be able to get in to his brooms.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Filch was the Hogwarts caretaker, a bad-tempered, failed wizard who waged a constant war against the students and, indeed, Peeves. However, Peeves paid no attention to Professor Lupin’s words, except to blow a loud wet raspberry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin gave a small sigh and took out his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>100 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is a useful little spell,’ he told the class over his shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please watch closely.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He raised the wand to shoulder height, said ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Waddiwasi! </i>’ and pointed it at Peeves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With the force of a bullet, the wad of chewing gum shot out of the keyhole and straight down Peeves’s left nostril; he whirled right way up and zoomed away, cursing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cool, sir!’ said Dean Thomas in amazement. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Dean,’ said Professor Lupin, putting his wand away again. ‘Shall we proceed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They set off again, the class looking at shabby Professor Lupin with increased respect. He led them down a second corridor and stopped, right outside the staff-room door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Inside, please,’ said Professor Lupin, opening it and standing back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The staff room, a long, panelled room full of old, mismatched chairs, was empty except for one teacher. Professor Snape was sitting in a low armchair, and he looked around as the class filed in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His eyes were glittering and there was a nasty sneer playing around his mouth. As Professor Lupin came in and made to close the door behind him, Snape said, ‘Leave it open, Lupin. I’d rather not witness this.’ He got to his feet and strode past the class, his black robes billowing behind him. At the doorway he turned on his heel and said, ‘Possibly no one’s warned you, Lupin, but this class contains Neville Longbottom. I would advise you not to entrust him with anything difficult. Not unless Miss Granger is hissing instructions in his ear.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville went scarlet. Harry glared at Snape; it was bad enough that he bullied Neville in his own classes, let alone doing it in front of other teachers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin had raised his eyebrows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was hoping that Neville would assist me with the first stage of the operation,’ he said, ‘and I am sure he will perform it admirably.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville’s face went, if possible, even redder. Snape’s lip curled, but he left, shutting the door with a snap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, then,’ said Professor Lupin, beckoning the class towards the end of the room, where there was nothing except an old wardrobe in which the teachers kept their spare robes. As Professor Lupin went to stand next to it, the wardrobe gave a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 101 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sudden wobble, banging off the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing to worry about,’ said Professor Lupin calmly, as a few people jumped backwards in alarm. ‘There’s a Boggart in there.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Most people seemed to feel that this  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> something to worry about. Neville gave Professor Lupin a look of pure terror, and Seamus Finnigan eyed the now rattling doorknob apprehensively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Boggarts like dark, enclosed spaces,’ said Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wardrobes, the gap beneath beds, the cupboards under sinks – I once met one that had lodged itself in a grandfather clock.  <i class=\"calibre4\">This</i> one moved in yesterday afternoon, and I asked the Headmaster if the staff would leave it to give my third-years some practice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, the first question we must ask ourselves is, what  <i class=\"calibre4\">is</i> a Boggart?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione put up her hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a shape-shifter,’ she said. ‘It can take the shape of whatever it thinks will frighten us most.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Couldn’t have put it better myself,’ said Professor Lupin, and Hermione glowed. ‘So the Boggart sitting in the darkness within has not yet assumed a form. He does not yet know what will frighten the person on the other side of the door. Nobody knows what a Boggart looks like when he is alone, but when I let him out, he will immediately become whatever each of us most fears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This means,’ said Professor Lupin, choosing to ignore Neville’s small splutter of terror, ‘that we have a huge advantage over the Boggart before we begin. Have you spotted it, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Trying to answer a question with Hermione next to him, bobbing up and down on the balls of her feet with her hand in the air, was very off-putting, but Harry had a go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – because there are so many of us, it won’t know what shape it should be?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Precisely,’ said Professor Lupin, and Hermione put her hand down looking a little disappointed. ‘It’s always best to have company when you’re dealing with a Boggart. He becomes confused. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Which should he become, a headless corpse or a flesh-eating slug? I once saw a Boggart make that very mistake – tried to frighten two people at once and turned himself into half a slug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Not remotely frightening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The charm that repels a Boggart is simple, yet it requires force of mind. You see, the thing that really finishes a Boggart is  <i class=\"calibre4\">laughter. </i> What you need to do is force it to assume a shape that you find amusing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>102 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We will practise the charm without wands first. After me, please …  <i class=\"calibre4\">riddikulus! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ said the class together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘Very good. But that was the easy part, I’m afraid. You see, the word alone is not enough. And this is where you come in, Neville.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wardrobe shook again, though not as much as Neville, who walked forward as though he was heading for the gallows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right, Neville,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘First things first: what would you say is the thing that frightens you most in the world?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville’s lips moved, but no noise came out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t catch that, Neville, sorry,’ said Professor Lupin cheerfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville looked around rather wildly, as though begging someone to help him, then said, in  barely  more  than  a  whisper, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly everyone laughed. Even Neville grinned apologetically. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin, however, looked thoughtful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape … hmmm … Neville, I believe you live with your grandmother?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – yes,’ said Neville nervously. ‘But – I don’t want the Boggart to turn into her, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, you misunderstand me,’ said Professor Lupin, now smiling. ‘I wonder, could you tell us what sort of clothes your grandmother usually wears?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville looked startled, but said, ‘Well … always the same hat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A tall one with a stuffed vulture on top. And a long dress … green, normally … and sometimes a fox-fur scarf.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And a handbag?’ prompted Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A big red one,’ said Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right then,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘Can you picture those clothes very clearly, Neville? Can you see them in your mind’s eye?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Neville uncertainly, plainly wondering what was coming next. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When the Boggart bursts out of this wardrobe, Neville, and sees you, it will assume the form of Professor Snape,’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you will raise your wand – thus – and cry “Riddikulus” – and concentrate hard on your grandmother’s clothes. If all goes well, Professor Boggart Snape will be forced into that vulture-topped </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 103 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hat, that green dress, that big red handbag.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a great shout of laughter. The wardrobe wobbled more violently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If Neville is successful, the Boggart is likely to turn his attention to each of us in turn,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘I would like all of you to take a moment now to think of the thing that scares you most, and imagine how you might force it to look comical …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The room went quiet. Harry thought … What scared him most in the world? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His first thought was Lord Voldemort – a Voldemort returned to full strength. But before he had even started to plan a possible counter-attack on a Boggart-Voldemort, a horrible image came floating to the surface of his mind … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A rotting, glistening hand, slithering back beneath a black cloak … a long, rattling breath from an unseen mouth … then a cold so penetrating it felt like drowning … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shivered, then looked around, hoping no one had noticed. Many people had their eyes shut tight. Ron was muttering to himself, ‘Take its legs off.’ Harry was sure he knew what that was about. Ron’s greatest fear was spiders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone ready?’ said Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt a lurch of fear. He wasn’t ready. How could you make a Dementor less frightening? But he didn’t want to ask for more time; everyone else was nodding and rolling up their sleeves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Neville, we’re going to back away,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘Let you have a clear field, all right? I’ll call the next person forward … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">everyone back, now, so Neville can get a clear shot –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They all retreated, backing against the walls, leaving Neville alone beside the wardrobe. He looked pale and frightened, but he had pushed up the sleeves of his robes and was holding his wand ready. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘On the count of three, Neville,’ said Professor Lupin, who was pointing his own wand at the handle of the wardrobe. ‘One – two </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– three –  <i class=\"calibre4\">now! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A jet of sparks shot from the end of Professor Lupin’s wand and hit the doorknob. The wardrobe burst open. Hook-nosed and menacing, Professor Snape stepped out, his eyes flashing at Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville backed away, his wand up, mouthing wordlessly. Snape was bearing down upon him, reaching inside his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘R-r-riddikulus!’ squeaked Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>104 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a noise like a whip-crack. Snape stumbled; he was wearing a long, lace-trimmed dress and a towering hat topped with a moth-eaten vulture, and swinging a huge crimson handbag from his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a roar of laughter; the Boggart paused, confused, and Professor Lupin shouted, ‘Parvati! Forward!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati walked forward, her face set. Snape rounded on her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was another crack, and where he had stood was a blood-stained, bandaged mummy; its sightless face was turned to Parvati and it began to walk towards her, very slowly, dragging its feet, its stiff arms rising – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ cried Parvati. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A bandage unravelled at the mummy’s feet; it became entan-gled, fell face forwards and its head rolled off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seamus!’ roared Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seamus darted past Parvati. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> Where the mummy had been was a woman with floor-length black hair and a skeletal, green-tinged face – a banshee. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She opened her mouth wide, and an unearthly sound filled the room, a long, wailing shriek which made the hair on Harry’s head stand on end – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ shouted Seamus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The banshee made a rasping noise and clutched her throat; her voice was gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> The banshee turned into a rat, which chased its tail in a circle, then –  <i class=\"calibre4\">crack! </i> – became a rattlesnake, which slithered and writhed before –  <i class=\"calibre4\">crack! </i> – becoming a single, bloody eyeball. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s confused!’ shouted Lupin. ‘We’re getting there! Dean!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dean hurried forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> The eyeball became a severed hand, which flipped over, and began to creep along the floor like a crab. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ yelled Dean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a snap, and the hand was trapped in a mousetrap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent! Ron, you next!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron leapt forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quite a few people screamed. A giant spider, six feet tall and covered in hair, was advancing on Ron, clicking its pincers menacingly. For a moment, Harry thought Ron had frozen. Then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ bellowed Ron, and the spider’s legs vanished. It </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Boggart in the Wardrobe 105 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">rolled over and over; Lavender Brown squealed and ran out of its way and it came to a halt at Harry’s feet. He raised his wand, ready, but – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here!’ shouted Professor Lupin suddenly, hurrying forward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The legless spider had vanished. For a second, everyone looked wildly around to see where it was. Then they saw a silvery white orb hanging in the air in front of Lupin, who said ‘Riddikulus!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">almost lazily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Forward, Neville, and finish him off!’ said Lupin, as the Boggart landed on the floor as a cockroach.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Crack! </i> Snape was back. This time Neville charged forward looking determined. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ he shouted, and they had a split second’s view of Snape in his lacy dress before Neville let out a great ‘Ha!’ of laughter, and the Boggart exploded, burst into a thousand tiny wisps of smoke, and was gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent!’ cried Professor Lupin, as the class broke into applause. ‘Excellent, Neville. Well done, everyone. Let me see … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">five points to Gryffindor for every person to tackle the Boggart – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ten for Neville because he did it twice – and five each to Hermione and Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I didn’t do anything,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You and Hermione answered my questions correctly at the start of the class, Harry,’ Lupin said lightly. ‘Very well, everyone, an excellent lesson. Homework, kindly read the chapter on Boggarts and summarise it for me … to be handed in on Monday. That will be all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Talking excitedly, the class left the staff room. Harry, however, wasn’t feeling cheerful. Professor Lupin had deliberately stopped him tackling the Boggart. Why? Was it because he’d seen Harry collapse on the train, and thought he wasn’t up to much? Had he thought Harry would pass out again? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But no one else seemed to have noticed anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see me take that banshee?’ shouted Seamus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the hand!’ said Dean, waving his own around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And Snape in that hat!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And my mummy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wonder why Professor Lupin’s frightened of crystal balls?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Lavender thoughtfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>106 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was the best Defence Against the Dark Arts lesson we’ve ever had, wasn’t it?’ said Ron excitedly, as they made their way back to the classroom to get their bags. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He seems a very good teacher,’ said Hermione approvingly. ‘But I wish I could have had a turn with the Boggart –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What would it have been for you?’ said Ron, sniggering. ‘A piece of homework that only got nine out of ten?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER EIGHT — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Flight of the Fat Lady </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In no time at all, Defence Against the Dark Arts had become most people’s favourite class. Only Draco Malfoy and his gang of Slytherins had anything bad to say about Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at the state of his robes,’ Malfoy would say in a loud whisper as Professor Lupin passed. ‘He dresses like our old house-elf.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But no one else cared that Professor Lupin’s robes were patched and frayed. His next few lessons were just as interesting as the first. After Boggarts, they studied Red Caps, nasty little goblin-like creatures that lurked wherever there had been bloodshed, in the dungeons of castles and the potholes of deserted battlefields, waiting to bludgeon those who had got lost. From Red Caps they moved on to Kappas, creepy water-dwellers that looked like scaly monkeys, with webbed hands itching to strangle unwitting waders in their ponds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry only wished he was as happy with some of his other classes. Worst of all was Potions. Snape was in a particularly vindictive mood these days, and no one was in any doubt why. The story of the Boggart assuming Snape’s shape, and the way that Neville had dressed it in his grandmother’s clothes, had travelled through the school like wildfire. Snape didn’t seem to find it funny. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His eyes flashed menacingly at the very mention of Professor Lupin’s name, and he was bullying Neville worse than ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was also growing to dread the hours he spent in Professor Trelawney’s stifling tower room, deciphering lop-sided shapes and symbols, trying to ignore the way Professor Trelawney’s enormous eyes filled with tears every time she looked at him. He couldn’t like Professor Trelawney, even though she was treated with respect bordering on reverence by many of the class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati Patil and Lavender Brown had taken to haunting Professor Trelawney’s tower room at lunchtimes, and always returned with </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>108 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">annoyingly superior looks on their faces, as though they knew things the others didn’t. They had also started using hushed voices whenever they spoke to Harry, as though he was on his deathbed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody really liked Care of Magical Creatures, which, after the action-packed first class, had become extremely dull. Hagrid seemed to have lost his confidence. They were now spending lesson after lesson learning how to look after Flobberworms, which had to be some of the most boring creatures in existence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why would anyone  <i class=\"calibre4\">bother</i> looking after them?’ said Ron, after yet another hour of poking shredded lettuce down the Flobberworms’ slimy throats. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At the start of October, however, Harry had something else to occupy him, something so enjoyable it made up for his unsatisfactory classes. The Quidditch season was approaching, and Oliver Wood, captain of the Gryffindor team, called a meeting one Thursday evening to discuss tactics for the new season. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were seven people on a Quidditch team: three Chasers, whose job it was to score goals by putting the Quaffle (a red, football-sized ball) through one of the fifty-foot-high hoops at each end of the pitch; two Beaters, who were equipped with heavy bats to repel the Bludgers (two heavy black balls which zoomed around trying to attack the players); a Keeper, who defended the goalposts, and the Seeker, who had the hardest job of all, that of catching the Golden Snitch, a tiny, winged, walnut-sized ball, whose capture ended the game and earned the Seeker’s team an extra one hundred and fifty points. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Oliver Wood was a burly seventeen-year-old, now in his seventh and final year at Hogwarts. There was a quiet sort of despera-tion in his voice as he addressed his six fellow team members in the chilly changing rooms on the edge of the darkening Quidditch pitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is our last chance –  <i class=\"calibre4\">my </i> last chance – to win the Quidditch Cup,’ he told them, striding up and down in front of them. ‘I’ll be leaving at the end of this year. I’ll never get another shot at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gryffindor haven’t won for seven years now. OK, so we’ve had the worst luck in the world – injuries – then the tournament getting called off last year …’ Wood swallowed, as though the memory still brought a lump to his throat. ‘But we also know we’ve got the  <i class=\"calibre4\">best – ruddy – team – in – the – school</i>,’ he said, punching a fist </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 109 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">into his other hand, the old manic glint back in his eye. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got three  <i class=\"calibre4\">superb</i> Chasers.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood pointed at Alicia Spinnet, Angelina Johnson and Katie Bell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got two  <i class=\"calibre4\">unbeatable </i> Beaters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop it, Oliver, you’re embarrassing us,’ said Fred and George Weasley together, pretending to blush. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And we’ve got a Seeker who has  <i class=\"calibre4\">never failed to win us a match! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood rumbled, glaring at Harry with a kind of furious pride. ‘And me,’ he added, as an afterthought. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We think you’re very good, too, Oliver,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cracking Keeper,’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The point is,’ Wood went on, resuming his pacing, ‘the Quidditch Cup should have had our name on it these last two years. Ever since Harry joined the team, I’ve thought the thing was in the bag. But we haven’t got it, and this year’s the last chance we’ll get to finally see our name on the thing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood spoke so dejectedly that even Fred and George looked sympathetic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oliver, this year’s our year,’ said Fred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll do it, Oliver!’ said Angelina. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Definitely,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Full of determination, the team started training sessions, three evenings a week. The weather was getting colder and wetter, the nights darker, but no amount of mud, wind or rain could tarnish Harry’s wonderful vision of finally winning the huge silver Quidditch Cup. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry returned to the Gryffindor common room one evening after training, cold and stiff but pleased with the way practice had gone, to find the room buzzing excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s happened?’ he asked Ron and Hermione, who were sitting in two of the best chairs by the fireside and completing some star charts for Astronomy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘First Hogsmeade weekend,’ said Ron, pointing at a notice that had appeared on the battered old notice-board. ‘End of October. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hallowe’en.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent,’ said Fred, who had followed Harry through the portrait hole. ‘I need to visit Zonko’s, I’m nearly out of Stink Pellets.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry threw himself into a chair beside Ron, his high spirits ebbing away. Hermione seemed to read his mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>110 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, I’m sure you’ll be able to go next time,’ she said. ‘They’re bound to catch Black soon, he’s been sighted once already.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Black’s not fool enough to try anything in Hogsmeade,’ said Ron. ‘Ask McGonagall if you can go this time, Harry, the next one might not be for ages –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron! </i>’ said Hermione. ‘Harry’s supposed to stay  <i class=\"calibre4\">in school</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He can’t be the only third-year left behind,’ said Ron. ‘Ask McGonagall, go on, Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I think I will,’ said Harry, making up his mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione opened her mouth to argue, but at that moment Crookshanks leapt lightly onto her lap. A large, dead spider was dangling from his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Does he have to eat that in front of us?’ said Ron, scowling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Clever Crookshanks, did you catch that all by yourself?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks slowly chewed up the spider, his yellow eyes fixed insolently on Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just keep him over there, that’s all,’ said Ron irritably, turning back to his star chart. ‘I’ve got Scabbers asleep in my bag.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry yawned. He really wanted to go to bed, but he still had his own star chart to complete. He pulled his bag towards him, took out parchment, ink and quill, and started work. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can copy mine, if you like,’ said Ron, labelling his last star with a flourish and shoving the chart towards Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, who disapproved of copying, pursed her lips, but didn’t say anything. Crookshanks was still staring unblinkingly at Ron, flicking the end of his bushy tail. Then, without warning, he pounced. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OY!’ Ron roared, seizing his bag, as Crookshanks sank four sets of claws deeply into it, and began tearing ferociously. ‘GET </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">OFF, YOU STUPID ANIMAL!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron tried to pull the bag away from Crookshanks, but Crookshanks clung on, spitting and slashing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, don’t hurt him!’ squealed Hermione. The whole common room was watching; Ron whirled the bag around, Crookshanks still clinging to it, and Scabbers came flying out of the top – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘CATCH THAT CAT!’ Ron yelled, as Crookshanks freed himself from the remnants of the bag, sprang over the table and chased after the terrified Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">George Weasley made a lunge for Crookshanks but missed; </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 111 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scabbers streaked through twenty pairs of legs and shot beneath an old chest of drawers. Crookshanks skidded to a halt, crouched low on his bandy legs and started making furious swipes beneath the chest of drawers with his front paw. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione hurried over; Hermione grabbed Crookshanks around the middle and heaved him away; Ron threw himself onto his stomach and, with great difficulty, pulled Scabbers out by the tail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at him!’ he said furiously to Hermione, dangling Scabbers in front of her. ‘He’s skin and bone! You keep that cat away from him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crookshanks doesn’t understand it’s wrong!’ said Hermione, her voice shaking. ‘All cats chase rats, Ron!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s something funny about that animal!’ said Ron, who was trying to persuade a frantically wiggling Scabbers back into his pocket. ‘It heard me say that Scabbers was in my bag!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,  what  rubbish,’  said  Hermione  impatiently.  ‘Crookshanks could  <i class=\"calibre4\">smell </i> him, Ron, how else d’you think –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That cat’s got it in for Scabbers!’ said Ron, ignoring the people around him, who were starting to giggle. ‘And Scabbers was here first,  <i class=\"calibre4\">and </i> he’s ill!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron marched through the common room and out of sight up the stairs to the boys’ dormitories. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was still in a bad mood with Hermione next day. He barely talked to her all through Herbology, even though he, Harry and Hermione were working together on the same Puffapod. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s Scabbers?’ Hermione asked timidly, as they stripped fat pink pods from the plants and emptied the shining beans into a wooden pail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s hiding at the bottom of my bed, shaking,’ said Ron angrily, missing the pail and scattering beans over the greenhouse floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Careful, Weasley, careful!’ cried Professor Sprout, as the beans burst into bloom before their very eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had Transfiguration next. Harry, who had resolved to ask Professor McGonagall after the lesson whether he could go into Hogsmeade with the rest, joined the queue outside the classroom, trying to decide how he was going to argue his case. He was distracted, however, by a disturbance at the front of the line. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lavender Brown seemed to be crying. Parvati had her arm </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>112 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">around her, and was explaining something to Seamus Finnigan and Dean Thomas, who were looking very serious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter, Lavender?’ said Hermione anxiously, as she, Harry and Ron went to join the group. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She got a letter from home this morning,’ Parvati whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s her rabbit, Binky. He’s been killed by a fox.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Hermione. ‘I’m sorry, Lavender.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I should have known!’ said Lavender tragically. ‘You know what day it is?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The sixteenth of October! “That thing you’re dreading, it will happen on the sixteenth of October!” Remember? She was right, she was right!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The whole class was gathered around Lavender now. Seamus shook his head seriously. Hermione hesitated; then she said, ‘You </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– you were dreading Binky being killed by a fox?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, not necessarily by a  <i class=\"calibre4\">fox</i>,’ said Lavender, looking up at Hermione with streaming eyes, ‘but I was  <i class=\"calibre4\">obviously</i> dreading him dying, wasn’t I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Hermione. She paused again. Then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Was Binky an  <i class=\"calibre4\">old</i> rabbit?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘N-no!’ sobbed Lavender. ‘H-he was only a baby!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati tightened her arm around Lavender’s shoulders. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then, why would you dread him dying?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati glared at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, look at it logically,’ said Hermione, turning to the rest of the group. ‘I mean, Binky didn’t even die today, did he, Lavender just got the news today –’ Lavender wailed loudly ‘– and she  <i class=\"calibre4\">can’t</i> have been dreading it, because it’s come as a real shock –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t mind Hermione, Lavender,’ said Ron loudly, ‘she doesn’t think other people’s pets matter very much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall opened the classroom door at that moment, which was perhaps lucky; Hermione and Ron were looking daggers at each other, and when they got into class, they seated themselves either side of Harry, and didn’t talk to each other all lesson. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry still hadn’t decided what he was going to say to Professor McGonagall when the bell rang at the end of the lesson, but it was she who brought up the subject of Hogsmeade first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One moment, please!’ she called, as the class made to leave. ‘As </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 113 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you’re all in my house, you should hand Hogsmeade permission forms to me before Hallowe’en. No form, no visiting the village, so don’t forget!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville put up his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, Professor, I – I think I’ve lost –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your grandmother sent yours to me directly, Longbottom,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘She seemed to think it was safer. Well, that’s all, you may leave.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ask her now,’ Ron hissed at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, but –’ Hermione began. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go for it, Harry,’ said Ron stubbornly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited for the rest of the class to disappear, then headed nervously for Professor McGonagall’s desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took a deep breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor, my aunt and uncle – er – forgot to sign my form,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall looked over her square spectacles at him, but didn’t say anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So – er – d’you think it would be all right – I mean, will it be OK if I – if I go to Hogsmeade?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall looked down and began shuffling papers on her desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m afraid not, Potter,’ she said. ‘You heard what I said. No form, no visiting the village. That’s the rule.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But – Professor, my aunt and uncle – you know, they’re Muggles, they don’t really understand about – about Hogwarts forms and stuff,’ Harry said, while Ron egged him on with vigor-ous nods. ‘If you said I could go –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But I don’t say so,’ said Professor McGonagall, standing up and piling her papers neatly into a drawer. ‘The form clearly states that the parent or guardian must give permission.’ She turned to look at him, with an odd expression on her face. Was it pity? ‘I’m sorry, Potter, but that’s my final word. You had better hurry, or you’ll be late for your next lesson.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was nothing to be done. Ron called Professor McGonagall a lot of names that greatly annoyed Hermione; Hermione assumed an ‘all for the best’ expression that made Ron even angrier, and Harry had to endure everyone in the class talking loudly and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>114 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">happily about what they were going to do first, once they got into Hogsmeade. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s always the feast,’ said Ron, in an effort to cheer Harry up. ‘You know, the Hallowe’en feast, in the evening.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Harry, gloomily, ‘great.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hallowe’en feast was always good, but it would taste a lot better if he was coming to it after a day in Hogsmeade with everyone else. Nothing anyone said made him feel any better about being left behind. Dean Thomas, who was good with a quill, had offered to forge Uncle Vernon’s signature on the form, but as Harry had already told Professor McGonagall he hadn’t had it signed, that was no good. Ron half-heartedly suggested the Invisibility Cloak, but Hermione stamped on that one, reminding Ron what Dumbledore had told them about the Dementors being able to see through them. Percy had what were possibly the least helpful words of comfort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They make a fuss about Hogsmeade, but I assure you, Harry, it’s not all it’s cracked up to be,’ he said seriously. ‘All right, the sweetshop’s rather good, but Zonko’s Joke Shop’s frankly dangerous, and yes, the Shrieking Shack’s always worth a visit, but really, Harry, apart from that, you’re not missing anything.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Hallowe’en morning, Harry awoke with the rest and went down to breakfast feeling thoroughly depressed, though doing his best to act normally. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll bring you lots of sweets back from Honeydukes,’ said Hermione, looking desperately sorry for him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, loads,’ said Ron. He and Hermione had finally forgotten their squabble about Crookshanks in the face of Harry’s disappointment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry about me,’ said Harry, in what he hoped was an offhand voice. ‘I’ll see you at the feast. Have a good time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He accompanied them to the Entrance Hall, where Filch, the caretaker, was standing inside the front doors, checking off names against a long list, peering suspiciously into every face, and making sure that no one was sneaking out who shouldn’t be going. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Staying here, Potter?’ shouted Malfoy, who was standing in line with Crabbe and Goyle. ‘Scared of passing the Dementors?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ignored him and made his solitary way up the marble stair-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 115 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">case, through the deserted corridors, and back to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Password?’ said the Fat Lady, jerking out of a doze. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fortuna Major,’ said Harry listlessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The portrait swung open and he climbed through the hole into the common room. It was full of chattering first- and second-years, and a few older students who had obviously visited Hogsmeade so often the novelty had worn off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry! Hi, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Colin Creevey, a second-year who was deeply in awe of Harry and never missed an opportunity to speak to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Aren’t you going to Hogsmeade, Harry? Why not? Hey –’ Colin looked eagerly around at his friends, ‘you can come and sit with us, if you like, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – no, thanks, Colin,’ said Harry, who wasn’t in the mood to have a lot of people staring avidly at the scar on his forehead. ‘I – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ve got to go to the library, got to get some work done.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After that, he had no choice but to turn right around and head back out of the portrait hole again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was the point of waking me up?’ the Fat Lady called grumpily after him as he walked away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wandered dispiritedly towards the library, but halfway there he changed his mind; he didn’t feel like working. He turned around and came face to face with Filch, who had obviously just seen off the last of the Hogsmeade visitors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ Filch snarled suspiciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Harry truthfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing!’ spat Filch, his jowls quivering unpleasantly. ‘A likely story! Sneaking around on your own, why aren’t you in Hogsmeade buying Stink Pellets and Belch Powder and Whizzing Worms like the rest of your nasty little friends?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shrugged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, get back to your common room where you belong!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snapped Filch, and he stood glaring until Harry had passed out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry didn’t go back to the common room; he climbed a staircase, thinking vaguely of visiting the Owlery to see Hedwig, and was walking along another corridor when a voice from inside one of the rooms said, ‘Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry doubled back to see who had spoken and met Professor Lupin, looking around his office door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>116 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ said Lupin, in a very different voice from Filch. ‘Where are Ron and Hermione?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hogsmeade,’ said Harry, in a would-be casual voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Lupin. He considered Harry for a moment. ‘Why don’t you come in? I’ve just taken delivery of a Grindylow for our next lesson.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A what?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He followed Lupin into his office. In the corner stood a very large tank of water. A sickly-green creature with sharp little horns had its face pressed against the glass, pulling faces and flexing its long, spindly fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Water demon,’ said Lupin, surveying the Grindylow thoughtfully. ‘We shouldn’t have much difficulty with him, not after the Kappas. The trick is to break his grip. You notice the abnormally long fingers? Strong, but very brittle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Grindylow bared its green teeth and then buried itself in a tangle of weed in a corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Cup of tea?’ Lupin said, looking around for his kettle. ‘I was just thinking of making one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right,’ said Harry awkwardly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin tapped the kettle with his wand and a blast of steam issued suddenly from the spout. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit down,’ said Lupin, taking the lid off a dusty tin. ‘I’ve only got teabags, I’m afraid – but I daresay you’ve had enough of tea leaves?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at him. Lupin’s eyes were twinkling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you know about that?’ Harry asked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor McGonagall told me,’ said Lupin, passing Harry a chipped mug of tea. ‘You’re not worried, are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He thought for a moment of telling Lupin about the dog he’d seen in Magnolia Crescent, but decided not to. He didn’t want Lupin to think he was a coward, especially since Lupin already seemed to think he couldn’t cope with a Boggart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something of Harry’s thoughts seemed to have shown on his face, because Lupin said, ‘Anything worrying you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Harry lied. He drank a bit of tea and watched the Grindylow brandishing a fist at him. ‘Yes,’ he said suddenly, putting his tea down on Lupin’s desk. ‘You know that day we fought the Boggart?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 117 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Lupin slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why didn’t you let me fight it?’ said Harry abruptly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin raised his eyebrows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would have thought that was obvious, Harry,’ he said, sounding surprised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who had expected Lupin to deny that he’d done any such thing, was taken aback. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ he said again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Lupin, frowning slightly, ‘I assumed that if the Boggart faced you, it would assume the shape of Lord Voldemort.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. Not only was this the last answer he’d expected, but Lupin had said Voldemort’s name. The only person Harry had ever heard say the name aloud (apart from himself) was Professor Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Clearly, I was wrong,’ said Lupin, still frowning at Harry. ‘But I didn’t think it a good idea for Lord Voldemort to materialise in the staff room. I imagined that people would panic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I did think of Voldemort first,’ said Harry honestly. ‘But then I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– I remembered those Dementors.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see,’ said Lupin thoughtfully. ‘Well, well … I’m impressed.’ He smiled slightly at the look of surprise on Harry’s face. ‘That suggests that what you fear most of all is – fear. Very wise, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know what to say to that, so he drank some more tea. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you’ve been thinking that I didn’t believe you capable of fighting the Boggart?’ said Lupin shrewdly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … yeah,’ said Harry. He was suddenly feeling a lot happier. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin, you know the Dementors –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was interrupted by a knock on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come in,’ called Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door opened, and in came Snape. He was carrying a goblet, which was smoking faintly, and stopped at the sight of Harry, his black eyes narrowing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, Severus,’ said Lupin, smiling. ‘Thanks very much. Could you leave it here on the desk for me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape set the smoking goblet down, his eyes wandering between Harry and Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was just showing Harry my Grindylow,’ said Lupin pleasantly, pointing at the tank. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fascinating,’ said Snape, without looking at it. ‘You should </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>118 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">drink that directly, Lupin.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, yes, I will,’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I made an entire cauldronful,’ Snape continued. ‘If you need more.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I should probably take some again tomorrow. Thanks very much, Severus.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not at all,’ said Snape, but there was a look in his eye Harry didn’t like. He backed out of the room, unsmiling and watchful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked curiously at the goblet. Lupin smiled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape has very kindly concocted a potion for me,’ he said. ‘I have never been much of a potion-brewer and this one is particularly complex.’ He picked up the goblet and sniffed it. ‘Pity sugar makes it useless,’ he added, taking a sip and shuddering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why –?’ Harry began. Lupin looked at him and answered the unfinished question. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve been feeling a bit off-colour,’ he said. ‘This potion is the only thing that helps. I am very lucky to be working alongside Professor Snape; there aren’t many wizards who are up to making it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin took another sip and Harry had a mad urge to knock the goblet out of his hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape’s very interested in the Dark Arts,’ he blurted out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really?’ said Lupin, looking only mildly interested as he took another gulp of potion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some people reckon –’ Harry hesitated, then plunged reckless-ly on, ‘some people reckon he’d do anything to get the Defence Against the Dark Arts job.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin drained the goblet and pulled a face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Disgusting,’ he said. ‘Well, Harry, I’d better get back to work. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ll see you at the feast later.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Harry, putting his empty teacup down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The empty goblet was still smoking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There you go,’ said Ron. ‘We got as much as we could carry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A shower of brilliantly coloured sweets fell into Harry’s lap. It was dusk, and Ron and Hermione had just turned up in the common room, pink-faced from the cold wind and looking as though they’d had the time of their lives. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thanks,’ said Harry, picking up a packet of tiny black Pepper </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 119 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Imps. ‘What’s Hogsmeade like? Where did you go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By the sound of it – everywhere. Dervish and Banges, the wizarding equipment shop, Zonko’s Joke Shop, into the Three Broomsticks for foaming mugs of hot Butterbeer and many places besides. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The post office, Harry! About two hundred owls, all sitting on shelves, all colour-coded depending on how fast you want your letter to get there!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Honeydukes have got a new kind of fudge, they were giving out free samples, there’s a bit, look –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We   <i class=\"calibre4\">think</i> we saw an ogre, honestly, they get all sorts at the Three Broomsticks –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wish we could have brought you some Butterbeer, really warms you up –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did you do?’ said Hermione, looking anxious. ‘Did you get any work done?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. ‘Lupin made me a cup of tea in his office. And then Snape came in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He told them all about the goblet. Ron’s mouth fell open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lupin drank it? </i>’ he gasped. ‘Is he mad?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione checked her watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better go down, you know, the feast’ll be starting in five minutes …’ They hurried through the portrait hole and into the crowd, still discussing Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if he – you know –’ Hermione dropped her voice, glancing nervously around, ‘if he  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> trying to – to poison Lupin – he wouldn’t have done it in front of Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, maybe,’ said Harry, as they reached the Entrance Hall and crossed into the Great Hall. It had been decorated with hundreds and hundreds of candle-filled pumpkins, a cloud of fluttering live bats and many flaming orange streamers, which were swimming lazily across the stormy ceiling like brilliant watersnakes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The food was delicious; even Hermione and Ron, who were full to bursting with Honeydukes sweets, managed second helpings of everything. Harry kept glancing at the staff table. Professor Lupin looked cheerful and as well as he ever did; he was talking animatedly to tiny little Professor Flitwick, the Charms teacher. Harry moved his eyes along the table, to the place where Snape sat. Was he imagining it, or were Snape’s eyes flickering towards Lupin more often than was natural? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>120 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The feast finished with an entertainment provided by the Hogwarts ghosts. They popped out of the walls and tables to do a spot of formation gliding; Nearly Headless Nick, the Gryffindor ghost, had a great success with a re-enactment of his own botched beheading. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It had been such a good evening that Harry’s good mood couldn’t even be spoiled by Malfoy, who shouted through the crowd as they all left the Hall, ‘The Dementors send their love, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione followed the rest of the Gryffindors along the usual path to Gryffindor Tower, but when they reached the corridor which ended with the portrait of the Fat Lady, they found it jammed with students. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why isn’t anyone going in?’ said Ron curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry peered over the heads in front of him. The portrait seemed to be closed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me through, please,’ came Percy’s voice, and he came bustling importantly through the crowd. ‘What’s the hold-up here? You can’t all have forgotten the password – excuse me, I’m Head Boy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then a silence fell over the crowd, from the front first, so that a chill seemed to spread down the corridor. They heard Percy say, in a suddenly sharp voice, ‘Somebody get Professor Dumbledore. Quick.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People’s heads turned; those at the back were standing on tiptoe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ said Ginny, who had just arrived. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next moment, Professor Dumbledore was there, sweeping towards the portrait; the Gryffindors squeezed together to let him through, and Harry, Ron and Hermione moved closer to see what the trouble was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, my –’ Hermione exclaimed and grabbed Harry’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Fat Lady had vanished from her portrait, which had been slashed so viciously that strips of canvas littered the floor; great chunks of it had been torn away completely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore took one quick look at the ruined painting and turned, his eyes sombre, to see Professors McGonagall, Lupin and Snape hurrying towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We need to find her,’ said Dumbledore. ‘Professor McGonagall, please go to Mr Filch at once and tell him to search every painting in the castle for the Fat Lady.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flight of the Fat Lady 121 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll be lucky!’ said a cackling voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Peeves the poltergeist, bobbing over the crowd and looking delighted, as he always did, at the sight of wreckage or worry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you mean, Peeves?’ said Dumbledore calmly, and Peeves’s grin faded a little. He didn’t dare taunt Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Instead he adopted an oily voice that was no better than his cackle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ashamed, Your Headship, sir. Doesn’t want to be seen. She’s a horrible mess. Saw her running through the landscape up on the fourth floor, sir, dodging between the trees. Crying something dreadful,’ he said happily. ‘Poor thing,’ he added, unconvincingly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did she say who did it?’ said Dumbledore quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes, Professorhead,’ said Peeves, with the air of one cradling a large bombshell in his arms. ‘He got very angry when she wouldn’t let him in, you see.’ Peeves flipped over, and grinned at Dumbledore from between his own legs. ‘Nasty temper he’s got, that Sirius Black.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER NINE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Grim Defeat </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Dumbledore sent all the Gryffindors back to the Great Hall, where they were joined ten minutes later by the students from Hufflepuff, Ravenclaw and Slytherin, who all looked extremely confused. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The teachers and I need to conduct a thorough search of the castle,’ Professor Dumbledore told them as Professors McGonagall and Flitwick closed all doors into the Hall. ‘I’m afraid that, for your own safety, you will have to spend the night here. I want the Prefects to stand guard over the entrances to the Hall and I am leaving the Head Boy and Girl in charge. Any disturbance should be reported to me immediately,’ he added to Percy, who was looking immensely proud and important. ‘Send word with one of the ghosts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Dumbledore paused, about to the leave the Hall, and said, ‘Oh, yes, you’ll be needing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One casual wave of his wand and the long tables flew to the edges of the Hall and stood themselves against the walls; another wave, and the floor was covered with hundreds of squashy purple sleeping bags. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sleep well,’ said Professor Dumbledore, closing the door behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hall immediately began to buzz excitedly; the Gryffindors were telling the rest of the school what had just happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone into their sleeping bags!’ shouted Percy. ‘Come on now, no more talking! Lights out in ten minutes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon,’ Ron said to Harry and Hermione; they seized three sleeping bags and dragged them into a corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think Black’s still in the castle?’ Hermione whispered anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore obviously thinks he might be,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 123 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s very lucky he picked tonight, you know,’ said Hermione, as they climbed fully dressed into their sleeping bags and propped themselves on their elbows to talk. ‘The one night we weren’t in the Tower …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I reckon he’s lost track of time, being on the run,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t realise it was Hallowe’en. Otherwise he’d have come bursting in here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione shuddered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All around them, people were asking each other the same question: ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">How did he get in? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe he knows how to Apparate,’ said a Ravenclaw a few feet away. ‘Just appear out of thin air, you know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Disguised himself, probably,’ said a Hufflepuff fifth-year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He could’ve flown in,’ suggested Dean Thomas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Honestly, am I the  <i class=\"calibre4\">only</i> person who’s ever bothered to read <i class=\"calibre4\">Hogwarts, A History? </i>’ said Hermione crossly to Harry and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably,’ said Ron. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because the castle’s protected by more than  <i class=\"calibre4\">walls</i>, you know,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione. ‘There are all sorts of enchantments on it, to stop people entering by stealth. You can’t just Apparate in here. And I’d like to see the disguise that could fool those Dementors. They’re guarding every single entrance to the grounds. They’d have seen him fly in, too. And Filch knows all the secret passages, they’ll have them covered …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The lights are going out now!’ Percy shouted. ‘I want everyone in their sleeping bags and no more talking!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The candles all went out at once. The only light now came from the silvery ghosts, who were drifting about talking seriously to the Prefects, and the enchanted ceiling, which, like the sky outside, was scattered with stars. What with that, and the whispering that still filled the Hall, Harry felt as though he was sleeping out of doors in a light wind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Once every hour, a teacher would reappear in the Hall to check that everything was quiet. Around three in the morning, when many students had finally fallen asleep, Professor Dumbledore came in. Harry watched him looking around for Percy, who had been prowling between the sleeping bags, telling people off for talking. Percy was only a short way away from Harry, Ron and Hermione, who quickly pretended to be asleep as Dumbledore’s footsteps drew nearer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>124 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Any sign of him, Professor?’ asked Percy in a whisper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No. All well here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everything under control, sir.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good. There’s no point moving them all now. I’ve found a tem-porary guardian for the Gryffindor portrait hole. You’ll be able to move them back in tomorrow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the Fat Lady, sir?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hiding in a map of Argyllshire on the second floor. Apparently she refused to let Black in without the password, so he attacked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She’s still very distressed, but once she’s calmed down, I’ll have Mr Filch restore her.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry heard the door of the Hall creak open again, and more footsteps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Headmaster?’ It was Snape. Harry kept quite still, listening hard. ‘The whole of the third floor has been searched. He’s not there. And Filch has done the dungeons; nothing there, either.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about the Astronomy Tower? Professor Trelawney’s room? The Owlery?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All searched …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well, Severus. I didn’t really expect Black to linger.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you any theory as to how he got in, Professor?’ asked Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry raised his head very slightly off his arms to free his other ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Many, Severus, each of them as unlikely as the next.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry opened his eyes a fraction and squinted up to where they stood; Dumbledore’s back was to him, but he could see Percy’s face, rapt with attention, and Snape’s profile, which looked angry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You remember the conversation we had, Headmaster, just before – ah – the start of term?’ said Snape, who was barely opening his lips, as though trying to block Percy out of the conversation. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I do, Severus,’ said Dumbledore, and there was something like warning in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It seems – almost impossible – that Black could have entered the school without inside help. I did express my concerns when you appointed –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I do not believe a single person inside this castle would have helped Black enter it,’ said Dumbledore, and his tone made it so </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 125 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">clear that the subject was closed that Snape didn’t reply. ‘I must go down to the Dementors,’ said Dumbledore. ‘I said I would inform them when our search was complete.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t they want to help, sir?’ said Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yes,’ said Dumbledore coldly. ‘But I’m afraid no Dementor will cross the threshold of this castle while I am Headmaster.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy looked slightly abashed. Dumbledore left the Hall, walking quickly and quietly. Snape stood for a moment, watching the Headmaster with an expression of deep resentment on his face, then he, too, left. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced sideways at Ron and Hermione. Both of them had their eyes open, too, reflecting the starry ceiling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was all that about?’ Ron mouthed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The school talked of nothing but Sirius Black for the next few days. The theories about how he had entered the castle became wilder and wilder; Hannah Abbott, from Hufflepuff, spent much of their next Herbology class telling anyone who’d listen that Black could turn into a flowering shrub. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Fat Lady’s ripped canvas had been taken off the wall and replaced with the portrait of Sir Cadogan and his fat grey pony. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody was very happy about this. Sir Cadogan spent half his time challenging people to duels, and the rest thinking up ridiculously complicated passwords, which he changed at least twice a day. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s barking mad,’ said Seamus Finnigan angrily to Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t we get anyone else?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘None of the other pictures wanted the job,’ said Percy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Frightened of what happened to the Fat Lady. Sir Cadogan was the only one brave enough to volunteer.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sir Cadogan, however, was the least of Harry’s worries. He was now being closely watched. Teachers found excuses to walk along corridors with him and Percy Weasley (acting, Harry suspected, on his mother’s orders) was tailing him everywhere like an extremely pompous guard dog. To cap it all, Professor McGonagall summoned Harry into her office, with such a sombre expression on her face Harry thought someone must have died. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s no point hiding it from you any longer, Potter,’ she said, in a very serious voice. ‘I know this will come as a shock to you, but Sirius Black –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>126 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know he’s after me,’ said Harry wearily. ‘I heard Ron’s dad telling his mum. Mr Weasley works for the Ministry of Magic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall seemed very taken aback. She stared at Harry for a moment or two, then said, ‘I see! Well, in that case, Potter, you’ll understand why I don’t think it’s a good idea for you to be practising Quidditch in the evenings. Out on the pitch with only your team members, it’s very exposed, Potter –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got our first match on Saturday!’ said Harry, outraged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got to train, Professor!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall considered him intently. Harry knew she was deeply interested in the Gryffindor team’s prospects; it had been she, after all, who’d suggested him as Seeker in the first place. He waited, holding his breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hmm …’ Professor McGonagall stood up and stared out of the window at the Quidditch pitch, just visible through the rain. ‘Well </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… goodness knows, I’d like to see us win the Cup at last … but all the same, Potter … I’d be happier if a teacher were present. I’ll ask Madam Hooch to oversee your training sessions.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The weather worsened steadily as the first Quidditch match drew nearer. Undaunted, the Gryffindor team were training harder than ever under the eye of Madam Hooch. Then, at their final training session before Saturday’s match, Oliver Wood gave his team some unwelcome news. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re not playing Slytherin!’ he told them, looking very angry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Flint’s just been to see me. We’re playing Hufflepuff instead.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why?’ chorused the rest of the team. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Flint’s excuse is that their Seeker’s arm’s still injured,’ said Wood, grinding his teeth furiously. ‘But it’s obvious why they’re doing it. Don’t want to play in this weather. Think it’ll damage their chances …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There had been strong winds and heavy rain all day, and as Wood spoke, they heard a distant rumble of thunder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">nothing wrong </i> with Malfoy’s arm!’ said Harry furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s faking it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know that, but we can’t prove it,’ said Wood bitterly. ‘And we’ve been practising all those moves assuming we’re playing Slytherin, and instead it’s Hufflepuff, and their style’s quite different. They’ve got a new captain and Seeker, Cedric Diggory –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Angelina, Alicia and Katie suddenly giggled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 127 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Wood, frowning at this light-hearted behaviour. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s that tall, good-looking one, isn’t he?’ said Angelina. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Strong and silent,’ said Katie, and they started to giggle again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s only silent because he’s too thick to string two words together,’ said Fred impatiently. ‘I don’t know why you’re worried, Oliver, Hufflepuff are a pushover. Last time we played them, Harry caught the Snitch in about five minutes, remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were playing in completely different conditions!’ Wood shouted, his eyes bulging slightly. ‘Diggory’s put a very strong side together! He’s an excellent Seeker! I was afraid you’d take it like this! We mustn’t relax! We must keep our focus! Slytherin are trying to wrong-foot us! We  <i class=\"calibre4\">must</i> win!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oliver, calm down!’ said Fred, looking slightly alarmed. ‘We’re taking Hufflepuff very seriously.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Seriously</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The day before the match, the winds reached howling point and the rain fell harder than ever. It was so dark inside the corridors and classrooms that extra torches and lanterns were lit. The Slytherin team were looking very smug indeed, and none more so than Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, if only my arm was feeling a bit better!’ he sighed, as the gale outside pounded the windows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had no room in his head to worry about anything except the match next day. Oliver Wood kept hurrying up to him between classes and giving him tips. The third time this happened,  Wood  talked  for  so  long  that Harry suddenly realised he was ten minutes late for Defence Against the Dark Arts, and set off at a run with Wood shouting after him, ‘Diggory’s got a very fast swerve, Harry, so you might want to try looping him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry skidded to a halt outside the Defence Against the Dark Arts classroom, pulled the door open and dashed inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry I’m late, Professor Lupin, I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But it wasn’t Professor Lupin who looked up at him from the teacher’s desk; it was Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This lesson began ten minutes ago, Potter, so I think we’ll make it ten points from Gryffindor. Sit down.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry didn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Professor Lupin?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He says he is feeling too ill to teach today,’ said Snape with a twisted smile. ‘I believe I told you to sit down?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>128 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry stayed where he was. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s wrong with him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s black eyes glittered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing life-threatening,’ he said, looking as though he wished it was. ‘Five more points from Gryffindor, and if I have to ask you to sit down again, it will be fifty.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry walked slowly to his seat and sat down. Snape looked around at the class. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As I was saying before Potter interrupted, Professor Lupin has not left any record of the topics you have covered so far –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, sir, we’ve done Boggarts, Red Caps, Kappas and Grindylows,’ said Hermione quickly, ‘and we’re just about to start –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Be quiet,’ said Snape coldly. ‘I did not ask for information. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I was merely commenting on Professor Lupin’s lack of organisation.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s the best Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher we’ve ever had,’ said Dean Thomas boldly, and there was a murmur of agree-ment from the rest of the class. Snape looked more menacing than ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You are easily satisfied. Lupin is hardly over-taxing you – I would expect first-years to be able to deal with Red Caps and Grindylows. Today we shall discuss –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched him flick through the textbook, to the very back chapter, which he must know they hadn’t covered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– werewolves,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But, sir,’ said Hermione, seemingly unable to restrain herself, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘we’re not supposed to do werewolves yet, we’re due to start Hinkypunks –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger,’ said Snape, in a voice of deadly calm, ‘I was under the impression that I was taking this lesson, not you. And I am telling you all to turn to page three hundred and ninety-four.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He glanced around again. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">All </i> of you!  <i class=\"calibre4\">Now! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With many bitter sidelong looks and some sullen muttering, the class opened their books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which of you can tell me how we distinguish between the werewolf and the true wolf?’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everyone sat in motionless silence; everyone except Hermione, whose hand, as it so often did, had shot straight into the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyone?’ Snape said, ignoring Hermione. His twisted smile was back. ‘Are you telling me that Professor Lupin hasn’t even </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 129 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">taught you the basic distinction between –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We told you,’ said Parvati suddenly, ‘we haven’t got as far as werewolves yet, we’re still on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Silence! </i>’ snarled Snape. ‘Well, well, well, I never thought I’d meet a third-year class who wouldn’t even recognise a werewolf when they saw one. I shall make a point of informing Professor Dumbledore how very behind you all are …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, sir,’ said Hermione, whose hand was still in the air, ‘the werewolf differs from the true wolf in several small ways. The snout of the werewolf –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That is the second time you have spoken out of turn, Miss Granger,’ said Snape coolly. ‘Five more points from Gryffindor for being an insufferable know-it-all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione went very red, put down her hand and stared at the floor with her eyes full of tears. It was a mark of how much the class loathed Snape that they were all glaring at him, because every one of them had called Hermione a know-it-all at least once, and Ron, who told Hermione she was a know-it-all at least twice a week, said loudly, ‘You asked us a question and she knows the answer! Why ask if you don’t want to be told?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The class knew instantly he’d gone too far. Snape advanced on Ron slowly, and the room held its breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Detention, Weasley,’ Snape said silkily, his face very close to Ron’s. ‘And if I ever hear you criticise the way I teach a class again, you will be very sorry indeed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one made a sound throughout the rest of the lesson. They sat and made notes on werewolves from the textbook, while Snape prowled up and down the rows of desks, examining the work they had been doing with Professor Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very poorly explained … that is incorrect, the Kappa is more commonly found in Mongolia … Professor Lupin gave this eight out of ten? I wouldn’t have given it three …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the bell rang at last, Snape held them back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You will each write an essay, to be handed in to me, on the ways you recognise and kill werewolves. I want two rolls of parchment  on  the  subject,  and  I  want  them  by  Monday  morning.  It  is time somebody took this class in hand. Weasley, stay behind, we need to arrange your detention.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione left the room with the rest of the class, who waited until they were well out of earshot, then burst into a </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>130 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">furious tirade about Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape’s never been like this with any of our other Defence Against the Dark Arts teachers, even if he did want the job,’ Harry said to Hermione. ‘Why’s he got it in for Lupin? D’you think this is all because of the Boggart?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ said Hermione pensively. ‘But I really hope Professor Lupin gets better soon …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron caught up with them five minutes later, in a towering rage. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you know what that –’ (he called Snape something that made Hermione say ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron! </i>’) ‘– is making me do? I’ve got to scrub out the bedpans in the hospital wing.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Without magic! </i>’ He was breathing deeply, his fists clenched. ‘Why couldn’t Black have hidden in Snape’s office, eh? He could have finished him off for us!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke extremely early next morning; so early that it was still dark. For a moment he thought the roaring of the wind had woken him, then he felt a cold breeze on the back of his neck and sat bolt upright – Peeves the poltergeist had been floating next to him, blowing hard in his ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did you do that for?’ said Harry furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves puffed out his cheeks, blew hard and zoomed backwards out of the room, cackling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry fumbled for his alarm clock and looked at it. It was half past four. Cursing Peeves, he rolled over and tried to get back to sleep, but it was very difficult, now he was awake, to ignore the sounds of the thunder rumbling overhead, the pounding of the wind against the castle walls and the distant creaking of the trees in the Forbidden Forest. In a few hours he would be out on the Quidditch pitch, battling through that gale. Finally he gave up any thought of more sleep, got up, dressed, picked up his Nimbus Two Thousand and walked quietly out of the dormitory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry opened the door, something brushed against his leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He bent down just in time to grab Crookshanks by the end of his bushy tail, and drag him outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, I reckon Ron was right about you,’ Harry told Crookshanks suspiciously. ‘There are plenty of mice around this place, go and chase them. Go on,’ he added, nudging Crookshanks down the spiral staircase with his foot, ‘leave Scabbers alone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The noise of the storm was even louder in the common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 131 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew better than to think the match would be cancelled; Quidditch matches weren’t called off for trifles such as thunder-storms. Nevertheless, he was starting to feel very apprehensive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood had pointed out Cedric Diggory to him in the corridor; Diggory was a fifth-year and a lot bigger than Harry. Seekers were usually light and speedy, but Diggory’s weight would be an advantage in this weather because he was less likely to be blown off course. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry whiled away the hours until dawn in front of the fire, getting up every now and then to stop Crookshanks sneaking up the boys’ staircase again. At long last Harry thought it must be time for breakfast, so he headed through the portrait hole alone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand and fight, you mangy cur!’ yelled Sir Cadogan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, shut up,’ Harry yawned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He revived a bit over a large bowl of porridge, and by the time he’d started on toast, the rest of the team had turned up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s going to be a tough one,’ said Wood, who wasn’t eating anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop worrying, Oliver,’ said Alicia soothingly, ‘we don’t mind a bit of rain.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But it was considerably more than a bit of rain. Such was the popularity of Quidditch that the whole school turned out to watch the match as usual, but they ran down the lawns towards the Quidditch pitch, heads bowed against the ferocious wind, umbrellas being whipped out of their hands as they went. Just before he entered the changing room, Harry saw Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle laughing and pointing at him from under an enormous umbrella on their way to the stadium. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The team changed into their scarlet robes and waited for Wood’s usual pre-match pep talk, but it didn’t come. He tried to speak several times, made an odd gulping noise, then shook his head hopelessly and beckoned them to follow him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wind was so strong that they staggered sideways as they walked out onto the pitch. If the crowd was cheering they couldn’t hear it over the fresh rolls of thunder. Rain was splattering over Harry’s glasses. How on earth was he going to see the Snitch in this? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hufflepuffs were approaching from the opposite side of the pitch, wearing canary-yellow robes. The captains walked up to each other and shook hands; Diggory smiled at Wood but Wood </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>132 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">now looked as though he had lockjaw and merely nodded. Harry saw Madam Hooch’s mouth form the words, ‘Mount your brooms.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled his right foot out of the mud with a squelch and swung it over his Nimbus Two Thousand. Madam Hooch put her whistle to her lips and gave it a blast that sounded shrill and distant –  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they were off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry rose fast, but his Nimbus was swerving slightly with the wind. He held it as steady as he could and turned, squinting into the rain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Within five minutes Harry was soaked to his skin and frozen, hardly able to see his team-mates, let alone the tiny Snitch. He flew backwards and forwards across the pitch, past blurred red and yellow shapes, with no idea of what was happening in the rest of the game. He couldn’t hear the commentary over the wind. The crowd was hidden beneath a sea of cloaks and battered umbrellas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Twice Harry came very close to being unseated by a Bludger; his vision was so clouded by the rain on his glasses he hadn’t seen them coming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He lost track of time. It was getting harder and harder to hold his broom straight. The sky was getting darker, as though night had decided to come early. Twice Harry nearly hit another player, without knowing whether it was a team-mate or opponent; everyone was now so wet, and the rain so thick, he could hardly tell them apart … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With the first flash of lightning came the sound of Madam Hooch’s whistle; Harry could just see the outline of Wood through the thick rain, gesturing him to the ground. The whole team splashed down into the mud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I called for time out!’ Wood roared at his team. ‘Come on, under here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They huddled at the edge of the pitch under a large umbrella; Harry took off his glasses and wiped them hurriedly on his robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the score?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re fifty points up,’ said Wood, ‘but unless we get the Snitch soon, we’ll be playing into the night.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve got no chance with these on,’ Harry said exasperatedly, waving his glasses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that very moment, Hermione appeared at his shoulder; she was holding her cloak over her head and was, inexplicably, beaming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 133 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve had an idea, Harry! Give me your glasses, quick!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He handed them to her and, as the team watched in amazement, Hermione tapped them with her wand and said, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Impervius! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There!’ she said, handing them back to Harry. ‘They’ll repel water!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood looked as though he could have kissed her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant!’ he called hoarsely after her, as she disappeared into the crowd. ‘OK, team, let’s go for it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s spell had done the trick. Harry was still numb with cold, still wetter than he’d ever been in his life, but he could see. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Full of fresh determination, he urged his broom through the tur-bulent air, staring in every direction for the Snitch, avoiding a Bludger, ducking beneath Diggory, who was streaking in the opposite direction … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was another clap of thunder, followed immediately by forked lightning. This was getting more and more dangerous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry needed to get the Snitch quickly – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned, intending to head back towards the middle of the pitch, but at that moment, another flash of lightning illuminated the stands, and Harry saw something that distracted him completely: the silhouette of an enormous shaggy black dog, clearly imprinted against the sky, motionless in the topmost, empty row of seats. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s numb hands slipped on the broom handle and his Nimbus dropped a few feet. Shaking his sodden fringe out of his eyes, he squinted back into the stands. The dog had vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ came Wood’s anguished yell from the Gryffindor goalposts. ‘Harry, behind you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked wildly around. Cedric Diggory was pelting up the pitch, and a tiny speck of gold was shimmering in the rain-filled air between them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a jolt of panic, Harry threw himself flat to the broom handle and zoomed towards the Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on!’ he growled at his Nimbus, as the rain whipped his face. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Faster! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But something odd was happening. An eerie silence was falling across the stadium. The wind, though as strong as ever, was forgetting to roar. It was as though someone had turned off the sound, as though Harry had gone suddenly deaf – what was going on? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>134 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then a horribly familiar wave of cold swept over him, inside him, just as he became aware of something moving on the pitch below … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before he’d had time to think, Harry had taken his eyes off the Snitch and looked down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At least a hundred Dementors, their hidden faces pointing up at him, were standing below. It was as though freezing water was rising in his chest, cutting at his insides. And then he heard it again … someone was screaming, screaming inside his head … a woman … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Not Harry, not Harry, please not Harry! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Stand aside, you silly girl … stand aside, now</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Not Harry, please no, take me, kill me instead </i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Numbing, swirling white mist was filling Harry’s brain … What was he doing? Why was he flying? He needed to help her … she was going to die … she was going to be murdered … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was falling, falling through the icy mist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Not Harry! Please … have mercy … have mercy</i> …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A shrill voice was laughing, the woman was screaming, and Harry knew no more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lucky the ground was so soft.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought he was dead for sure.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But he didn’t even break his glasses.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could hear the voices whispering, but they made no sense whatsoever. He didn’t have a clue where he was, or how he’d got there, or what he’d been doing before he got there. All he knew was that every inch of him was aching as though it had been beaten. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was the scariest thing I’ve ever seen in my life.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scariest … the scariest thing … hooded black figures … cold … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">screaming … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s eyes snapped open. He was lying in the hospital wing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor Quidditch team, spattered with mud from head to foot, was gathered around his bed. Ron and Hermione were also there, looking as though they’d just climbed out of a swimming pool. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ said Fred, who looked extremely white underneath the mud. ‘How’re you feeling?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It  was  as  though  Harry’s  memory  was  on  fast  forward.  The </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Grim Defeat 135 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">lightning … the Grim … the Snitch … and the Dementors … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened?’ he said, sitting up so suddenly they all gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You fell off,’ said Fred. ‘Must’ve been – what – fifty feet?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We thought you’d died,’ said Alicia, who was shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione made a small, squeaky noise. Her eyes were extremely bloodshot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But the match,’ said Harry. ‘What happened? Are we having a replay?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one said anything. The horrible truth sank into Harry like a stone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We didn’t –  <i class=\"calibre4\">lose? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Diggory got the Snitch,’ said George. ‘Just after you fell. He didn’t realise what had happened. When he looked back and saw you on the ground, he tried to call it off. Wanted a re-match. But they won fair and square … even Wood admits it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is Wood?’ said Harry, suddenly realising he wasn’t there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Still in the showers,’ said Fred. ‘We think he’s trying to drown himself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put his face to his knees, his hands gripping his hair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred grabbed his shoulder and shook it roughly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon, Harry, you’ve never missed the Snitch before.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There had to be one time you didn’t get it,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not over yet,’ said Fred. ‘We lost by a hundred points, right? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So if Hufflepuff lose to Ravenclaw and we beat Ravenclaw and Slytherin …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hufflepuff’ll have to lose by at least two hundred points,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if they beat Ravenclaw …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No way, Ravenclaw are too good. But if Slytherin lose against Hufflepuff …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It all depends on the points – a margin of a hundred either way –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay there, not saying a word. They had lost … for the first time ever, he had lost a Quidditch match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After ten minutes or so, Madam Pomfrey came over to tell the team to leave him in peace. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll come and see you later,’ Fred told him. ‘Don’t beat yourself up, Harry, you’re still the best Seeker we’ve ever had.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The team trooped out, trailing mud behind them. Madam Pomfrey shut the door behind them, looking disapproving. Ron </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>136 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and Hermione moved nearer to Harry’s bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore was really angry,’ Hermione said in a quaking voice. ‘I’ve never seen him like that before. He ran onto the pitch as you fell, waved his wand, and you sort of slowed down before you hit the ground. Then he whirled his wand at the Dementors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Shot silver stuff at them. They left the stadium straight away … he was furious they’d come into the grounds, we heard him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then he magicked you onto a stretcher,’ said Ron. ‘And walked up to school with you floating on it. Everyone thought you were …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His voice faded away, but Harry hardly noticed. He was thinking about what the Dementors had done to him … about the screaming voice. He looked up and saw Ron and Hermione looking at him so anxiously that he quickly cast around for something matter-of-fact to say. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did someone get my Nimbus?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione looked quickly at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry, looking from one to the other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … when you fell off, it got blown away,’ said Hermione hesitantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And it hit – it hit – oh, Harry – it hit the Whomping Willow.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s insides lurched. The Whomping Willow was a very violent tree which stood alone in the middle of the grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And?’ he said, dreading the answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, you know the Whomping Willow,’ said Ron. ‘It – it doesn’t like being hit.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Flitwick brought it back just before you came round,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione in a very small voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slowly, she reached down for a bag at her feet, turned it upside-down and tipped a dozen bits of splintered wood and twig onto the bed, the only remains of Harry’s faithful, finally beaten broomstick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Marauder’s Map </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey insisted on keeping Harry in the hospital wing for the rest of the weekend. He didn’t argue or complain, but he wouldn’t let her throw away the shattered remnants of his Nimbus Two Thousand. He knew he was being stupid, knew that the Nimbus was beyond repair, but Harry couldn’t help it; he felt as though he’d lost one of his best friends. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had a stream of visitors, all intent on cheering him up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid sent him a bunch of earwiggy flowers that looked like yellow cabbages and Ginny Weasley, blushing furiously, turned up with a ‘get well’ card she had made herself, which sang shrilly unless Harry kept it shut under his bowl of fruit. The Gryffindor team visited again on Sunday morning, this time accompanied by Wood, who told Harry, in a hollow, dead sort of voice, that he didn’t blame him in the slightest. Ron and Hermione only left Harry’s bedside at night. But nothing anyone said or did could make Harry feel any better, because they only knew half of what was troubling him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He hadn’t told anyone about the Grim, not even Ron and Hermione, because he knew Ron would panic and Hermione would scoff. The fact remained, however, that it had now appeared twice, and both appearances had been followed by near-fatal accidents; the first time, he had nearly been run over by the Knight Bus; the second, fallen fifty feet from his broomstick. Was the Grim going to haunt him until he actually died? Was he going to spend the rest of his life looking over his shoulder for the beast? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then there were the Dementors. Harry felt sick and humili-ated every time he thought of them. Everyone said the Dementors were horrible, but no one else collapsed every time they went near one … no one else heard echoes in their head of their dying parents. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>138 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For Harry knew who that screaming voice belonged to now. He had heard her words, heard them over and over again during the night hours in the hospital wing while he lay awake, staring at the strips of moonlight on the ceiling. When the Dementors approached him, he heard the last moments of his mother’s life, her attempts to protect him, Harry, from Lord Voldemort, and Voldemort’s laughter before he murdered her … Harry dozed fit-fully, sinking into dreams full of clammy, rotted hands and petrified pleading, jerking awake only to dwell again on the sound of his mother’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a relief to return on Monday to the noise and bustle of the main school, where he was forced to think about other things, even if he had to endure Draco Malfoy’s taunting. Malfoy was almost beside himself with glee at Gryffindor’s defeat. He had finally taken off his bandages, and celebrated having the full use of both arms again by doing spirited imitations of Harry falling off his broom. Malfoy spent much of their next Potions class doing Dementor imitations across the dungeon; Ron finally cracked, flinging a large, slippery crocodile heart at Malfoy, which hit him in the face and caused Snape to take fifty points from Gryffindor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If Snape’s taking Defence Against the Dark Arts again, I’m going off sick,’ said Ron, as they headed towards Lupin’s classroom after lunch. ‘Check who’s in there, Hermione.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione peered around the classroom door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin was back at work. It certainly looked as though he had been ill. His old robes were hanging more loosely on him and there were dark shadows beneath his eyes; nevertheless, he smiled at the class as they took their seats, and they burst at once into an explosion of complaints about Snape’s behaviour while Lupin had been ill. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not fair, he was only filling in, why should he set us homework?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We don’t know anything about werewolves –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– two rolls of parchment!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you tell Professor Snape we haven’t covered them yet?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin asked, frowning slightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The babble broke out again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, but he said we were really behind –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 139 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– he wouldn’t listen –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘–  <i class=\"calibre4\">two rolls of parchment! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin smiled at the look of indignation on every face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t worry. I’ll speak to Professor Snape. You don’t have to do the essay.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh  <i class=\"calibre4\">no</i>,’ said Hermione, looking very disappointed. ‘I’ve already finished it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had a very enjoyable lesson. Professor Lupin had brought along a glass box containing a Hinkypunk, a little one-legged creature who seemed as though he was made of wisps of smoke, rather frail and harmless-looking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lures travellers into bogs,’ said Professor Lupin, as they took notes. ‘You notice the lantern dangling from his hand? Hops ahead – people follow the light – then –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hinkypunk made a horrible squelching noise against the glass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When the bell rang, everyone gathered up their things and headed for the door, Harry amongst them, but – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait a moment, Harry,’ Lupin called, ‘I’d like a word.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry doubled back and watched Professor Lupin covering the Hinkypunk’s box with a cloth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard about the match,’ said Lupin, turning back to his desk and starting to pile books into his briefcase, ‘and I’m sorry about your broomstick. Is there any chance of fixing it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. ‘The tree smashed it to bits.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin sighed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They planted the Whomping Willow the same year that I arrived at Hogwarts. People used to play a game, trying to get near enough to touch the trunk. In the end, a boy called Davey Gudgeon nearly lost an eye, and we were forbidden to go near it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No broomstick would have a chance.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you hear about the Dementors, too?’ said Harry with difficulty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin looked at him quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, I did. I don’t think any of us have seen Professor Dumbledore that angry. They have been growing restless for some time … furious at his refusal to let them inside the grounds … I suppose they were the reason you fell?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. He hesitated, and then the question he had to ask burst from him before he could stop himself. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Why? </i> Why do </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>140 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they affect me like that? Am I just –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It has nothing to do with weakness,’ said Professor Lupin sharply, as though he had read Harry’s mind. ‘The Dementors affect you worse than the others because there are horrors in your past that the others don’t have.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A ray of wintry sunlight fell across the classroom, illuminating Lupin’s grey hairs and the lines on his young face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dementors are among the foulest creatures that walk this earth. They infest the darkest, filthiest places, they glory in decay and despair, they drain peace, hope and happiness out of the air around them. Even Muggles feel their presence, though they can’t see them. Get too near a Dementor and every good feeling, every happy memory, will be sucked out of you. If it can, the Dementor will feed on you long enough to reduce you to something like itself – soulless and evil. You’ll be left with nothing but the worst experiences of your life. And the worst that has happened to  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i>, Harry, is enough to make anyone fall off their broom. You have nothing to feel ashamed of.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘When they get near me –’ Harry stared at Lupin’s desk, his throat tight, ‘I can hear Voldemort murdering my mum.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin made a sudden motion with his arm as though he had made to grip Harry’s shoulder, but thought better of it. There was a moment’s silence; then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why did they have to come to the match?’ said Harry bitterly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re getting hungry,’ said Lupin coolly, shutting his briefcase with a snap. ‘Dumbledore won’t let them into the school, so their supply of human prey has dried up … I don’t think they could resist the large crowd around the Quidditch pitch. All that excitement … emotions running high … it was their idea of a feast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Azkaban must be terrible,’ Harry muttered. Lupin nodded grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The fortress is set on a tiny island, way out to sea, but they don’t need walls and water to keep the prisoners in, not when they’re all trapped inside their own heads, incapable of a single cheerful thought. Most of them go mad within weeks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Sirius Black escaped from them,’ Harry said slowly. ‘He got away …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin’s briefcase slipped from the desk; he had to stoop quickly to catch it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ he said, straightening up. ‘Black must have found a way to fight them. I wouldn’t have believed it possible … Dementors are </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 141 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">supposed to drain a wizard of his powers if he is left with them too long …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You</i> made that Dementor on the train back off,’ said Harry suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There are – certain defences one can use,’ said Lupin. ‘But there was only one Dementor on the train. The more there are, the more difficult it becomes to resist.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What defences?’ said Harry at once. ‘Can you teach me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t pretend to be an expert at fighting Dementors, Harry – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">quite the contrary …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if the Dementors come to another Quidditch match, I need to be able to fight them –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin looked into Harry’s determined face, hesitated, then said, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … all right. I’ll try and help. But it’ll have to wait until next term, I’m afraid. I have a lot to do before the holidays. I chose a very inconvenient time to fall ill.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What with the promise of Anti-Dementor lessons from Lupin, the thought that he might never have to hear his mother’s death again, and the fact that Ravenclaw flattened Hufflepuff in their Quidditch match at the end of November, Harry’s mood took a definite upturn. Gryffindor were not out of the running after all, although they could not afford to lose another match. Wood became repossessed of his manic energy, and worked his team as hard as ever in the chilly haze of rain that persisted into December. Harry saw no hint of a Dementor within the grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore’s anger seemed to be keeping them at their stations at the entrances. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Two weeks before the end of term, the sky lightened suddenly to a dazzling, opaline white and the muddy grounds were revealed one morning covered in glittering frost. Inside the castle, there was a buzz of Christmas in the air. Professor Flitwick, the Charms teacher, had already decorated his classroom with shimmering lights that turned out to be real, fluttering fairies. The students were all happily discussing their plans for the holidays. Both Ron and Hermione had decided to remain at Hogwarts, and though Ron said it was because he couldn’t stand two weeks with Percy, and Hermione insisted she needed to use the library, Harry wasn’t fooled; they were doing it to keep him company, and he was very grateful. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>142 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To everyone’s delight except Harry’s, there was to be another Hogsmeade trip on the very last weekend of term. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can do all our Christmas shopping there!’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mum and Dad would really love those Toothflossing Stringmints from Honeydukes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Resigned to the fact that he would be the only third-year staying behind again, Harry borrowed a copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Which Broomstick</i> from Wood, and decided to spend the day reading up on the different makes. He had been riding one of the school brooms at team practice, an ancient Shooting Star, which was very slow and jerky; he definitely needed a new broom of his own. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On the Saturday morning of the Hogsmeade trip, Harry bid goodbye to Ron and Hermione, who were wrapped in cloaks and scarves, then turned up the marble staircase alone, and headed back towards Gryffindor Tower. Snow had started to fall outside the windows, and the castle was very still and quiet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Psst – Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned, halfway along the third-floor corridor, to see Fred and George peering out at him from behind a statue of a humpbacked, one-eyed witch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing?’ said Harry curiously. ‘How come you’re not going to Hogsmeade?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve come to give you a bit of festive cheer before we go,’ said Fred, with a mysterious wink. ‘Come in here …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He nodded towards an empty classroom to the left of the one-eyed statue. Harry followed Fred and George inside. George closed the door quietly and then turned, beaming, to look at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Early Christmas present for you, Harry,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred pulled something from inside his cloak with a flourish and laid it on one of the desks. It was a large, square, very worn piece of parchment with nothing written on it. Harry, suspecting one of Fred and George’s jokes, stared at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that supposed to be?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This, Harry, is the secret of our success,’ said George, patting the parchment fondly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s a wrench, giving it to you,’ said Fred, ‘but we decided last night, your need’s greater than ours.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway, we know it off by heart,’ said George. ‘We bequeath it to you. We don’t really need it any more.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 143 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what do I need with a bit of old parchment?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A bit of old parchment!’ said Fred, closing his eyes with a grimace  as  though  Harry  had  mortally  offended  him.  ‘Explain, George.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … when we were in our first year, Harry – young, carefree and innocent –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry snorted. He doubted whether Fred and George had ever been innocent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– well, more innocent than we are now – we got into a spot of bother with Filch.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We let off a Dungbomb in the corridor and it upset him for some reason –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So he hauled us off to his office and started threatening us with the usual –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– detention –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– disembowelment –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and we couldn’t help noticing a drawer in one of his filing cabinets marked  <i class=\"calibre4\">Confiscated and Highly Dangerous. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t tell me –’ said Harry, starting to grin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, what would you’ve done?’ said Fred. ‘George caused a diversion by dropping another Dungbomb, I whipped the drawer open and grabbed –  <i class=\"calibre4\">this</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not as bad as it sounds, you know,’ said George. ‘We don’t reckon Filch ever found out how to work it. He probably suspected what it was, though, or he wouldn’t have confiscated it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And you know how to work it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh yes,’ said Fred, smirking. ‘This little beauty’s taught us more than all the teachers in this school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re winding me up,’ said Harry, looking at the ragged old bit of parchment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, are we?’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took out his wand, touched the parchment lightly and said, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I solemnly swear that I am up to no good. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And at once, thin ink lines began to spread like a spider’s web from the point that George’s wand had touched. They joined each other, they criss-crossed, they fanned into every corner of the parchment; then words began to blossom across the top, great, curly green words, that proclaimed: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>144 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Messrs Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Purveyors of Aids to Magical Mischief-Makers</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">are proud to present </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">THE MARAUDER’S MAP </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a map showing every detail of the Hogwarts castle and grounds. But the truly remarkable thing was the tiny ink dots moving around it, each labelled with a name in minuscule writing. Astounded, Harry bent over it. A labelled dot in the top left corner showed that Professor Dumbledore was pacing his study; the caretaker’s cat, Mrs Norris, was prowling the second floor, and Peeves the poltergeist was currently bouncing around the trophy room. And as Harry’s eyes travelled up and down the familiar corridors, he noticed something else. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This map showed a set of passages he had never entered. And many of them seemed to lead – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right into Hogsmeade,’ said Fred, tracing one of them with his finger. ‘There are seven in all. Now, Filch knows about these four </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">–’ he pointed them out, ‘– but we’re sure we’re the only ones who know about  <i class=\"calibre4\">these</i>. Don’t bother with the one behind the mirror on the fourth floor. We used it until last winter, but it’s caved in – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">completely blocked. And we don’t reckon anyone’s ever used this one, because the Whomping Willow’s planted right over the entrance. But this one here, this one leads right into the cellar of Honeydukes. We’ve used it loads of times. And as you might’ve noticed, the entrance is right outside this room, through that one-eyed old crone’s hump.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs,’ sighed George, patting the heading of the map. ‘We owe them so much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Noble men, working tirelessly to help a new generation of law-breakers,’ said Fred solemnly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said George briskly, ‘don’t forget to wipe it after you’ve used it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– or anyone can read it,’ Fred said warningly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just tap it again and say, “Mischief managed!” And it’ll go blank.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, young Harry,’ said Fred, in an uncanny impersonation of Percy, ‘mind you behave yourself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you in Honeydukes,’ said George, winking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They left the room, both smirking in a satisfied sort of way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 145 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood there, gazing at the miraculous map. He watched the tiny ink Mrs Norris turn left and pause to sniff at something on the floor. If Filch really didn’t know … he wouldn’t have to pass the Dementors at all … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But even as he stood there, flooded with excitement, something Harry had once heard Mr Weasley say came floating out of his memory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Never trust anything that can think for itself, if you can’t see where</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">it keeps its brain. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This map was one of those dangerous magical objects Mr Weasley had been warning against …  <i class=\"calibre4\">Aids to Magical Mischief-Makers  </i>… but then, Harry reasoned, he only wanted to use it to get  into  Hogsmeade,  it  wasn’t  as  though  he  wanted  to  steal  anything or attack anyone … and Fred and George had been using it for years without anything horrible happening … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry traced the secret passage to Honeydukes with his finger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, quite suddenly, as though following orders, he rolled up the map, stuffed it inside his robes, and hurried to the door of the classroom. He opened it a couple of inches. There was no one outside. Very carefully, he edged out of the room and slipped behind the statue of the one-eyed witch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What did he have to do? He pulled out the map again and saw, to his astonishment, that a new ink figure had appeared upon it, labelled ‘Harry Potter’. This figure was standing exactly where the real Harry was standing, about halfway down the third-floor corridor. Harry watched carefully. His little ink self appeared to be tapping the witch with his minute wand. Harry quickly took out his real wand and tapped the statue. Nothing happened. He looked back at the map. The tiniest speech bubble had appeared next to his figure. The word inside said ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dissendium</i>’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dissendium! </i>’ Harry whispered, tapping the stone witch again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At once, the statue’s hump opened wide enough to admit a fairly thin person. Harry glanced quickly up and down the corridor, then tucked the map away again, hoisted himself into the hole headfirst, and pushed himself forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He slid a considerable way down what felt like a stone slide, then landed on cold, damp earth. He stood up, looking around. It was pitch dark. He held up his wand, muttered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos! </i>’ and saw that he was in a very narrow, low, earthy passageway. He raised the map, tapped it with the tip of his wand and muttered, ‘Mischief </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>146 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">managed!’ The map went blank at once. He folded it carefully, tucked it inside his robes, then, heart beating fast, both excited and apprehensive, he set off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The passage twisted and turned, more like the burrow of a giant rabbit than anything else. Harry hurried along it, stumbling now and then on the uneven floor, holding his wand out in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took ages, but Harry had the thought of Honeydukes to sus-tain him. After what felt like an hour, the passage began to rise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Panting, Harry sped up, his face hot, his feet very cold. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ten  minutes  later,  he  came  to  the  foot  of  some  worn  stone steps which rose out of sight above him. Careful not to make any noise, Harry began to climb. A hundred steps, two hundred steps, he lost count as he climbed, watching his feet … then, without warning, his head hit something hard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It seemed to be a trapdoor. Harry stood there, massaging the top of his head, listening. He couldn’t hear any sounds above him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Very slowly, he pushed the trapdoor open and peered over the edge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was in a cellar which was full of wooden crates and boxes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry climbed out of the trapdoor and replaced it – it blended so perfectly with the dusty floor that it was impossible to tell it was there. Harry crept slowly towards the wooden staircase that led upstairs. Now he could definitely hear voices, not to mention the tinkle of a bell and the opening and shutting of a door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wondering what he ought to do, he suddenly heard a door open much closer at hand; somebody was about to come downstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And get another box of Jelly Slugs, dear, they’ve nearly cleaned us out –’ said a woman’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A pair of feet was coming down the staircase. Harry leapt behind an enormous crate and waited for the footsteps to pass. He heard the man shifting boxes against the wall opposite. He might not get another chance – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quickly and silently, Harry dodged out from his hiding place and climbed the stairs; looking back, he saw an enormous back-side and a shiny bald head buried in a box. Harry reached the door at the top of the stairs, slipped through it, and found himself behind the counter of Honeydukes – he ducked, crept sideways and then straightened up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 147 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Honeydukes was so crowded with Hogwarts students that no one looked twice at Harry. He edged amongst them, looking around, and suppressed a laugh as he imagined the look that would spread over Dudley’s piggy face if he could see where Harry was now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There were shelves upon shelves of the most succulent-looking sweets imaginable. Creamy chunks of nougat, shimmering pink squares of coconut ice, fat, honey-coloured toffees; hundreds of different kinds of chocolate in neat rows; there was a large barrel of Every Flavour Beans, and another of Fizzing Whizzbees, the levitating sherbet balls that Ron had mentioned; along yet another wall were ‘Special Effects’ sweets: Drooble’s Best Blowing Gum (which filled a room with bluebell-coloured bubbles that refused to pop for days), the strange, splintery Toothflossing Stringmints, tiny black Pepper Imps (‘breathe fire for your friends!’), Ice Mice (‘hear your teeth chatter and squeak!’), peppermint creams shaped like toads (‘hop realistically in the stomach!’), fragile sugar-spun quills and exploding bonbons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry squeezed himself through a crowd of sixth-years and saw a sign hanging in the furthest corner of the shop (‘Unusual Tastes’). </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione were standing underneath it, examining a tray of blood-flavoured lollipops. Harry sneaked up behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Urgh, no, Harry won’t want one of those, they’re for vampires, I expect,’ Hermione was saying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How about these?’ said Ron, shoving a jar of Cockroach Cluster under Hermione’s nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Definitely not,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron nearly dropped the jar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry! </i>’ squealed Hermione. ‘What are you doing here? How – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">how did you –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wow!’ said Ron, looking very impressed. ‘You’ve learnt to Apparate!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Course I haven’t,’ said Harry. He dropped his voice so that none of the sixth-years could hear him and told them all about the Marauder’s Map. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How come Fred and George never gave it to  <i class=\"calibre4\">me! </i>’ said Ron, outraged. ‘I’m their brother!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Harry isn’t going to keep it!’ said Hermione, as though the idea was ludicrous. ‘He’s going to hand it in to Professor McGonagall, aren’t you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>148 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I’m not!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you mad?’ said Ron, goggling at Hermione. ‘Hand in something that good?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I hand it in, I’ll have to say where I got it! Filch would know Fred and George nicked it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what about Sirius Black?’ Hermione hissed. ‘He could be using one of the passages on that map to get into the castle! The teachers have got to know!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He can’t be getting in through a passage,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There are seven secret tunnels on the map, right? Fred and George reckon Filch already knows about four of them. And the other three – one of them’s caved in, so no one can get through it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One of them’s got the Whomping Willow planted over the entrance, so you can’t get out of it. And the one I just came through – well – it’s really hard to see the entrance to it down in the cellar – so unless he knew it was there –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hesitated. What if Black did know the passage was there? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, however, cleared his throat significantly, and pointed to a notice pasted on the inside of the sweetshop door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">BY ORDER OF THE MINISTRY OF MAGIC </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Customers are reminded that until further notice, Dementors</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">will be patrolling the streets of Hogsmeade every night after</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">sundown. This measure has been put in place for the safety of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hogsmeade residents and will be lifted upon the recapture of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Sirius Black. It is therefore advisable that you complete your</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">shopping well before nightfall. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Merry Christmas! </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ said Ron quietly. ‘I’d like to see Black try and break into Honeydukes with Dementors swarming all over the village. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Anyway, Hermione, the Honeydukes owners would hear a breakin, wouldn’t they? They live over the shop!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, but – but –’ Hermione seemed to be struggling to find another problem. ‘Look, Harry still shouldn’t be coming into Hogsmeade, he hasn’t got a signed form! If anyone finds out, he’ll be in so much trouble! And it’s not nightfall yet – what if Sirius Black turns up today? Now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’d have a job spotting Harry in this,’ said Ron, nodding through the mullioned windows at the thick, swirling snow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 149 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Hermione, it’s Christmas, Harry deserves a break.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione bit her lip, looking extremely worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you going to report me?’ Harry asked her, grinning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – of course not – but honestly, Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seen the Fizzing Whizzbees, Harry?’ said Ron, grabbing him and leading him over to their barrel. ‘And the Jelly Slugs? And the Acid Pops? Fred gave me one of those when I was seven – it burnt a hole right through my tongue. I remember Mum walloping him with her broomstick.’ Ron stared broodingly into the Acid Pop box. ‘Reckon Fred’d take a bit of Cockroach Cluster if I told him they were peanuts?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Ron and Hermione had paid for all their sweets, the three of them left Honeydukes for the blizzard outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hogsmeade looked like a Christmas card; the little thatched cottages and shops were all covered in a layer of crisp snow; there were holly wreaths on the doors and strings of enchanted candles hanging in the trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shivered; unlike the other two, he didn’t have his cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They headed up the street, heads bowed against the wind, Ron and Hermione shouting through their scarves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s the Post Office –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Zonko’s is up there –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We could go up to the Shrieking Shack –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tell you what,’ said Ron, his teeth chattering, ‘shall we go for a Butterbeer in the Three Broomsticks?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was more than willing; the wind was fierce and his hands were freezing, so they crossed the road, and in a few minutes were entering the tiny inn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was extremely crowded, noisy, warm and smoky. A curvy sort of woman with a pretty face was serving a bunch of rowdy warlocks up at the bar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s Madam Rosmerta,’ said Ron. ‘I’ll get the drinks, shall I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he added, going slightly red. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione made their way to the back of the room, where there was a small, vacant table between the window and a handsome Christmas tree which stood next to the fireplace. Ron came back five minutes later, carrying three foaming tankards of hot Butterbeer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Happy Christmas!’ he said happily, raising his tankard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry drank deeply. It was the most delicious thing he’d ever </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>150 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">tasted and seemed to heat every bit of him from the inside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A sudden breeze ruffled his hair. The door of the Three Broomsticks had opened again. Harry looked over the rim of his tankard and choked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professors McGonagall and Flitwick had just entered the pub in a flurry of snowflakes, shortly followed by Hagrid, who was deep in conversation with a portly man in a lime-green bowler hat and a pinstriped cloak: Cornelius Fudge, Minister for Magic. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In an instant, Ron and Hermione had both placed hands on the top of Harry’s head and forced him off his stool and under the table. Dripping with Butterbeer and crouching out of sight, Harry clutched his empty tankard and watched the teachers’ and Fudge’s feet move towards the bar, pause, then turn and walk right towards him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Somewhere above him, Hermione whispered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mobiliarbus! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Christmas tree beside their table rose a few inches off the ground, drifted sideways and landed with a soft thump right in front of their table, hiding them from view. Staring through the dense lower branches, Harry saw four sets of chair legs move back from the table right beside theirs, then heard the grunts and sighs of the teachers and Minister as they sat down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next he saw another pair of feet, wearing sparkly turquoise high heels, and heard a woman’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A small Gillywater –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mine,’ said Professor McGonagall’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Four pints of mulled mead –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ta, Rosmerta,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A cherry syrup and soda with ice and umbrella –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mmm!’ said Professor Flitwick, smacking his lips. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you’ll be the redcurrant rum, Minister.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Rosmerta, m’dear,’ said Fudge’s voice. ‘Lovely to see you again, I must say. Have one yourself, won’t you? Come and join us …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, thank you very much, Minister.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched the glittering heels march away and back again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His heart was pounding uncomfortably in his throat. Why hadn’t it occurred to him that this was the last weekend of term for the teachers, too? And how long were they going to sit there? He needed time to sneak back into Honeydukes if he wanted to return to school tonight … Hermione’s leg gave a nervous twitch </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 151 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">next to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So, what brings you to this neck of the woods, Minister?’ came Madam Rosmerta’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry saw the lower part of Fudge’s thick body twist in his chair as though he was checking for eavesdroppers. Then he said in a quiet voice, ‘What else, m’dear, but Sirius Black? I daresay you heard what happened up at the school at Hallowe’en?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I did hear a rumour,’ admitted Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you tell the whole pub, Hagrid?’ said Professor McGonagall exasperatedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think Black’s still in the area, Minister?’ whispered Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure of it,’ said Fudge shortly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know that the Dementors have searched my pub twice?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Madam Rosmerta, a slight edge to her voice. ‘Scared all my customers away … it’s very bad for business, Minister.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rosmerta, m’dear, I don’t like them any more than you do,’ said Fudge uncomfortably. ‘Necessary precaution … unfortunate, but there you are … I’ve just met some of them. They’re in a fury against Dumbledore – he won’t let them inside the castle grounds.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I should think not,’ said Professor McGonagall sharply. ‘How are we supposed to teach with those horrors floating around?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hear, hear!’ squeaked tiny Professor Flitwick, whose feet were dangling a foot from the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All the same,’ demurred Fudge, ‘they are here to protect you all from something much worse … we all know what Black’s capable of …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you know, I still have trouble believing it,’ said Madam Rosmerta thoughtfully. ‘Of all the people to go over to the Dark side, Sirius Black was the last I’d have thought … I mean, I remember him when he was a boy at Hogwarts. If you’d told me then what he was going to become, I’d have said you’d had too much mead.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t know the half of it, Rosmerta,’ said Fudge gruffly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The worst he did isn’t widely known.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The worst?’ said Madam Rosmerta, her voice alive with curios-ity. ‘Worse than murdering all those poor people, you mean?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I certainly do,’ said Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t believe that. What could possibly be worse?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You say you remember him at Hogwarts, Rosmerta,’ murmured </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>152 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall. ‘Do you remember who his best friend was?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Naturally,’ said Madam Rosmerta, with a small laugh. ‘Never saw one without the other, did you? The number of times I had them in here – ooh, they used to make me laugh. Quite the double act, Sirius Black and James Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dropped his tankard with a loud clunk. Ron kicked him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Precisely,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Black and Potter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ringleaders of their little gang. Both very bright, of course – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">exceptionally bright, in fact – but I don’t think we’ve ever had such a pair of troublemakers –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I dunno,’ chuckled Hagrid. ‘Fred and George Weasley could give ’em a run fer their money.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d have thought Black and Potter were brothers!’ chimed in Professor Flitwick. ‘Inseparable!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course they were,’ said Fudge. ‘Potter trusted Black beyond all his other friends. Nothing changed when they left school. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black was best man when James married Lily. Then they named him godfather to Harry. Harry has no idea, of course. You can imagine how the idea would torment him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because Black turned out to be in league with You-Know-Who?’ whispered Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Worse even than that, m’dear …’ Fudge dropped his voice and proceeded in a sort of low rumble. ‘Not many people are aware that the Potters knew You-Know-Who was after them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore, who was of course working tirelessly against You-Know-Who, had a number of useful spies. One of them tipped him off, and he alerted James and Lily at once. He advised them to go into hiding. Well, of course, You-Know-Who wasn’t an easy person to hide from. Dumbledore told them that their best chance was the Fidelius Charm.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How does that work?’ said Madam Rosmerta, breathless with interest. Professor Flitwick cleared his throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An immensely complex spell,’ he said squeakily, ‘involving the magical concealment of a secret inside a single, living soul. The information is hidden inside the chosen person, or Secret Keeper, and is henceforth impossible to find – unless, of course, the Secret Keeper chooses to divulge it. As long as the Secret Keeper refused to speak, You-Know-Who could search the village where Lily and James were staying for years and never find them, not even if he </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 153 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">had his nose pressed against their sitting-room window!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So Black was the Potters’ Secret Keeper?’ whispered Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Naturally,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘James Potter told Dumbledore that Black would die rather than tell where they were, that Black was planning to go into hiding himself … and yet, Dumbledore remained worried. I remember him offering to be the Potters’ Secret Keeper himself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He suspected Black?’ gasped Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He was sure that somebody close to the Potters had been keeping You-Know-Who informed of their movements,’ said Professor McGonagall darkly. ‘Indeed, he had suspected for some time that someone on our side had turned traitor and was passing a lot of information to You-Know-Who.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But James Potter insisted on using Black?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He did,’ said Fudge heavily. ‘And then, barely a week after the Fidelius Charm had been performed –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Black betrayed them?’ breathed Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He did indeed. Black was tired of his double-agent role, he was ready to declare his support openly for You-Know-Who, and he seems to have planned this for the moment of the Potters’ death. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But, as we all know, You-Know-Who met his downfall in little Harry Potter. Powers gone, horribly weakened, he fled. And this left Black in a very nasty position indeed. His Master had fallen at the very moment when he, Black, had shown his true colours as a traitor. He had no choice but to run for it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Filthy, stinkin’ turncoat!’ Hagrid said, so loudly that half the bar went quiet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shh!’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I met him!’ growled Hagrid. ‘I musta bin the last ter see him before he killed all them people! It was me what rescued Harry from Lily an’ James’s house after they was killed! Jus’ got him outta the ruins, poor little thing, with a great slash across his forehead, an’ his parents dead … an’ Sirius Black turns up, on that flyin’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">motorbike he used ter ride. Never occurred ter me what he was doin’ there. I didn’ know he’d bin Lily an’ James’s Secret Keeper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Thought he’d jus’ heard the news o’ You-Know-Who’s attack an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">come ter see what he could do. White an’ shakin’, he was. An’ yeh know what I did? I COMFORTED THE MURDERIN’ TRAITOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid roared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>154 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, please!’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Keep your voice down!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How was I ter know he wasn’ upset abou’ Lily an’ James? It was You-Know-Who he cared abou’! An’ then he says, “Give Harry ter me, Hagrid, I’m his godfather, I’ll look after him –” Ha! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I’d had me orders from Dumbledore, an’ I told Black no, Dumbledore said Harry was ter go ter his aunt an’ uncle’s. Black argued, but in the end he gave in. Told me ter take his motorbike ter get Harry there. “I won’ need it any more,” he says. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I shoulda known there was somethin’ fishy goin’ on then. He loved  that  motorbike,  what  was  he  givin’  it  ter  me  for?  Why wouldn’ he need it any more? Fact was, it was too easy ter trace. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore knew he’d bin the Potters’ Secret Keeper. Black knew he was goin’ ter have ter run fer it that night, knew it was a matter o’ hours before the Ministry was after him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">But what if I’d given Harry to him, eh? </i> I bet he’d’ve pitched him off the bike halfway out ter sea. His bes’ friend’s son! But when a wizard goes over ter the dark side, there’s nothin’ and no one that matters to ’em any more …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A long silence followed Hagrid’s story. Then Madam Rosmerta said with some satisfaction, ‘But he didn’t manage to disappear, did he? The Ministry of Magic caught up with him next day!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Alas, if only we had,’ said Fudge bitterly. ‘It was not we who found him. It was little Peter Pettigrew – another of the Potters’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">friends. Maddened by grief, no doubt, and knowing that Black had been the Potters’ Secret Keeper, he went after Black himself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pettigrew … that fat little boy who was always tagging around after them at Hogwarts?’ said Madam Rosmerta. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hero-worshipped Black and Potter,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Never quite in their league, talent-wise. I was often rather sharp with him. You can imagine how I – how I regret that now …’ She sounded as though she had a sudden head cold. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There, now, Minerva,’ said Fudge kindly, ‘Pettigrew died a hero’s death. Eye-witnesses – Muggles, of course, we wiped their memories later – told us how Pettigrew cornered Black. They say he was sobbing. “Lily and James, Sirius! How could you!” And then he went for his wand. Well, of course, Black was quicker. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Blew Pettigrew to smithereens …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall blew her nose and said thickly, ‘Stupid boy … foolish boy … he was always hopeless at duelling … should </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Marauder’s Map 155 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">have left it to the Ministry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I tell yeh, if I’d got ter Black before little Pettigrew did, I wouldn’t’ve messed around with wands – I’d’ve ripped him limb – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">from – limb,’ Hagrid growled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t know what you’re talking about, Hagrid,’ said Fudge sharply. ‘Nobody but trained Hit Wizards from the Magical Law Enforcement Squad would have stood a chance against Black once he was cornered. I was Junior Minister in the Department of Magical Catastrophes at the time, and I was one of the first on the scene after Black murdered all those people. I – I will never forget it. I still dream about it sometimes. A crater in the middle of the street, so deep it had cracked the sewer below. Bodies everywhere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Muggles screaming. And Black standing there laughing, with what was left of Pettigrew in front of him … a heap of blood-stained robes and a few – a few fragments –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge’s voice stopped abruptly. There was the sound of five noses being blown. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there you have it, Rosmerta,’ said Fudge thickly. ‘Black was taken away by twenty members of the Magical Law Enforcement Patrol and Pettigrew received the Order of Merlin, First Class, which I think was some comfort to his poor mother. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s been in Azkaban ever since.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Rosmerta let out a long sigh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is it true he’s mad, Minister?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish I could say that he was,’ said Fudge slowly. ‘I certainly believe his master’s defeat unhinged him for a while. The murder of Pettigrew and all those Muggles was the action of a cornered and desperate man – cruel … pointless. Yet I met Black on my last inspection of Azkaban. You know, most of the prisoners in there sit muttering to themselves in the dark, there’s no sense in them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">but I was shocked at how  <i class=\"calibre4\">normal</i> Black seemed. He spoke quite rationally to me. It was unnerving. You’d have thought he was merely bored – asked if I’d finished with my newspaper, cool as you please, said he missed doing the crossword. Yes, I was astounded at how little effect the Dementors seemed to be having on him – and he was one of the most heavily guarded in the place, you know. Dementors outside his door, day and night.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But  what  do  you  think  he’s  broken  out  to  do?’  said  Madam Rosmerta. ‘Good gracious, Minister, he isn’t trying to rejoin You-Know-Who, is he?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>156 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I daresay that is his – er – eventual plan,’ said Fudge evasively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But we hope to catch Black long before that. I must say, You-Know-Who alone and friendless is one thing … but give him back his most devoted servant, and I shudder to think how quickly he’ll rise again …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a small chink of glass on wood. Someone had set down their glass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, Cornelius, if you’re dining with the Headmaster, we’d better head back up to the castle,’ said Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One by one, the pairs of feet in front of Harry took the weight of their owners once more; hems of cloaks swung into sight and Madam Rosmerta’s glittering heels disappeared behind the bar. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of the Three Broomsticks opened again, there was another flurry of snow, and the teachers disappeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione’s faces appeared under the table. They were both staring at him, lost for words. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER ELEVEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Firebolt </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t have a very clear idea of how he had managed to get back into the Honeydukes cellar, through the tunnel and into the castle once more. All he knew was that the return trip seemed to take no time at all, and that he hardly noticed what he was doing, because his head was still pounding with the conversation he had just heard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Why had nobody ever told him? Dumbledore, Hagrid, Mr Weasley, Cornelius Fudge … why hadn’t anyone ever mentioned the fact that Harry’s parents had died because their best friend had betrayed them? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione watched Harry nervously all through dinner, not daring to talk about what they’d overheard, because Percy was sitting close by them. When they went upstairs to the crowded common room, it was to find Fred and George had set off half-a-dozen Dungbombs in a fit of end-of-term high spirits. Harry, who didn’t want Fred and George asking him whether he’d reached Hogsmeade or not, sneaked quietly up to the empty dormitory, and headed straight for his bedside cabinet. He pushed his books aside and quickly found what he was looking for – the leather-bound photo album Hagrid had given him two years ago, which was full of wizard pictures of his mother and father. He sat down on his bed, drew the hangings around him, and started turning the pages, searching, until … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stopped on a picture of his parents’ wedding day. There was his father waving up at him, beaming, the untidy black hair Harry had inherited standing up in all directions. There was his mother, alight with happiness, arm in arm with his Dad. And there … that must be him. Their best man … Harry had never given him a thought before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If he hadn’t known it was the same person, he would never </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>158 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">have guessed it was Black in this old photograph. His face wasn’t sunken and waxy, but handsome, full of laughter. Had he already been working for Voldemort when this picture had been taken? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Was he already planning the deaths of the two people next to him? Did he realise he was facing twelve years in Azkaban, twelve years which would make him unrecognisable? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">But the Dementors don’t affect him, </i> Harry thought, staring into the handsome, laughing face.  <i class=\"calibre4\">He doesn’t have to hear my Mum</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">screaming if they get too close </i>– </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slammed the album shut, reached over and stuffed it back into his cabinet, took off his robes and glasses and got into bed, making sure the hangings were hiding him from view. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The dormitory door opened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry?’ said Ron’s voice uncertainly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry lay still, pretending to be asleep. He heard Ron leave again, and rolled over on his back, his eyes wide open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A hatred such as he had never known before was coursing through Harry like poison. He could see Black laughing at him through the darkness, as though somebody had pasted the picture from the album over his eyes. He watched, as though somebody was playing him a piece of film, Sirius Black blasting Peter Pettigrew (who resembled Neville Longbottom) into a thousand pieces. He could hear (though he had no idea what Black’s voice might sound like) a low, excited mutter. ‘It has happened, my Lord … the Potters have made me their Secret Keeper …’ And then came another voice, laughing shrilly, the same laugh that Harry heard inside his head whenever the Dementors drew near … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, you – you look terrible.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hadn’t got to sleep until daybreak. He had awoken to find the dormitory deserted, dressed and gone down the spiral staircase to a common room that was completely empty except for Ron, who was eating a Peppermint Toad and massaging his stomach, and Hermione, who had spread her homework over three tables. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is everyone?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gone! It’s the first day of the holidays, remember?’ said Ron, watching Harry closely. ‘It’s nearly lunchtime, I was going to come and wake you up in a minute.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slumped into a chair next to the fire. Snow was still </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 159 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">falling outside the windows. Crookshanks was spread out in front of the fire like a large, ginger rug. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You really don’t look well, you know,’ Hermione said, peering anxiously into his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m fine,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, listen,’ said Hermione, exchanging a look with Ron, ‘you must be really upset about what we heard yesterday. But the thing is, you mustn’t go doing anything stupid.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like what?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Like trying to go after Black,’ said Ron sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could tell they had rehearsed this conversation while he had been asleep. He didn’t say anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You won’t, will you, Harry?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because Black’s not worth dying for,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked at them. They didn’t seem to understand at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you know what I see and hear every time a Dementor gets too near me?’ Ron and Hermione shook their heads, looking apprehensive. ‘I can hear my mum screaming and pleading with Voldemort. And if you’d heard your mum screaming like that, just about to be killed, you wouldn’t forget it in a hurry. And if you found out someone who was supposed to be a friend of hers betrayed her and sent Voldemort after her –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s nothing you can do!’ said Hermione, looking stricken. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Dementors will catch Black and he’ll go back to Azkaban and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– and serve him right!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You heard what Fudge said. Black isn’t affected by Azkaban like normal people are. It’s not a punishment for him like it is for the others.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So what are you saying?’ said Ron, looking very tense. ‘You want to – to kill Black or something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be silly,’ said Hermione in a panicky voice. ‘Harry doesn’t want to kill anyone, do you, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Again, Harry didn’t answer. He didn’t know what he wanted to do. All he knew was that the idea of doing nothing, while Black was at liberty, was almost more than he could stand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy knows,’ he said abruptly. ‘Remember what he said to me in Potions? “If it was me, I’d hunt him down myself … I’d want revenge.” ’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re going to take Malfoy’s advice instead of ours?’ said Ron furiously. ‘Listen … you know what Pettigrew’s mother got back </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>160 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">after Black had finished with him? Dad told me – the Order of Merlin, First Class, and Pettigrew’s finger in a box. That was the biggest bit of him they could find. Black’s a madman, Harry, and he’s dangerous –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy’s dad must have told him,’ said Harry, ignoring Ron. ‘He was right in Voldemort’s inner circle –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Say You-Know-Who, will you? </i>’ interjected Ron angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– so obviously, the Malfoys knew Black was working for Voldemort –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– and Malfoy’d love to see you blown into about a million pieces, like Pettigrew! Get a grip, Malfoy’s just hoping you’ll get yourself killed before he has to play you at Quidditch.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">please</i>,’ said Hermione, her eyes now shining with tears, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">please</i> be sensible. Black did a terrible, terrible thing, but d-don’t put yourself in danger, it’s what Black wants … oh, Harry, you’d be playing right into Black’s hands if you went looking for him. Your mum and dad wouldn’t want you to get hurt, would they? They’d never want you to go looking for Black!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll never know what they’d have wanted because, thanks to Black, I’ve never spoken to them,’ said Harry shortly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a silence, in which Crookshanks stretched luxuri-ously, flexing his claws. Ron’s pocket quivered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look,’ said Ron, obviously casting around for a change of subject, ‘it’s the holidays! It’s nearly Christmas! Let’s – let’s go down and see Hagrid. We haven’t visited him for ages!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Hermione quickly. ‘Harry isn’t supposed to leave the castle, Ron –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, let’s go,’ said Harry, sitting up, ‘and I can ask him how come he never mentioned Black when  he  told  me  all  about  my parents!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Further discussion of Sirius Black plainly wasn’t what Ron had had in mind. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Or we could have a game of chess,’ he said hastily, ‘or Gobstones. Percy left a set –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, let’s visit Hagrid,’ said Harry firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So they got their cloaks from their dormitories and set off through the portrait hole (‘Stand and fight, you yellow-bellied mongrels!’), down through the empty castle and out through the oak front doors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They made their way slowly down the lawn, making a shallow </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 161 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">trench in the glittering, powdery snow, their socks and the hems of their cloaks soaked and freezing. The Forbidden Forest looked as though it had been enchanted, each tree smattered with silver, and Hagrid’s cabin looked like an iced cake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron knocked, but there was no answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not out, is he?’ said Hermione, who was shivering under her cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had his ear to the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s a weird noise,’ he said. ‘Listen – is that Fang?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione put their ears to the door, too. From inside the cabin came a series of low, throbbing moans. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Think we’d better go and get someone?’ said Ron nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid!’ called Harry, thumping the door. ‘Hagrid, are you in there?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a sound of heavy footsteps, then the door creaked open. Hagrid stood there with his eyes red and swollen; tears splashing down the front of his leather waistcoat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’ve heard!’ he bellowed, and he flung himself onto Harry’s neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid being at least twice the size of a normal man, this was no laughing matter. Harry, about to collapse under Hagrid’s weight, was rescued by Ron and Hermione, who each seized Hagrid under an arm and heaved him, Harry helping, back into the cabin. Hagrid allowed himself to be steered into a chair and slumped over the table, sobbing uncontrollably, his face glazed with tears which dripped down into his tangled beard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, what  <i class=\"calibre4\">is</i> it?’ said Hermione, aghast. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry spotted an official-looking letter lying open on the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s this, Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s  sobs  redoubled,  but  he  shoved  the  letter  towards Harry, who picked it up and read aloud: <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Mr Hagrid, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Further to our inquiry into the attack by a Hippogriff on a</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">student in your class, we have accepted the assurances of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Professor Dumbledore that you bear no responsibility for the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">regrettable incident. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, that’s OK, then, Hagrid!’ said Ron, clapping Hagrid on the shoulder. But Hagrid continued to sob, and waved one of his </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>162 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">gigantic hands, inviting Harry to read on. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">However, we must register our concern about the Hippogriff</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">in question. We have decided to uphold the official complaint of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Lucius Malfoy, and this matter will therefore be taken to the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures. The hearing will take place on April 20th, and we ask you to present</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">yourself and your Hippogriff at the Committee’s offices in</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">London on that date. In the meantime, the Hippogriff should be</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">kept tethered and isolated. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Yours in fellowship ... </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There followed a list of the school governors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Ron. ‘But you said Buckbeak isn’t a bad Hippogriff, Hagrid. I bet he’ll get off –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh don’ know them gargoyles at the Committee fer the Disposal o’ Dangerous Creatures!’ choked Hagrid, wiping his eyes on his sleeve. ‘They’ve got it in fer interestin’ creatures!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A sudden sound from the corner of Hagrid’s cabin made Harry, Ron and Hermione whip around. Buckbeak the Hippogriff was lying in the corner, chomping on something that was oozing blood all over the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I couldn’ leave him tied up out there in the snow!’ choked Hagrid. ‘All on his own! At Christmas!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione looked at each other. They had never seen eye to eye with Hagrid about what he called ‘interesting creatures’ and other people called ‘terrifying monsters’. On the other hand, there didn’t seem to be any particular harm in Buckbeak. In fact, by Hagrid’s usual standards, he was positively cute. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ll have to put up a good strong defence, Hagrid,’ said Hermione, sitting down and laying a hand on Hagrid’s massive forearm. ‘I’m sure you can prove Buckbeak is safe.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Won’ make no diff’rence!’ sobbed Hagrid. ‘Them Disposal devils, they’re all in Lucius Malfoy’s pocket! Scared o’ him! An’ if I lose the case, Buckbeak –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid drew his finger swiftly across his throat, then gave a great wail and lurched forwards, his face in his arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about Dumbledore, Hagrid?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s done more’n enough fer me already,’ groaned Hagrid. ‘Got enough on his plate what with keepin’ them Dementors outta the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 163 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">castle, an’ Sirius Black lurkin’ around –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron and Hermione looked quickly at Harry, as though expecting him to start berating Hagrid for not telling him the truth about Black. But Harry couldn’t bring himself to do it, not now he saw Hagrid so miserable and scared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Listen, Hagrid,’ he said, ‘you can’t give up. Hermione’s right, you just need a good defence. You can call us as witnesses –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure I’ve read about a case of Hippogriff-baiting,’ said Hermione thoughtfully, ‘where the Hippogriff got off. I’ll look it up for you, Hagrid, and see exactly what happened.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid howled still more loudly. Harry and Hermione looked at Ron to help them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – shall I make a cup of tea?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s what my mum does whenever someone’s upset,’ Ron muttered, shrugging. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At last, after many more assurances of help, with a steaming mug of tea in front of him, Hagrid blew his nose on a handkerchief the size of a tablecloth and said, ‘Yer right. I can’ afford to go ter pieces. Gotta pull meself together …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fang the boarhound came timidly out from under the table and laid his head on Hagrid’s knee. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve not bin meself lately,’ said Hagrid, stroking Fang with one hand and mopping his face with the other. ‘Worried abou’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak, an’ no one likin’ me classes –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We do like them!’ lied Hermione at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, they’re great!’ said Ron, crossing his fingers under the table. ‘Er – how are the Flobberworms?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dead,’ said Hagrid gloomily. ‘Too much lettuce.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no!’ said Ron, his lip twitching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An’ them Dementors make me feel ruddy terrible an’ all,’ said Hagrid, with a sudden shudder. ‘Gotta walk past ’em ev’ry time I want a drink in the Three Broomsticks. ’S like bein’ back in Azkaban –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He fell silent, gulping his tea. Harry, Ron and Hermione watched him breathlessly. They had never heard Hagrid talk about his brief spell in Azkaban before. After a brief pause, Hermione said timidly, ‘Is it awful in there, Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’ve no idea,’ said Hagrid quietly. ‘Never bin anywhere like it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Thought I was goin’ mad. Kep’ goin’ over horrible stuff in me  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>164 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">mind … the day I got expelled from Hogwarts … day me Dad died </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… day I had ter let Norbert go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His eyes filled with tears. Norbert was the baby dragon Hagrid had once won in a game of cards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh can’ really remember who yeh are after a while. An’ yeh can’ see the point o’ livin’ at all. I used ter hope I’d jus’ die in me sleep … when they let me out, it was like bein’ born again, ev’rythin’ came floodin’ back, it was the bes’ feelin’ in the world. Mind, the Dementors weren’t keen on lettin’ me go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you were innocent!’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid snorted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Think that matters to them? They don’ care. Long as they’ve got a couple o’ hundred humans stuck there with ’em, so they can leech all the happiness out of ’em, they don’ give a damn who’s guilty an’ who’s not.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid went quiet for a moment, staring into his tea. Then he said quietly, ‘Thought o’ jus’ letting Buckbeak go … tryin’ ter make him fly away … but how d’yeh explain ter a Hippogriff it’s gotta go inter hidin’? An’ – an’ I’m scared o’ breakin’ the law …’ He looked up at them, tears leaking down his face again. ‘I don’ ever want ter go back ter Azkaban.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The trip to Hagrid’s, though far from fun, had nevertheless had the effect Ron and Hermione had hoped. Though Harry had by no means forgotten about Black, he couldn’t brood constantly on revenge if he wanted to help Hagrid win his case against the Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures. He, Ron and Hermione went to the library next day, and returned to the empty common room laden with books which might help prepare a defence for Buckbeak. The three of them sat in front of the roaring fire, slowly turning the pages of dusty volumes about famous cases of marauding beasts, speaking occasionally when they ran across something relevant. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here’s something … there was a case in 1722 … but the Hippogriff was convicted – urgh, look what they did to it, that’s disgusting –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This might help, look – a Manticore savaged someone in 1296, and they let the Manticore off – oh – no, that was only because everyone was too scared to go near it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Meanwhile, in the rest of the castle, the usual magnificent </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 165 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Christmas decorations had been put up, despite the fact that hardly any of the students remained to enjoy them. Thick streamers of holly and mistletoe were strung along the corridors, mysterious lights shone from inside every suit of armour and the Great Hall was filled with its usual twelve Christmas trees, glittering with golden stars. A powerful and delicious smell of cooking pervaded the corridors, and by Christmas Eve, it had grown so strong that even Scabbers poked his nose out of the shelter of Ron’s pocket to sniff hopefully at the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Christmas morning, Harry was woken by Ron throwing his pillow at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oy! Presents!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry reached for his glasses and put them on, squinting through the semi-darkness to the foot of his bed, where a small heap of parcels had appeared. Ron was already ripping the paper off his own presents. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Another jumper from Mum … maroon  <i class=\"calibre4\">again </i>… see if you’ve got one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had. Mrs Weasley had sent him a scarlet jumper with the Gryffindor lion knitted on the front, also a dozen home-baked mince pies, some Christmas cake and a box of nut brittle. As he moved all these things aside, he saw a long, thin package lying underneath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said Ron, looking over, a freshly unwrapped pair of maroon socks in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry ripped the parcel open and gasped as a magnificent, gleaming broomstick rolled out onto his bedspread. Ron dropped his socks and jumped off his bed for a closer look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t believe it,’ he said hoarsely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a Firebolt, identical to the dream broom Harry had gone to see every day in Diagon Alley. Its handle glittered as he picked it up. He could feel it vibrating, and let go; it hung in mid-air, unsupported, at exactly the right height for him to mount it. His eyes moved from the golden registration number at the top of the handle right down to the perfectly smooth, streamlined birch twigs that made up the tail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who sent it to you?’ said Ron in a hushed voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look and see if there’s a card,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron ripped apart the Firebolt’s wrappings. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>166 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing! Blimey, who’d spend that much on you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well,’ said Harry, feeling stunned, ‘I’m betting it wasn’t the Dursleys.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I bet it was Dumbledore,’ said Ron, now walking round and round the Firebolt, taking in every glorious inch. ‘He sent you the Invisibility Cloak anonymously …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was my dad’s, though,’ said Harry. ‘Dumbledore was just passing it on to me. He wouldn’t spend hundreds of Galleons on me. He can’t go giving students stuff like this –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s why he wouldn’t say it was from him!’ said Ron. ‘In case some git like Malfoy said it was favouritism. Hey, Harry –’ Ron gave a great whoop of laughter, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Malfoy! </i> Wait ’til he sees you on this! He’ll be sick as a pig! This is an  <i class=\"calibre4\">international</i>-standard broom, this is!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t believe this,’ Harry muttered, running a hand along the Firebolt, while Ron sank onto Harry’s bed, laughing his head off at the thought of Malfoy. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Who </i>–?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ said Ron, controlling himself. ‘I know who it could’ve been – Lupin!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry, now starting to laugh himself. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lupin? </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Listen, if he had this much gold, he’d be able to buy himself some new robes.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, but he likes you,’ said Ron. ‘And he was away when your Nimbus got smashed, and he might’ve heard about it and decided to visit Diagon Alley and get this for you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean, he was away?’ said Harry. ‘He was ill when I was playing in that match.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, he wasn’t in the hospital wing,’  said  Ron.  ‘I  was  there, cleaning out the bedpans on that detention from Snape, remember?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry frowned at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t see Lupin affording something like this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re you two laughing about?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had just come in, wearing her dressing-gown and carrying Crookshanks, who was looking very grumpy, with a string of tinsel tied around his neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t bring him in here!’ said Ron, hurriedly snatching Scabbers from the depths of his bed and stowing him in his pyjama pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione wasn’t listening. She dropped Crookshanks onto Seamus’s empty bed and stared, open-mouthed, at the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 167 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry! </i> Who sent you  <i class=\"calibre4\">that? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No idea,’ said Harry. ‘There wasn’t a card or anything with it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To his great surprise, Hermione did not appear either excited or intrigued by this news. On the contrary, her face fell, and she bit her lip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter with you?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know,’ said Hermione slowly, ‘but it’s a bit odd, isn’t it? I mean, this is supposed to be quite a good broom, isn’t it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron sighed exasperatedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the best broom there is, Hermione,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So it must’ve been really expensive …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably cost more than all the Slytherins’ brooms put together,’ said Ron happily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … who’d send Harry something as expensive as that, and not even tell him they’d sent it?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who cares?’ said Ron, impatiently. ‘Listen, Harry, can I have a go on it? Can I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t think anyone should ride that broom just yet!’ said Hermione shrilly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you think Harry’s going to do with it – sweep the floor?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But before Hermione could answer, Crookshanks sprang from Seamus’s bed, right at Ron’s chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GET – HIM – OUT – OF – HERE!’ Ron bellowed, as Crookshanks’s claws ripped his pyjamas and Scabbers attempted a wild escape over his shoulder. Ron seized Scabbers by the tail and aimed a misjudged kick at Crookshanks which hit the trunk at the end of Harry’s bed, knocking it over and causing Ron to hop on the spot, howling with pain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks’s fur suddenly stood on end. A shrill, tinny whistling was filling the room. The Pocket Sneakoscope had become dislodged from Uncle Vernon’s old socks and was whirling and gleaming on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I forgot about that!’ Harry said, bending down and picking up the Sneakoscope. ‘I never wear those socks if I can help it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Sneakoscope whirled and whistled in his palm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks was hissing and spitting at it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’d better take that cat out of here, Hermione,’ said Ron furiously; he was sitting on Harry’s bed nursing his toe. ‘Can’t you </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>168 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">shut that thing up?’ he added to Harry, as Hermione strode out of the room, Crookshanks’s yellow eyes still fixed maliciously on Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stuffed the Sneakoscope back inside the socks and threw it back into his trunk. All that could be heard now was Ron’s stifled moans of pain and rage. Scabbers was huddled in Ron’s hands. It had been a while since Harry had seen him out of Ron’s pocket, and he was unpleasantly surprised to see that Scabbers, once so fat, was now very skinny; patches of fur seemed to have fallen out, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not looking too good, is he?’ Harry said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s stress!’ said Ron. ‘He’d be fine if that stupid great furball left him alone!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry, remembering what the woman at the Magical Menagerie had said about rats only living three years, couldn’t help feeling that unless Scabbers had powers he had never revealed, he was reaching the end of his life. And despite Ron’s frequent complaints that Scabbers was both boring and useless, he was sure Ron would be very miserable if Scabbers died. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Christmas spirit was definitely thin on the ground in the Gryffindor common room that morning. Hermione had shut Crookshanks in her dormitory, but was furious with Ron for trying to kick him; Ron was still fuming about Crookshanks’s fresh attempt to eat Scabbers. Harry gave up trying to make them talk to each other, and devoted himself to examining the Firebolt, which he had brought down to the common room with him. For some  reason  this  seemed  to  annoy  Hermione  as  well;  she  didn’t say anything, but she kept looking darkly at the broom as though it, too, had been criticising her cat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At lunchtime they went down to the Great Hall, to find that the house tables had been moved against the walls again, and that a single table, set for twelve, stood in the middle of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professors Dumbledore, McGonagall, Snape, Sprout and Flitwick were there, along with Filch, the caretaker, who had taken off his usual brown coat and was wearing a very old and rather mouldy-looking tail coat. There were only three other students: two extremely nervous-looking first-years and a sullen-faced Slytherin fifth-year. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Merry Christmas!’ said Dumbledore, as Harry, Ron and Hermione approached the table. ‘As there are so few of us, it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 169 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">seemed foolish to use the house tables … sit down, sit down!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione sat down side by side at the end of the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crackers!’ said Dumbledore enthusiastically, offering the end of a large silver one to Snape, who took it reluctantly and tugged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a bang like a gunshot, the cracker flew apart to reveal a large, pointed witch’s hat topped with a stuffed vulture. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, remembering the Boggart, caught Ron’s eye and they both grinned; Snape’s mouth thinned and he pushed the hat towards Dumbledore, who swapped it for his wizard’s hat at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tuck in!’ he advised the table, beaming around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Harry was helping himself to roast potatoes, the doors of the Great Hall opened again. It was Professor Trelawney, gliding towards them as though on wheels. She had put on a green sequined dress in honour of the occasion, making her look more than ever like a glittering, oversize dragonfly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sybill, this is a pleasant surprise!’ said Dumbledore, standing up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have been crystal-gazing, Headmaster,’ said Professor Trelawney, in her mistiest, most faraway voice, ‘and to my Astonishment, I saw myself abandoning my solitary luncheon and coming to join you. Who am I to refuse the promptings of fate? I at once hastened from my tower, and I do beg you to forgive my lateness …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly, certainly,’ said Dumbledore, his eyes twinkling. ‘Let me draw you up a chair –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he did indeed draw a chair in mid-air with his wand, which revolved for a few seconds before falling with a thud between Professors Snape and McGonagall. Professor Trelawney, however, did not sit down; her enormous eyes had been roving around the table, and she suddenly uttered a kind of soft scream. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I dare not, Headmaster! If I join the table, we shall be thirteen! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nothing could be more unlucky! Never forget that when thirteen dine together, the first to rise will be the first to die!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll risk it, Sybill,’ said Professor McGonagall impatiently. ‘Do sit down, the turkey’s getting stone cold.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney hesitated, then lowered herself into the empty chair, eyes shut and mouth clenched tight, as though expecting a thunderbolt to hit the table. Professor McGonagall poked a large spoon into the nearest tureen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>170 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tripe, Sybill?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney ignored her. Eyes open again, she looked around once more and said, ‘But where is dear Professor Lupin?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m afraid the poor fellow is ill again,’ said Dumbledore, indicating that everybody should start serving themselves. ‘Most unfortunate that it should happen on Christmas Day.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But surely you already knew that, Sybill?’ said Professor McGonagall, her eyebrows raised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney gave Professor McGonagall a very cold look. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly I knew, Minerva,’ she said quietly. ‘But one does not parade the fact that one is All-Knowing. I frequently act as though I am not possessed of the Inner Eye, so as not to make others nervous.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That explains a great deal,’ said Professor McGonagall tartly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s voice suddenly became a good deal less misty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you must know, Minerva, I have seen that poor Professor Lupin will not be with us for very long. He seems aware, himself, that his time is short. He positively fled when I offered to crystal-gaze for him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Imagine that,’ said Professor McGonagall drily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I doubt,’ said Dumbledore, in a cheerful but slightly raised voice, which put an end to Professor McGonagall and Professor Trelawney’s conversation, ‘that Professor Lupin is in any immediate danger. Severus, you’ve made the Potion for him again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, Headmaster,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good,’ said Dumbledore. ‘Then he should be up and about in no time … Derek, have you had any of these chipolatas? They’re excellent.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The first-year boy went furiously red on being addressed directly by Dumbledore, and took the platter of sausages with trembling hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney behaved almost normally until the very end of Christmas dinner, two hours later. Full to bursting with Christmas dinner and still wearing their cracker hats, Harry and Ron got up first from the table and she shrieked loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dears! Which of you left his seat first? Which?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dunno,’ said Ron, looking uneasily at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I doubt it will make much difference,’ said Professor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Firebolt 171 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">McGonagall coldly, ‘unless a mad axe-man is waiting outside the doors to slaughter the first into the Entrance Hall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Even Ron laughed. Professor Trelawney looked highly affronted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Coming?’ Harry said to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ Hermione muttered. ‘I want a quick word with Professor McGonagall.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Probably trying to see if she can take any more classes,’ yawned Ron as they made their way into the Entrance Hall, which was completely devoid of mad axe-men. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When they reached the portrait hole they found Sir Cadogan enjoying a Christmas party with a couple of monks, several previous Headmasters of Hogwarts and his fat pony. He pushed up his visor and toasted them with a flagon of mead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Merry – hic – Christmas! Password?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scurvy cur,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the same to you, sir!’ roared Sir Cadogan, as the painting swung forward to admit them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went straight up to the dormitory, collected his Firebolt and the Broomstick Servicing Kit Hermione had given him for his birthday, brought them downstairs and tried to find something to do to the Firebolt; however, there were no bent twigs to clip, and the handle was so shiny already it seemed pointless to polish it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He and Ron simply sat admiring it from every angle, until the portrait hole opened, and Hermione came in, accompanied by Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Though Professor McGonagall was Head of Gryffindor house, Harry had only seen her in the common room once before, and that had been to make a very grave announcement. He and Ron stared at her, both holding the Firebolt. Hermione walked around them, sat down, picked up the nearest book and hid her face behind it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So that’s it, is it?’ said Professor McGonagall beadily, walking over to the fireside and staring at the Firebolt. ‘Miss Granger has just informed me that you have been sent a broomstick, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron looked around at Hermione. They could see her forehead reddening over the top of her book, which was upside-down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘May I?’ said Professor McGonagall, but she didn’t wait for an answer before pulling the Firebolt out of their hands. She examined it carefully from handle to twig-ends. ‘Hmm. And there was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>172 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">no note at all, Potter? No card? No message of any kind?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry blankly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see …’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Well, I’m afraid I will have to take this, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘W-what?’ said Harry, scrambling to his feet. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It will need to be checked for jinxes,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘Of course, I’m no expert, but I daresay Madam Hooch and Professor Flitwick will strip it down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Strip it down?’ repeated Ron, as though Professor McGonagall was mad. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It shouldn’t take more than a few weeks,’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘You will have it back if we are sure it is jinx-free.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s nothing wrong with it!’ said Harry, his voice shaking slightly. ‘Honestly, Professor –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You can’t know that, Potter,’ said Professor McGonagall, quite kindly, ‘not until you’ve flown it, at any rate, and I’m afraid that is out of the question until we are certain that it has not been tam-pered with. I shall keep you informed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall turned on her heel and carried the Firebolt out of the portrait hole, which closed behind her. Harry stood staring after her, the tin of High-Finish Polish still clutched in his hands. Ron, however, rounded on Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What did you go running to McGonagall for? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione threw her book aside. She was still pink in the face, but stood up and faced Ron defiantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because I thought – and Professor McGonagall agrees with me </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– that that broom was probably sent to Harry by Sirius Black!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWELVE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Patronus </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry knew that Hermione had meant well, but that didn’t stop him being angry with her. He had been the owner of the best broom in the world for a few short hours, and now, because of her interference, he didn’t know whether he would ever see it again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was positive that there was nothing wrong with the Firebolt now, but what sort of state would it be in once it had been subjected to all sorts of anti-jinx tests? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was furious with Hermione, too. As far as he was concerned, the stripping-down of a brand-new Firebolt was nothing less than criminal damage. Hermione, who remained convinced that she had acted for the best, started avoiding the common room. Harry and Ron supposed she had taken refuge in the library, and didn’t try and persuade her to come back. All in all, they were glad when the rest of the school returned shortly after New Year, and Gryffindor Tower became crowded and noisy again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood sought Harry out on the night before term started. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Had a good Christmas?’ he said, and then, without waiting for an answer, he sat down, lowered his voice and said, ‘I’ve been doing some thinking over Christmas, Harry. After the last match, you know. If the Dementors come to the next one … I mean … we can’t afford you to – well –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood broke off, looking awkward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m working on it,’ said Harry quickly. ‘Professor Lupin said he’d train me to ward the Dementors off. We should be starting this week; he said he’d have time after Christmas.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah,’ said Wood, his expression clearing. ‘Well, in that case – I really didn’t want to lose you as Seeker, Harry. And have you ordered a new broom yet?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>174 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What! You’d better get a move on, you know – you can’t ride that Shooting Star against Ravenclaw!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He got a Firebolt for Christmas,’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A  <i class=\"calibre4\">Firebolt? </i> No! Seriously? A – a real  <i class=\"calibre4\">Firebolt? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t get excited, Oliver,’ said Harry gloomily. ‘I haven’t got it any more. It was confiscated.’ And he explained all about how the Firebolt was now being checked for jinxes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jinxed? How could it be jinxed?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius Black,’ Harry said wearily. ‘He’s supposed to be after me. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So McGonagall reckons he might have sent it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Waving aside the information that a famous murderer was after his Seeker, Wood said, ‘But Black couldn’t have bought a Firebolt! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’s on the run! The whole country’s on the lookout for him! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How could he just walk into Quality Quidditch Supplies and buy a broomstick?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ said Harry, ‘but McGonagall still wants to strip it down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood went pale. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll go and talk to her, Harry,’ he promised. ‘I’ll make her see reason … a Firebolt … a real Firebolt, on our team … she wants Gryffindor to win as much as we do … I’ll make her see sense … a <i class=\"calibre4\">Firebolt </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lessons started again next day. The last thing anyone felt like doing was spending two hours in the grounds on a raw January morning, but Hagrid had provided a bonfire full of salamanders for their enjoyment, and they spent an unusually good lesson collecting dry wood and leaves to keep the fire blazing, while the flame-loving lizards scampered up and down the crumbling, white-hot logs. The first Divination lesson of the new term was much less fun; Professor Trelawney was now teaching them palmistry, and she lost no time in informing Harry that he had the shortest life-lines she had ever seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Defence Against the Dark Arts that Harry was keen to get to; after his conversation with Wood, he wanted to get started on his Anti-Dementor lessons as soon as possible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah yes,’ said Lupin, when Harry reminded him of his promise at the end of class. ‘Let me see … how about eight o’clock on Thursday evening? The History of Magic classroom should be large enough … I’ll have to think carefully about how we’re going </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 175 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">to do this … we can’t bring a real Dementor into the castle to practise on …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Still looks ill, doesn’t he?’ said Ron, as they walked down the corridor, heading to dinner. ‘What d’you reckon’s the matter with him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud and impatient ‘tuh’ from behind them. It was Hermione, who had been sitting at the feet of a suit of armour, re-packing her bag, which was so full of books it wouldn’t close. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what are you tutting at us for?’ said Ron irritably. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ said Hermione in a lofty voice, heaving her bag back over her shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, you were,’ said Ron. ‘I said I wonder what’s wrong with Lupin, and you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, isn’t it  <i class=\"calibre4\">obvious? </i>’ said Hermione, with a look of madden-ing superiority. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you don’t want to tell us, don’t,’ snapped Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine,’ said Hermione haughtily, and she marched off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She doesn’t know,’ said Ron, staring resentfully after Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000002999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s just trying to get us to talk to her again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At eight o’clock on Thursday evening, Harry left Gryffindor Tower for the History of Magic classroom. It was dark and empty when he arrived, but he lit the lamps with his wand and had waited only five minutes when Professor Lupin turned up, carrying a large packing case, which he heaved onto Professor Binns’ desk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Another Boggart,’ said Lupin, stripping off his cloak. ‘I’ve been combing the castle ever since Tuesday, and very luckily, I found this one lurking inside Mr Filch’s filing cabinet. It’s the nearest we’ll get to a real Dementor. The Boggart will turn into a Dementor when he sees you, so we’ll be able to practise on him. I can store him in my office when we’re not using him; there’s a cupboard under my desk he’ll like.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Harry, trying to sound as though he wasn’t apprehensive at all and merely glad that Lupin had found such a good sub-stitute for a real Dementor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So …’ Professor Lupin had taken out his own wand, and indicated that Harry should do the same. ‘The spell I am going to try and teach you is highly advanced magic, Harry – well beyond Ordinary Wizarding Level. It is called the Patronus Charm.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>176 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How does it work?’ said Harry nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, when it works correctly, it conjures up a Patronus,’ said Lupin, ‘which is a kind of Anti-Dementor – a guardian which acts as a shield between you and the Dementor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had a sudden vision of himself crouching behind a Hagrid-sized figure holding a large club. Professor Lupin continued, ‘The Patronus is a kind of positive force, a projection of the very things that the Dementor feeds upon – hope, happiness, the desire to survive – but it cannot feel despair, as real humans can, so the Dementors can’t hurt it. But I must warn you, Harry, that the Charm might be too advanced for you. Many qualified wizards have difficulty with it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does a Patronus look like?’ said Harry curiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Each one is unique to the wizard who conjures it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And how do you conjure it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘With an incantation, which will work only if you are concentrating, with all your might, on a single, very happy memory.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry cast about for a happy memory. Certainly, nothing that had happened to him at the Dursleys’ was going to do. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Finally, he settled on the moment when he had first ridden a broomstick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ he said, trying to recall as exactly as possible the wonderful, soaring sensation in his stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The incantation is this –’ Lupin cleared his throat, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">patronum! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expecto patronum, </i>’ Harry repeated under his breath, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">patronum. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Concentrating hard on your happy memory?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – yeah –’ said Harry, quickly forcing his thoughts back to that first broom-ride. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expecto patrono</i> – no,  <i class=\"calibre4\">patronum  </i>– sorry – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto patronum</i>,  <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto patronum</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something whooshed suddenly out of the end of his wand; it looked like a wisp of silvery gas. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see that?’ said Harry excitedly. ‘Something happened!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very good,’ said Lupin, smiling. ‘Right then – ready to try it on a Dementor?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ Harry said, gripping his wand very tightly, and moving into the middle of the deserted classroom. He tried to keep his mind on flying, but something else kept intruding … any second now, he might hear his mother again … but he shouldn’t think </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 177 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">that, or he  <i class=\"calibre4\">would </i> hear her again, and he didn’t want to … or did he? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin grasped the lid of the packing case and pulled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A Dementor rose slowly from the box, its hooded face turned towards Harry, one glistening, scabbed hand gripping its cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The lamps around the classroom flickered and went out. The Dementor stepped from the box and started to sweep silently towards Harry, drawing a deep, rattling breath. A wave of piercing cold broke over him – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expecto patronum! </i>’ Harry yelled. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expecto patronum! Expecto</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the classroom and the Dementor were dissolving … Harry was falling again through thick white fog, and his mother’s voice was louder than ever, echoing inside his head – ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Not Harry! Not</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry! Please – I’ll do anything</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Stand aside – stand aside, girl</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jerked back to life. He was lying flat on his back on the floor. The classroom lamps were alight again. He didn’t have to ask what had happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry,’ he muttered, sitting up and feeling cold sweat trickling down behind his glasses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you all right?’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes …’ Harry pulled himself up on one of the desks and leant against it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here –’ Lupin handed him a Chocolate Frog. ‘Eat this before we try again. I didn’t expect you to do it first time. In fact, I would have been astounded if you had.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s getting worse,’ Harry muttered, biting the Frog’s head off. ‘I could hear her louder that time – and him – Voldemort –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin looked paler than usual. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, if you don’t want to continue, I will more than understand –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I do!’ said Harry fiercely, stuffing the rest of the Chocolate Frog into his mouth. ‘I’ve got to! What if the Dementors turn up at our match against Ravenclaw? I can’t afford to fall off again. If we lose this game we’ve lost the Quidditch Cup!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right then …’ said Lupin. ‘You might want to select another memory, a happy memory, I mean, to concentrate on … that one doesn’t seem to have been strong enough …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought hard, and decided his feelings when Gryffindor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>178 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">had won the House Championship last year had definitely qualified as very happy. He gripped his wand tightly again, and took up his position in the middle of the classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ said Lupin, gripping the box lid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready,’ said Harry, trying hard to fill his head with happy thoughts about Gryffindor winning, and not dark thoughts about what was going to happen when the box opened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go!’ said Lupin, pulling off the lid. The room went icily cold and dark once more. The Dementor glided forwards, drawing its rattly breath; one rotting hand was extending towards Harry – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Expecto patronum!’ Harry yelled. ‘Expecto patronum! Expecto pat–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">White fog obscured his senses … big, blurred shapes were moving around him … then came a new voice, a man’s voice, shouting, panicking – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lily, take Harry and go! It’s him! Go! Run! I’ll hold him off</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The sounds of someone stumbling from a room – a door bursting</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">open – a cackle of high-pitched laughter –</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! Harry … wake up …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin  was  tapping  Harry  hard  on  the  face.  This  time  it  was  a minute before Harry understood why he was lying on a dusty classroom floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I heard my dad,’ Harry mumbled. ‘That’s the first time I’ve ever heard him – he tried to take on Voldemort himself, to give my mum time to run for it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry suddenly realised that there were tears on his face mingling with the sweat. He bent his face low as possible, wiping them off on his robes, pretending to do up his shoelace, so that Lupin wouldn’t see. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You heard James?’ said Lupin, in a strange voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ Face dry, Harry looked up. ‘Why – you didn’t know my dad, did you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – I did, as a matter of fact,’ said Lupin. ‘We were friends at Hogwarts. Listen, Harry – perhaps we should leave it here for tonight. This charm is ridiculously advanced … I shouldn’t have suggested putting you through this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Harry. He got up again. ‘I’ll have one more go! I’m not thinking of happy enough things, that’s what it is … hang on …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He racked his brains. A really, really happy memory … one that he could turn into a good, strong Patronus … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 179 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moment when he’d first found out he was a wizard, and would be leaving the Dursleys for Hogwarts! If that wasn’t a happy memory, he didn’t know what was … concentrating very hard on how he had felt when he’d realised he’d be leaving Privet Drive, Harry got to his feet and faced the packing case once more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ said Lupin, who looked as though he was doing this against his better judgement. ‘Concentrating hard? All right – go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled off the lid of the case for the third time, and the Dementor rose out of it; the room fell cold and dark – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘EXPECTO PATRONUM!’ Harry bellowed. ‘EXPECTO </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">PATRONUM! EXPECTO PATRONUM!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The screaming inside Harry’s head had started again – except this time, it sounded as though it was coming from a badly tuned radio. Softer and louder and softer again … and he could still see the Dementor … it had halted … and then a huge, silver shadow came bursting out of the end of Harry’s wand, to hover between him and the Dementor, and though Harry’s legs felt like water, he was still on his feet … though for how much longer, he wasn’t sure … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Riddikulus!’ roared Lupin, springing forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud crack, and Harry’s cloudy Patronus vanished along with the Dementor; he sank into a chair, feeling as exhausted as if he’d just run a mile, his legs shaking. Out of the corner of his eye, he saw Professor Lupin forcing the Boggart back into the packing case with his wand; it had turned into a silvery orb again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent!’ Lupin said, striding over to where Harry sat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent, Harry! That was definitely a start!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can we have another go? Just one more go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not now,’ said Lupin firmly. ‘You’ve had enough for one night. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He handed Harry a large bar of Honeydukes’ best chocolate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Eat the lot, or Madam Pomfrey will be after my blood. Same time next week?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Harry. He took a bite of the chocolate and watched Lupin extinguishing the lamps that had rekindled with the disappearance of the Dementor. A thought had just occurred to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin?’ he said. ‘If you knew my dad, you must’ve known Sirius Black as well.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin turned very quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What gives you that idea?’ he said sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>180 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing – I mean, I just knew they were friends at Hogwarts, too …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin’s face relaxed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, I knew him,’ he said shortly. ‘Or I thought I did. You’d better get off, Harry, it’s getting late.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry left the classroom, walked along the corridor and around a corner, then took a detour behind a suit of armour and sank down on its plinth to finish his chocolate, wishing he hadn’t mentioned Black, as Lupin was obviously not keen on the subject. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Harry’s thoughts wandered back to his mother and father … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He felt drained and strangely empty, even though he was so full of chocolate. Terrible though it was to hear his parents’ last moments replayed inside his head, these were the only times Harry had heard their voices since he was a very small child. But he’d never be able to produce a proper Patronus if he half wanted to hear his parents again … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re dead,’ he told himself sternly. ‘They’re dead, and listening to echoes of them won’t bring them back. You’d better get a grip on yourself if you want that Quidditch Cup.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He stood up, crammed the last bit of chocolate into his mouth and headed back to Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ravenclaw played Slytherin a week after the start of term. Slytherin won, though narrowly. According to Wood, this was good news for Gryffindor, who would take second place if they beat Ravenclaw too. He therefore increased the number of team practices to five a week. This meant that with Lupin’s Anti-Dementor classes, which in themselves were more draining than six Quidditch practices, Harry had just one night a week to do all his homework. Even so, he wasn’t showing the strain nearly as much as Hermione, whose immense workload finally seemed to be getting to her. Every night, without fail, Hermione was to be seen in a corner of the common room, several tables spread with books, Arithmancy charts, Rune dictionaries, diagrams of Muggles lifting heavy objects, and file upon file of extensive notes; she barely spoke to anybody, and snapped when she was interrupted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s she doing it?’ Ron muttered to Harry one evening, as Harry sat finishing a nasty essay on Undetectable Poisons for Snape. Harry looked up. Hermione was barely visible behind a tottering pile of books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 181 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Doing what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Getting to all her classes!’ Ron said. ‘I heard her talking to Professor Vector, that Arithmancy witch, this morning. They were going on about yesterday’s lesson, but Hermione can’t’ve been there, because she was with us in Care of Magical Creatures! And Ernie McMillan told me she’s never missed a Muggle Studies class, but half of them are at the same time as Divination, and she’s never missed one of them, either!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry  didn’t  have  time  to  fathom  the  mystery  of  Hermione’s impossible timetable at the moment; he really needed to get on with Snape’s essay. Two seconds later, however, he was interrupted again, this time by Wood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bad news, Harry. I’ve just been to see Professor McGonagall about the Firebolt. She – er – got a bit shirty with me. Told me I’d got my priorities wrong. Seemed to think I cared more about winning the Cup than I do about you staying alive. Just because I told her I didn’t care if it threw you off, as long as you caught the Snitch on it first.’ Wood shook his head in disbelief. ‘Honestly, the way she was yelling at me … you’d think I’d said something terrible. Then I asked her how much longer she was going to keep it …’ He screwed up his face and imitated Professor McGonagall’s severe voice, ‘ “As long as necessary, Wood” … I reckon it’s time you ordered a new broom, Harry. There’s an order form at the back of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Which Broomstick</i> … you could get a Nimbus Two Thousand and One, like Malfoy’s got.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not buying anything Malfoy thinks is good,’ said Harry flatly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">January faded imperceptibly into February, with no change in the bitterly cold weather. The match against Ravenclaw was drawing nearer and nearer, but Harry still hadn’t ordered a new broom. He was now asking Professor McGonagall for news of the Firebolt after every Transfiguration lesson, Ron standing hopefully at his shoulder, Hermione rushing past with her face averted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Potter, you can’t have it back yet,’ Professor McGonagall told him the twelfth time this happened, before he’d even opened his mouth. ‘We’ve checked for most of the usual curses, but Professor Flitwick believes the broom might be carrying a Hurling Hex. I shall  <i class=\"calibre4\">tell </i> you once we’ve finished checking it. Now, please stop badgering me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>182 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To make matters even worse, Harry’s Anti-Dementor lessons were not going nearly as well as he had hoped. Several sessions on, he was able to produce an indistinct, silvery shadow every time the Boggart-Dementor approached him, but his Patronus was too feeble to drive the Dementor away. All it did was hover, like a semi-transparent cloud, draining Harry of energy as he fought to keep it there. Harry felt angry with himself, guilty about his secret desire to hear his parents’ voices again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re expecting too much of yourself,’ said Professor Lupin sternly, in their fourth week of practice. ‘For a thirteen-year-old wizard, even an indistinct Patronus is a huge achievement. You aren’t passing out any more, are you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought a Patronus would – charge the Dementors down or something,’ said Harry dispiritedly. ‘Make them disappear –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The true Patronus does do that,’ said Lupin. ‘But you’ve achieved a great deal in a very short space of time. If the Dementors put in an appearance at your next Quidditch match, you will be able to keep them at bay long enough to get back to the ground.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You said it’s harder if there are loads of them,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have complete confidence in you,’ said Lupin, smiling. ‘Here </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– you’ve earned a drink. Something from the Three Broomsticks, you won’t have tried it before –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled two bottles out of his briefcase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Butterbeer!’ said Harry, without thinking. ‘Yeah, I like that stuff!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin raised an eyebrow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – Ron and Hermione brought me some back from Hogsmeade,’ Harry lied quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I see,’ said Lupin, though he still looked slightly suspicious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – let’s drink to a Gryffindor victory against Ravenclaw! Not that I’m supposed to take sides, as a teacher …’ he added hastily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They drank the Butterbeer in silence, until Harry voiced something he’d been wondering for a while. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s under a Dementor’s hood?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Lupin lowered his bottle thoughtfully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hmmm … well, the only people who really know are in no condition to tell us. You see, the Dementor only lowers its hood to use its last and worst weapon.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 183 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They call it the Dementors’ Kiss,’ said Lupin, with a slightly twisted smile. ‘It’s what Dementors do to those they wish to destroy  utterly.  I  suppose  there  must  be  some  kind  of  mouth under there, because they clamp their jaws upon the mouth of the victim and – and suck out his soul.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry accidentally spat out a bit of Butterbeer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What – they kill –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no,’ said Lupin. ‘Much worse than that. You can exist without your soul, you know, as long as your brain and heart are still working. But you’ll have no sense of self any more, no memory, no … anything. There’s no chance at all of recovery. You’ll just – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">exist. As an empty shell. And your soul is gone for ever … lost.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin drank a little more Butterbeer, then said, ‘It’s the fate that awaits Sirius Black. It was in the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> this morning. The Ministry have given the Dementors permission to perform it if they find him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat stunned for a moment at the idea of someone having their soul sucked out through their mouth. But then he thought of Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He deserves it,’ he said suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You think so?’ said Lupin lightly. ‘Do you really think anyone deserves that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry defiantly. ‘For … for some things …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He would have liked to have told Lupin about the conversation he’d overheard about Black in the Three Broomsticks, about Black betraying his mother and father, but it would have involved revealing that he’d gone to Hogsmeade without permission, and he knew Lupin wouldn’t be very impressed by that. So he finished his Butterbeer, thanked Lupin, and left the History of Magic classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry half wished that he hadn’t asked what was under a Dementor’s hood, the answer had been so horrible, and he was so lost in unpleasant thoughts of what it would feel like to have your soul sucked out of you that he walked headlong into Professor McGonagall halfway up the stairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do watch where you’re going, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry, Professor –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve just been looking for you in the Gryffindor common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Well, here it is, we’ve done everything we could think of, and there doesn’t seem to be anything wrong with it at all – you’ve got </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>184 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">a very good friend somewhere, Potter …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s jaw dropped. She was holding out his Firebolt, and it looked as magnificent as ever. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can have it back?’ Harry said weakly. ‘Seriously?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seriously,’ said Professor McGonagall, and she was actually smiling. ‘I daresay you’ll need to get the feel of it before Saturday’s match, won’t you? And Potter –  <i class=\"calibre4\">do  </i> try and win, won’t you? Or we’ll be out of the running for the eighth year in a row, as Professor Snape was kind enough to remind me only last night …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Speechless, Harry carried the Firebolt back upstairs towards Gryffindor Tower. As he turned a corner, he saw Ron dashing towards him, grinning from ear to ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She gave it to you? Excellent! Listen, can I still have a go on it? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Tomorrow?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah … anything …’ said Harry, his heart lighter than it had been  in  a  month.  ‘You  know  what  –  we  should  make  it  up  with Hermione. She was only trying to help …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, all right,’ said Ron. ‘She’s in the common room now – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">working, for a change.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They turned into the corridor to Gryffindor Tower and saw Neville Longbottom, pleading with Sir Cadogan, who seemed to be refusing him entrance. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wrote them down,’ Neville was saying tearfully, ‘but I must’ve dropped them somewhere!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A likely tale!’ roared Sir Cadogan. Then, spotting Harry and Ron, ‘Good even, my fine young yeomen! Come clap this loon in irons, he is trying to force entry to the chambers within!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, shut up,’ said Ron, as he and Harry drew level with Neville. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve lost the passwords!’ Neville told them miserably. ‘I made him tell me what passwords he was going to use this week, because he keeps changing them, and now I don’t know what I’ve done with them!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oddsbodikins,’ said Harry to Sir Cadogan, who looked extremely disappointed and reluctantly swung forwards to let them into the common room. There was a sudden, excited murmur as every head turned and the next moment, Harry was surrounded by people exclaiming over his Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’d you get it, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Will you let me have a go?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus 185 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you ridden it yet, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ravenclaw’ll have no chance, they’re all on Cleansweep Sevens!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can I just  <i class=\"calibre4\">hold </i> it, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">After ten minutes or so, during which the Firebolt was passed around and admired from every angle, the crowd dispersed and Harry and Ron had a clear view of Hermione, the only person who hadn’t rushed over to them, bent over her work, and carefully avoiding their eyes. Harry and Ron approached her table and at last, she looked up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I got it back,’ said Harry, grinning at her and holding up the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See, Hermione? There wasn’t anything wrong with it!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – there  <i class=\"calibre4\">might</i> have been!’ said Hermione. ‘I mean, at least you know now that it’s safe!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I suppose so,’ said Harry. ‘I’d better put it upstairs –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll take it!’ said Ron eagerly. ‘I’ve got to give Scabbers his Rat Tonic.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He took the Firebolt, and, holding it as if it were made of glass, carried it away up the boys’ staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can I sit down, then?’ Harry asked Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose so,’ said Hermione, moving a great stack of parchment off a chair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around at the cluttered table, at the long Arithmancy essay on which the ink was still glistening, at the even longer Muggle Studies essay (‘Explain why Muggles Need Electricity’) and at the Rune translation Hermione was now poring over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How are you getting through all this stuff?’ Harry asked her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, well – you know – working hard,’ said Hermione. Close to, Harry saw that she looked almost as tired as Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why don’t you just drop a couple of subjects?’ Harry asked, watching her lifting books as she searched for her Rune dictio-nary. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I couldn’t do that!’ said Hermione, looking scandalised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Arithmancy looks terrible,’ said Harry, picking up a very complicated-looking number chart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, no, it’s wonderful!’ said Hermione earnestly. ‘It’s my favourite subject! It’s –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But exactly what was wonderful about Arithmancy, Harry never </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>186 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">found out. At that precise moment, a strangled yell echoed down the boys’ staircase. The whole common room fell silent, staring, petrified, at the entrance. There came hurried footsteps, growing louder and louder – and then, Ron came leaping into view, dragging with him a bedsheet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘LOOK!’ he bellowed, striding over to Hermione’s table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘LOOK!’ he yelled, shaking the sheets in her face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, what –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SCABBERS! LOOK! SCABBERS!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was leaning away from Ron, looking utterly bewildered. Harry looked down at the sheet Ron was holding. There was something red on it. Something that looked horribly like – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘BLOOD!’ Ron yelled into the stunned silence. ‘HE’S GONE! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">AND YOU KNOW WHAT WAS ON THE FLOOR?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘N-no,’ said Hermione, in a trembling voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron threw something down onto Hermione’s Rune translation. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione and Harry leant forward. Lying on top of the weird, spiky shapes were several long, ginger cat hairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER THIRTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It looked like the end of Ron and Hermione’s friendship. Each was so angry with the other that Harry couldn’t see how they’d ever make it up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was enraged that Hermione had never taken Crookshanks’s attempts to eat Scabbers seriously, hadn’t bothered to keep a close enough watch on him and was still trying to pretend that Crookshanks was innocent by suggesting Ron look for Scabbers under all the boys’ beds. Hermione, meanwhile, maintained fiercely that Ron had no proof that Crookshanks had eaten Scabbers, that the ginger hairs might have been there since Christmas, and that Ron had been prejudiced against her cat ever since Crookshanks had landed on Ron’s head in the Magical Menagerie. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Personally, Harry was sure that Crookshanks had eaten Scabbers, and when he tried to point out to Hermione that the evidence all pointed that way, she lost her temper with Harry, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, side with Ron, I knew you would!’ she said shrilly. ‘First the Firebolt, now Scabbers, everything’s my fault, isn’t it! Just leave me alone, Harry, I’ve got a lot of work to do!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had taken the loss of his rat very hard indeed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Ron, you were always saying how boring Scabbers was,’ said Fred bracingly. ‘And he’s been off-colour for ages, he was wasting away. It was probably better for him to snuff it quickly. One swallow – he probably didn’t feel a thing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Fred! </i>’ said Ginny indignantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All he did was eat and sleep, Ron, you said it yourself,’ said George. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He bit Goyle for us once!’ Ron said miserably. ‘Remember, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, that’s true,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘His finest hour,’ said Fred, unable to keep a straight face. ‘Let </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>188 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the scar on Goyle’s finger stand as a lasting tribute to his memory. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Oh, come on, Ron, get yourself down to Hogsmeade and buy a new rat. What’s the point of moaning?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">In a last-ditch attempt to cheer Ron up, Harry persuaded him to come along to the Gryffindor team’s final practice before the Ravenclaw match, so that he could have a go on the Firebolt after they’d finished. This did seem to take Ron’s mind off Scabbers for a moment (‘Brilliant! Can I try and shoot a few goals on it?’) so they set off for the Quidditch pitch together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch, who was still overseeing Gryffindor practices to keep an eye on Harry, was just as impressed with the Firebolt as everyone else had been. She took it in her hands before take-off and gave them the benefit of her professional opinion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at the balance on it! If the Nimbus series has a fault, it’s a slight list to the tail-end – you often find they develop a drag after a few years. They’ve updated the handle, too, a bit slimmer than the Cleansweeps, reminds me of the old Silver Arrows – a pity they’ve stopped making them, I learnt to fly on one, and a very fine old broom it was too … ’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She continued in this vein for some time, until Wood said, ‘Er – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch? Is it OK if Harry has the Firebolt back? Only we need to practise …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – right – here you are, then, Potter,’ said Madam Hooch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll sit over here with Weasley …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She and Ron left the pitch to sit in the stadium, and the Gryffindor team gathered around Wood for his final instructions for tomorrow’s match. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, I’ve just found out who Ravenclaw are playing as Seeker. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’s Cho Chang. She’s a fourth-year, and she’s pretty good … I really hoped she wouldn’t be fit, she’s had some problems with injuries …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood scowled his displeasure that Cho Chang had made a full recovery, then said, ‘On the other hand, she rides a Comet Two Sixty, which is going to look like a joke next to the Firebolt.’ He gave Harry’s broom a look of fervent admiration, then said, ‘OK, everyone, let’s go –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And at long last, Harry mounted his Firebolt, and kicked off from the ground. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was better than he’d ever dreamed. The Firebolt turned with the lightest touch; it seemed to obey his thoughts rather than his grip. It sped across the pitch at such speed that the stadium  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw 189 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">turned into a green and grey blur; Harry turned it so sharply that Alicia Spinnet screamed, then he went into a perfectly controlled dive, brushing the grassy pitch with his toes before rising thirty, forty, fifty feet into the air again – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, I’m letting the Snitch out!’ Wood called. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned and raced a Bludger towards the goalposts; he outstripped it easily, saw the Snitch dart out from behind Wood and within ten seconds had caught it tightly in his hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The team cheered madly. Harry let the Snitch go again, gave it a minute’s head start, then tore after it, weaving in and out of the others; he spotted it lurking near Katie Bell’s knee, looped her easily, and caught it again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the best practice ever; the team, inspired by the presence of the Firebolt in their midst, performed their best moves fault-lessly, and by the time they hit the ground again, Wood didn’t have a single criticism to make, which, as George Weasley pointed out, was a first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t see what’s going to stop us tomorrow!’ said Wood. ‘Not unless – Harry, you’ve sorted your Dementor problem, haven’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Harry, thinking of his feeble Patronus and wishing it was stronger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Dementors won’t turn up again, Oliver, Dumbledore’d do his nut,’ said Fred confidently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, let’s hope not,’ said Wood. ‘Anyway – good work, everyone. Let’s get back to the Tower – turn in early …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m staying out for a bit, Ron wants a go on the Firebolt,’ Harry told Wood, and while the rest of the team headed off to the changing rooms, Harry strode over to Ron, who vaulted the barrier to the stands and came to meet him. Madam Hooch had fallen asleep in her seat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here you go,’ said Harry, handing Ron the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, an expression of ecstasy on his face, mounted the broom and zoomed off into the gathering darkness while Harry walked around the edge of the pitch, watching him. Night had fallen before Madam Hooch awoke with a start, told Harry and Ron off for not waking her, and insisted that they go back to the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shouldered the Firebolt and he and Ron walked out of the shadowy stadium, discussing the Firebolt’s superbly smooth action, its phenomenal acceleration and its pinpoint turning. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>190 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were halfway towards the castle when Harry, glancing to his left, saw something that made his heart turn over – a pair of eyes, gleaming out of the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stopped dead, his heart banging against his ribs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the matter?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pointed. Ron pulled out his wand and muttered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A beam of light fell across the grass, hit the bottom of a tree and illuminated its branches; there, crouching amongst the bud-ding leaves, was Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of it!’ Ron roared, and he stooped down and seized a stone lying on the grass, but before he could do anything else, Crookshanks had vanished with one swish of his long ginger tail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See?’ Ron said furiously, chucking the stone down again. ‘She’s still letting him wander about wherever he wants – probably washing down Scabbers with a couple of birds now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t say anything. He took a deep breath as relief seeped through him; he had been sure for a moment that those eyes had belonged to the Grim. They set off for the castle once more. Slightly ashamed of his moment of panic, Harry didn’t say anything to Ron – nor did he look left or right until they had reached the well lit Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went down to breakfast next morning with the rest of the boys in his dormitory, all of whom seemed to think the Firebolt deserved a sort of guard of honour. As Harry entered the Great Hall, heads turned in the direction of the Firebolt, and there was a good deal of excited muttering. Harry saw, with enormous satisfaction, that the Slytherin team were all looking thunderstruck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you see his face?’ said Ron gleefully, looking back at Malfoy. ‘He can’t believe it! This is brilliant!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood, too, was basking in the reflected glory of the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Put it here, Harry,’ he said, laying the broom in the middle of the table and carefully turning it so that its name faced upwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">People from the Ravenclaw and Hufflepuff tables were soon coming over to look. Cedric Diggory came over to congratulate Harry on having acquired such a superb replacement for his Nimbus, and Percy’s Ravenclaw girlfriend, Penelope Clearwater, asked if she could actually hold the Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, now, Penny, no sabotage!’ said Percy heartily, as she examined the Firebolt closely. ‘Penelope and I have got a bet on,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw 191 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he told the team. ‘Ten Galleons on the outcome of the match!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Penelope put the Firebolt down again, thanked Harry and went back to her table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – make sure you win,’ said Percy, in an urgent whisper. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">haven’t got ten Galleons</i>. Yes, I’m coming, Penny!’ And he bustled off to join her in a piece of toast. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sure you can manage that broom, Potter?’ said a cold, drawling voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Draco Malfoy had arrived for a closer look, Crabbe and Goyle right behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, reckon so,’ said Harry casually. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Got plenty of special features, hasn’t it?’ said Malfoy, eyes glittering maliciously. ‘Shame it doesn’t come with a parachute – in case you get too near a Dementor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle sniggered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pity you can’t attach an extra arm to yours, Malfoy,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then it could catch the Snitch for you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor team laughed loudly. Malfoy’s pale eyes narrowed, and he stalked away. They watched him rejoin the rest of the Slytherin team, who put their heads together, no doubt asking Malfoy whether Harry’s broom really was a Firebolt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At a quarter to eleven, the Gryffindor team set off for the changing rooms. The weather couldn’t have been more different from their match against Hufflepuff. It was a clear, cool day, with a very light breeze; there would be no visibility problems this time, and Harry, though nervous, was starting to feel the excitement only a Quidditch match could bring. They could hear the rest of the school moving into the stadium beyond. Harry took off his black school robes, removed his wand from his pocket, and stuck it inside the T-shirt he was going to wear under his Quidditch robes. He only hoped he wouldn’t need it. He wondered suddenly whether Professor Lupin was in the crowd, watching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know what we’ve got to do,’ said Wood, as they prepared to leave the changing rooms. ‘If we lose this match, we’re out of the running. Just – just fly like you did in practice yesterday, and we’ll be OK!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked out onto the pitch to tumultuous applause. The Ravenclaw team, dressed in blue, were already standing in the middle of the pitch. Their Seeker, Cho Chang, was the only girl in their team. She was shorter than Harry by about a head, and  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>192 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t help noticing, nervous as he was, that she was extremely pretty. She smiled at Harry as the teams faced each other behind their captains, and he felt a slight jolt in the region of his stomach that he didn’t think had anything to do with nerves. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wood, Davies, shake hands,’ Madam Hooch said briskly, and Wood shook hands with the Ravenclaw captain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mount your brooms … on my whistle … three – two – one –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry kicked off into the air and the Firebolt zoomed higher and faster than any other broom; he soared around the stadium and began squinting around for the Snitch, listening all the while to the commentary, which was being provided by the Weasley twins’ friend, Lee Jordan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re off, and the big excitement this match is the Firebolt which Harry Potter is flying for Gryffindor. According to  <i class=\"calibre4\">Which</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Broomstick</i>, the Firebolt’s going to be the broom of choice for the national teams at this year’s World Championship –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jordan, would you mind telling us what’s going on in the match?’ interrupted Professor McGonagall’s voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right you are, Professor – just giving a bit of background information. The Firebolt, incidentally, has a built-in auto-brake and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jordan!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, OK, Gryffindor in possession, Katie Bell of Gryffindor heading for goal …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry streaked past Katie in the opposite direction, gazing around for a glint of gold and noticing that Cho Chang was tailing him closely. She was undoubtedly a very good flier – she kept cutting across him, forcing him to change direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Show her your acceleration, Harry!’ Fred yelled, as he whooshed past in pursuit of a Bludger that was aiming for Alicia. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry urged the Firebolt forward as they rounded the Ravenclaw goalposts and Cho fell behind. Just as Katie succeeded in scoring the first goal of the match, and the Gryffindor end of the pitch went wild, he saw it – the Snitch was close to the ground, flitting near one of the barriers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dived; Cho saw what he was doing and tore after him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was speeding up, excitement flooding him; dives were his speciality. He was ten feet away – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then a Bludger, hit by one of the Ravenclaw Beaters, came pelting out of nowhere; Harry veered off course, avoiding it by an </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw 193 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">inch, and in those few, crucial seconds, the Snitch had vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a great ‘Ooooooh’ of disappointment from the Gryffindor supporters, but much applause for their Beater from the Ravenclaw end. George Weasley vented his feelings by hitting the second Bludger directly at the offending Beater, who was forced to roll right over in mid-air to avoid it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gryffindor lead by eighty points to zero, and look at that Firebolt go! Potter’s really putting it through its paces now. See it turn – Chang’s Comet is just no match for it. The Firebolt’s precision-balance is really noticeable in these long –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘JORDAN! ARE YOU BEING PAID TO ADVERTISE FIREBOLTS? GET ON WITH THE COMMENTARY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ravenclaw were pulling back; they had now scored three goals, which put Gryffindor only fifty points ahead – if Cho got the Snitch before him, Ravenclaw would win. Harry dropped lower, narrowly avoiding a Ravenclaw Chaser, scanning the pitch frantically. A glint of gold, a flutter of tiny wings – the Snitch was circling the Gryffindor goalpost … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry accelerated, eyes fixed on the speck of gold ahead – but next second, Cho had appeared out of thin air, blocking him – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HARRY, THIS IS NO TIME TO BE A GENTLEMAN!’ Wood roared, as Harry swerved to avoid a collision. ‘KNOCK HER OFF </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">HER BROOM IF YOU HAVE TO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned and caught sight of Cho; she was grinning. The Snitch had vanished again. Harry turned his Firebolt upwards and was soon twenty feet above the game. Out of the corner of his eye, he saw Cho following him … she’d decided to mark him rather than search for the Snitch herself. Right then … if she wanted to tail him, she’d have to take the consequences … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He dived again, and Cho, thinking he’d seen the Snitch, tried to follow. Harry pulled out of the dive very sharply, she hurtled downwards; he rose fast as a bullet once more, and then saw it, for the third time: the Snitch was glittering way above the pitch at the Ravenclaw end. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He accelerated; so, many feet below, did Cho. He was winning, gaining on the Snitch with every second – then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh!’ screamed Cho, pointing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Distracted, Harry looked down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Three Dementors, three tall, black, hooded Dementors, were looking up at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>194 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t stop to think. Plunging a hand down the neck of his robes, he whipped out his wand and roared, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expecto patronum! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something silver white, something enormous, erupted from the end of his wand. He knew it had shot directly at the Dementors but didn’t pause to watch; his mind still miraculously clear, he looked ahead – he was nearly there. He stretched out the hand still grasping his wand and just managed to close his fingers over the small, struggling Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch’s whistle sounded, Harry turned around in mid-air and saw six scarlet blurs bearing down on him. Next moment, the whole team were hugging him so hard he was nearly pulled off his broom. Down below he could hear the roars of the Gryffindors in the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s my boy!’ Wood kept yelling. Alicia, Angelina and Katie had all kissed Harry, and Fred had him in a grip so tight Harry felt as though his head would come off. In complete disarray, the team managed to make its way back to the ground. Harry got off his broom and looked up to see a gaggle of Gryffindor supporters sprinting onto the pitch, Ron in the lead. Before he knew it, he had been engulfed by the cheering crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes!’ Ron yelled, yanking Harry’s arm into the air. ‘Yes! Yes!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well  <i class=\"calibre4\">done</i>, Harry!’ said Percy, looking delighted. ‘Ten Galleons to me! Must find Penelope, excuse me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good on you, Harry!’ roared Seamus Finnigan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ruddy brilliant!’ boomed Hagrid over the heads of the milling Gryffindors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was quite some Patronus,’ said a voice in Harry’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned around to see Professor Lupin, who looked both shaken and pleased. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Dementors didn’t affect me at all!’ Harry said excitedly. ‘I didn’t feel a thing!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That would be because they – er – weren’t Dementors,’ said Professor Lupin. ‘Come and see –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He led Harry out of the crowd until they were able to see the edge of the pitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You gave Mr Malfoy quite a fright,’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared. Lying in a crumpled heap on the ground were Malfoy, Crabbe, Goyle and Marcus Flint, the Slytherin team captain, all struggling to remove themselves from long, black, hooded robes. It looked as though Malfoy had been standing on Goyle’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw 195 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">shoulders. Standing over them, with an expression of the utmost fury on her face, was Professor McGonagall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An unworthy trick!’ she was shouting. ‘A low and cowardly attempt to sabotage the Gryffindor Seeker! Detention for all of you, and fifty points from Slytherin! I shall be speaking to Professor Dumbledore about this, make no mistake! Ah, here he comes now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If anything could have set the seal on Gryffindor’s victory, it was this. Ron, who had fought his way through to Harry’s side, doubled up with laughter as they watched Malfoy fighting to extricate himself from the robe, Goyle’s head still stuck inside it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Harry!’ said George, fighting his way over. ‘Party! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor common room, now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Harry, and feeling happier than he had done in ages, he and the rest of the team led the way, still in their scarlet robes, out of the stadium and back up to the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It felt as though they had already won the Quidditch Cup; the party went on all day and well into the night. Fred and George Weasley disappeared for a couple of hours and returned with arm-fuls of bottles of Butterbeer, pumpkin fizz and several bags full of Honeydukes sweets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you do that?’ squealed Angelina Johnson, as George started throwing Peppermint Toads into the crowd. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘With a little help from Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred muttered in Harry’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Only one person wasn’t joining in the festivities. Hermione, incredibly, was sitting in a corner, attempting to read an enormous book entitled  <i class=\"calibre4\">Home Life and Social Habits of British Muggles</i>. Harry broke away from the table where Fred and George had started jug-gling Butterbeer bottles, and went over to her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you even come to the match?’ he asked her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course I did,’ said Hermione, in a strangely high-pitched voice, not looking up. ‘And I’m very glad we won, and I think you did really well, but I need to read this by Monday.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Hermione, come and have some food,’ Harry said, looking over at Ron and wondering whether he was in a good enough mood to bury the hatchet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t, Harry, I’ve still got four hundred and twenty-two pages to read!’ said Hermione, now sounding slightly hysterical. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>196 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Anyway …’ she glanced over at Ron, too, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i> doesn’t want me to join in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was no arguing with this, as Ron chose that moment to say loudly, ‘If Scabbers hadn’t just been  <i class=\"calibre4\">eaten</i>, he could have had some of these Fudge Flies, he used to really like them –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione burst into tears. Before Harry could say or do anything, she had tucked the enormous book under her arm, and, still sobbing, run towards the staircase to the girls’ dormitories and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can’t you give her a break?’ Harry asked Ron quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Ron flatly. ‘If she just acted like she was sorry – but she’ll never admit she’s wrong, Hermione. She’s still acting like Scabbers has gone on holiday or something.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor party only ended when Professor McGonagall turned up in her tartan dressing-gown and hair-net at one in the morning, to insist that they all went to bed. Harry and Ron climbed the stairs to their dormitory, still discussing the match. At last, exhausted, Harry climbed into bed, twitched the hangings of his four-poster shut to block out a ray of moonlight, lay back and felt himself almost instantly drifting off to sleep … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had a very strange dream. He was walking through a forest, his Firebolt over his shoulder, following something silvery white. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was winding its way through the trees ahead, and he could only catch glimpses of it between the leaves. Anxious to catch up with it, he sped up, but as he moved faster, so did his quarry. Harry broke into a run and ahead, he heard hooves gathering speed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Now he was running flat out, and ahead he could hear galloping. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he turned a corner into a clearing and – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A A A A A A A A A A A A A A R R R R R R R R R R R R G G G H H H H H ! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry woke as suddenly as though he’d been hit in the face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Disorientated in the total darkness, he fumbled with his hangings </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– he could hear movements around him, and Seamus Finnigan’s voice from the other side of the room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s going on?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry thought he heard the dormitory door slam. At last finding the divide in his curtains, he ripped them back, and at the same moment, Dean Thomas lit his lamp. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was sitting up in bed, the hangings torn from one side, a look of the utmost terror on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor versus Ravenclaw 197 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Black! Sirius Black! With a knife!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here! Just now! Slashed the curtains! Woke me up!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You sure you weren’t dreaming, Ron?’ said Dean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at the curtains! I tell you, he was here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They all scrambled out of bed; Harry reached the dormitory door first, and they sprinted back down the staircase. Doors opened behind them, and sleepy voices called after them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Who shouted?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’re you doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The common room was lit by the glow of the dying fire, still littered with debris from the party. It was deserted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you  <i class=\"calibre4\">sure </i> you weren’t dreaming, Ron?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m telling you, I saw him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s all the noise?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor McGonagall told us to go to bed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A few of the girls had come down their staircase, pulling on dressing-gowns and yawning. Boys, too, were reappearing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent, are we carrying on?’ said Fred Weasley brightly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone back upstairs!’ said Percy, hurrying into the common room and pinning his Head Boy badge to his pyjamas as he spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Perce – Sirius Black!’ said Ron faintly. ‘In our dormitory! With a knife! Woke me up!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The common room went very still. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nonsense!’ said Percy, looking startled. ‘You had too much to eat, Ron – had a nightmare –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m telling you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, really, enough’s enough!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall was back. She slammed the portrait behind her as she entered the common room and stared furiously around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am delighted that Gryffindor won the match, but this is getting ridiculous! Percy, I expected better of you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I certainly didn’t authorise this, Professor!’ said Percy, puffing himself up indignantly. ‘I was just telling them all to get back to bed! My brother Ron here had a nightmare –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘IT WASN’T A NIGHTMARE!’ Ron yelled. ‘PROFESSOR, I WOKE UP, AND SIRIUS BLACK WAS STANDING OVER ME, HOLDING A KNIFE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>198 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t be ridiculous, Weasley, how could he possibly have got through the portrait hole?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ask him!’ said Ron, pointing a shaking finger at the back of Sir Cadogan’s picture. ‘Ask him if he saw –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Glaring suspiciously at Ron, Professor McGonagall pushed the portrait back open and went outside. The whole common room listened with bated breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sir Cadogan, did you just let a man enter Gryffindor Tower?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly, good lady!’ cried Sir Cadogan. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a stunned silence, both inside and outside the common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You – you  <i class=\"calibre4\">did? </i>’ said Professor McGonagall. ‘But – but the password!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He had ’em!’ said Sir Cadogan proudly. ‘Had the whole week’s, my lady! Read ’em off a little piece of paper!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall pulled herself back through the portrait hole to face the stunned crowd. She was white as chalk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Which person,’ she said, her voice shaking, ‘which abysmally foolish person wrote down this week’s passwords and left them lying around?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was utter silence, broken by the smallest of terrified squeaks. Neville Longbottom, trembling from head to fluffy-slippered toes, raised his hand slowly into the air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FOURTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Snape’s Grudge </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one in Gryffindor Tower slept that night. They knew that the castle was being searched again, and the whole house stayed awake in the common room, waiting to hear whether Black had been caught. Professor McGonagall came back at dawn, to tell them that he had again escaped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everywhere they went next day they saw signs of tighter security; Professor Flitwick could be seen teaching the front doors to recognise a large picture of Sirius Black; Filch was suddenly bustling up and down the corridors, boarding up everything from tiny cracks in the walls to mouse holes. Sir Cadogan had been sacked. His portrait had been taken back to its lonely landing on the seventh floor, and the Fat Lady was back. She had been expertly restored, but was still extremely nervous, and had only agreed to return to her job on condition that she was given extra protection. A bunch of surly security trolls had been hired to guard her. They paced the corridor in a menacing group, talking in grunts and comparing the size of their clubs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t help noticing that the statue of the one-eyed witch on the third floor remained unguarded and unblocked. It seemed that Fred and George had been right in thinking that they </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– and now Harry, Ron and Hermione – were the only ones who knew about the hidden passageway within it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you reckon we should tell someone?’ Harry asked Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We know he’s not coming in through Honeydukes,’ said Ron dismissively. ‘We’d’ve heard if the shop had been broken into.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was glad Ron took this view. If the one-eyed witch was boarded up too, he would never be able to go into Hogsmeade again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had become an instant celebrity. For the first time in his life, people were paying more attention to him than to Harry, and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>200 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it was clear that Ron was rather enjoying the experience. Though still severely shaken by the night’s events, he was happy to tell anyone who asked, what had happened, with a wealth of detail. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… I was asleep, and I heard this ripping noise, and I thought it was in my dream, you know? But then there was this draught … I woke up and one side of the hangings on my bed had been pulled down … I rolled over … and I saw him standing over me … like a skeleton, with loads of filthy hair … holding this great long knife, must’ve been twelve inches … and he looked at me, and I looked at him, and then I yelled, and he scarpered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why, though?’ Ron added to Harry, as the group of second-year girls who had been listening to his chilling tale departed. ‘Why did he scarper?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had been wondering the same thing. Why had Black, having got the wrong bed, not silenced Ron and proceeded to Harry? Black had proved twelve years ago that he didn’t mind murdering innocent people, and this time he had been facing five unarmed boys, four of whom were asleep. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He must’ve known he’d have a job getting back out of the castle once you’d yelled and woken people up,’ said Harry thoughtfully. ‘He’d’ve had to kill the whole house to get back through the portrait hole … then he would’ve met the teachers …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville was in total disgrace. Professor McGonagall was so furious with him she had banned him from all future Hogsmeade visits, given him a detention and forbidden anyone to give him the password into the Tower. Poor Neville was forced to wait outside the common room every night for somebody to let him in, while the security trolls leered unpleasantly at him. None of these punishments, however, came close to matching the one his grandmother had in store for him. Two days after Black’s break-in, she sent Neville the very worst thing a Hogwarts student could receive over breakfast – a Howler. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The school owls swooped into the Great Hall, carrying the post as usual, and Neville choked as a huge barn owl landed in front of him, a scarlet envelope clutched in its beak. Harry and Ron, who were sitting opposite him, recognised the letter as a Howler at once – Ron had got one from his mother the year before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Run for it, Neville,’ Ron advised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville didn’t need telling twice. He seized the envelope and, holding it before him like a bomb, sprinted out of the Hall, while </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 201 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the Slytherin table exploded with laughter at the sight of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard the Howler go off in the Entrance Hall – Neville’s grandmother’s voice, magically magnified to a hundred times its usual volume, shrieking about how he had brought shame on the whole family. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was too busy feeling sorry for Neville to notice immediately that he had a letter, too. Hedwig got his attention by nipping him sharply on the wrist. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ouch! Oh – thanks, Hedwig …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tore open the envelope while Hedwig helped herself to some of Neville’s cornflakes. The note inside said: <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Harry and Ron, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">How about having tea with me this evening round six? I’ll</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">come and collect you from the castle. WAIT FOR ME IN THE </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">ENTRANCE HALL, YOU’RE NOT ALLOWED OUT ON YOUR </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">OWN. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Cheers, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hagrid </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He probably wants to hear all about Black!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So at six o’clock that evening, Harry and Ron left Gryffindor Tower, passed the security trolls at a run, and headed down to the Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was already waiting for them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, Hagrid!’ said Ron. ‘S’pose you want to hear about Saturday night, do you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve already heard all abou’ it,’ said Hagrid, opening the front doors and leading them outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh,’ said Ron, looking slightly put out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The first thing they saw on entering Hagrid’s cabin was Buckbeak, who was stretched out on top of Hagrid’s patchwork quilt, his enormous wings folded tight to his body, enjoying a large plate of dead ferrets. Averting his eyes from this unpleasant sight, Harry saw a gigantic, hairy brown suit and a very horrible yellow and orange tie hanging from the top of Hagrid’s wardrobe door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are they for, Hagrid?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Buckbeak’s case against the Committee fer the Disposal o’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dangerous Creatures,’ said Hagrid. ‘This Friday. Him an’ me’ll be </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>202 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">goin’ down ter London together. I’ve booked two beds on the Knight Bus …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt a nasty pang of guilt. He had completely forgotten that Buckbeak’s trial was so near, and judging by the uneasy look on Ron’s face, he had, too. They had also forgotten their promise about helping him prepare Buckbeak’s defence; the arrival of the Firebolt had driven it clean out of their minds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid poured them tea and offered them a plate of Bath buns, but they knew better than to accept; they had had too much experience of Hagrid’s cooking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I got somethin’ ter discuss with you two,’ said Hagrid, sitting himself between them and looking uncharacteristically serious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about her?’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s in a righ’ state, that’s what. She’s bin comin’ down ter visit me a lot since Chris’mas. Bin feelin’ lonely. Firs’ yeh weren’ talking to her because o’ the Firebolt, now yer not talkin’ to her because her cat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– ate Scabbers!’ Ron interjected angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because her cat acted like all cats do,’ Hagrid continued doggedly. ‘She’s cried a fair few times, yeh know. Goin’ through a rough time at the moment. Bitten off more’n she can chew, if yeh ask me, all the work she’s tryin’ ter do. Still found time ter help me with Buckbeak’s case, mind … she’s found some really good stuff fer me … reckon he’ll stand a good chance now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, we should’ve helped as well – sorry –’ Harry began awkwardly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not blamin’ yeh!’ said Hagrid, waving Harry’s apology aside. ‘Gawd knows yeh’ve had enough ter be gettin’ on with, I’ve seen yeh practisin’ Quidditch ev’ry hour o’ the day an’ night – but I gotta tell yeh, I thought you two’d value yer friend more’n broomsticks or rats. Tha’s all.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron exchanged uncomfortable looks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really upset, she was, when Black nearly stabbed yeh, Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She’s got her heart in the right place, Hermione has, an’ you two not talkin’ to her –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If she’d just get rid of that cat, I’d speak to her again!’ Ron said angrily. ‘But she’s still sticking up for it! It’s a maniac, and she won’t hear a word against it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 203 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, well, people can be a bit stupid abou’ their pets,’ said Hagrid wisely. Behind him, Buckbeak spat a few ferret bones onto Hagrid’s pillow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They spent the rest of their visit discussing Gryffindor’s improved chances for the Quidditch Cup. At nine o’clock, Hagrid walked them back up to the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A large group of people was bunched around the notice-board when they returned to the common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hogsmeade, next weekend!’ said Ron, craning over the heads to read the new notice. ‘What d’you reckon?’ he added quietly to Harry, as they went to sit down. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, Filch hasn’t done anything about the passage into Honeydukes …’ Harry said, even more quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ said a voice in his right ear. Harry started and looked around at Hermione, who was sitting at the table right behind them and clearing a space in the wall of books that had been hiding her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, if you go into Hogsmeade again … I’ll tell Professor McGonagall about that map!’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can you hear someone talking, Harry?’ growled Ron, not looking at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, how can you let him go with you? After what Sirius Black nearly did to  <i class=\"calibre4\">you! </i> I mean it, I’ll tell –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So now you’re trying to get Harry expelled!’ said Ron furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Haven’t you done enough damage this year?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione opened her mouth to respond, but with a soft hiss, Crookshanks leapt onto her lap. Hermione took one frightened look at the expression on Ron’s face, gathered Crookshanks up and hurried away towards the girls’ dormitories. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So how about it?’ Ron said to Harry, as though there had been no interruption. ‘Come on, last time we went you didn’t see anything. You haven’t even been inside Zonko’s yet!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around to check that Hermione was well out of earshot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ he said. ‘But I’m taking the Invisibility Cloak this time.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On Saturday morning, Harry packed his Invisibility Cloak in his bag, slipped the Marauder’s Map into his pocket and went down to breakfast with everyone else. Hermione kept shooting suspicious looks down the table at him, but he avoided her eye, and  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>204 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">was careful to let her see him walking back up the marble staircase in the Entrance Hall as everybody else proceeded to the front doors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Bye!’ Harry called to Ron. ‘See you when you get back!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron grinned and winked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hurried up to the third floor, slipping the Marauder’s Map out of his pocket as he went. Crouching behind the one-eyed witch, he smoothed it out. A tiny dot was moving in his direction. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry squinted at it. The minuscule writing next to it read ‘Neville Longbottom’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry quickly pulled out his wand, muttered ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Dissendium! </i>’ and shoved his bag into the statue, but before he could climb in himself, Neville came around the corner. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry! I forgot you weren’t going to Hogsmeade either!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hi, Neville,’ said Harry, moving swiftly away from the statue and pushing the map back into his pocket. ‘What are you up to?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nothing,’ shrugged Neville. ‘Want a game of Exploding Snap?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – not now – I was going to go to the library and do that vampire essay for Lupin –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll come with you!’ said Neville brightly. ‘I haven’t done it either!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – hang on – yeah, I forgot, I finished it last night!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Brilliant, you can help me!’ said Neville, his round face anxious. ‘I don’t understand that thing about the garlic at all – do they have to eat it, or –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Neville broke off with a small gasp, looking over Harry’s shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Snape. Neville took a quick step behind Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And what are you two doing here?’ said Snape, coming to a halt and looking from one to the other. ‘An odd place to meet –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">To Harry’s immense disquiet, Snape’s black eyes flicked to the doorways on either side of them, and then to the one-eyed witch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re not – meeting here,’ said Harry. ‘We just – met here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed?’ said Snape. ‘You have a habit of turning up in unexpected places, Potter, and you are rarely there for no reason … I suggest the pair of you return to Gryffindor Tower, where you belong.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Neville set off without another word. As they turned the corner, Harry looked back. Snape was running one of his hands over the one-eyed witch’s head, examining it closely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry managed to shake Neville off at the Fat Lady by telling </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 205 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">him the password, then pretending he’d left his vampire essay in the library and doubling back. Once out of sight of the security trolls, he pulled out the map again and held it close to his nose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The third-floor corridor seemed to be deserted. Harry scanned the map carefully and saw, with a leap of relief, that the tiny dot labelled ‘Severus Snape’ was now back in its office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sprinted back to the one-eyed witch, opened her hump, heaved himself inside and slid down to meet his bag at the bottom of the stone chute. He wiped the Marauder’s Map blank again, then set off at a run. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, completely hidden beneath the Invisibility Cloak, emerged into the sunlight outside Honeydukes and prodded Ron in the back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s me,’ he muttered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What kept you?’ Ron hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape was hanging around …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They set off up the High Street. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where are you?’ Ron kept muttering out of the corner of his mouth. ‘Are you still there? This feels weird …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went to the Post Office; Ron pretended to be checking the price of an owl to Bill in Egypt so that Harry could have a good look around. The owls sat hooting softly down at him, at least three hundred of them; from Great Greys right down to tiny little Scops owls (‘Local Deliveries Only’) which were so small they could have sat in the palm of Harry’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then they visited Zonko’s, which was so packed with students Harry had to exercise great care not to tread on anyone and cause a panic. There were jokes and tricks to fulfil even Fred and George’s wildest dreams; Harry gave Ron whispered orders and passed him some gold from under the Cloak. They left Zonko’s with their money bags considerably lighter than they had been on entering, but their pockets bulging with Dungbombs, Hiccough Sweets, Frog Spawn Soap and a Nose-Biting Teacup apiece. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The day was fine and breezy, and neither of them felt like staying indoors, so they walked past the Three Broomsticks and climbed a slope to visit the Shrieking Shack, the most haunted dwelling in Britain. It stood a little way above the rest of the village, and even in daylight was slightly creepy, with its boarded windows and dank overgrown garden. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>206 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Even the Hogwarts ghosts avoid it,’ said Ron, as they leaned on the fence, looking up at it. ‘I asked Nearly Headless Nick … he says he’s heard a very rough crowd live here. No one can get in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fred and George tried, obviously, but all the entrances are sealed shut …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, feeling hot from their climb, was just considering taking off the Cloak for a few minutes, when they heard voices nearby. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Someone was climbing towards the house from the other side of the hill; moments later, Malfoy had appeared, followed closely by Crabbe and Goyle. Malfoy was speaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… should have an owl from Father any time now. He had to go to the hearing to tell them about my arm … about how I couldn’t use it for three months …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle sniggered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I really wish I could hear that great hairy moron trying to defend  himself  …  “There’s  no  ’arm  in  ’im,  ’onest  –”  …  that Hippogriff’s as good as dead –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy suddenly caught sight of Ron. His pale face split in a malevolent grin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you doing, Weasley?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy looked up at the crumbling house behind Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Suppose you’d love to live here, wouldn’t you, Weasley? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dreaming about having your own bedroom? I heard your family all sleep in one room – is that true?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry seized the back of Ron’s robes to stop him leaping on Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Leave him to me,’ he hissed in Ron’s ear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The opportunity was too perfect to miss. Harry crept silently around behind Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle, bent down and scooped a large handful of mud out of the path. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We were just discussing your friend Hagrid,’ Malfoy said to Ron. ‘Just trying to imagine what he’s saying to the Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures. D’you think he’ll cry when they cut off his Hippogriff’s –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SPLAT! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy’s head jerked forwards as the mud hit him; his silver-blond hair was suddenly dripping in muck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What the –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had to hold onto the fence to keep himself standing, he was laughing so hard. Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle spun stupidly on </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 207 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the spot, staring wildly around, Malfoy trying to wipe his hair clean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was that? Who did that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very haunted up here, isn’t it?’ said Ron, with the air of one commenting on the weather. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle were looking scared. Their bulging muscles were no use against ghosts. Malfoy was staring madly around at the deserted landscape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sneaked along the path, where a particularly sloppy puddle yielded some foul-smelling, green sludge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SPLATTER! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle caught some this time. Goyle hopped furiously on the spot, trying to rub it out of his small, dull eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It came from over there!’ said Malfoy, wiping his face, and staring at a spot some six feet to the left of Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe blundered forwards, his long arms outstretched like a zombie. Harry dodged around him, picked up a stick, and lobbed it at Crabbe’s back. Harry doubled up with silent laughter as Crabbe did a kind of pirouette in mid-air, trying to see who had thrown it. As Ron was the only person Crabbe could see, it was Ron he started towards, but Harry stuck out his leg. Crabbe stumbled – and his huge, flat foot caught the hem of Harry’s Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt a great tug, then the Cloak slid off his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a split second, Malfoy stared at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AAARGH!’ he yelled, pointing at Harry’s head. Then he turned tail and ran, at breakneck speed, back down the hill, Crabbe and Goyle behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tugged the Cloak up again, but the damage was done. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ Ron said, stumbling forward and staring hopelessly at the point where Harry had disappeared, ‘you’d better run for it! If Malfoy tells anyone – you’d better get back to the castle, quick –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See you later,’ said Harry, and without another word, he tore back down the path towards Hogsmeade. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Would Malfoy believe what he had seen? Would anyone believe Malfoy? Nobody knew about the Invisibility Cloak – nobody except Dumbledore. Harry’s stomach turned over – Dumbledore would know exactly what had happened, if Malfoy said anything – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Back into Honeydukes, back down the cellar steps, across the stone floor, through the trapdoor – Harry pulled off the Cloak, tucked it under his arm, and ran, flat out, along the passage … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>208 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy would get back first … how long would it take him to find a teacher? Panting, a sharp pain in his side, Harry didn’t slow down until he reached the stone slide. He would have to leave the Cloak where it was, it was too much of a giveaway if Malfoy had tipped off a teacher. He hid it in a shadowy corner, then started to climb, fast as he could, his sweaty hands slipping on the sides of the chute. He reached the inside of the witch’s hump, tapped it with his wand, stuck his head through and hoisted himself out; the hump closed, and just as Harry jumped out from behind the statue, he heard quick footsteps approaching. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Snape. He approached Harry at a swift walk, his black robes swishing, then stopped in front of him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a look of suppressed triumph about him. Harry tried to look innocent, all too aware of his sweaty face and his muddy hands, which he quickly hid in his pockets. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come with me, Potter,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry followed him downstairs, trying to wipe his hands clean on the inside of his robes without Snape noticing. They walked down the stairs to the dungeons and then into Snape’s office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had only been in here once before, and he had been in very serious trouble then, too. Snape had acquired a few more horrible slimy things in jars since last time, all standing on shelves behind his desk, glinting in the firelight and adding to the threatening atmosphere. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sit,’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat. Snape, however, remained standing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mr Malfoy has just been to see me with a strange story, Potter,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t say anything. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He tells me that he was up by the Shrieking Shack when he ran into Weasley – apparently alone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Still, Harry didn’t speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mr Malfoy states that he was standing talking to Weasley, when a large amount of mud hit him on the back of the head. How do you think that could have happened?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tried to look mildly surprised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know, Professor.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s eyes were boring into Harry’s. It was exactly like trying to stare out a Hippogriff. Harry tried hard not to blink. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 209 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mr Malfoy then saw an extraordinary apparition. Can you imagine what it might have been, Potter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry, now trying to sound innocently curious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was your head, Potter. Floating in mid-air.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a long silence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe he’d better go to Madam Pomfrey,’ said Harry. ‘If he’s seeing things like –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What would your head have been doing in Hogsmeade, Potter?’ said Snape softly. ‘Your head is not allowed in Hogsmeade. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No part of your body has permission to be in Hogsmeade.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know that,’ said Harry, striving to keep his face free of guilt or fear. ‘It sounds like Malfoy’s having hallucin–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy is not having hallucinations,’ snarled Snape, and he bent down, a hand on each arm of Harry’s chair, so that their faces were a foot apart. ‘If your head was in Hogsmeade, so was the rest of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve been up in Gryffindor Tower,’ said Harry. ‘Like you told –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Can anyone confirm that?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t say anything. Snape’s thin mouth curled into a horrible smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So,’ he said, straightening up again. ‘Everyone from the Minister for Magic downwards has been trying to keep famous Harry Potter safe from Sirius Black. But famous Harry Potter is a law unto himself. Let the ordinary people worry about his safety! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Famous Harry Potter goes where he wants to, with no thought for the consequences.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stayed silent. Snape was trying to provoke him into telling the truth. He wasn’t going to do it. Snape had no proof – yet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How extraordinarily like your father you are, Potter,’ Snape said suddenly, his eyes glinting. ‘He, too, was exceedingly arrogant. A small amount of talent on the Quidditch pitch made him think he was a cut above the rest of us, too. Strutting around the place with his friends and admirers … the resemblance between you is uncanny.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dad didn’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">strut</i>,’ said Harry, before he could stop himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And nor do I.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your father didn’t set much store by rules, either,’ Snape went on, pressing his advantage, his thin face full of malice. ‘Rules were for lesser mortals, not Quidditch Cup-winners. His head was so swollen –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>210 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SHUT UP!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was suddenly on his feet. Rage such as he had not felt since his last night in Privet Drive was thundering through him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He didn’t care that Snape’s face had gone rigid, the black eyes flashing dangerously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What did you say to me, Potter? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I told you to shut up about my dad!’ Harry yelled. ‘I know the truth, all right? He saved your life! Dumbledore told me! You wouldn’t even be here if it weren’t for my dad!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s sallow skin had gone the colour of sour milk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And did the Headmaster tell you the circumstances in which your father saved my life?’ he whispered. ‘Or did he consider the details too unpleasant for precious Potter’s delicate ears?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry bit his lip. He didn’t know what had happened and didn’t want to admit it – but Snape seemed to have guessed the truth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would hate you to run away with a false idea of your father, Potter,’ he said, a terrible grin twisting his face. ‘Have you been imagining some act of glorious heroism? Then let me correct you  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– your saintly father and his friends played a highly amusing joke on me that would have resulted in my death if your father hadn’t got cold feet at the last moment. There was nothing brave about what he did. He was saving his own skin as much as mine. Had their joke succeeded, he would have been expelled from Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s uneven, yellowish teeth were bared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Turn out your pockets, Potter!’ he spat suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t move. There was a pounding in his ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Turn out your pockets, or we go straight to the Headmaster! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pull them out, Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cold with dread, Harry slowly pulled out the bag of Zonko’s tricks and the Marauder’s Map. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape picked up the Zonko’s bag. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron gave them to me,’ said Harry, praying he’d get a chance to tip Ron off before Snape saw him. ‘He – brought them back from Hogsmeade last time –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed? And you’ve been carrying them round ever since? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">How very touching … and what is this?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape had picked up the map. Harry tried with all his might to keep his face impassive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 211 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Spare bit of parchment,’ he shrugged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape turned it over, his eyes on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Surely you don’t need such a very  <i class=\"calibre4\">old </i> piece of parchment?’ he said. ‘Why don’t I just – throw this away?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His hand moved towards the fire. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ Harry said quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So!’ said Snape, his long nostrils quivering. ‘Is this another treasured gift from Mr Weasley? Or is it – something else? A letter, perhaps, written in invisible ink? Or – instructions to get into Hogsmeade without passing the Dementors?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry blinked. Snape’s eyes gleamed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let me see, let me see …’ he muttered, taking out his wand and smoothing the map out on his desk. ‘Reveal your secret!’ he said, touching the wand to the parchment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nothing happened. Harry clenched his hands to stop them shaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Show yourself!’ Snape said, tapping the map sharply. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It stayed blank. Harry was taking deep, calming breaths. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Severus Snape, master of this school, commands you to yield the information you conceal!’ Snape said, hitting the map with his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As though an invisible hand was writing upon it, words appeared on the smooth surface of the map. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Moony presents his compliments to Professor Snape, and begs</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">him to keep his abnormally large nose out of other people’s business. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape froze. Harry stared, dumbstruck, at the message. But the map didn’t stop there. More writing was appearing beneath the first. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Prongs agrees with Mr Moony, and would like to add that</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Professor Snape is an ugly git. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It would have been very funny if the situation hadn’t been so serious. And there was more … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Padfoot would like to register his astonishment that an idiot</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">like that ever became a Professor. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry closed his eyes in horror. When he’d opened them, the map had had its last word. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mr Wormtail bids Professor Snape good day, and advises him to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">wash his hair, the slimeball. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited for the blow to fall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So …’ said Snape softly. ‘We’ll see about this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>212 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He strode across to his fire, seized a fistful of glittering powder from a jar on the fireplace, and threw it into the flames. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lupin!’ Snape called into the fire. ‘I want a word!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Utterly bewildered, Harry stared at the fire. A large shape had appeared in it, revolving very fast. Seconds later, Professor Lupin was clambering out of the fireplace, brushing ash off his shabby robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You called, Severus?’ said Lupin mildly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I certainly did,’ said Snape, his face contorted with fury as he strode back to his desk. ‘I have just asked Potter to empty his pockets. He was carrying this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape pointed at the parchment, on which the words of Messrs Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs were still shining. An odd, closed expression appeared on Lupin’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well?’ said Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin continued to stare at the map. Harry had the impression that Lupin was doing some very quick thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Well? </i>’ said Snape again. ‘This parchment is plainly full of Dark Magic. This is supposed to be your area of expertise, Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where do you imagine Potter got such a thing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin  looked  up  and,  by  the  merest  half  glance  in  Harry’s direction, warned him not to interrupt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Full of Dark Magic?’ he repeated mildly. ‘Do you really think so, Severus? It looks to me as though it is merely a piece of parchment that insults anybody who tries to read it. Childish, but surely not dangerous? I imagine Harry got it from a joke-shop –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed?’ said Snape. His jaw had gone rigid with anger. ‘You think a joke-shop could supply him with such a thing? You don’t think it more likely that he got it  <i class=\"calibre4\">directly from the manufacturers? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t understand what Snape was talking about. Nor, apparently, did Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You mean, from Mr Wormtail or one of these people?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, do you know any of these men?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You see, Severus?’ said Lupin, turning back to Snape. ‘It looks like a Zonko product to me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Right on cue, Ron came bursting into the office. He was completely out of breath, and stopped just short of Snape’s desk, clutching the stitch in his chest and trying to speak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – gave – Harry – that – stuff,’ he choked. ‘Bought – it – in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s Grudge 213 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Zonko’s – ages – ago …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well!’ said Lupin, clapping his hands together and looking around cheerfully. ‘That seems to clear that up! Severus, I’ll take this back, shall I?’ He folded the map and tucked it inside his robes. ‘Harry, Ron, come with me, I need a word about my vampire essay. Excuse us, Severus.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t dare look at Snape as they left his office. He, Ron and Lupin walked all the way back into the Entrance Hall before speaking. Then Harry turned to Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor, I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want to hear explanations,’ said Lupin shortly. He glanced around the empty Entrance Hall and lowered his voice. ‘I happen to know that this map was confiscated by Mr Filch many years ago. Yes, I know it’s a map,’ he said, as Harry and Ron looked amazed. ‘I don’t want to know how it fell into your possession. I am, however,  <i class=\"calibre4\">astounded</i> that you didn’t hand it in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Particularly after what happened the last time a student left information about the castle lying around. And I can’t let you have it back, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had expected that, and was too keen for explanations to protest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why did Snape think I’d got it from the manufacturers?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because …’ Lupin hesitated, ‘because these mapmakers would have wanted to lure you out of school. They’d think it extremely entertaining.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you  <i class=\"calibre4\">know </i> them?’ said Harry, impressed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve met,’ he said shortly. He was looking at Harry more seriously than ever before. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t expect me to cover up for you again, Harry. I cannot make you take Sirius Black seriously. But I would have thought that what you have heard when the Dementors draw near you would have had more of an effect on you. Your parents gave their lives to keep you alive, Harry. A poor way to repay them – gam-bling their sacrifice for a bag of magic tricks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He walked away, leaving Harry feeling worse by far than he had at any point in Snape’s office. Slowly, he and Ron mounted the marble staircase. As Harry passed the one-eyed witch, he remembered the Invisibility Cloak – it was still down there, but he didn’t dare go and get it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s my fault,’ said Ron abruptly. ‘I persuaded you to go. Lupin’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>214 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">right, it was stupid, we shouldn’t’ve done it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He broke off; they had reached the corridor where the security trolls were pacing, and Hermione was walking towards them. One look at her face convinced Harry that she had heard what had happened. His heart plummeted – had she told Professor McGonagall? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come to have a good gloat?’ said Ron savagely, as she stopped in front of them. ‘Or have you just been to tell on us?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Hermione. She was holding a letter in her hands and her lip was trembling. ‘I just thought you ought to know … Hagrid lost his case. Buckbeak is going to be executed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER FIFTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Quidditch Final </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He – he sent me this,’ Hermione said, holding out the letter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took it. The parchment was damp, and enormous teardrops had smudged the ink so badly in places that it was very difficult to read. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Hermione, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">We lost. I’m allowed to bring him back to Hogwarts. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Execution date to be fixed. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Beaky has enjoyed London. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I won’t forget all the help you gave us. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hagrid</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They can’t do this,’ said Harry. ‘They can’t. Buckbeak isn’t dangerous.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Malfoy’s dad’s frightened the Committee into it,’ said Hermione, wiping her eyes. ‘You know what he’s like. They’re a bunch of doddery old fools, and they were scared. There’ll be an appeal, though, there always is. Only I can’t see any hope … nothing will have changed.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, it will,’ said Ron fiercely. ‘You won’t have to do all the work alone this time, Hermione. I’ll help.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, Ron!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione flung her arms around Ron’s neck and broke down completely. Ron, looking quite terrified, patted her very awkwardly on the top of the head. Finally, Hermione drew away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, I’m really, really sorry about Scabbers …’ she sobbed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh – well – he was old,’ said Ron, looking thoroughly relieved that she had let go of him. ‘And he was a bit useless. You never know, Mum and Dad might get me an owl now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>216 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The safety measures imposed on the students since Black’s second break-in made it impossible for Harry, Ron and Hermione to go and visit Hagrid in the evenings. Their only chance of talking to him was during Care of Magical Creatures lessons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He seemed numb with shock at the verdict. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’S all my fault. Got all tongue-tied. They was all sittin’ there in black robes an’ I kep’ droppin’ me notes and forgettin’ all them dates yeh looked up fer me, Hermione. An’ then Lucius Malfoy stood up an’ said his bit, and the Committee jus’ did exac’ly what he told ’em …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s still the appeal!’ said Ron fiercely. ‘Don’t give up yet, we’re working on it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They were walking back up to the castle with the rest of the class. Ahead they could see Malfoy, who was walking with Crabbe and Goyle, and kept looking back, laughing derisively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’S no good, Ron,’ said Hagrid sadly as they reached the castle steps. ‘That Committee’s in Lucius Malfoy’s pocket. I’m jus’ gonna make sure the rest o’ Beaky’s time is the happiest he’s ever had. I owe him that …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid turned round and hurried back towards his cabin, his face buried in his handkerchief. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look at him blubber!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy, Crabbe and Goyle had been standing just inside the castle doors, listening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have you ever seen anything quite as pathetic?’ said Malfoy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And he’s supposed to be our teacher!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron both made furious moves towards Malfoy, but Hermione got there first – SMACK! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She had slapped Malfoy around the face with all the strength she could muster. Malfoy staggered. Harry, Ron, Crabbe and Goyle stood flabbergasted as Hermione raised her hand again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t you  <i class=\"calibre4\">dare</i> call Hagrid pathetic, you foul – you evil –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione!’ said Ron weakly, and he tried to grab her hand as she swung it back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get  <i class=\"calibre4\">off</i>, Ron!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione pulled out her wand. Malfoy stepped backwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crabbe and Goyle looked at him for instructions, thoroughly bewildered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘C’mon,’ Malfoy muttered, and next moment, all three of them had disappeared into the passageway to the dungeons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 217 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Hermione! </i>’ Ron said again, sounding both stunned and impressed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, you’d better beat him in the Quidditch final!’ Hermione said shrilly. ‘You just better had, because I can’t stand it if Slytherin win!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re due in Charms,’ said Ron, still goggling at Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better go.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They hurried up the marble staircase towards Professor Flitwick’s classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re late, boys!’ said Professor Flitwick reprovingly, as Harry opened the classroom door. ‘Come along, quickly, wands out, we’re experimenting with Cheering Charms today. We’ve already divided into pairs –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron hurried to a desk at the back and opened their bags. Ron looked behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Hermione gone?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around, too. Hermione hadn’t entered the classroom, yet Harry knew she had been right next to him when he had opened the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s weird,’ said Harry, staring at Ron. ‘Maybe – maybe she went to the bathroom or something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione didn’t turn up all lesson. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She could’ve done with a Cheering Charm on her, too,’ said Ron, as the class left for lunch, all grinning broadly – the Cheering Charms had left them with a feeling of great content-ment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione wasn’t at lunch either. By the time they had finished their apple pie, the after-effects of the Cheering Charms were wearing off, and Harry and Ron had started to get slightly worried. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t think Malfoy did something to her?’ Ron said anxiously, as they hurried upstairs towards Gryffindor Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They passed the security trolls, gave the Fat Lady the password (‘Flibbertigibbet’) and scrambled through the portrait hole into the common room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was sitting at a table, fast asleep, her head resting on an open Arithmancy book. They went to sit down either side of her. Harry prodded her awake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wh-what?’ said Hermione, waking with a start, and staring wildly around. ‘Is it time to go? W-which lesson have we got now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>218 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Divination, but it’s not for another twenty minutes,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, why didn’t you come to Charms?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What? Oh no!’ Hermione squeaked. ‘I forgot to go to Charms!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But how could you forget?’ said Harry. ‘You were with us till we were right outside the classroom!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t believe it!’ Hermione wailed. ‘Was Professor Flitwick angry? Oh, it was Malfoy, I was thinking about him and I lost track of things!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know what, Hermione?’ said Ron, looking down at the enormous Arithmancy book Hermione had been using as a pillow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I reckon you’re cracking up. You’re trying to do too much.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I’m not!’ said Hermione, brushing her hair out of her eyes and staring hopelessly around for her bag. ‘I just made a mistake, that’s all! I’d better go and see Professor Flitwick and say sorry … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I’ll see you in Divination!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione joined them at the foot of the ladder to Professor Trelawney’s classroom twenty minutes later, looking extremely harassed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t believe I missed Cheering Charms! And I bet they come up in our exams. Professor Flitwick hinted they might!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Together they climbed the ladder into the dim, stifling tower room. Glowing on every little table was a crystal ball full of pearly white mist. Harry, Ron and Hermione sat down together at the same rickety table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought we weren’t starting crystal balls until next term,’ Ron muttered, casting a wary eye around for Professor Trelawney, in case she was lurking nearby. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t complain, this means we’ve finished palmistry,’ Harry muttered back. ‘I was getting sick of her flinching every time she looked at my hands.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good day to you!’ said the familiar, misty voice, and Professor Trelawney made her usual dramatic entrance out of the shadows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati and Lavender quivered with excitement, their faces lit by the milky glow of their crystal ball. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have decided to introduce the crystal ball a little earlier than I had planned,’ said Professor Trelawney, seating herself with her back to the fire and gazing around. ‘The fates have informed me that your examination in June will concern the Orb, and I am anxious to give you sufficient practice.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione snorted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 219 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, honestly … “the fates have informed her” … who sets the exam? She does! What an amazing prediction!’ she said, not troubling to keep her voice low. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was hard to tell whether Professor Trelawney had heard them, as her face was hidden in shadow. She continued, however, as though she had not. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crystal-gazing is a particularly refined art,’ she said dreamily. ‘I do not expect any of you to See when first you peer into the Orb’s infinite depths. We shall start by practising relaxing the conscious mind and external eyes’ – Ron began to snigger uncontrollably, and had to stuff his fist in his mouth to stifle the noise – ‘so as to clear the Inner Eye and the superconscious. Perhaps, if we are lucky, some of you will See before the end of the class.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And so they began. Harry, at least, felt extremely foolish, staring blankly at the crystal ball, trying to keep his mind empty when thoughts such as ‘this is stupid’ kept drifting across it. It didn’t help that Ron kept breaking into silent giggles and Hermione kept tutting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Seen anything yet?’ Harry asked them, after a quarter of an hour’s quiet crystal-gazing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, there’s a burn on this table,’ said Ron, pointing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone’s spilled their candle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is such a waste of time,’ Hermione hissed. ‘I could be practising something useful. I could be catching up on Cheering Charms –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney rustled past. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Would anyone like me to help them interpret the shadowy portents within their Orb?’ she murmured over the clinking of her bangles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t need help,’ Ron whispered. ‘It’s obvious what this means. There’s going to be loads of fog tonight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both Harry and Hermione burst out laughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, really!’ said Professor Trelawney, as everyone’s heads turned in their direction. Parvati and Lavender were looking scandalised. ‘You are disturbing the clairvoyant vibrations!’ She approached their table and peered into their crystal ball. Harry felt his heart sinking. He was sure he knew what was coming … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There is something here!’ Professor Trelawney whispered, lowering her face to the ball, so that it was reflected twice in her huge glasses. ‘Something moving … but what is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>220 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was prepared to bet everything he owned, including his Firebolt,  that  it  wasn’t  good  news,  whatever  it  was.  And  sure enough … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dear …’ Professor Trelawney breathed, gazing up at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It is here, plainer than ever before … my dear, stalking towards you, growing ever closer … the Gr–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, for  <i class=\"calibre4\">goodness</i>’ sake!’ said Hermione, loudly. ‘Not that ridiculous Grim  <i class=\"calibre4\">again! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney raised her enormous eyes to Hermione’s face. Parvati whispered something to Lavender, and they both glared at Hermione, too. Professor Trelawney stood up, surveying Hermione with unmistakeable anger. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I  am  sorry  to  say  that  from  the  moment  you  have  arrived  in this class, my  <i class=\"calibre4\">dear</i>, it has been apparent that you do not have what the noble art of Divination requires. Indeed, I don’t remember ever meeting a student whose mind was so hopelessly Mundane.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a moment’s silence. Then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fine!’ said Hermione suddenly, getting up and cramming <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the Future </i> back into her bag. ‘Fine!’ she repeated, swinging the bag over her shoulder and almost knocking Ron off his chair. ‘I give up! I’m leaving!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And to the whole class’s amazement, Hermione strode over to the trapdoor, kicked it open, and climbed down the ladder out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a few minutes for the class to settle down again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney seemed to have forgotten all about the Grim. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She turned abruptly from Harry and Ron’s table, breathing rather heavily as she tugged her gauzy shawl more closely to her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ooooo!’ said Lavender suddenly, making everyone start. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oooooo, Professor Trelawney, I’ve just remembered! You saw her leaving, didn’t you? Didn’t you, Professor? “<i class=\"calibre4\">Around Easter, one of</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">our number will leave us for ever! </i>” You said it  <i class=\"calibre4\">ages</i> ago, Professor!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney gave her a dewy smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, my dear, I did indeed know that Miss Granger would be leaving us. One hopes, however, that one might have mistaken the Signs … the Inner Eye can be a burden, you know …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lavender and Parvati looked deeply impressed, and moved over so that Professor Trelawney could join their table instead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some day Hermione’s having, eh?’ Ron muttered to Harry, looking awed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 221 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced into the crystal ball, but saw nothing but swirling white mist. Had Professor Trelawney really seen the Grim again? Would he? The last thing he needed was another near-fatal accident, with the Quidditch final drawing ever nearer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Easter holidays were not exactly relaxing. The third-years had never had so much homework. Neville Longbottom seemed close to a nervous collapse, and he wasn’t the only one. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Call this a holiday!’ Seamus Finnigan roared at the common room one afternoon. ‘The exams are ages away, what’re they playing at?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But nobody had as much to do as Hermione. Even without Divination, she was taking more subjects than anybody else. She was usually last to leave the common room at night, first to arrive at the library next morning; she had shadows like Lupin’s under her eyes, and seemed constantly close to tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron had taken over responsibility for Buckbeak’s appeal. When he wasn’t doing his own work, he was poring over enormously thick volumes with names like  <i class=\"calibre4\">The Handbook of Hippogriff</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Psychology  </i> and <i class=\"calibre4\"> Fowl or Foul? A Study of Hippogriff Brutality. </i> He was so absorbed, he even forgot to be horrible to Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, meanwhile, had to fit in his homework around Quidditch practice every day, not to mention endless discussions of tactics with Wood. The Gryffindor–Slytherin match would take place on the first Saturday after the Easter holidays. Slytherin were leading the tournament by exactly two hundred points. This meant (as Wood constantly reminded his team) that they needed to win the match by more than that amount to win the Cup. It also meant that the burden of winning fell largely on Harry, because capturing the Snitch was worth one hundred and fifty points. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you must  <i class=\"calibre4\">only  </i> catch it if we’re  <i class=\"calibre4\">more</i> than fifty points up,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood told Harry constantly. ‘Only if we’re more than fifty points up, Harry, or we win the match but lose the Cup. You’ve got that, haven’t you? You must only catch the Snitch if we’re –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I KNOW, OLIVER!’ Harry yelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The whole of Gryffindor house was obsessed with the coming match. Gryffindor hadn’t won the Quidditch Cup since the leg-endary Charlie Weasley (Ron’s second-oldest brother) had been </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>222 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seeker. But Harry doubted whether any of them, even Wood, wanted to win as much as he did. The enmity between Harry and Malfoy was at its highest point ever. Malfoy was still smarting about the mud-throwing incident in Hogsmeade, and even more furious that Harry had somehow wormed his way out of punishment. Harry hadn’t forgotten Malfoy’s attempt to sabotage him in the match against Ravenclaw, but it was the matter of Buckbeak that made him most determined to beat Malfoy in front of the entire school. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Never, in anyone’s memory, had a match approached in such a highly charged atmosphere. By the time the holidays were over, tension between the two teams and their houses was at breaking-point. A number of small scuffles broke out in the corridors, cul-minating in a nasty incident in which a Gryffindor fourth-year and a Slytherin sixth-year ended up in the hospital wing with leeks sprouting out of their ears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was having a particularly bad time of it. He couldn’t walk to class without Slytherins sticking out their legs and trying to trip him up; Crabbe and Goyle kept popping up wherever he went, and slouching away looking disappointed when they saw him surrounded by people. Wood had given instructions that Harry should be accompanied everywhere, in case the Slytherins tried to put him out of action. The whole of Gryffindor house took up the challenge enthusiastically, so that it was impossible for Harry to get to classes on time because he was surrounded by a vast, chattering crowd. Harry was more concerned for his Firebolt’s safety than his own. When he wasn’t flying it, he locked it securely in his trunk, and frequently dashed back up to Gryffindor Tower at break-times to check that it was still there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All usual pursuits were abandoned in the Gryffindor common room the night before the match. Even Hermione had put down her books. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t work, I can’t concentrate,’ she said nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a great deal of noise. Fred and George Weasley were dealing with the pressure by being louder and more exuberant than ever. Oliver Wood was crouched over a model of a Quidditch pitch in the corner, prodding little figures across it with his wand and muttering to himself. Angelina, Alicia and Katie were laughing at Fred and George’s jokes. Harry was sitting with Ron and </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 223 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, removed from the centre of things, trying not to think about the next day, because every time he did, he had the horrible sensation that something very large was fighting to get out of his stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re going to be fine,’ Hermione told him, though she looked positively terrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got a  <i class=\"calibre4\">Firebolt! </i>’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ said Harry, his stomach writhing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It came as a relief when Wood suddenly stood up and yelled, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Team! Bed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry slept badly. First he dreamed that he had overslept, and that Wood was yelling, ‘Where were you? We had to use Neville instead!’ Then he dreamed that Malfoy and the rest of the Slytherin team arrived for the match riding dragons. He was flying at breakneck speed, trying to avoid a spurt of flames from Malfoy’s steed’s mouth, when he realised he had forgotten his Firebolt. He fell through the air and woke with a start. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a few seconds before Harry remembered that the match hadn’t taken place yet, that he was safe in bed and that the Slytherin team definitely wouldn’t be allowed to play on dragons. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was feeling very thirsty. As quietly as he could, he got out of his four-poster and went to pour himself some water from the silver jug beneath the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The grounds were still and quiet. No breath of wind disturbed the treetops in the Forbidden Forest; the Whomping Willow was motionless and innocent-looking. It looked as though conditions for the match would be perfect. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry set down his goblet and was about to turn back to his bed when something caught his eye. An animal of some kind was prowling across the silvery lawn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry dashed to his bedside table, snatched up his glasses and put them on, then hurried back to the window. It couldn’t be the Grim – not now – not right before the match – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He peered out at the grounds again and, after a minute’s frantic searching, spotted it. It was skirting the edge of the Forest now … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it wasn’t the Grim at all … it was a cat … Harry clutched the window-ledge in relief as he recognised the bottle-brush tail. It was only Crookshanks … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Or  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> it only Crookshanks? Harry squinted, pressing his nose </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>224 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">flat against the glass. Crookshanks seemed to have come to a halt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was sure he could see something else moving in the shadow of the trees, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And next moment, it had emerged: a gigantic, shaggy black dog, moving stealthily across the lawn, Crookshanks trotting at its side. Harry stared. What did this mean? If Crookshanks could see the dog as well, how could it be an omen of Harry’s death? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ Harry hissed. ‘Ron! Wake up!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Huh?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I need you to tell me if you can see something!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’S all dark, Harry,’ Ron muttered thickly. ‘What’re you on about?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Down here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked quickly back out of the window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks and the dog had vanished. Harry climbed onto the window-sill to look right down into the shadows of the castle, but they weren’t there. Where had they gone? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A loud snore told him Ron had fallen asleep again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and the rest of the Gryffindor team entered the Great Hall next day to enormous applause. Harry couldn’t help grinning broadly as he saw that both the Ravenclaw and Hufflepuff tables were clapping them, too. The Slytherin table hissed loudly as they passed. Harry noticed that Malfoy looked even paler than usual. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood spent the whole of breakfast urging his team to eat, while touching nothing himself. Then he hurried them off to the pitch before anyone else had finished, so they could get an idea of the conditions. As they left the Great Hall, everyone applauded again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good luck, Harry!’ called Cho Chang. Harry felt himself blushing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK … no wind to speak of … sun’s a bit bright, that could impair your vision, watch out for it … ground’s fairly hard, good, that’ll give us a fast kick-off …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wood paced the pitch, staring around with the team behind him. Finally they saw the front doors of the castle open in the distance, and the rest of the school spill onto the lawn. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Changing rooms,’ said Wood tersely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">None of them spoke as they changed into their scarlet robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wondered if they were feeling like he was: as though he’d eaten something extremely wriggly for breakfast. In what seemed like no time at all, Wood was saying, ‘OK, it’s time, let’s go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 225 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked out onto the pitch to a tidal wave of noise. Three-quarters of the crowd were wearing scarlet rosettes, waving scarlet flags with the Gryffindor lion upon them or brandishing banners with slogans such as ‘GO GRYFFINDOR!’ and ‘LIONS FOR THE </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">CUP!’ Behind the Slytherin goalposts, however, two hundred people were wearing green; the silver serpent of Slytherin glittered on their flags, and Professor Snape sat in the very front row, wearing green like everyone else, and a very grim smile. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And here are the Gryffindors!’ yelled Lee Jordan, who was acting as commentator as usual. ‘Potter, Bell, Johnson, Spinnet, Weasley, Weasley and Wood. Widely acknowledged as the best side Hogwarts has seen in a good few years –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lee’s comments were drowned by a tide of ‘boos’ from the Slytherin end. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And here come the Slytherin team, led by captain Flint. He’s made some changes in the line-up and seems to be going for size rather than skill –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">More boos from the Slytherin crowd. Harry, however, thought Lee had a point. Malfoy was easily the smallest person on the Slytherin team; the rest of them were enormous. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Captains, shake hands!’ said Madam Hooch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flint and Wood approached each other and grasped each other’s hands very tightly; it looked as though each was trying to break the other’s fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mount your brooms!’ said Madam Hooch. ‘Three … two … one …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The sound of her whistle was lost in the roar from the crowd as fourteen brooms rose into the air. Harry felt his hair fly back off his forehead; his nerves left him in the thrill of the flight; he glanced around, saw Malfoy on his tail, and sped off in search of the Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And it’s Gryffindor in possession, Alicia Spinnet of Gryffindor with the Quaffle, heading straight for the Slytherin goalposts, looking good, Alicia! Argh, no – Quaffle intercepted by Warrington, Warrington of Slytherin tearing up the pitch – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHAM! – nice Bludger work there by George Weasley, Warrington drops the Quaffle, it’s caught by – Johnson, Gryffindor back in possession, come on, Angelina – nice swerve round Montague –  <i class=\"calibre4\">duck, Angelina, that’s a Bludger! </i>– SHE </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SCORES! TEN–ZERO TO GRYFFINDOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Angelina punched the air as she soared round the end of the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>226 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">pitch; the sea of scarlet below was screaming its delight – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OUCH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Angelina was nearly thrown from her broom as Marcus Flint went smashing into her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry!’ said Flint, as the crowd below booed. ‘Sorry, didn’t see her!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Next moment, Fred Weasley had chucked his Beater’s club at the back of Flint’s head. Flint’s nose smashed into the handle of his broom and began to bleed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That will do!’ shrieked Madam Hooch, zooming between them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Penalty to Gryffindor for an unprovoked attack on their Chaser! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Penalty to Slytherin for deliberate damage to  <i class=\"calibre4\">their </i> Chaser!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come off it, Miss!’ howled Fred, but Madam Hooch blew her whistle and Alicia flew forward to take the penalty. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Alicia!’ yelled Lee into the silence that had descended on the crowd. ‘YES! SHE’S BEATEN THE KEEPER! TWENTY–</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ZERO TO GRYFFINDOR!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned the Firebolt sharply to watch Flint, still bleeding freely, fly forwards to take the Slytherin penalty. Wood was hover-ing in front of the Gryffindor goalposts, his jaw clenched. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ ’Course, Wood’s a superb Keeper!’ Lee Jordan told the crowd, as Flint waited for Madam Hooch’s whistle. ‘Superb! Very difficult to pass – very difficult indeed – YES! I DON’T BELIEVE IT! HE’S </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">SAVED IT!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Relieved, Harry zoomed away, gazing around for the Snitch, but still making sure he caught every word of Lee’s commentary. It was essential that he hold Malfoy off the Snitch until Gryffindor was more than fifty points up … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gryffindor in possession, no, Slytherin in possession – no! – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Gryffindor back in possession and it’s Katie Bell, Katie Bell for Gryffindor with the Quaffle, she’s streaking up the pitch – THAT </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WAS DELIBERATE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Montague, a Slytherin Chaser, had swerved in front of Katie, and instead of seizing the Quaffle, had grabbed her head. Katie cartwheeled in the air, managed to stay on her broom but dropped the Quaffle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch’s whistle rang out again as she soared over to Montague and began shouting at him. A minute later, Katie had put another penalty past the Slytherin Keeper. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THIRTY–ZERO! TAKE THAT, YOU DIRTY, CHEATING –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 227 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Jordan, if you can’t commentate in an unbiased way –!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m telling it like it is, Professor!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt a huge jolt of excitement. He had seen the Snitch – it was shimmering at the foot of one of the Gryffindor goalposts – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">but he mustn’t catch it yet. And if Malfoy saw it … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Faking a look of sudden concentration, Harry pulled his Firebolt round and sped off towards the Slytherin end. It worked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy went haring after him, clearly thinking Harry had seen the Snitch there … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHOOSH. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">One of the Bludgers came streaking past Harry’s right ear, hit by the gigantic Slytherin Beater, Derrick. Next moment – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">WHOOSH. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The second Bludger had grazed Harry’s elbow. The other Beater, Bole, was closing in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had a fleeting glimpse of Bole and Derrick zooming towards him, clubs raised – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned the Firebolt upwards at the last second, and Bole and Derrick collided with a sickening crunch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha haaa!’ yelled Lee Jordan, as the Slytherin Beaters lurched away from each other, clutching their heads. ‘Too bad, boys! You’ll need to get up earlier than that to beat a Firebolt! And it’s Gryffindor in possession again, as Johnson takes the Quaffle – Flint alongside her – poke him in the eye, Angelina! – it was a joke, Professor, it was a joke – oh, no – Flint in possession, Flint flying towards the Gryffindor goalposts, come on, now, Wood, save –!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Flint had scored; there was an eruption of cheers from the Slytherin end and Lee swore so badly that Professor McGonagall tried to tug the magical megaphone away from him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorry, Professor, sorry! Won’t happen again! So, Gryffindor in the lead, thirty points to ten, and Gryffindor in possession –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was turning into the dirtiest match Harry had ever played in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Enraged that Gryffindor had taken such an early lead, the Slytherins were rapidly resorting to any means to take the Quaffle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Bole hit Alicia with his club and tried to say he’d thought she was a Bludger. George Weasley elbowed Bole in the face in retaliation. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch awarded both teams penalties, and Wood pulled off another spectacular save, making the score forty–ten to Gryffindor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Snitch had disappeared again. Malfoy was still keeping </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>228 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">close to Harry as he soared over the match, looking around for it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">once Gryffindor were fifty points ahead … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Katie scored. Fifty–ten. Fred and George Weasley were swooping around her, clubs raised, in case any of the Slytherins were thinking of revenge. Bole and Derrick took advantage of Fred and George’s absence to aim both Bludgers at Wood; they caught him in the stomach, one after the other, and he rolled over in the air, clutching his broom, completely winded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch was beside herself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">You do not attack the Keeper unless the Quaffle is within the scoring area! </i>’ she shrieked at Bole and Derrick. ‘Gryffindor penalty!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Angelina scored. Sixty–ten. Moments later, Fred Weasley pelted a Bludger at Warrington, knocking the Quaffle out of his hands; Alicia seized it and put it through the Slytherin goal: seventy–ten. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Gryffindor crowd below were screaming themselves hoarse </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– Gryffindor were sixty points in the lead, and if Harry caught the Snitch now, the Cup was theirs. Harry could almost feel hundreds of eyes following him as he soared around the pitch, high above the rest of the game, with Malfoy speeding along behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then he saw it. The Snitch was sparkling twenty feet above him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry put on a huge burst of speed, the wind roaring in his ears; he stretched out his hand, but suddenly, the Firebolt was slowing down – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Horrified, he looked around. Malfoy had thrown himself forward, grabbed hold of the Firebolt’s tail and was pulling it back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was angry enough to hit Malfoy, but he couldn’t reach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy was panting with the effort of holding onto the Firebolt, but his eyes were sparkling maliciously. He had achieved what he’d wanted – the Snitch had disappeared again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Penalty! Penalty to Gryffindor! I’ve never seen such tactics!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Hooch screeched, shooting up to where Malfoy was sliding back onto his Nimbus Two Thousand and One. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YOU CHEATING SCUM!’ Lee Jordan was howling into the megaphone, dancing out of Professor McGonagall’s reach. ‘YOU </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">FILTHY, CHEATING B–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor McGonagall didn’t even bother to tell him off. She was actually shaking her fist in Malfoy’s direction; her hat had </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Quidditch Final 229 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">fallen off, and she, too, was shouting furiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Alicia took Gryffindor’s penalty, but she was so angry she missed by several feet. The Gryffindor team was losing concentration and the Slytherins, delighted by Malfoy’s foul on Harry, were being spurred on to greater heights. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Slytherin in possession, Slytherin heading for goal – Montague scores –’ Lee groaned. ‘Seventy–twenty to Gryffindor …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was now marking Malfoy so closely their knees kept hitting each other. Harry wasn’t going to let Malfoy anywhere near the Snitch … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of it, Potter!’ Malfoy yelled in frustration, as he tried to turn and found Harry blocking him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Angelina Johnson gets the Quaffle for Gryffindor, come on, Angelina, COME ON!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked round. Every single Slytherin player apart from Malfoy, even the Slytherin Keeper, was streaking up the pitch towards Angelina – they were all going to block her – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wheeled the Firebolt about, bent so low he was lying flat along the handle and kicked it forwards. Like a bullet, he shot towards the Slytherins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AAAAAAARRRGH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They scattered as the Firebolt zoomed towards them; Angelina’s way was clear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SHE SCORES! SHE SCORES! Gryffindor lead by eighty points to twenty!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, who had almost pelted headlong into the stands, skidded to a halt in mid-air, reversed and zoomed back into the middle of the pitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then he saw something to make his heart stand still. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy was diving, a look of triumph on his face – there, a few feet above the grass below, was a tiny, golden glimmer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry urged the Firebolt downwards but Malfoy was miles ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go! Go! Go!’ Harry urged his broom. They were gaining on Malfoy … Harry flattened himself to the broom handle as Bole sent a Bludger at him … he was at Malfoy’s ankles … he was level – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry threw himself forwards, taking both hands off his broom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He knocked Malfoy’s arm out of the way and – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YES!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pulled out of his dive, his hand in the air, and the stadium </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>230 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">exploded. Harry soared above the crowd, an odd ringing in his ears. The tiny golden ball was held tight in his fist, beating its wings hopelessly against his fingers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Wood was speeding towards him, half-blinded by tears; he seized Harry around the neck and sobbed unrestrainedly into his shoulder. Harry felt two large thumps as Fred and George hit them; then Angelina, Alicia and Katie’s voices, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">We’ve won the Cup! </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">We’ve won the Cup! </i>’ Tangled together in a many-armed hug, the Gryffindor team sank, yelling hoarsely, back to earth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wave upon wave of crimson supporters was pouring over the barriers onto the pitch. Hands were raining down on their backs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had a confused impression of noise and bodies pressing in on him. Then he, and the rest of the team, were hoisted onto the shoulders of the crowd. Thrust into the light, he saw Hagrid, plastered with crimson rosettes – ‘Yeh beat ’em, Harry, yeh beat ’em! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wait till I tell Buckbeak!’ There was Percy, jumping up and down like a maniac, all dignity forgotten. Professor McGonagall was sobbing harder even than Wood, wiping her eyes with an enormous Gryffindor flag; and there, fighting their way towards Harry, were Ron and Hermione. Words failed them. They simply beamed, as Harry was borne towards the stands, where Dumbledore stood waiting with the enormous Quidditch Cup. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">If only there had been a Dementor around … As a sobbing Wood passed Harry the Cup, as he lifted it into the air, Harry felt he could have produced the world’s best Patronus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SIXTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Professor Trelawney’s </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prediction </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000003999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s euphoria at finally winning the Quidditch Cup lasted at least a week. Even the weather seemed to be celebrating; as June approached, the days became cloudless and sultry, and all anybody felt like doing was strolling into the grounds and flopping down on the grass with several pints of iced pumpkin juice, perhaps playing a casual game of Gobstones or watching the giant squid propel itself dreamily across the surface of the lake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But they couldn’t. The exams were nearly upon them, and instead of lazing around outside, the students were forced to remain inside the castle, trying to bully their brains into concentrating while enticing wafts of summer air drifted in through the windows. Even Fred and George Weasley had been spotted working; they were about to take their O.W.Ls (Ordinary Wizarding Levels). Percy was getting ready to sit his N.E.W.Ts (Nastily Exhausting Wizarding Tests), the highest qualification Hogwarts offered. As Percy hoped to enter the Ministry of Magic, he needed top grades. He was becoming increasingly edgy, and gave very severe punishments to anybody who disturbed the quiet of the common room in the evenings. In fact, the only person who seemed more anxious than Percy was Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron had given up asking her how she was managing to attend several classes at once, but they couldn’t restrain themselves when they saw the exam timetable she had drawn up for herself. The first column read: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">MONDAY </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">9 o’clock, Arithmancy </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">9 o’clock, Transfiguration </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>232 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lunch </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">1 o’clock, Charms </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">1 o’clock, Ancient Runes </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione?’ Ron said cautiously, because she was liable to explode when interrupted these days. ‘Er – are you sure you’ve copied down these times right?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ snapped Hermione, picking up the exam timetable and examining it. ‘Yes, of course I have.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is there any point asking how you’re going to sit two exams at once?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Hermione shortly. ‘Has either of you seen my copy of <i class=\"calibre4\">Numerology and Grammatica? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yeah, I borrowed it for a bit of bedtime reading,’ said Ron, but very quietly. Hermione started shifting heaps of parchment around on her table, looking for the book. Just then, there was a rustle at the window and Hedwig fluttered through it, a note clutched tightly in her beak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s from Hagrid,’ said Harry, ripping the note open. ‘Buckbeak’s appeal – it’s set for the sixth.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s the day we finish our exams,’ said Hermione, still looking everywhere for her Arithmancy book. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And they’re coming up here to do it,’ said Harry, still reading from the letter. ‘Someone from the Ministry of Magic and – and an executioner.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked up, startled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re bringing the executioner to the appeal! But that sounds as though they’ve already decided!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, it does,’ said Harry slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They can’t!’ Ron howled. ‘I’ve spent  <i class=\"calibre4\">ages</i> reading up stuff for him, they can’t just ignore it all!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry had a horrible feeling that the Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures had had its mind made up for it by Mr Malfoy. Draco, who had been noticeably subdued since Gryffindor’s triumph in the Quidditch final, seemed to regain some of his old swagger over the next few days. From sneering comments Harry overheard, Malfoy was certain Buckbeak was going to be killed, and seemed thoroughly pleased with himself for bringing it about. It was all Harry could do to stop himself imitating Hermione and hitting Malfoy in the face on these </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 233 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">occasions. And the worst thing of all was that they had no time or opportunity to go and see Hagrid, because the strict new security measures had not been lifted, and Harry didn’t dare retrieve his Invisibility Cloak from below the one-eyed witch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Exam week began and an unnatural hush fell over the castle. The third-years emerged from Transfiguration at lunch-time on Monday limp and ashen-faced, comparing results and bemoaning the difficulty of the tasks they had been set, which had included turning a teapot into a tortoise. Hermione irritated the rest by fussing about how her tortoise had looked more like a turtle, which was the least of everyone else’s worries. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Mine still had a spout for a tail, what a nightmare …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Were the tortoises  <i class=\"calibre4\">supposed </i> to breathe steam?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It still had a willow-patterned shell, d’you think that’ll count against me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, after a hasty lunch, it was straight back upstairs for the Charms exam. Hermione had been right; Professor Flitwick did indeed  test  them  on  Cheering  Charms.  Harry  slightly  overdid  his out of nerves and Ron, who was partnering him, ended up in fits of hysterical laughter and had to be led away to a quiet room for an hour before he was ready to perform the Charm himself. After dinner, the students hurried back to their common rooms, not to relax, but to start revising for Care of Magical Creatures, Potions and Astronomy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid presided over the Care of Magical Creatures exam the following morning with a very preoccupied air indeed; his heart didn’t seem to be in it at all. He had provided a large tub of fresh Flobberworms for the class, and told them that, to pass the test, their Flobberworm had to still be alive at the end of one hour. As Flobberworms flourished best if left to their own devices, it was the easiest exam any of them had ever sat, and also gave Harry, Ron and Hermione plenty of opportunity to speak to Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Beaky’s gettin’ a bit depressed,’ Hagrid told them, bending low on the pretence of checking that Harry’s Flobberworm was still alive. ‘Bin cooped up too long. But still … we’ll know day after tomorrow – one way or the other.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had Potions that afternoon, which was an unqualified dis-aster. Try as Harry might, he couldn’t get his Confusing Concoction to thicken, and Snape, standing watching with an air </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>234 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">of vindictive pleasure, scribbled something that looked suspiciously like a zero onto his notes before moving away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then came Astronomy at midnight, up on the tallest tower; History of Magic on Wednesday morning, in which Harry scribbled everything Florean Fortescue had ever told him about medieval witch hunts, while wishing he could have had one of Fortescue’s choco-nut sundaes with him in the stifling classroom. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wednesday afternoon meant Herbology, in the greenhouses under a baking hot sun; then back to the common room once more, with the backs of their necks sunburnt, thinking longingly of this time next day, when it would all be over. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Their second from last exam, on Thursday morning, was Defence Against the Dark Arts. Professor Lupin had compiled the most unusual exam any of them had ever taken; a sort of obstacle course outside in the sun, where they had to wade across a deep paddling pool containing a Grindylow, cross a series of potholes full of Red Caps, squish their way across a patch of marsh, ignoring the misleading directions from a Hinkypunk, then climb into an old trunk and battle with a new Boggart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Excellent, Harry,’ Lupin muttered, as Harry climbed out of the trunk, grinning. ‘Full marks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Flushed with his success, Harry hung around to watch Ron and Hermione. Ron did very well until he reached the Hinkypunk, which successfully confused him into sinking waist-high into the quagmire. Hermione did everything perfectly until she reached the trunk with the Boggart in it. After about a minute inside it, she burst out again, screaming. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione!’ said Lupin, startled. ‘What’s the matter?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘P-P-Professor McGonagall!’ Hermione gasped, pointing into the trunk. ‘Sh-she said I’d failed everything!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a little while to calm Hermione down. When at last she had regained a grip on herself, she, Harry and Ron went back to the castle. Ron was still slightly inclined to laugh at Hermione’s Boggart, but an argument was averted by the sight that met them on the top of the steps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cornelius Fudge, sweating slightly in his pinstriped cloak, was standing there staring out at the grounds. He started at the sight of Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hello there, Harry!’ he said. ‘Just had an exam, I expect? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nearly finished?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 235 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry. Hermione and Ron, not being on speaking terms with the Minister for Magic, hovered awkwardly in the background. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lovely day,’ said Fudge, casting an eye over the lake. ‘Pity … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">pity …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He sighed deeply and looked down at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m here on an unpleasant mission, Harry. The Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures required a witness to the execution of a mad Hippogriff. As I needed to visit Hogwarts to check on the Black situation, I was asked to step in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Does that mean the appeal’s already happened?’ Ron interrupted, stepping forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, no, it’s scheduled for this afternoon,’ said Fudge, looking curiously at Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then you might not have to witness an execution at all!’ said Ron stoutly. ‘The Hippogriff might get off!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before Fudge could answer, two wizards came through the castle doors behind him. One was so ancient he appeared to be with-ering before their very eyes; the other was tall and strapping, with a thin black moustache. Harry gathered that they were representatives of the Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous Creatures, because the very old wizard squinted towards Hagrid’s cabin and said in a feeble voice, ‘Dear, dear, I’m getting too old for this … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">two o’clock, isn’t it, Fudge?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The black-moustached man was fingering something in his belt; Harry looked and saw that he was running one broad thumb along the blade of a shining axe. Ron opened his mouth to say something, but Hermione nudged him hard in the ribs and jerked her head towards the Entrance Hall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why’d you stop me?’ said Ron angrily, as they entered the Great Hall for lunch. ‘Did you see them? They’ve even got the axe ready! This isn’t justice!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, your dad works for the Ministry. You can’t go saying things like that to his boss!’ said Hermione, but she, too, looked very upset. ‘As long as Hagrid keeps his head this time, and argues his case properly, they can’t possibly execute Buckbeak …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry could tell Hermione didn’t really believe what she was saying. All around them, people were talking excitedly as they ate their lunch, happily anticipating the end of exams that afternoon, but Harry, Ron and Hermione, lost in worry about </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>236 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid and Buckbeak, didn’t join in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Ron’s last exam was Divination; Hermione’s, Muggle Studies. They walked up the marble staircase together. Hermione left them on the first floor and Harry and Ron proceeded all the way up to the seventh, where many of their class were sitting on the spiral staircase to Professor Trelawney’s classroom, trying to cram in a bit of last-minute revision. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She’s seeing us all separately,’ Neville informed them, as they went to sit down next to him. He had his copy of  <i class=\"calibre4\">Unfogging the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Future</i> open on his lap at the pages devoted to crystal-gazing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Have either of you ever seen  <i class=\"calibre4\">anything </i> in a crystal ball?’ he asked them unhappily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nope,’ said Ron, in an offhand voice. He kept checking his watch; Harry knew that he was counting down the time until Buckbeak’s appeal started. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The queue of people outside the classroom shortened very slowly. As each person climbed back down the silver ladder, the rest of the class hissed, ‘What did she ask? Was it OK?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But they all refused to say. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She says the crystal ball’s told her that, if I tell you, I’ll have a horrible accident!’ squeaked Neville, as he clambered back down the ladder towards Harry and Ron, who had now reached the landing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s convenient,’ snorted Ron. ‘You know, I’m starting to think Hermione was right about her’ (he jabbed his thumb towards the trapdoor overhead), ‘she’s a right old fraud.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah,’ said Harry, looking at his own watch. It was now two o’clock. ‘Wish she’d hurry up …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Parvati came back down the ladder glowing with pride. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She says I’ve got all the makings of a true Seer,’ she informed Harry and Ron. ‘I saw  <i class=\"calibre4\">loads</i> of stuff … well, good luck!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She hurried off down the spiral staircase towards Lavender. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ronald Weasley,’ said the familiar, misty voice from over their heads. Ron grimaced at Harry, and climbed the silver ladder out of sight. Harry was now the only person left to be tested. He settled himself on the floor with his back against the wall, listening to a fly buzzing in the sunny window, his mind across the grounds with Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Finally, after about twenty minutes, Ron’s large feet reappeared on the ladder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 237 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’d it go?’ Harry asked him, standing up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Rubbish,’ said Ron. ‘Couldn’t see a thing, so I made some stuff up. Don’t think she was convinced, though …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Meet you in the common room,’ Harry muttered, as Professor Trelawney’s voice called, ‘Harry Potter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The tower room was hotter than ever before; the curtains were closed, the fire was alight, and the usual sickly scent made Harry cough as he stumbled through the clutter of chairs and tables to where Professor Trelawney sat waiting for him before a large crystal ball. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good day, my dear,’ she said softly. ‘If you would kindly gaze into the Orb … take your time, now … then tell me what you see within it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry bent over the crystal ball and stared, stared as hard as he could, willing it to show him something other than swirling white fog, but nothing happened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well?’ Professor Trelawney prompted delicately. ‘What do you see?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The heat was overpowering and his nostrils were stinging with the perfumed smoke wafting from the fire beside them. He thought of what Ron had just said, and decided to pretend. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er –,’ said Harry, ‘a dark shape … um …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What does it resemble?’ whispered Professor Trelawney. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Think, now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry cast his mind around and it landed on Buckbeak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A Hippogriff,’ he said firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed!’ whispered Professor Trelawney, scribbling keenly on the parchment perched upon her knees. ‘My boy, you may well be seeing the outcome of poor Hagrid’s trouble with the Ministry of Magic! Look closer … does the Hippogriff appear to … have its head?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Harry firmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you sure?’ Professor Trelawney urged him. ‘Are you quite sure, dear? You don’t see it writhing on the ground, perhaps, and a shadowy figure raising an axe behind it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Harry, starting to feel slightly sick. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No blood? No weeping Hagrid?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Harry again, wanting more than ever to leave the room and the heat. ‘It looks fine, it’s – flying away …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney sighed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>238 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, dear, I think we’ll leave it there … a little disappointing … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">but I’m sure you did your best.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Relieved, Harry got up, picked up his bag and turned to go, but then a loud, harsh voice spoke behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">It will happen tonight. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry wheeled around. Professor Trelawney had gone rigid in her armchair; her eyes were unfocused and her mouth sagging. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘S-sorry?’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Professor Trelawney didn’t seem to hear him. Her eyes started to roll. Harry stood there in a panic. She looked as though she was about to have some sort of seizure. He hesitated, thinking of running to the hospital wing – and then Professor Trelawney spoke again, in the same harsh voice, quite unlike her own: </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">The Dark Lord lies alone and friendless, abandoned by his follow-ers. His servant has been chained these twelve years. Tonight, before</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">midnight, the servant will break free and set out to rejoin his master. </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Dark Lord will rise again with his servant’s aid, greater and more</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">terrible than ever before. Tonight … before midnight … the servant … </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">will set out … to rejoin … his master …</i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s head fell forwards onto her chest. She made a grunting sort of noise. Then, quite suddenly, her head snapped up again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m so sorry, dear boy,’ she said dreamily. ‘The heat of the day, you know … I drifted off for a moment …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood there, still staring. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Is there anything wrong, my dear?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You – you just told me that the – the Dark Lord’s going to rise again … that his servant’s going to go back to him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney looked thoroughly startled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The  Dark  Lord?  He  Who  Must  Not  Be  Named?  My  dear  boy, that’s hardly something to joke about … rise again, indeed …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you just said it! You said the Dark Lord –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think you must have dozed off too, dear!’ said Professor Trelawney. ‘I would certainly not presume to predict anything quite as far-fetched as  <i class=\"calibre4\">that! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry climbed back down the ladder and the spiral staircase, wondering … had he just heard Professor Trelawney make a real prediction? Or had that been her idea of an impressive end to the test? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Five minutes later he was dashing past the security trolls </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 239 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">outside the entrance to Gryffindor Tower, Professor Trelawney’s words still resounding in his head. People were striding past him in the opposite direction, laughing and joking, heading for the grounds and a bit of long-awaited freedom; by the time he had reached the portrait hole and entered the common room, it was almost deserted. Over in a corner, however, sat Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Trelawney,’ Harry panted, ‘just told me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he stopped abruptly at the sight of their faces. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Buckbeak lost,’ said Ron weakly. ‘Hagrid’s just sent this.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s note was dry this time, no tears had splattered it, yet his hand seemed to have shaken so much as he wrote that it was hardly legible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Lost appeal. They’re going to execute at sunset. Nothing you</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">can do. Don’t come down. I don’t want you to see it. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hagrid</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got to go,’ said Harry at once. ‘He can’t just sit there on his own, waiting for the executioner!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sunset, though,’ said Ron, who was staring out of the window in a glazed sort of way. ‘We’d never be allowed … specially you, Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sank his head into his hands, thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If we only had the Invisibility Cloak …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is it?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry told her about leaving it in the passageway under the one-eyed witch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… if Snape sees me anywhere near there again, I’m in serious trouble,’ he finished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s true,’ said Hermione, getting to her feet. ‘If he sees  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">how do you open the witch’s hump again?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You – you tap it and say, “Dissendium”,’ said Harry. ‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione didn’t wait for the rest of his sentence; she strode across the room, pushed the Fat Lady’s portrait open and vanished from sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘She hasn’t gone to get it?’ Ron said, staring after her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She had. Hermione returned a quarter of an hour later with the silvery Cloak folded carefully under her robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, I don’t know what’s got into you lately!’ said Ron, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>240 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">astounded. ‘First you hit Malfoy, then you walk out on Professor Trelawney –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked rather flattered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They went down to dinner with everybody else, but did not return to Gryffindor Tower afterwards. Harry had the Cloak hidden down the front of his robes; he had to keep his arms folded to hide the lump. They skulked in an empty chamber off the Entrance Hall, listening, until they were sure it was deserted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard a last pair of people hurrying across the Hall, and a door slamming. Hermione poked her head around the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ she whispered, ‘no one there – Cloak on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Walking very close together so that nobody would see them, they crossed the Hall on tiptoe beneath the Cloak, then walked down the stone front steps into the grounds. The sun was already sinking behind the Forbidden Forest, gilding the top branches of the trees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached Hagrid’s cabin and knocked. He was a minute in answering, and when he did, he looked all around for his visitor, pale-faced and trembling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s us,’ Harry hissed. ‘We’re wearing the Invisibility Cloak. Let us in and we can take it off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh shouldn’ve come!’ Hagrid whispered, but he stood back, and they stepped inside. Hagrid shut the door quickly and Harry pulled off the Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid was not crying, nor did he throw himself upon their necks. He looked like a man who did not know where he was or what to do. This helplessness was worse to watch than tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wan’ some tea?’ he said. His great hands were shaking as he reached for the kettle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Buckbeak, Hagrid?’ said Hermione hesitantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I – I took him outside,’ said Hagrid, spilling milk all over the table as he filled up the jug. ‘He’s tethered in me pumpkin patch. Thought he oughta see the trees an’ – an’ smell fresh air – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">before –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s hand trembled so violently that the milk jug slipped from his grasp and shattered all over the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll do it, Hagrid,’ said Hermione quickly, hurrying over and starting to clean up the mess. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s another one in the cupboard,’ Hagrid said, sitting down </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 241 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and wiping his forehead on his sleeve. Harry glanced at Ron, who looked back hopelessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Isn’t there anything anyone can do, Hagrid?’ Harry asked fiercely, sitting down next to him. ‘Dumbledore –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s tried,’ said Hagrid. ‘He’s got no power ter overrule the Committee. He told ’em Buckbeak’s all right, but they’re scared … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">yeh know what Lucius Malfoy’s like … threatened ’em, I expect … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">an’ the executioner, Macnair, he’s an old pal o’ Malfoy’s … but it’ll be quick an’ clean … an’ I’ll be beside him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid swallowed. His eyes were darting all over the cabin, as though looking for some shred of hope or comfort. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore’s gonna come down while it – while it happens. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wrote me this mornin’. Said he wants ter – ter be with me. Great man, Dumbledore …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione, who had been rummaging in Hagrid’s cupboard for another milk jug, let out a small, quickly stifled sob. She straightened up with the new jug in her hands, fighting back tears. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll stay with you, too, Hagrid,’ she began, but Hagrid shook his shaggy head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh’re ter go back up ter the castle. I told yeh, I don’ wan’ yeh watchin’. An’ yeh shouldn’ be down here anyway … if Fudge an’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore catch yeh out without permission, Harry, yeh’ll be in big trouble.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silent tears were now streaming down Hermione’s face, but she hid them from Hagrid, bustling around making tea. Then, as she picked up the milk bottle to pour some into the jug, she let out a shriek. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron! I – I don’t believe it – it’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">Scabbers! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gaped at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you talking about?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione carried the milk jug over to the table and turned it upside-down. With a frantic squeak, and much scrambling to get back inside, Scabbers the rat came sliding out onto the table. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers!’ said Ron blankly. ‘Scabbers, what are you doing here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He grabbed the struggling rat and held him up to the light. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scabbers looked dreadful. He was thinner than ever, large tufts of hair had fallen out leaving wide bald patches, and he writhed in Ron’s hands as though desperate to free himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK, Scabbers!’ said Ron. ‘No cats! There’s nothing here to hurt you!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>242 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid suddenly stood up, his eyes fixed on the window. His normally ruddy face had gone the colour of parchment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’re comin’ …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry, Ron and Hermione whipped around. A group of men was walking down the distant castle steps. In front was Albus Dumbledore, his silver beard gleaming in the dying sun. Next to him trotted Cornelius Fudge. Behind them came the feeble old Committee member and the executioner, Macnair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh gotta go,’ said Hagrid. Every inch of him was trembling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They mustn’ find yeh here … go on, now …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stuffed Scabbers into his pocket and Hermione picked up the Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll let yeh out the back way,’ said Hagrid. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They followed him to the door into his back garden. Harry felt strangely unreal, and even more so when he saw Buckbeak a few yards away, tethered to a tree behind Hagrid’s pumpkin patch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak seemed to know something was happening. He turned his sharp head from side to side, and pawed the ground nervously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK, Beaky,’ said Hagrid softly. ‘It’s OK …’ He turned to Harry, Ron and Hermione. ‘Go on,’ he said. ‘Get goin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But they didn’t move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, we can’t –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll tell them what really happened –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They can’t kill him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go!’ said Hagrid fiercely. ‘It’s bad enough without you lot in trouble an’ all!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had no choice. As Hermione threw the Cloak over Harry and Ron, they heard voices at the front of the cabin. Hagrid looked at the place where they had just vanished from sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go quick,’ he said hoarsely. ‘Don’ listen …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And he strode back into his cabin as someone knocked at the front door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Slowly, in a kind of horrified trance, Harry, Ron and Hermione set off silently around Hagrid’s house. As they reached the other side, the front door closed with a sharp snap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Please, let’s hurry,’ Hermione whispered. ‘I can’t stand it, I can’t bear it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They started up the sloping lawn towards the castle. The sun was sinking fast now; the sky had turned to a clear, purple-tinged grey, but to the west there was a ruby-red glow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney’s Prediction 243 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron stopped dead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, please, Ron,’ Hermione began. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s Scabbers – he won’t – stay put –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was bent over, trying to keep Scabbers in his pocket, but the rat was going berserk; squeaking madly, twisting and flailing, trying to sink his teeth into Ron’s hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers, it’s me, you idiot, it’s Ron,’ Ron hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They heard a door open behind them and men’s voices. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh Ron, please let’s move, they’re going to do it!’ Hermione breathed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK – Scabbers, stay  <i class=\"calibre4\">put</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They walked forwards; Harry, like Hermione, was trying not to listen to the rumble of voices behind them. Ron stopped again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I can’t hold him – Scabbers, shut up, everyone’ll hear us –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The rat was squealing wildly, but not loudly enough to cover up the sounds drifting from Hagrid’s garden. There was a jumble of indistinct male voices, a silence and then, without warning, the unmistakeable swish and thud of an axe. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione swayed on the spot. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They did it!’ she whispered to Harry. ‘I d-don’t believe it – they did it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER SEVENTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Cat, Rat and Dog </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s mind had gone blank with shock. The three of them stood transfixed with horror under the Invisibility Cloak. The very last rays of the setting sun were casting a bloody light over the long-shadowed grounds. Then, behind them, they heard a wild howling. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid,’ Harry muttered. Without thinking about what he was doing, he made to turn back, but both Ron and Hermione seized his arms. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can’t,’ said Ron, who was paper white. ‘He’ll be in worse trouble if they know we’ve been to see him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s breathing was shallow and uneven. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How – could – they?’ she choked. ‘How  <i class=\"calibre4\">could </i> they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on,’ said Ron, whose teeth seemed to be chattering. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They set off back towards the castle, walking slowly to keep themselves hidden under the Cloak. Light was fading fast now. By the time they reached open ground, darkness was settling like a spell around them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers, keep still,’ Ron hissed, clamping his hand over his chest. The rat was wriggling madly. Ron came to a sudden halt, trying to force Scabbers deeper into his pocket. ‘What’s the matter with you, you stupid rat? Stay still – OUCH! He bit me!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron, be quiet!’ Hermione whispered urgently. ‘Fudge’ll be out here in a minute –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He won’t – stay – put –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Scabbers was plainly terrified. He was writhing with all his might, trying to break free of Ron’s grip. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s the  <i class=\"calibre4\">matter</i> with him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry had just seen – slinking towards them, his body low to the ground, wide yellow eyes glinting eerily in the darkness – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks. Whether he could see them, or was following the sound of Scabbers’s squeaks, Harry couldn’t tell. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 245 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crookshanks!’ Hermione moaned. ‘No, go away, Crookshanks! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Go away!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the cat was getting nearer – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Scabbers – NO!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Too late – the rat had slipped between Ron’s clutching fingers, hit the ground and scampered away. In one bound, Crookshanks sprang after him, and before Harry or Hermione could stop him, Ron had thrown the Invisibility Cloak off himself and pelted away into the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ron! </i>’ Hermione moaned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She and Harry looked at each other, then followed at a sprint; it was impossible to run full out under the Cloak; they pulled it off and it streamed behind them like a banner as they hurtled after Ron; they could hear his feet thundering along ahead, and his shouts at Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get away from him – get away – Scabbers, come  <i class=\"calibre4\">here </i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a loud thud. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Gotcha! </i> Get off, you stinking cat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione almost fell over Ron; they skidded to a stop right in front of him. He was sprawled on the ground, but Scabbers was back in his pocket; he had both hands held tight over the quivering lump. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron – come on – back under the Cloak –’ Hermione panted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore – the Minister – they’ll be coming back out in a minute –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But before they could cover themselves again, before they could even catch their breath, they heard the soft pounding of gigantic paws. Something was bounding towards them out of the dark – an enormous, pale-eyed, jet-black dog. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry reached for his wand, but too late – the dog had made an enormous leap and its front paws hit him on the chest. He keeled over backwards in a whirl of hair; he felt its hot breath, saw inch-long teeth – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But the force of its leap had carried it too far; it rolled off him; dazed, feeling as though his ribs were broken, Harry tried to stand up; he could hear it growling as it skidded around for a new attack. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was on his feet. As the dog sprang back towards them, he pushed Harry aside; the dog’s jaws fastened instead around Ron’s outstretched arm. Harry lunged at it and seized a handful of the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>246 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">brute’s hair, but it was dragging Ron away as easily as if he were a rag-doll – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then, out of nowhere, something hit Harry so hard across the face he was knocked off his feet again. He heard Hermione shriek with pain and fall, too. Harry groped for his wand, blinking blood out of his eyes – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Lumos! </i>’ he whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The wand-light showed him the trunk of a thick tree; they had chased Scabbers into the shadow of the Whomping Willow and its branches were creaking as though in a high wind, whipping backwards and forwards to stop them going nearer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And there, at the base of the trunk, was the dog, dragging Ron backwards into a large gap in the roots – Ron was fighting furiously, but his head and torso were slipping out of sight – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron!’ Harry shouted, trying to follow, but a heavy branch whipped lethally through the air and he was forced backwards again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All they could see now was one of Ron’s legs, which he had hooked around a root in an effort to stop the dog pulling him further underground. Then a horrible crack cut the air like a gunshot; Ron’s leg had broken, and next second, his foot had vanished from sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry – we’ve got to go for help –’ Hermione cried; she was bleeding, too; the Willow had cut her across the shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No! That thing’s big enough to eat him, we haven’t got time –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re never going to get through without help –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Another branch whipped down at them, twigs clenched like knuckles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If that dog can get in, we can,’ Harry panted, darting here and there, trying to find a way through the vicious, swishing branches, but he couldn’t get an inch nearer to the tree-roots without being in range of the tree’s blows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, help, help,’ Hermione whispered frantically, dancing uncertainly on the spot, ‘please …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks darted forwards. He slithered between the batter-ing branches like a snake and placed his front paws upon a knot on the trunk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Abruptly, as though the tree had been turned to marble, it stopped moving. Not a leaf twitched or shook. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Crookshanks!’ Hermione whispered uncertainly. She now </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 247 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">grasped Harry’s arm painfully hard. ‘How did he know –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s friends with that dog,’ said Harry grimly. ‘I’ve seen them together. Come on – and keep your wand out –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They covered the distance to the trunk in seconds, but before they had reached the gap in the roots, Crookshanks had slid into it with a flick of his bottle-brush tail. Harry went next; he crawled forwards, headfirst, and slid down an earthy slope to the bottom of a very low tunnel. Crookshanks was a little way along, his eyes flashing in the light from Harry’s wand. Seconds later, Hermione slithered down beside him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s Ron?’ she whispered in a terrified voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This way,’ said Harry, setting off, bent-backed, after Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where does this tunnel come out?’ Hermione asked breathlessly from behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know … it’s marked on the Marauder’s Map but Fred and George said no one’s ever got into it. It goes off the edge of the map, but it looked like it ends up in Hogsmeade …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They moved as fast as they could, bent almost double; ahead of them, Crookshanks’s tail bobbed in and out of view. On and on went the passage; it felt at least as long as the one to Honeydukes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">All Harry could think of was Ron, and what the enormous dog might be doing to him … he was drawing breath in sharp, painful gasps, running at a crouch … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then the tunnel began to rise; moments later it twisted, and Crookshanks had gone. Instead, Harry could see a patch of dim light through a small opening. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He and Hermione paused, gasping for breath, edging forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both raised their wands to see what lay beyond. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was a room, a very disordered, dusty room. Paper was peeling from the walls; there were stains all over the floor; every piece of furniture was broken as though somebody had smashed it. The windows were all boarded-up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced at Hermione, who looked very frightened, but nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled himself out of the hole, staring around. The room was deserted, but a door to their right stood open, leading to a shadowy hallway. Hermione suddenly grabbed Harry’s arm again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Her wide eyes were travelling around the boarded windows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ she whispered. ‘I think we’re in the Shrieking Shack.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>248 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around. His eyes fell on a wooden chair near them. Large chunks had been torn out of it; one of the legs had been ripped off entirely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ghosts didn’t do that,’ he said slowly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, there was a creak overhead. Something had moved upstairs. Both of them looked up at the ceiling. Hermione’s grip on Harry’s arm was so tight he was losing feeling in his fingers. He raised his eyebrows at her; she nodded again and let go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Quietly as they could, they crept out into the hall and up the crumbling staircase. Everything was covered in a thick layer of dust except the floor, where a wide, shiny stripe had been made by something being dragged upstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They reached the dark landing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Nox</i>,’ they whispered together, and the lights at the end of their wands went out. Only one door was open. As they crept towards it, they heard movement from behind it; a low moan, and then a deep, loud purring. They exchanged a last look, a last nod. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wand held tightly before him, Harry kicked the door wide open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">On a magnificent four-poster bed with dusty hangings, lay Crookshanks, purring loudly at the sight of them. On the floor beside him, clutching his leg, which stuck out at a strange angle, was Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione dashed across to him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron – are you OK?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where’s the dog?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not a dog,’ Ron moaned. His teeth were gritted with pain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, it’s a trap –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">He’s the dog … he’s an Animagus </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron was staring over Harry’s shoulder. Harry wheeled around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a snap, the man in the shadows closed the door behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A mass of filthy, matted hair hung to his elbows. If eyes hadn’t been shining out of the deep, dark sockets, he might have been a corpse. The waxy skin was stretched so tightly over the bones of his face, it looked like a skull. His yellow teeth were bared in a grin. It was Sirius Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ he croaked, pointing Ron’s wand at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s and Hermione’s wands shot out of their hands, high in </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 249 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the air, and Black caught them. Then he took a step closer. His eyes were fixed on Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I thought you’d come and help your friend,’ he said hoarsely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His voice sounded as though he had long ago lost the habit of using it. ‘Your father would have done the same for me. Brave of you, not to run for a teacher. I’m grateful … it will make everything much easier …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The taunt about his father rang in Harry’s ears as though Black had bellowed it. A boiling hate erupted in Harry’s chest, leaving no place for fear. For the first time in his life, he wanted his wand back in his hand, not to defend himself, but to attack … to kill. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Without knowing what he was doing, he started forwards, but there was a sudden movement on either side of him and two pairs of hands grabbed him and held him back. ‘No, Harry!’ Hermione gasped in a petrified whisper; Ron, however, spoke to Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you want to kill Harry, you’ll have to kill us, too!’ he said fiercely, though the effort of standing up had drained him of still more colour, and he swayed slightly as he spoke. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something flickered in Black’s shadowed eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lie down,’ he said quietly to Ron. ‘You will damage that leg even more.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did you hear me?’ Ron said weakly, though he was clinging painfully to Harry to stay upright. ‘You’ll have to kill all three of us!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’ll only be one murder here tonight,’ said Black, and his grin widened. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why’s that?’ Harry spat, trying to wrench himself free of Ron and Hermione. ‘Didn’t care last time, did you? Didn’t mind slaughtering all those Muggles to get at Pettigrew … What’s the matter, gone soft in Azkaban?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ Hermione whimpered. ‘Be quiet!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HE KILLED MY MUM AND DAD!’ Harry roared, and with a huge effort he broke free of Hermione and Ron’s restraint and lunged forwards – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had forgotten about magic – he had forgotten that he was short and skinny and thirteen, whereas Black was a tall, full-grown man. All Harry knew was that he wanted to hurt Black as badly as he could and that he didn’t care how much he got hurt in return … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps it was the shock of Harry doing something so stupid, but Black didn’t raise the wands in time. One of Harry’s hands </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>250 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">fastened over Black’s wasted wrist, forcing the wandtips away; the knuckles of Harry’s other hand collided with the side of Black’s head and they fell, backwards, into the wall – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was screaming; Ron was yelling; there was a blinding flash as the wands in Black’s hand sent into the air a jet of sparks which missed Harry’s face by inches; Harry felt the shrunken arm under his fingers twisting madly, but he clung on, his other hand punching every part of Black it could find. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Black’s free hand had found Harry’s throat – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ he hissed. ‘I’ve waited too long –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The fingers tightened, Harry choked, his glasses askew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he saw Hermione’s foot swing out of nowhere. Black let go of Harry with a grunt of pain. Ron had thrown himself on Black’s wand hand and Harry heard a faint clatter – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He fought free of the tangle of bodies and saw his own wand rolling across the floor; he threw himself towards it but – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Argh!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks had joined the fray; both sets of front claws had sunk themselves deep into Harry’s arm; Harry threw him off, but Crookshanks now darted towards Harry’s wand – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NO YOU DON’T!’ roared Harry, and he aimed a kick at Crookshanks that made the cat leap aside, spitting; Harry snatched up his wand and turned – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way!’ he shouted at Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They didn’t need telling twice. Hermione, gasping for breath, her lip bleeding, scrambled aside, snatching up her and Ron’s wands. Ron crawled to the four-poster and collapsed onto it, panting, his white face now tinged with green, both hands clutching his broken leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black was sprawled at the bottom of the wall. His thin chest rose and fell rapidly as he watched Harry walking slowly nearer, his wand pointing straight at Black’s heart. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Going to kill me, Harry?’ he whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stopped right above him, his wand still pointing at Black’s chest, looking down at him. A livid bruise was rising around Black’s left eye and his nose was bleeding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You killed my parents,’ said Harry, his voice shaking slightly, but his wand hand quite steady. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black stared up at him out of those sunken eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t deny it,’ he said, very quietly. ‘But if you knew the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 251 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">whole story –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The whole story?’ Harry repeated, a furious pounding in his ears. ‘You sold them to Voldemort, that’s all I need to know!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve got to listen to me,’ Black said, and there was a note of urgency in his voice now. ‘You’ll regret it if you don’t … you don’t understand …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I understand a lot better than you think,’ said Harry, and his voice shook more than ever. ‘You never heard her, did you? My mum … trying to stop Voldemort killing me … and you did that … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you did it …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before either of them could say another word, something ginger streaked past Harry; Crookshanks leapt onto Black’s chest, and settled himself there, right over Black’s heart. Black blinked and looked down at the cat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get off,’ he murmured, trying to push Crookshanks off him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Crookshanks sank his claws into Black’s robes and wouldn’t shift. He turned his ugly, squashed face to Harry, and looked up at him with those great yellow eyes. To his right, Hermione gave a dry sob. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared down at Black and Crookshanks, his grip tighten-ing on the wand. So what if he had to kill the cat, too? It was in league with Black … if it was prepared to die, trying to protect Black,  that  wasn’t  Harry’s  business  …  if  Black  wanted  to  save  it, that only proved he cared more for Crookshanks than Harry’s parents … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry raised the wand. Now was the moment to do it. Now was the moment to avenge his mother and father. He was going to kill Black. He had to kill Black. This was his chance … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The seconds lengthened, and still Harry stood frozen there, wand poised, Black staring up at him, Crookshanks on his chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s ragged breathing came from the bed; Hermione was quite silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then came a new sound – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Muffled footsteps were echoing up through the floor – someone was moving downstairs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WE’RE UP HERE!’ Hermione screamed suddenly. ‘WE’RE UP </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">HERE – SIRIUS BLACK –  <i class=\"calibre4\">QUICK! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black made a startled movement that almost dislodged Crookshanks; Harry gripped his wand convulsively –  <i class=\"calibre4\">Do it now! </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said a voice in his head – but the footsteps were thundering up  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>252 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the stairs and Harry still hadn’t done it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of the room burst open in a shower of red sparks and Harry wheeled around as Professor Lupin came hurtling into the room, his face bloodless, his wand raised and ready. His eyes flickered over Ron, lying on the floor, over Hermione, cowering next to the door, to Harry, standing there with his wand covering Black, and then to Black himself, crumpled and bleeding at Harry’s feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ Lupin shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s  wand  flew  once  more  out  of  his  hand;  so  did  the  two Hermione was holding. Lupin caught them all deftly, then moved into the room, staring at Black, who still had Crookshanks lying protectively across his chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood there, feeling suddenly empty. He hadn’t done it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His nerve had failed him.  Black  was  going  to  be  handed  back  to the Dementors. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Lupin spoke, in an odd voice, a voice that shook with some suppressed emotion. ‘Where is he, Sirius?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked quickly at Lupin. He didn’t understand what Lupin meant. Who was Lupin talking about? He turned to look at Black again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s face was quite expressionless. For a few seconds, he didn’t move at all. Then, very slowly, he raised his empty hand, and pointed straight at Ron. Mystified, Harry glanced around at Ron, who looked bewildered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then …’ Lupin muttered, staring at Black so intently it seemed he was trying to read his mind, ‘… why hasn’t he shown himself before now? Unless –’ Lupin’s eyes suddenly widened, as though he was seeing something beyond Black, something none of the rest could see, ‘– unless  <i class=\"calibre4\">he</i> was the one … unless you switched … without telling me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Very slowly, his sunken gaze never leaving Lupin’s face, Black nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin,’ Harry interrupted loudly, ‘what’s going –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But he never finished the question, because what he saw made his voice die in his throat. Lupin was lowering his wand. Next moment, he had walked to Black’s side, seized his hand, pulled him to his feet so that Crookshanks fell to the floor, and embraced Black like a brother. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt as though the bottom had dropped out of his stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 253 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I DON’T BELIEVE IT!’ Hermione screamed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin let go of Black and turned to her. She had raised herself off the floor, and was pointing at Lupin, wild-eyed. ‘You – you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– you and him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, calm down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I didn’t tell anyone!’ Hermione shrieked. ‘I’ve been covering up for you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, listen to me, please!’ Lupin shouted. ‘I can explain –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could feel himself shaking, not with fear, but with a fresh wave of fury. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I trusted you,’ he shouted at Lupin, his voice wavering out of control, ‘and all the time you’ve been his friend!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re wrong,’ said Lupin. ‘I haven’t been Sirius’ friend for twelve years, but I am now … let me explain …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NO!’ Hermione screamed, ‘Harry, don’t trust him, he’s been helping Black get into the castle, he wants you dead too –  <i class=\"calibre4\">he’s a</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">werewolf! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a ringing silence. Everyone’s eyes were now on Lupin, who looked remarkably calm, though rather pale. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not at all up to your usual standard, Hermione,’ he said. ‘Only one out of three, I’m afraid. I have not been helping Sirius get into the castle and I certainly don’t want Harry dead …’ An odd shiver passed over his face. ‘But I won’t deny that I am a werewolf.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron made a valiant effort to get up again, but fell back with a whimper of pain. Lupin made towards him, looking concerned, but Ron gasped, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Get away from me, werewolf! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin stopped dead. Then, with an obvious effort, he turned to Hermione and said, ‘How long have you known?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ages,’ Hermione whispered. ‘Since I did Professor Snape’s essay …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll be delighted,’ said Lupin coolly. ‘He set that essay hoping someone would realise what my symptoms meant. Did you check the lunar chart and realise that I was always ill at the full moon? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Or did you realise that the Boggart changed into the moon when it saw me?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Both,’ Hermione said quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin forced a laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re the cleverest witch of your age I’ve ever met, Hermione.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not,’ Hermione whispered. ‘If I’d been a bit cleverer, I’d </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>254 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">have told everyone what you are!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But they already know,’ said Lupin. ‘At least, the staff do.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore hired you when he knew you were a werewolf?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron gasped. ‘Is he mad?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Some of the staff thought so,’ said Lupin. ‘He had to work very hard to convince certain teachers that I’m trustworthy –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘AND HE WAS WRONG!’ Harry yelled. ‘YOU’VE BEEN HELPING HIM ALL THE TIME!’ He was pointing at Black, who had crossed to the four-poster bed and sunk onto it, his face hidden in one shaking hand. Crookshanks leapt up beside him and stepped onto his lap, purring. Ron edged away from both of them, dragging his leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I have  <i class=\"calibre4\">not </i> been helping Sirius,’ said Lupin. ‘If you’ll give me a chance, I’ll explain. Look –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He separated Harry, Ron and Hermione’s wands and threw each back to its owner; Harry caught his, stunned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There,’ said Lupin, sticking his own wand back into his belt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re armed, we’re not. Now will you listen?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t know what to think. Was it a trick? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you haven’t been helping him,’ he said, with a furious glance at Black, ‘how did you know he was here?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The map,’ said Lupin. ‘The Marauder’s Map. I was in my office examining it –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know how to work it?’ Harry said suspiciously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course I know how to work it,’ said Lupin, waving his hand impatiently. ‘I helped write it. I’m Moony – that was my friends’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">nickname for me at school.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You  <i class=\"calibre4\">wrote</i> –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The important thing is, I was watching it carefully this evening, because I had an idea that you, Ron and Hermione might try and sneak out of the castle to visit Hagrid before his Hippogriff was executed. And I was right, wasn’t I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had started to pace up and down, looking at them. Little patches of dust rose at his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You might have been wearing your father’s old Cloak, Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How d’you know about the Cloak?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The number of times I saw James disappearing under it …’ said Lupin, waving an impatient hand again. ‘The point is, even if you’re wearing an Invisibility Cloak you show up on the Marauder’s Map. I watched you cross the grounds and enter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Cat, Rat and Dog 255 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s hut. Twenty minutes later, you left Hagrid, and set off back towards the castle. But you were now accompanied by somebody else.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry. ‘No, we weren’t!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I couldn’t believe my eyes,’ said Lupin, still pacing, and ignoring Harry’s interruption. ‘I thought the map must be malfunction-ing. How could he be with you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one was with us!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And then I saw another dot, moving fast towards you, labelled Sirius Black … I saw him collide with you, I watched as he pulled two of you into the Whomping Willow –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One of us!’ Ron said angrily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Ron,’ said Lupin. ‘Two of you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had stopped his pacing, his eyes moving over Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you think I could have a look at the rat?’ he said evenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Ron. ‘What’s Scabbers got to do with it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everything,’ said Lupin. ‘Could I see him, please?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron hesitated, then put a hand inside his robes. Scabbers emerged, thrashing desperately; Ron had to seize his long bald tail to stop him escaping. Crookshanks stood up on Black’s lap and made a soft hissing noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin moved closer to Ron. He seemed to be holding his breath as he gazed intently at Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ Ron said again, holding Scabbers close to him, looking scared. ‘What’s my rat got to do with anything?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s not a rat,’ croaked Sirius Black suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you mean – of course he’s a rat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, he’s not,’ said Lupin quietly. ‘He’s a wizard.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An Animagus,’ said Black, ‘by the name of Peter Pettigrew.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER EIGHTEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Moony, Wormtail, </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Padfoot and Prongs </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a few seconds for the absurdity of this statement to sink in. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Ron voiced what Harry was thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re both mental.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ridiculous!’ said Hermione faintly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Peter Pettigrew’s dead!’ said Harry. ‘He killed him twelve years ago!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pointed at Black, whose face twitched convulsively. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I meant to,’ he growled, his yellow teeth bared, ‘but little Peter got the better of me … not this time, though!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Crookshanks was thrown to the floor as Black lunged at Scabbers; Ron yelled with pain as Black’s weight fell on his broken leg. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius, NO!’ Lupin yelled, launching himself forwards and dragging Black away from Ron again, ‘WAIT! You can’t do it just like that – they need to understand – we’ve got to explain –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We can explain afterwards!’ snarled Black, trying to throw Lupin off, one hand still clawing the air as it tried to reach Scabbers, who was squealing like a piglet, scratching Ron’s face and neck as he tried to escape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They’ve – got – a – right – to – know – everything!’ Lupin panted, still trying to restrain Black. ‘Ron’s kept him as a pet! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There are parts of it even I don’t understand! And Harry – you owe Harry the truth, Sirius!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black stopped struggling, though his hollowed eyes were still fixed on Scabbers, who was clamped tightly under Ron’s bitten, scratched and bleeding hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right, then,’ Black said, without taking his eyes off the rat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Tell them whatever you like. But make it quick, Remus. I want to </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs 257 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">commit the murder I was imprisoned for …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re nutters, both of you,’ said Ron shakily, looking round at Harry and Hermione for support. ‘I’ve had enough of this. I’m off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tried to heave himself up on his good leg, but Lupin raised his wand again, pointing it at Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re going to hear me out, Ron,’ he said quietly. ‘Just keep a tight hold on Peter while you listen.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HE’S NOT PETER, HE’S SCABBERS!’ Ron yelled, trying to force the rat back into his front pocket, but Scabbers was fighting too hard; Ron swayed and overbalanced, and Harry caught him and pushed him back down to the bed. Then, ignoring Black, Harry turned to Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There were witnesses who saw Pettigrew die,’ he said. ‘A whole street full of them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They didn’t see what they thought they saw!’ said Black savagely, still watching Scabbers struggling in Ron’s hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Everyone thought Sirius killed Peter,’ said Lupin, nodding. ‘I believed it myself – until I saw the map tonight. Because the Marauder’s Map never lies … Peter’s alive. Ron’s holding him, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at Ron, and as their eyes met they agreed, silently: Black and Lupin were both out of their minds. Their story made no sense whatsoever. How could Scabbers be Peter Pettigrew? Azkaban must have unhinged Black after all – but why was Lupin playing along with him? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then Hermione spoke, in a trembling, would-be calm sort of voice, as though trying to will Professor Lupin to talk sensibly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Professor Lupin … Scabbers can’t  be  Pettigrew  …  it  just can’t be true, you know it can’t …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why can’t it be true?’ Lupin said calmly, as though they were in class, and Hermione had simply spotted a problem in an experiment with Grindylows. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Because … because people would know if Peter Pettigrew had been an Animagus. We did Animagi in class with Professor McGonagall. And I looked them up when I did my homework – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the Ministry keeps tabs on witches and wizards who can become animals; there’s a register showing what animal they become, and their markings and things … and I went and looked Professor McGonagall up on the register, and there have only been seven Animagi this century, and Pettigrew’s name wasn’t on the list –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>258 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry barely had time to marvel inwardly at the effort Hermione put into her homework, when Lupin started to laugh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right again, Hermione!’ he said. ‘But the Ministry never knew that there used to be three unregistered Animagi running around Hogwarts.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you’re going to tell them the story, get a move on, Remus,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snarled Black, who was still watching Scabbers’s every desperate move. ‘I’ve waited twelve years, I’m not going to wait much longer.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All right … but you’ll need to help me, Sirius,’ said Lupin, ‘I only know how it began …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin broke off. There had been a loud creak behind him. The bedroom door had opened of its own accord. All five of them stared at it. Then Lupin strode towards it and looked out into the landing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one there …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This place is haunted!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not,’ said Lupin, still looking at the door in a puzzled way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Shrieking Shack was never haunted … the screams and howls the villagers used to hear were made by me.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He pushed his greying hair out of his eyes, thought for a moment, then said, ‘That’s where all of this starts – with my becoming a werewolf. None of this could have happened if I hadn’t been bitten … and if I hadn’t been so foolhardy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked sober and tired. Ron started to interrupt, but Hermione said, ‘Shh!’ She was watching Lupin very intently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I was a very small boy when I received the bite. My parents tried everything, but in those days there was no cure. The Potion that Professor Snape has been making for me is a very recent dis-covery. It makes me safe, you see. As long as I take it in the week preceding the full moon, I keep my mind when I transform …  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I am able to curl up in my office, a harmless wolf, and wait for the moon to wane again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Before the Wolfsbane Potion was discovered, however, I became a fully fledged monster once a month. It seemed impossible that I would be able to come to Hogwarts. Other parents weren’t likely to want their children exposed to me. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then Dumbledore became Headmaster, and he was sympathetic. He said that, as long as we took certain precautions, there was no reason I shouldn’t come to school …’ Lupin sighed, and looked  directly  at  Harry.  ‘I  told  you,  months  ago,  that  the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs 259 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Whomping Willow was planted the year I came to Hogwarts. The truth is that it was planted  <i class=\"calibre4\">because </i> I had come to Hogwarts. This house –’ Lupin looked miserably around the room, ‘– the tunnel that leads to it – they were built for my use. Once a month, I was smuggled out of the castle, into this place, to transform. The tree was placed at the tunnel mouth to stop anyone coming across me while I was dangerous.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t see where this story was going, but he was listening raptly all the same. The only sound apart from Lupin’s voice was Scabbers’s frightened squeaking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My transformations in those days were – were terrible. It is very painful to turn into a werewolf. I was separated from humans to bite, so I bit and scratched myself instead. The villagers heard the noise and the screaming and thought they were hearing particularly violent spirits. Dumbledore encouraged the rumour … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">even now, when the house has been silent for years, the villagers don’t dare approach it … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But apart from my transformations, I was happier than I had ever been in my life. For the first time ever, I had friends, three great friends. Sirius Black … Peter Pettigrew … and, of course, your father, Harry – James Potter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, my three friends could hardly fail to notice that I disappeared once a month. I made up all sorts of stories. I told them my mother was ill, and that I had to go home to see her … I was terrified they would desert me the moment they found out what I was. But of course, they, like you, Hermione, worked out the truth … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And they didn’t desert me at all. Instead they did something for me that would make my transformations not only bearable, but the best times of my life. They became Animagi.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My dad, too?’ said Harry, astounded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, indeed,’ said Lupin. ‘It took them the best part of three years to work out how to do it. Your father and Sirius here were the cleverest students in the school, and lucky they were, because the Animagus transformation can go horribly wrong – one reason the Ministry keeps a close watch on those attempting to do it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peter needed all the help he could get from James and Sirius. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Finally, in our fifth year, they managed it. They could each turn into a different animal at will.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But how did that help you?’ said Hermione, sounding puzzled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>260 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They couldn’t keep me company as humans, so they kept me company as animals,’ said Lupin. ‘A werewolf is only a danger to people. They sneaked out of the castle every month under James’s Invisibility Cloak. They transformed … Peter, as the smallest, could slip beneath the Willow’s attacking branches and touch the knot that freezes it. They would then slip down the tunnel and join me. Under their influence, I became less dangerous. My body was still wolfish, but my mind seemed to become less so while I was with them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hurry up, Remus,’ snarled Black, who was still watching Scabbers with a horrible sort of hunger in his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m getting there, Sirius, I’m getting there … well, highly exciting possibilities were open to us now we could all transform. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Soon we were leaving the Shrieking Shack and roaming the school grounds and the village by night. Sirius and James transformed into such large animals, they were able to keep a werewolf in check. I doubt whether any Hogwarts students ever found out more about the Hogwarts grounds and Hogsmeade than we did … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And that’s how we came to write the Marauder’s Map, and sign it with our nicknames. Sirius is Padfoot. Peter is Wormtail. James was Prongs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What sort of animal –?’ Harry began, but Hermione cut across him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was still really dangerous! Running around in the dark with a werewolf! What if you’d given the others the slip, and bitten somebody?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A thought that still haunts me,’ said Lupin heavily. ‘And there were near misses, many of them. We laughed about them afterwards. We were young, thoughtless – carried away with our own cleverness.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I sometimes felt guilty about betraying Dumbledore’s trust, of course … he had admitted me to Hogwarts when no other Headmaster would have done so, and he had no idea I was breaking the rules he had set down for my own and others’ safety. He never knew I had led three fellow students into becoming Animagi illegally. But I always managed to forget my guilty feelings every time we sat down to plan our next month’s adventure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And I haven’t changed …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin’s face had hardened, and there was self-disgust in his voice. ‘All this year, I have been battling with myself, wondering </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs 261 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">whether I should tell Dumbledore that Sirius was an Animagus. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But I didn’t do it. Why? Because I was too cowardly. It would have meant admitting that I’d betrayed his trust while I was at school, admitting that I’d led others along with me … and Dumbledore’s trust has meant everything to me. He let me into Hogwarts as a boy, and he gave me a job, when I have been shunned all my adult life, unable to find paid work because of what I am. And so I convinced myself that Sirius was getting into the school using Dark Arts he learnt from Voldemort, that being an Animagus had nothing to do with it … so, in a way, Snape’s been right about me all along.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Snape?’ said Black harshly, taking his eyes off Scabbers for the first time in minutes and looking up at Lupin. ‘What’s Snape got to do with it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s here, Sirius,’ said Lupin heavily. ‘He’s teaching here as well.’ He looked up at Harry, Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape was at school with us. He fought very hard against my appointment to the Defence Against the Dark Arts job. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He has been telling Dumbledore all year that I am not to be trusted. He has his reasons … you see, Sirius here played a trick on him which nearly killed him, a trick which involved me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black made a derisive noise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It served him right,’ he sneered. ‘Sneaking around, trying to find out what we were up to … hoping he could get us expelled …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Severus was very interested in where I went every month,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin told Harry, Ron and Hermione. ‘We were in the same year, you know, and we – er – didn’t like each other very much. He especially disliked James. Jealous, I think, of James’s talent on the Quidditch pitch … anyway, Snape had seen me crossing the grounds with Madam Pomfrey one evening as she led me towards the Whomping Willow to transform. Sirius thought it would be – er – amusing, to tell Snape all he had to do was prod the knot on the tree-trunk with a long stick, and he’d be able to get in after me. Well, of course, Snape tried it – if he’d got as far as this house, he’d have met a fully grown werewolf – but your father, who’d heard what Sirius had done, went after Snape and pulled him back, at great risk to his life … Snape glimpsed me, though, at the end of the tunnel. He was forbidden to tell anybody by Dumbledore, but from that time on he knew what I was …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>262 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So that’s why Snape doesn’t like you,’ said Harry slowly, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘because he thought you were in on the joke?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s right,’ sneered a cold voice from the wall behind Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Severus Snape was pulling off the Invisibility Cloak, his wand pointing directly at Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER NINETEEN — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Servant of  </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Lord Voldemort </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione screamed. Black leapt to his feet. Harry jumped as though he’d received a huge electric shock. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I found this at the base of the Whomping Willow,’ said Snape, throwing the Cloak aside, careful to keep his wand pointing directly at Lupin’s chest. ‘Very useful, Potter, I thank you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape was slightly breathless, but his face was full of suppressed triumph. ‘You’re wondering, perhaps, how I knew you were here?’ he said, his eyes glittering. ‘I’ve just been to your office, Lupin. You forgot to take your Potion tonight, so I took a gobletful along. And very lucky I did … lucky for me, I mean. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lying on your desk was a certain map. One glance at it told me all I needed to know. I saw you running along this passageway and out of sight.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Severus –’ Lupin began, but Snape overrode him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ve told the Headmaster again and again that you’ve been helping your old friend Black into the castle, Lupin, and here’s the proof. Not even I dreamed you would have the nerve to use this old place as your hideout –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Severus, you’re making a mistake,’ said Lupin urgently. ‘You haven’t heard everything – I can explain – Sirius is not here to kill Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Two more for Azkaban tonight,’ said Snape, his eyes now gleaming fanatically. ‘I shall be interested to see how Dumbledore takes this … he was quite convinced you were harmless, you know, Lupin … a  <i class=\"calibre4\">tame</i> werewolf …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You fool,’ said Lupin softly. ‘Is a schoolboy grudge worth putting an innocent man back inside Azkaban?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BANG! Thin, snake-like cords burst from the end of Snape’s </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>264 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">wand and twisted themselves around Lupin’s mouth, wrists and ankles; he overbalanced and fell to the floor, unable to move. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With a roar of rage, Black started towards Snape, but Snape pointed his wand straight between Black’s eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Give me a reason,’ he whispered. ‘Give me a reason to do it, and I swear I will.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black stopped dead. It would have been impossible to say which face showed more hatred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry  stood  there,  paralysed,  not  knowing  what  to  do  or  who to believe. He glanced around at Ron and Hermione. Ron looked just as confused as he did, still fighting to keep hold of the struggling Scabbers. Hermione, however, took an uncertain step towards Snape and said, in a very breathless voice, ‘Professor Snape – it – it wouldn’t hurt to hear what they’ve got to say, w-would it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger, you are already facing suspension from this school,’ Snape spat. ‘You, Potter and Weasley are out of bounds, in the company of a convicted murderer and a werewolf. For once in your life,  <i class=\"calibre4\">hold your tongue</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if – if there  <i class=\"calibre4\">was</i> a mistake –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘KEEP  QUIET,  YOU  STUPID  GIRL!’  Snape  shouted,  looking suddenly quite deranged. ‘DON’T TALK ABOUT WHAT YOU </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">DON’T UNDERSTAND!’ A few sparks shot out of the end of his wand, which was still pointing at Black’s face. Hermione fell silent. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Vengeance is very sweet,’ Snape breathed at Black. ‘How I hoped I would be the one to catch you …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The joke’s on you again, Severus,’ snarled Black. ‘As long as this boy brings his rat up to the castle –’ he jerked his head at Ron, ‘– I’ll come quietly …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Up to the castle?’ said Snape silkily. ‘I don’t think we need to go that far. All I have to do is call the Dementors once we get out of the Willow. They’ll be very pleased to see you, Black … pleased enough to give you a little kiss, I daresay …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">What little colour there was in Black’s face left it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You – you’ve got to hear me out,’ he croaked. ‘The rat – look at the rat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But there was a mad glint in Snape’s eye that Harry had never seen before. He seemed beyond reason. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, all of you,’ he said. He clicked his fingers, and the </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 265 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">ends of the cords that bound Lupin flew to his hands. ‘I’ll drag the werewolf. Perhaps the Dementors will have a kiss for him, too –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Before he knew what he was doing, Harry had crossed the room in three strides, and blocked the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get out of the way, Potter, you’re in enough trouble already,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">snarled Snape. ‘If I hadn’t been here to save your skin –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin could have killed me about a hundred times this year,’ Harry said. ‘I’ve been alone with him loads of times, having defence lessons against the Dementors. If he was helping Black, why didn’t he just finish me off then?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t ask me to fathom the way a werewolf’s mind works,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hissed Snape. ‘Get out of the way, Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YOU’RE PATHETIC!’ Harry yelled. ‘JUST BECAUSE THEY </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">MADE A FOOL OF YOU AT SCHOOL YOU WON’T EVEN </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">LISTEN –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘SILENCE!  I  WILL  NOT  BE  SPOKEN  TO  LIKE  THAT!’  Snape shrieked, looking madder than ever. ‘Like father, like son, Potter! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">I have just saved your neck, you should be thanking me on bend-ed knee! You would have been well served if he’d killed you! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">You’d have died like your father, too arrogant to believe you might be mistaken in Black – now get out of the way, or I will  <i class=\"calibre4\">make</i> you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">GET OUT OF THE WAY, POTTER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry made up his mind in a split second. Before Snape could take even one step towards him, he had raised his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ he yelled – except that his wasn’t the only voice that shouted. There was a blast that made the door rattle on its hinges; Snape was lifted off his feet and slammed into the wall, then slid down it to the floor, a trickle of blood oozing from under his hair. He had been knocked out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked around. Both Ron and Hermione had tried to dis-arm Snape at exactly the same moment. Snape’s wand soared in a high arc and landed on the bed next to Crookshanks. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You shouldn’t have done that,’ said Black, looking at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You should have left him to me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry avoided Black’s eyes. He wasn’t sure, even now, that he’d done the right thing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We attacked a teacher … we attacked a teacher …’ Hermione whimpered, staring at the lifeless Snape with frightened eyes. ‘Oh, we’re going to be in so much trouble –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin was struggling against his bonds. Black bent down </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>266 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">quickly and untied him. Lupin straightened up, rubbing his arms where the ropes had cut into them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Harry,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m still not saying I believe you,’ Harry retorted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then it’s time we offered you some proof,’ said Black. ‘You, boy </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– give me Peter. Now.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron clutched Scabbers closer to his chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come off it,’ he said weakly. ‘Are you trying to say you broke out of Azkaban just to get your hands on  <i class=\"calibre4\">Scabbers? </i> I mean …’ he looked up at Harry and Hermione for support. ‘OK, say Pettigrew could turn into a rat – there are millions of rats – how’s he supposed to know which one he’s after if he was locked up in Azkaban?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know, Sirius, that’s a fair question,’ said Lupin, turning to Black and frowning slightly. ‘How  <i class=\"calibre4\">did </i> you find out where he was?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black put one of his claw-like hands inside his robes and took out a crumpled piece of paper, which he smoothed flat, and held out to show the others. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was the photograph of Ron and his family that had appeared in the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> the previous summer, and there, on Ron’s shoulder, was Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How did you get this?’ Lupin asked Black, thunderstruck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fudge,’ said Black. ‘When he came to inspect Azkaban last year, he gave me his paper. And there was Peter, on the front page </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… on this boy’s shoulder … I knew him at once … how many times had I seen him transform? And the caption said the boy would be going back to Hogwarts … to where Harry was …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My God,’ said Lupin softly, staring from Scabbers to the picture in the paper and back again. ‘His front paw …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about it?’ said Ron defiantly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s got a toe missing,’ said Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course,’ Lupin breathed, ‘so simple … so  <i class=\"calibre4\">brilliant </i>… He cut it off himself?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Just before he transformed,’ said Black. ‘When I cornered him, he yelled for the whole street to hear that I’d betrayed Lily and James. Then, before I could curse him, he blew apart the street with the wand behind his back, killed everyone within twenty feet of himself – and sped down into the sewer with the other rats …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t you ever hear, Ron?’ said Lupin. ‘The biggest bit of Peter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 267 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they found was his finger.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look, Scabbers probably had a fight with another rat or something! He’s been in my family for ages, right –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Twelve years, in fact,’ said Lupin. ‘Didn’t you ever wonder why he was living so long?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We – we’ve been taking good care of him!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not looking too good at the moment, though, is he?’ said Lupin. ‘I’d guess he’s been losing weight ever since he heard Sirius was on the loose again …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s been scared of that mad cat!’ said Ron, nodding towards Crookshanks, who was still purring on the bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But that wasn’t right, Harry thought suddenly … Scabbers had been looking ill before he met Crookshanks … ever since Ron’s return from Egypt … since the time when Black had escaped … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This cat isn’t mad,’ said Black hoarsely. He reached out a bony hand and stroked Crookshanks’s fluffy head. ‘He’s the most intelligent of his kind I’ve ever met. He recognised Peter for what he was straight away. And when he met me, he knew I was no dog. It was a while before he trusted me. Finally, I managed to communicate to him what I was after, and he’s been helping me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What do you mean?’ breathed Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He tried to bring Peter to me, but couldn’t … so he stole the passwords into Gryffindor Tower for me … As I understand it, he took them from a boy’s bedside table …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s brain seemed to be sagging under the weight of what he was hearing. It was absurd … and yet … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But Peter got wind of what was going on and ran for it … this cat – Crookshanks, did you call him? – told me Peter had left blood on the sheets … I suppose he bit himself … well, faking his own death had worked once …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">These words jolted Harry to his senses. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And why did he fake his death?’ he said furiously. ‘Because he knew you were about to kill him like you killed my parents!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Lupin. ‘Harry –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And now you’ve come to finish him off!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, I have,’ said Black, with an evil look at Scabbers. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Then I should’ve let Snape take you!’ Harry shouted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Lupin hurriedly, ‘don’t you see? All this time we’ve thought Sirius betrayed your parents, and Peter tracked him down </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>268 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– but it was the other way around, don’t you see?  <i class=\"calibre4\">Peter  </i> betrayed your mother and father – Sirius tracked  <i class=\"calibre4\">Peter </i> down –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THAT’S NOT TRUE!’ Harry yelled. ‘HE WAS THEIR SECRET </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">KEEPER! HE SAID SO BEFORE YOU TURNED UP, HE SAID HE </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">KILLED THEM!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was pointing at Black, who shook his head slowly; the sunken eyes were suddenly over-bright. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry … I as good as killed them,’ he croaked. ‘I persuaded Lily and James to change to Peter at the last moment, persuaded them to use him as Secret Keeper instead of me … I’m to blame, I know it … the night they died, I’d arranged to check on Peter, make sure he was still safe, but when I arrived at his hiding place, he’d gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Yet there was no sign of a struggle. It didn’t feel right. I was scared. I set out for your parents’ house straight away. And when I saw their house, destroyed, and their bodies – I realised what Peter must have done. What I’d done.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His voice broke. He turned away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Enough of this,’ said Lupin, and there was a steely note in his voice Harry had never heard before. ‘There’s one certain way to prove what really happened. Ron,  <i class=\"calibre4\">give me that rat. </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are you going to do with him if I give him to you?’ Ron asked Lupin tensely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Force him to show himself,’ said Lupin. ‘If he really is a rat, it won’t hurt him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron hesitated, then at long last held out Scabbers and Lupin took him. Scabbers began to squeak without stopping, twisting and turning, his tiny black eyes bulging in his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready, Sirius?’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black had already retrieved Snape’s wand from the bed. He approached Lupin and the struggling rat, and his wet eyes suddenly seemed to be burning in his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Together?’ he said quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think so,’ said Lupin, holding Scabbers tightly in one hand and his wand in the other. ‘On the count of three. One – two – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">THREE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A flash of blue-white light erupted from both wands; for a moment, Scabbers was frozen in mid-air, his small black form twisting madly – Ron yelled – the rat fell and hit the floor. There was another blinding flash of light and then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was like watching a speeded-up film of a growing tree. A </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 269 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">head was shooting upwards from the ground; limbs were sprouting; next moment, a man was standing where Scabbers had been, cringing and wringing his hands. Crookshanks was spitting and snarling on the bed, the hair on his back standing up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was a very short man, hardly taller than Harry and Hermione. His thin, colourless hair was unkempt and there was a large bald patch on top. He had the shrunken appearance of a plump man who had lost a lot of weight in a short time. His skin looked grubby, almost like Scabbers’s fur, and something of the rat lingered around his pointed nose, his very small, watery eyes. He looked around at them all, his breathing fast and shallow. Harry saw his eyes dart to the door and back again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, hello, Peter,’ said Lupin pleasantly, as though rats frequently erupted into old schoolfriends around him. ‘Long time, no see.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘S-Sirius … R-Remus …’ Even Pettigrew’s voice was squeaky. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Again, his eyes darted towards the door. ‘My friends … my old friends …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s wand arm rose, but Lupin seized him around the wrist, gave him a warning look, then turned again to Pettigrew, his voice light and casual. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve been having a little chat, Peter, about what happened the night Lily and James died. You might have missed the finer points while you were squeaking around down there on the bed –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Remus,’ gasped Pettigrew, and Harry could see beads of sweat breaking out over his pasty face, ‘you don’t believe him, do you … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He tried to kill me, Remus …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So we’ve heard,’ said Lupin, more coldly. ‘I’d like to clear up one or two little matters with you, Peter, if you’d be so –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s come to try and kill me again!’ Pettigrew shrieked suddenly, pointing at Black, and Harry saw that he used his middle finger, because his index was missing. ‘He killed Lily and James and now he’s going to kill me, too … you’ve got to help me, Remus …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s face looked more skull-like than ever as he stared at Pettigrew with his fathomless eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No one’s going to try and kill you until we’ve sorted a few things out,’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sorted things out?’ squealed Pettigrew, looking wildly about him once more, eyes taking in the boarded windows and, again, the only door. ‘I knew he’d come after me! I knew he’d be back for </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>270 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">me! I’ve been waiting for this for twelve years!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You knew Sirius was going to break out of Azkaban?’ said Lupin, his brow furrowed. ‘When nobody has ever done it before?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s got Dark powers the rest of us can only dream of!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew shouted shrilly. ‘How else did he get out of there? I suppose He Who Must Not Be Named taught him a few tricks!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black started to laugh, a horrible, mirthless laugh that filled the whole room. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Voldemort, teach me tricks?’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew flinched as though Black had brandished a whip at him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What, scared to hear your old master’s name?’ said Black. ‘I don’t blame you, Peter. His lot aren’t very happy with you, are they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t know – what you mean, Sirius –’ muttered Pettigrew, his breathing faster than ever. His whole face was shining with sweat now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You haven’t been hiding from  <i class=\"calibre4\">me</i> for twelve years,’ said Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’ve been hiding from Voldemort’s old supporters. I heard things in Azkaban, Peter … they all think you’re dead, or you’d have to answer to them … I’ve heard them screaming all sorts of things in their sleep. Sounds like they think the double-crosser double-crossed them. Voldemort went to the Potters’ on your information … and Voldemort met his downfall there. And not all Voldemort’s supporters ended up in Azkaban, did they? There are still plenty out here, biding their time, pretending they’ve seen the error of their ways … If they ever got wind that you were still alive, Peter –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Don’t know … what you’re talking about …’ said Pettigrew again, more shrilly than ever. He wiped his face on his sleeve and looked up at Lupin. ‘You don’t believe this – this madness, Remus –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I must admit, Peter, I have difficulty in understanding why an innocent man would want to spend twelve years as a rat,’ said Lupin evenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Innocent, but scared!’ squealed Pettigrew. ‘If Voldemort’s supporters were after me, it was because I put one of their best men in Azkaban – the spy, Sirius Black!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s face contorted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How dare you,’ he growled, sounding suddenly like the bear-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 271 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sized dog he had been. ‘I, a spy for Voldemort? When did I ever sneak around people who were stronger and more powerful than myself? But you, Peter – I’ll never understand why I didn’t see you were the spy from the start. You always liked big friends who’d look  after  you,  didn’t  you?  It  used  to  be  us  …  me  and  Remus  … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and James …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew wiped his face again; he was almost panting for breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Me, a spy … must be out of your mind … never … don’t know how you can say such a –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Lily and James only made you Secret Keeper because I suggested it,’ Black hissed, so venomously that Pettigrew took a step backwards. ‘I thought it was the perfect plan … a bluff … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Voldemort would be sure to come after me, would never dream they’d use a weak, talentless thing like you … it must have been the finest moment of your miserable life, telling Voldemort you could hand him the Potters.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew was muttering distractedly; Harry caught words like </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘far-fetched’ and ‘lunacy’, but he couldn’t help paying more attention to the ashen colour of Pettigrew’s face, and the way his eyes continued to dart towards the windows and door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin?’ said Hermione timidly. ‘Can – can I say something?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Certainly, Hermione,’ said Lupin courteously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – Scabbers – I mean, this – this man – he’s been sleeping in Harry’s dormitory for three years. If he’s working for You Know Who, how come he never tried to hurt Harry before now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There!’ said Pettigrew shrilly, pointing at Hermione with his maimed hand. ‘Thank you! You see, Remus? I have never hurt a hair of Harry’s head! Why should I?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll tell you why,’ said Black. ‘Because you never did anything for anyone unless you could see what was in it for you. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Voldemort’s been in hiding for twelve years, they say he’s half-dead. You weren’t about to commit murder right under Albus Dumbledore’s nose, for a wreck of a wizard who’d lost all his power, were you? You’d want to be quite sure he was the biggest bully in the playground before you went back to him, wouldn’t you? Why else did you find a wizard family to take you in? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Keeping an ear out for news, weren’t you, Peter? Just in case your old protector regained strength, and it was safe to rejoin him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew opened his mouth and closed it several times. He </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>272 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">seemed to have lost the ability to talk. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Er – Mr Black – Sirius?’ said Hermione timidly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black jumped at being addressed like this and stared at Hermione as though being spoken to politely was something he’d long forgotten. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you don’t mind me asking, how – how did you get out of Azkaban, if you didn’t use Dark Magic?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you!’ gasped Pettigrew, nodding frantically at her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Exactly! Precisely what I –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Lupin silenced him with a look. Black was frowning slightly at Hermione, but not as though he was annoyed with her. He seemed to be pondering his answer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know how I did it,’ he said slowly. ‘I think the only reason I never lost my mind is that I knew I was innocent. That wasn’t a happy thought, so the Dementors couldn’t suck it out of me … but it kept me sane and knowing who I am … helped me keep my powers … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">so when it all became … too much … I could transform in my cell </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… become a dog. Dementors can’t see, you know …’ He swallowed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They feel their way towards people by sensing their emotions … they could tell that my feelings were less – less human, less complex when I was a dog … but they thought, of course, that I was losing my mind like everyone else in there, so it didn’t trouble them. But I was weak, very weak, and I had no hope of driving them away from me without a wand … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then I saw Peter in that picture … I realised he was at Hogwarts with Harry … perfectly positioned to act, if one hint reached his ears that the Dark Side was gathering strength again …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew was shaking his head, mouthing noiselessly, but staring all the while at Black as though hypnotised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… ready to strike the moment he could be sure of allies … to deliver the last Potter to them. If he gave them Harry, who’d dare say he’d betrayed Lord Voldemort? He’d be welcomed back with honours … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So you see, I had to do something. I was the only one who knew Peter was still alive …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry remembered what Mr Weasley had told Mrs Weasley. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The guards say he’s been talking in his sleep … always the same words … “<i class=\"calibre4\">He’s at Hogwarts</i>”.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was as if someone had lit a fire in my head, and the Dementors couldn’t destroy it … it wasn’t a happy feeling … it was </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 273 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">an obsession … but it gave me strength, it cleared my mind. So, one night when they opened my door to bring food, I slipped past them as a dog … it’s so much harder for them to sense animal emotions that they were confused … I was thin, very thin … thin enough to slip through the bars … I swam as a dog back to the mainland … I journeyed north and slipped into the Hogwarts grounds as a dog … I’ve been living in the Forest ever since … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">except when I come to watch the Quidditch, of course … you fly as well as your father did, Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He looked at Harry, who did not look away. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Believe me,’ croaked Black. ‘Believe me. I never betrayed James and Lily. I would have died before I betrayed them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And at long last, Harry believed him. Throat too tight to speak, he nodded. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew had fallen to his knees as though Harry’s nod had been his own death sentence. He shuffled forward on his knees, grovelling, his hands clasped in front of him as though praying. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius – it’s me … it’s Peter … your friend … you wouldn’t …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black kicked out and Pettigrew recoiled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s enough filth on my robes without you touching them,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Remus!’ Pettigrew squeaked, turning to Lupin instead, writhing imploringly in front of him. ‘You don’t believe this … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Wouldn’t Sirius have told you they’d changed the plan?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not if he thought I was the spy, Peter,’ said Lupin. ‘I assume that’s why you didn’t tell me, Sirius?’ he said casually over Pettigrew’s head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Forgive me, Remus,’ said Black. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not at all, Padfoot, old friend,’ said Lupin, who was now rolling up his sleeves. ‘And will you, in turn, forgive me for believing  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> were the spy?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course,’ said Black, and the ghost of a grin flitted across his gaunt face. He, too, began rolling up his sleeves. ‘Shall we kill him together?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, I think so,’ said Lupin grimly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You wouldn’t … you won’t …’ gasped Pettigrew. And he scrambled around to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ron … haven’t I been a good friend … a good pet? You won’t let them kill me, Ron, will you … you’re on my side, aren’t you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>274 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Ron was staring at Pettigrew with the utmost revulsion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I let you sleep in my  <i class=\"calibre4\">bed! </i>’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Kind boy … kind master …’ Pettigrew crawled towards Ron, </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘you won’t let them do it … I was your rat … I was a good pet …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If you made a better rat than human, it’s not much to boast about, Peter,’ said Black harshly. Ron, going still paler with pain, wrenched his broken leg out of Pettigrew’s reach. Pettigrew turned on his knees, staggered forwards and seized the hem of Hermione’s robes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sweet girl … clever girl … you – you won’t let them … help me …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione pulled her robes out of Pettigrew’s clutching hands and backed away against the wall, looking horrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew knelt, trembling uncontrollably, and turned his head slowly towards Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry … Harry … you look just like your father … just like him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HOW DARE YOU SPEAK TO HARRY?’ roared Black. ‘HOW </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">DARE YOU FACE HIM? HOW DARE YOU TALK ABOUT JAMES </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">IN FRONT OF HIM?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ whispered Pettigrew, shuffling towards him, hands outstretched, ‘Harry, James wouldn’t have wanted me killed … James would have understood, Harry … he would have shown me mercy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Both Black and Lupin strode forwards, seized Pettigrew’s shoulders and threw him backwards onto the floor. He sat there, twitching with terror, staring up at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You sold Lily and James to Voldemort,’ said Black, who was shaking too. ‘Do you deny it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew burst into tears. It was horrible to watch: he looked like an oversized, balding baby, cowering on the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius, Sirius, what could I have done? The Dark Lord … you have no idea … he has weapons you can’t imagine … I was scared, Sirius, I was never brave like you and Remus and James. I never meant it to happen … He Who Must Not Be Named forced me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘DON’T LIE!’ bellowed Black. ‘YOU’D BEEN PASSING INFORMATION TO HIM FOR A YEAR BEFORE LILY AND JAMES </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">DIED! YOU WERE HIS SPY!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He – he was taking over everywhere!’ gasped Pettigrew. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wh-what was there to be gained by refusing him?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was there to be gained by fighting the most evil wizard </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Servant of Lord Voldemort 275 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">who has ever existed?’ said Black, with a terrible fury in his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Only innocent lives, Peter!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You don’t understand!’ whined Pettigrew. ‘He would have killed me, Sirius!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THEN YOU SHOULD HAVE DIED!’ roared Black. ‘DIED </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">RATHER THAN BETRAY YOUR FRIENDS, AS WE WOULD </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">HAVE DONE FOR YOU!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black and Lupin stood shoulder to shoulder, wands raised. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You should have realised,’ said Lupin quietly. ‘If Voldemort didn’t kill you, we would. Goodbye, Peter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione covered her face with her hands and turned to the wall. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘NO!’ Harry yelled. He ran forwards, placing himself in front of Pettigrew, facing the wands. ‘You can’t kill him,’ he said breathlessly. ‘You can’t.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black and Lupin both looked staggered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, this piece of vermin is the reason you have no parents,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black snarled. ‘This cringing bit of filth would have seen you die, too, without turning a hair. You heard him. His own stinking skin meant more to him than your whole family.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ Harry panted. ‘We’ll take him up to the castle. We’ll hand him over to the Dementors. He can go to Azkaban … just don’t kill him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ gasped Pettigrew, and he flung his arms around Harry’s knees. ‘You – thank you – it’s more than I deserve – thank you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get off me,’ Harry spat, throwing Pettigrew’s hands off him in disgust. ‘I’m not doing this for you. I’m doing it because I don’t reckon my dad would’ve wanted his best friends to become killers </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– just for you.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">No one moved or made a sound except Pettigrew, whose breath was coming in wheezes as he clutched his chest. Black and Lupin were looking at each other. Then, with one movement, they lowered their wands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re the only person who has the right to decide, Harry,’ said Black. ‘But think … think what he did …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He can go to Azkaban,’ Harry repeated. ‘If anyone deserves that place, he does …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew was still wheezing behind him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Very well,’ said Lupin. ‘Stand aside, Harry.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry hesitated. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to tie him up,’ said Lupin. ‘That’s all, I swear.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>276 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped out of the way. Thin cords shot from Lupin’s wand this time, and next moment, Pettigrew was wriggling on the floor, bound and gagged. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if you transform, Peter,’ growled Black, his own wand pointing at Pettigrew, too, ‘we  <i class=\"calibre4\">will </i> kill you. You agree, Harry?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked down at the pitiful figure on the floor, and nodded so that Pettigrew could see him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ said Lupin, suddenly business-like. ‘Ron, I can’t mend bones nearly as well as Madam Pomfrey, so I think it’s best if we just strap your leg up until we can get you to the hospital wing.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He hurried over to Ron, bent down, tapped Ron’s leg with his wand and muttered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Ferula</i>.’ Bandages spun up Ron’s leg, strapping it tightly to a splint. Lupin helped him to his feet; Ron put his weight gingerly on the leg and didn’t wince. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s better,’ he said. ‘Thanks.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What about Professor Snape?’ said Hermione in a small voice, looking down at Snape’s prone figure. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s nothing seriously wrong with him,’ said Lupin, bending over Snape and checking his pulse. ‘You were just a little – over-enthusiastic. Still out cold. Er – perhaps it will be best if we don’t revive him until we’re safely back in the castle. We can take him like this …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He muttered, ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Mobilicorpus</i>.’ As though invisible strings were tied to Snape’s wrists, neck and knees, he was pulled into a standing position, head still lolling unpleasantly, like a grotesque puppet. He hung a few inches above the ground, his limp feet dangling. Lupin picked up the Invisibility Cloak and tucked it safely into his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And two of us should be chained to this,’ said Black, nudging Pettigrew with his toe. ‘Just to make sure.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll do it,’ said Lupin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And me,’ said Ron savagely, limping forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black conjured heavy manacles from thin air; soon Pettigrew was upright again, left arm chained to Lupin’s right, right arm to Ron’s left. Ron’s face was set. He seemed to have taken Scabbers’s true identity as a personal insult. Crookshanks leapt lightly off the bed and led the way out of the room, his bottle-brush tail held jauntily high. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWENTY — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">The Dementors’ Kiss </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had never been part of a stranger group. Crookshanks led the way down the stairs; Lupin, Pettigrew and Ron went next, looking like contestants in a six-legged race. Next came Professor Snape, drifting creepily along, his toes hitting each stair as they descended, held up by his own wand, which was being pointed at him by Sirius. Harry and Hermione brought up the rear. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Getting back into the tunnel was difficult. Lupin, Pettigrew and Ron had to turn sideways to manage it; Lupin still had Pettigrew covered with his wand. Harry could see them edging awkwardly along the tunnel in single file. Crookshanks was still in the lead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry went right after Sirius, who was still making Snape drift along ahead of them; he kept bumping his lolling head on the low ceiling. Harry had the impression Sirius was making no effort to prevent this. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You know what this means?’ Sirius said abruptly to Harry, as they made their slow progress along the tunnel. ‘Turning Pettigrew in?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re free,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes …’ said Sirius. ‘But I’m also – I don’t know if anyone ever told you – I’m your godfather.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I knew that,’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … your parents appointed me your guardian,’ said Sirius stiffly. ‘If anything happened to them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry waited. Did Sirius mean what he thought he meant? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll understand, of course, if you want to stay with your aunt and uncle,’ said Sirius. ‘But … well … think about it. Once my name’s cleared … if you wanted a … a different home …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Some sort of explosion took place in the pit of Harry’s stomach. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What – live with you?’ he said, accidentally cracking his head </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>278 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">on a bit of rock protruding from the ceiling. ‘Leave the Dursleys?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course, I thought you wouldn’t want to,’ said Sirius quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I understand. I just thought I’d –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you mad?’ said Harry, his voice easily as croaky as Sirius’. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course I want to leave the Dursleys! Have you got a house? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When can I move in?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sirius turned right around to look at him; Snape’s head was scraping the ceiling but Sirius didn’t seem to care. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You want to?’ he said. ‘You mean it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I mean it!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sirius’ gaunt face broke into the first true smile Harry had seen upon it. The difference it made was startling, as though a person ten years younger was shining through the starved mask; for a moment, he was recognisable as the man who had laughed at Harry’s parents’ wedding. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They did not speak again until they had reached the end of the tunnel. Crookshanks darted up first; he had evidently pressed his paw to the knot on the trunk, because Lupin, Pettigrew and Ron clambered upwards without any sound of savaging branches. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sirius saw Snape up through the hole, then stood back for Harry and Hermione to pass. At last, all of them were out. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The grounds were very dark now, the only light came from the distant windows of the castle. Without a word, they set off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew was still wheezing and occasionally whimpering. Harry’s mind was buzzing. He was going to leave the Dursleys. He was going to live with Sirius Black, his parents’ best friend … he felt dazed … What would happen when he told the Dursleys he was going to live with the convict they’d seen on television? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One wrong move, Peter,’ said Lupin threateningly, ahead. His wand was still pointed sideways at Pettigrew’s chest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silently they tramped through the grounds, the castle lights growing slowly larger. Snape was still drifting weirdly ahead of Sirius, his chin bumping on his chest. And then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A cloud shifted. There were suddenly dim shadows on the ground. Their party was bathed in moonlight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape collided with Lupin, Pettigrew and Ron, who had stopped abruptly. Sirius froze. He flung out an arm to make Harry and Hermione stop. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could see Lupin’s silhouette. He had gone rigid. Then his limbs began to shake. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementors’ Kiss 279 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh my –’ Hermione gasped. ‘He didn’t take his Potion tonight! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He’s not safe!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Run,’ Sirius whispered. ‘Run! Now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Harry couldn’t run. Ron was chained to Pettigrew and Lupin. He leapt forwards but Sirius caught him around the chest and threw him back. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Leave it to me – RUN!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a terrible snarling noise. Lupin’s head was lengthening. So was his body. His shoulders were hunching. Hair was sprouting visibly on his face and hands, which were curling into clawed paws. Crookshanks’s fur was on end again, he was backing away – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the werewolf reared, snapping its long jaws, Sirius disappeared from Harry’s side. He had transformed. The enormous, bear-like dog bounded forwards. As the werewolf wrenched itself free of the manacle binding it, the dog seized it about the neck and pulled it backwards, away from Ron and Pettigrew. They were locked, jaw to jaw, claws ripping at each other – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood, transfixed by the sight; too intent upon the battle to notice anything else. It was Hermione’s scream that alerted him – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Pettigrew had dived for Lupin’s dropped wand. Ron, unsteady on his bandaged leg, fell. There was a bang, a burst of light – and Ron lay motionless on the ground. Another bang – Crookshanks flew into the air and back to the earth in a heap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Expelliarmus! </i>’ Harry yelled, pointing his own wand at Pettigrew; Lupin’s wand flew high into the air and out of sight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stay where you are!’ Harry shouted, running forwards. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Too late. Pettigrew had transformed. Harry saw his bald tail whip through the manacle on Ron’s outstretched arm, and heard a scurrying through the grass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a howl and a rumbling growl; Harry turned to see the werewolf taking flight; it was galloping into the Forest – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius, he’s gone, Pettigrew transformed!’ Harry yelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sirius was bleeding; there were gashes across his muzzle and back, but at Harry’s words he scrambled up again, and in an instant, the sound of his paws was fading to silence as he pounded away across the grounds. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione dashed over to Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What did he do to him?’ Hermione whispered. Ron’s eyes were </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>280 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">only half-closed; his mouth hung open. He was definitely alive, they could hear him breathing, but he didn’t seem to recognise them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked desperately around. Black and Lupin both gone … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they had no one but Snape for company, still hanging, unconscious, in mid-air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d better get them up to the castle and tell someone,’ said Harry, pushing his hair out of his eyes, trying to think straight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But then, out of the darkness, they heard a yelping, a whining; a dog in pain … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius,’ Harry muttered, staring into the darkness. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He had a moment’s indecision, but there was nothing they could do for Ron at the moment, and by the sound of it, Black was in trouble – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry set off at a run, Hermione right behind him. The yelping seemed to be coming from near the lake. They pelted towards it, and Harry, running flat out, felt the cold without realising what it must mean – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The yelping stopped abruptly. As they reached the lake’s shore they saw why – Sirius had turned back into a man. He was crouched on all fours, his hands over his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Nooo</i>,’ he moaned. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Noooo … please </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then Harry saw them. Dementors, at least a hundred of them, gliding in a black mass around the lake towards them. He spun around, the familiar, icy cold penetrating his insides, fog starting to obscure his vision; more were appearing out of the darkness on every side; they were encircling them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, think of something happy!’ Harry yelled, raising his wand, blinking furiously to try and clear his vision, shaking his head to rid it of the faint screaming that had started inside it – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I’m going to live with my godfather. I’m leaving the Dursleys. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He forced himself to think of Sirius, and only Sirius, and began to chant: ‘Expecto patronum! Expecto patronum!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black gave a shudder, rolled over and lay motionless on the ground, pale as death. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">He’ll be all right. I’m going to go and live with him. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Expecto patronum! Hermione, help me! Expecto patronum!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Expecto –’ Hermione whispered, ‘expecto – expecto –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Dementors’ Kiss 281 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But she couldn’t do it. The Dementors were closing in, barely ten feet from them. They formed a solid wall around Harry and Hermione, and were getting closer … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘EXPECTO PATRONUM!’ Harry yelled, trying to blot the screaming from his ears. ‘EXPECTO PATRONUM!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A thin wisp of silver escaped his wand and hovered like mist before him. At the same moment, Harry felt Hermione collapse next to him. He was alone … completely alone … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Expecto – expecto patronum –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry felt his knees hit the cold grass. Fog was clouding his eyes. With a huge effort, he fought to remember – Sirius was innocent – innocent –  <i class=\"calibre4\">we’ll be OK – I’m going to live with him –</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Expecto patronum!’ he gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">By the feeble light of his formless Patronus, he saw a Dementor halt, very close to him. It couldn’t walk through the cloud of silver mist Harry had conjured. A dead, slimy hand slid out from under the cloak. It made a gesture as though to sweep the Patronus aside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No –  <i class=\"calibre4\">no</i> –’ Harry gasped. ‘He’s innocent … expecto – expecto patronum –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He could feel them watching him, hear their rattling breath like an evil wind around him. The nearest Dementor seemed to be considering him. Then it raised both its rotting hands – and lowered its hood. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where there should have been eyes, there was only thin, grey, scabbed skin, stretched blankly over empty sockets. But there was a mouth … a gaping, shapeless hole, sucking the air with the sound of a death-rattle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A paralysing terror filled Harry so that he couldn’t move or speak. His Patronus flickered and died. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">White fog was blinding him. He had to fight …  <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto patronum </i>… he couldn’t see … and in the distance, he heard the familiar screaming …  <i class=\"calibre4\">expecto patronum </i>… he groped in the mist for Sirius, and found his arm … they weren’t going to take him … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But a pair of strong, clammy hands suddenly wrapped themselves around Harry’s neck. They were forcing his face upwards … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he could feel its breath … it was going to get rid of him first … he could feel its putrid breath … his mother was screaming in his ears … she was going to be the last thing he ever heard – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, through the fog that was drowning him, he thought </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>282 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">he saw a silvery light, growing brighter and brighter … he felt himself fall forwards onto the grass – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Face down, too weak to move, sick and shaking, Harry opened his eyes. The blinding light was illuminating the grass around him … The screaming had stopped, the cold was ebbing away … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Something was driving the Dementors back … it was circling around him and Sirius and Hermione … the rattling, sucking sounds of the Dementors were fading. They were leaving … the air was warm again … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">With every ounce of strength he could muster, Harry raised his head a few inches and saw an animal amidst the light, galloping away across the lake. Eyes blurred with sweat, Harry tried to make out what it was … it was bright as a unicorn. Fighting to stay conscious, Harry watched it canter to a halt as it reached the opposite shore. For a moment, Harry saw, by its brightness, somebody welcoming it back … raising his hand to pat it … someone who looked strangely familiar … but it couldn’t be … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t understand. He couldn’t think any more. He felt the last of his strength leave him, and his head hit the ground as he fainted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWENTY-ONE — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Hermione’s Secret </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shocking business … shocking … miracle none of them died … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">never heard the like … by thunder, it was lucky you were there, Snape …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Minister.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Order of Merlin, Second Class, I’d say. First Class, if I can wangle it!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you very much indeed, Minister.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Nasty cut you’ve got there … Black’s work, I suppose?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As a matter of fact, it was Potter, Weasley and Granger, Minister …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">No! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Black had bewitched them, I saw it immediately. A Confundus Charm, to judge by their behaviour. They seemed to think there was a possibility he was innocent. They weren’t responsible for their actions. On the other hand, their interference might have permitted Black to escape … they obviously thought they were going to catch Black single-handed. They’ve got away with a great deal before now … I’m afraid it’s given them a rather high opinion of themselves … and of course Potter has always been allowed an extraordinary amount of licence by the Headmaster –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, well, Snape … Harry Potter, you know … we’ve all got a bit of a blind spot where he’s concerned.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And yet – is it good for him to be given so much special treat-ment? Personally I try to treat him like any other student. And any other student would be suspended – at the very least – for leading his friends into such danger. Consider, Minister: against all school rules – after all the precautions put in place for his protection – out of bounds, at night, consorting with a werewolf and a murderer – and I have reason to believe he has been visiting Hogsmeade illegally, too –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>284 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, well … we shall see, Snape, we shall see … the boy has undoubtedly been foolish …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry lay listening with his eyes tight shut. He felt very groggy. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The words he was hearing seemed to be travelling very slowly from his ears to his brain, so that it was difficult to understand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">His limbs felt like lead; his eyelids too heavy to lift … he wanted to lie here, on this comfortable bed, for ever … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What amazes me most is the behaviour of the Dementors … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you’ve really no idea what made them retreat, Snape?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, Minister. By the time I had come round they were heading back to their positions at the entrances …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Extraordinary. And yet Black, and Harry, and the girl –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘All unconscious by the time I reached them. I bound and gagged Black, naturally, conjured stretchers and brought them all straight back to the castle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a pause. Harry’s brain seemed to be moving a little faster, and as it did, a gnawing sensation grew in the pit of his stomach … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He opened his eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Everything was slightly blurred. Somebody had removed his glasses. He was lying in the dark hospital wing. At the very end of the ward, he could make out Madam Pomfrey with her back to him, bending over a bed. Harry squinted. Ron’s red hair was visible beneath Madam Pomfrey’s arm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved his head over on the pillow. In the bed to his right lay Hermione. Moonlight was falling across her bed. Her eyes were open, too. She looked petrified, and when she saw that Harry was awake, pressed a finger to her lips, then pointed to the hospital-wing door. It was ajar, and the voices of Cornelius Fudge and Snape were coming through it from the corridor outside. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey now came walking briskly up the dark ward to Harry’s bed. He turned to look at her. She was carrying the largest block of chocolate he had ever seen in his life. It looked like a small boulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ah, you’re awake!’ she said briskly. She placed the chocolate on Harry’s bedside table and began breaking it apart with a small hammer. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How’s Ron?’ said Harry and Hermione together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’ll live,’ said Madam Pomfrey grimly. ‘As for you two … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you’ll be staying here until I’m satisfied you’re – Potter, what do </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 285 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">you think you’re doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was sitting up, putting his glasses back on and picking up his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I need to see the Headmaster,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Potter,’ said Madam Pomfrey soothingly, ‘it’s all right. They’ve got Black. He’s locked away upstairs. The Dementors will be performing the Kiss any moment now –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WHAT?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry jumped up out of bed; Hermione had done the same. But his shout had been heard in the corridor outside; next second, Cornelius Fudge and Snape had entered the ward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, Harry, what’s this?’ said Fudge, looking agitated. ‘You should be in bed – has he had any chocolate?’ he asked Madam Pomfrey anxiously. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Minister, listen!’ Harry said. ‘Sirius Black’s innocent! Peter Pettigrew faked his own death! We saw him tonight! You can’t let the Dementors do that thing to Sirius, he’s –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Fudge was shaking his head with a small smile on his face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, Harry, you’re very confused, you’ve been through a dreadful ordeal, lie back down, now, we’ve got everything under control …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YOU HAVEN’T!’ Harry yelled. ‘YOU’VE GOT THE WRONG </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">MAN!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Minister, listen, please,’ Hermione said; she had hurried to Harry’s side and was gazing imploringly into Fudge’s face. ‘I saw him, too. It was Ron’s rat, he’s an Animagus, Pettigrew, I mean, and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You see, Minister?’ said Snape. ‘Confunded, both of them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black’s done a very good job on them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘WE’RE NOT CONFUNDED!’ Harry roared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Minister! Professor!’ said Madam Pomfrey angrily. ‘I must insist that you leave. Potter is my patient, and he should not be distressed!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not distressed, I’m trying to tell them what happened!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry said furiously. ‘If they’d just listen –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000004999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Madam Pomfrey suddenly stuffed a large chunk of chocolate into Harry’s mouth. He choked, and she seized the opportunity to force him back onto the bed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now,  <i class=\"calibre4\">please</i>, Minister, these children need care. Please leave –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door opened again. It was Dumbledore. Harry swallowed his mouthful of chocolate with great difficulty, and got up again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>286 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore, Sirius Black –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘For heaven’s sake!’ said Madam Pomfrey hysterically. ‘Is this a hospital wing or not? Headmaster, I must insist –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My apologies, Poppy, but I need a word with Mr Potter and Miss Granger,’ said Dumbledore calmly. ‘I have just been talking to Sirius Black –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I suppose he’s told you the same fairy tale he’s planted in Potter’s mind?’ spat Snape. ‘Something about a rat, and Pettigrew being alive –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That, indeed, is Black’s story,’ said Dumbledore, surveying Snape closely through his half-moon spectacles. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And does my evidence count for nothing?’ snarled Snape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Peter Pettigrew was not in the Shrieking Shack, nor did I see any sign of him in the grounds.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was because you were knocked out, Professor!’ said Hermione earnestly. ‘You didn’t arrive in time to hear –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Miss Granger, HOLD YOUR TONGUE!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, Snape,’ said Fudge, startled, ‘the young lady is disturbed in her mind, we must make allowances –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I would like to speak to Harry and Hermione alone,’ said Dumbledore abruptly. ‘Cornelius, Severus, Poppy – please leave us.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Headmaster!’ spluttered Madam Pomfrey. ‘They need treat-ment, they need rest –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This cannot wait,’ said Dumbledore. ‘I must insist.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey pursed her lips and strode away into her office at the end of the ward, slamming the door behind her. Fudge consulted the large gold pocket watch dangling from his waistcoat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘The Dementors should have arrived by now,’ he said. ‘I’ll go and meet them. Dumbledore, I’ll see you upstairs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He crossed to the door and held it open for Snape, but Snape hadn’t moved. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You surely don’t believe a word of Black’s story?’ Snape whispered, his eyes fixed on Dumbledore’s face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I wish to speak to Harry and Hermione alone,’ Dumbledore repeated. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape took a step towards Dumbledore. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius Black showed he was capable of murder at the age of sixteen,’ he breathed. ‘You haven’t forgotten that, Headmaster? You haven’t forgotten that he once tried to kill  <i class=\"calibre4\">me? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘My  memory  is  as  good  as  it  ever  was,  Severus,’  said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 287 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape turned on his heel and marched through the door Fudge was still holding. It closed behind them and Dumbledore turned to Harry and Hermione. They both burst into speech at the same time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor, Black’s telling the truth – we  <i class=\"calibre4\">saw</i> Pettigrew –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– he escaped when Professor Lupin turned into a werewolf –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– he’s a rat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– Pettigrew’s front paw, I mean, finger, he cut it off –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– Pettigrew attacked Ron, it wasn’t Sirius –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Dumbledore held up his hand to stem the flood of explanations. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It is your turn to listen, and I beg you will not interrupt me, because there is very little time,’ he said quietly. ‘There is not a shred of proof to support Black’s story, except your word – and the word of two thirteen-year-old wizards will not convince anybody. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A street full of eye-witnesses swore they saw Sirius murder Pettigrew. I myself gave evidence to the Ministry that Sirius had been the Potters’ Secret Keeper.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin can tell you –’ Harry said, unable to stop himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Lupin is currently deep in the Forest, unable to tell anyone anything. By the time he is human again, it will be too late, Sirius will be worse than dead. I might add that werewolves are so mistrusted by most of our kind that his support will count for very little – and the fact that he and Sirius are old friends –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Listen to me, Harry</i>. It is too late, you understand me? You must see that Professor Snape’s version of events is far more convincing than yours.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He hates Sirius,’ Hermione said desperately. ‘All because of some stupid trick Sirius played on him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius has not acted like an innocent man. The attack on the Fat Lady – entering Gryffindor Tower with a knife – without Pettigrew, alive or dead, we have no chance of overturning Sirius’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">sentence.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">But you believe us</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,  I  do,’  said  Dumbledore  quietly.  ‘But  I  have  no  power  to make other men see the truth, or to overrule the Minister for Magic …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>288 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared up into the grave face and felt as though the ground beneath him was falling sharply away. He had grown used to the idea that Dumbledore could solve anything. He had expected Dumbledore to pull some amazing solution out of the air. But no … their last hope was gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What we need,’ said Dumbledore slowly, and his light-blue eyes moved from Harry to Hermione, ‘is more  <i class=\"calibre4\">time</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ Hermione began. And then her eyes became very round. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OH!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now, pay attention,’ said Dumbledore, speaking very low, and very clearly. ‘Sirius is locked in Professor Flitwick’s office on the seventh floor. Thirteenth window from the right of the West Tower. If all goes well, you will be able to save more than one innocent life tonight. But remember this, both of you.  <i class=\"calibre4\">You must not</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">be seen</i>. Miss Granger, you know the law – you know what is at stake …  <i class=\"calibre4\">you – must – not – be – seen</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t have a clue what was going on. Dumbledore had turned on his heel and looked back as he reached the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am going to lock you in. It is –’ he consulted his watch, ‘five minutes to midnight. Miss Granger, three turns should do it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Good luck.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Good luck?’ Harry repeated, as the door closed behind Dumbledore. ‘Three turns? What’s he talking about? What are we supposed to do?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione was fumbling with the neck of her robes, pulling from beneath them a very long, very fine gold chain. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, come here,’ she said urgently. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Quick! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved towards her, completely bewildered. She was holding the chain out. He saw a tiny, sparkling hour-glass hanging from it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She had thrown the chain around his neck, too. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ she said breathlessly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What are we doing?’ Harry said, completely lost. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione turned the hour-glass over three times. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The dark ward dissolved. Harry had the sensation that he was flying, very fast, backwards. A blur of colours and shapes rushed past him; his ears were pounding. He tried to yell but couldn’t hear his own voice – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then he felt solid ground beneath his feet, and everything </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 289 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">came into focus again – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was standing next to Hermione in the deserted Entrance Hall and a stream of golden sunlight was falling across the paved floor from the open front doors. He looked wildly around at Hermione, the chain of the hour-glass cutting into his neck. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione, what –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘In here!’ Hermione seized Harry’s arm and dragged him across the hall to the door of a broom cupboard; she opened it, pushed him inside amongst the buckets and mops, followed him in, then slammed the door behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What – how – Hermione, what happened?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve gone back in time,’ Hermione whispered, lifting the chain off Harry’s neck in the darkness. ‘Three hours back …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry found his own leg and gave it a very hard pinch. It hurt a lot, which seemed to rule out the possibility that he was having a very bizarre dream. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shh! Listen! Someone’s coming! I think – I think it might be us!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione had her ear pressed against the cupboard door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Footsteps across the hall … yes, I think it’s us going down to Hagrid’s!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Are you telling me,’ Harry whispered, ‘that we’re here in this cupboard and we’re out there, too?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes,’ said Hermione, her ear still glued to the cupboard door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m sure it’s us … it doesn’t sound like more than three people … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">and we’re walking slowly because we’re under the Invisibility Cloak –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She broke off, still listening intently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve gone down the front steps …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione sat down on an upturned bucket; looking desperately anxious, Harry wanted a few questions answered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where did you  <i class=\"calibre4\">get</i> that hourglass thing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s called a Time-Turner,’ Hermione whispered, ‘and I got it from Professor McGonagall on our first day back. I’ve been using it all year to get to all my lessons. Professor McGonagall made me swear I wouldn’t tell anyone. She had to write all sorts of letters to the Ministry of Magic so I could have one. She had to tell them that I was a model student, and that I’d never, ever use it for anything except my studies … I’ve been turning it back so I could do </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>290 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">hours over again, that’s how I’ve been doing several lessons at once, see? But … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">I don’t understand what Dumbledore wants us to do</i>. Why did  he  tell  us  to  go  back  three  hours? How’s that going to help Sirius?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared at her shadowy face. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There must be something that happened around now he wants us to change,’ he said slowly. ‘What happened? We were walking down to Hagrid’s three hours ago …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This  <i class=\"calibre4\">is </i> three hours ago, and we  <i class=\"calibre4\">are </i> walking down to Hagrid’s,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Hermione. ‘We just heard ourselves leaving …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry frowned; he felt as though he was screwing up his whole brain in concentration. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore just said – just said we could save more than one innocent life …’ And then it hit him. ‘Hermione, we’re going to save Buckbeak!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But – how will that help Sirius?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Dumbledore said – he just told us where the window is – the window of Flitwick’s office! Where they’ve got Sirius locked up! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’ve got to fly Buckbeak up to the window and rescue Sirius! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sirius can escape on Buckbeak – they can escape together!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">From what Harry could see of Hermione’s face, she looked terrified. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If we manage that without being seen, it’ll be a miracle!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, we’ve got to try, haven’t we?’ said Harry. He stood up and pressed his own ear against the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Doesn’t sound like anyone’s there … come on, let’s go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pushed the cupboard door open. The Entrance Hall was deserted. As quietly and quickly as they could, they darted out of the cupboard and down the stone steps. The shadows were already lengthening, the tops of the trees in the Forbidden Forest gilded once more with gold. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If anyone’s looking out of the window –’ Hermione squeaked, looking up at the castle behind them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll run for it,’ said Harry determinedly. ‘Straight into the Forest, all right? We’ll have to hide behind a tree or something and keep a lookout –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, but we’ll go round by the greenhouses!’ said Hermione breathlessly. ‘We need to keep out of sight of Hagrid’s front door, or we’ll see us! We must be nearly at Hagrid’s by now!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 291 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Still working out what she meant, Harry set off at a sprint, Hermione behind him. They tore across the vegetable gardens to the greenhouses, paused for a moment behind them, then set off again, fast as they could, skirting around the Whomping Willow, tearing towards the shelter of the Forest … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Safe in the shadows of the trees, Harry turned around; seconds later, Hermione arrived beside him, panting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right,’ she gasped, ‘we need to sneak over to Hagrid’s. Keep out of sight, Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They made their way silently through the trees, keeping to the very edge of the Forest. Then, as they glimpsed the front of Hagrid’s house, they heard a knock upon his door. They moved quickly behind a wide oak trunk and peered out from either side. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid had appeared in his doorway, shaking and white, looking around to see who had knocked. And Harry heard his own voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s us. We’re wearing the Invisibility Cloak. Let us in and we can take it off.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeh shouldn’ve come!’ Hagrid whispered. He stood back, then shut the door quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is the weirdest thing we’ve ever done,’ Harry said fervently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Let’s move along a bit,’ Hermione whispered. ‘We need to get nearer to Buckbeak!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They crept through the trees until they saw the nervous Hippogriff, tethered to the fence around Hagrid’s pumpkin patch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now?’ Harry whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Hermione. ‘If we steal him now, those Committee people will think Hagrid set him free! We’ve got to wait until they’ve seen he’s tied outside!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s going to give us about sixty seconds,’ said Harry. This was starting to seem impossible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">At that moment, there was a crash of breaking china from inside Hagrid’s cabin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s Hagrid breaking the milk jug,’ Hermione whispered. ‘I’m going to find Scabbers in a moment –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sure enough, a few minutes later, they heard Hermione’s shriek of surprise. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione,’ said Harry suddenly, ‘what if we – we just run in there, and grab Pettigrew –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No!’ said Hermione in a terrified whisper. ‘Don’t you understand? We’re breaking one of the most important wizarding laws! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>292 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody’s supposed to change time, nobody! You heard Dumbledore, if we’re seen –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’d only be seen by ourselves and Hagrid!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, what do you think you’d do if you saw yourself bursting into Hagrid’s house?’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d – I’d think I’d gone mad,’ said Harry, ‘or I’d think there was some Dark Magic going on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Exactly! </i> You wouldn’t understand, you might even attack yourself! Don’t you see? Professor McGonagall told me what awful things have happened when wizards have meddled with time … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">loads of them ended up killing their past or future selves by mistake!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK!’ said Harry. ‘It was just an idea, I just thought –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Hermione nudged him, and pointed towards the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry moved his head a few inches to get a clear view of the distant front doors. Dumbledore, Fudge, the old Committee member and Macnair the executioner were coming down the steps. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re about to come out!’ Hermione breathed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And sure enough, moments later, Hagrid’s back door opened, and Harry saw himself, Ron and Hermione walking out of it with Hagrid. It was, without a doubt, the strangest sensation of his life, standing behind the tree, and watching himself in the pumpkin patch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s OK, Beaky, it’s OK …’ Hagrid said to Buckbeak. Then he turned to Harry, Ron and Hermione. ‘Go on. Get goin’.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid, we can’t –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll tell them what really happened –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘They can’t kill him –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go! It’s bad enough without you lot in trouble an’ all!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry watched the Hermione in the pumpkin patch throw the Invisibility Cloak over himself and Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Go quick. Don’ listen …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a knock on Hagrid’s front door. The execution party had arrived. Hagrid turned around and headed back into his cabin, leaving the back door ajar. Harry watched the grass flatten in patches all around the cabin and heard three pairs of feet retreating. He, Ron and Hermione had gone … but the Harry and Hermione hidden in the trees could now hear what was happening inside the cabin through the back door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is the beast?’ came the cold voice of Macnair. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 293 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Out – outside,’ Hagrid croaked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry pulled his head out of sight as Macnair’s face appeared at Hagrid’s window, staring out at Buckbeak. Then they heard Fudge. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We – er – have to read you the official notice of execution, Hagrid. I’ll make it quick. And then you and Macnair need to sign it. Macnair, you’re supposed to listen too, that’s procedure –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Macnair’s face vanished from the window. It was now or never. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wait here,’ Harry whispered to Hermione. ‘I’ll do it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As Fudge’s voice started again, Harry darted out from behind his tree, vaulted the fence into the pumpkin patch and approached Buckbeak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">It is the decision of the Committee for the Disposal of Dangerous</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Creatures that the Hippogriff Buckbeak, hereafter called the con-demned, shall be executed on the sixth of June at sundown </i>–’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Careful not to blink, Harry stared up into Buckbeak’s fierce orange eye once more, and bowed. Buckbeak sank to his scaly knees and then stood up again. Harry began to fumble with the rope tying Buckbeak to the fence. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> sentenced to execution by beheading, to be carried out by the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Committee’s appointed executioner, Walden Macnair </i>…’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on, Buckbeak,’ Harry murmured, ‘come on, we’re going to help you. Quietly … quietly …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… <i class=\"calibre4\"> as witnessed below</i>. Hagrid, you sign here …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry threw all his weight onto the rope, but Buckbeak had dug in his front feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, let’s get this over with,’ said the reedy voice of the Committee member from inside Hagrid’s cabin. ‘Hagrid, perhaps it would be better if you stayed inside –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No, I – I wan’ ter be with him … I don’ wan’ him ter be alone –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Footsteps echoed from within the cabin. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Buckbeak, move! </i>’ Harry hissed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry tugged harder on the rope around Buckbeak’s neck. The Hippogriff began to walk, rustling its wings irritably. They were still ten feet away from the Forest, in plain view of Hagrid’s back door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘One moment, please, Macnair,’ came Dumbledore’s voice. ‘You need to sign, too.’ The footsteps stopped. Harry heaved on the rope. Buckbeak snapped his beak and walked a little faster. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s white face was sticking out from behind a tree. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, hurry!’ she mouthed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>294 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry could still hear Dumbledore’s voice talking from within the cabin. He gave the rope another wrench. Buckbeak broke into a grudging trot. They had reached the trees … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick! Quick!’ Hermione moaned, darting out from behind her tree, seizing the rope too and adding her weight to make Buckbeak move faster. Harry looked over his shoulder; they were now blocked from sight; they couldn’t see Hagrid’s garden at all. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stop!’ he whispered to Hermione. ‘They might hear us –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hagrid’s back door had opened with a bang. Harry, Hermione and Buckbeak stood quite still; even the Hippogriff seemed to be listening intently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Silence … then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is it?’ said the reedy voice of the Committee member. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Where is the beast?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was tied here!’ said the executioner furiously. ‘I saw it! Just here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How extraordinary,’ said Dumbledore. There was a note of amusement in his voice. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Beaky!’ said Hagrid huskily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a swishing noise, and the thud of an axe. The executioner seemed to have swung it into the fence in anger. And then came the howling, and this time they could hear Hagrid’s words through his sobs. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Gone! Gone! Bless his little beak, he’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">gone! </i> Musta pulled himself free! Beaky, yeh clever boy!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak started to strain against the rope, trying to get back to Hagrid. Harry and Hermione tightened their grip and dug their heels into the Forest floor to stop him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Someone untied him!’ the executioner was snarling. ‘We should search the grounds, the Forest –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Macnair, if Buckbeak has indeed been stolen, do you really think the thief will have led him away on foot?’ said Dumbledore, still sounding amused. ‘Search the skies, if you will … Hagrid, I could do with a cup of tea. Or a large brandy.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘O’ – o’ course, Professor,’ said Hagrid, who sounded weak with happiness. ‘Come in, come in …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione listened closely. They heard footsteps, the soft cursing of the executioner, the snap of the door, and then silence once more. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Now what?’ whispered Harry, looking around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 295 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll have to hide in here,’ said Hermione, who looked very shaken. ‘We need to wait until they’ve gone back to the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then we wait until it’s safe to fly Buckbeak up to Sirius’ window. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He won’t be there for another couple of hours … oh, this is going to be difficult …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She looked nervously over her shoulder into the depths of the Forest. The sun was setting now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’re going to have to move,’ said Harry, thinking hard. ‘We’ve got to be able to see the Whomping Willow, or we won’t know what’s going on.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Hermione, getting a firmer grip on Buckbeak’s rope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But we’ve got to keep out of sight, Harry, remember …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They moved around the edge of the Forest, darkness falling thickly around them, until they were hidden behind a clump of trees through which they could make out the Willow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s Ron!’ said Harry suddenly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A dark figure was sprinting across the lawn and its shout echoed through the still night air. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get away from him – get away – Scabbers, come  <i class=\"calibre4\">here</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then they saw two more figures materialise out of nowhere. Harry watched himself and Hermione chasing after Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Then he saw Ron dive. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Gotcha! </i> Get off, you stinking cat –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s Sirius!’ said Harry. The great shape of the dog had bounded out from the roots of the Willow. They saw him bowl Harry over, then seize Ron … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Looks even worse from here, doesn’t it?’ said Harry, watching the dog pulling Ron into the roots. ‘Ouch – look, I just got walloped by the tree – and so did you – this is  <i class=\"calibre4\">weird</i> –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Whomping Willow was creaking and lashing out with its lower branches; they could see themselves darting here and there, trying to reach the trunk. And then the tree froze. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That was Crookshanks pressing the knot,’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And there we go …’ Harry muttered. ‘We’re in.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moment they disappeared, the tree began to move again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Seconds later, they heard footsteps quite close by. Dumbledore, Macnair, Fudge and the old Committee member were making their way up to the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right after we’d gone down into the passage!’ said Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If  <i class=\"calibre4\">only</i> Dumbledore had come with us …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>296 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Macnair and Fudge would’ve come, too,’ said Harry bitterly. ‘I bet you anything Fudge would’ve told Macnair to murder Sirius on the spot …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They watched the four men climb the castle steps and disappear from view. For a few minutes the scene was deserted. Then – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here comes Lupin!’ said Harry, as they saw another figure sprinting down the stone steps and haring towards the Willow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at the sky. Clouds were obscuring the moon completely. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They watched Lupin seize a broken branch from the ground and prod the knot on the trunk. The tree stopped fighting, and Lupin, too, disappeared into the gap in its roots. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If he’d only grabbed the Cloak,’ said Harry. ‘It’s just lying there …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He turned to Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I just dashed out now and grabbed it, Snape’d never be able to get it and –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">we mustn’t be seen! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How can you stand this?’ he asked Hermione fiercely. ‘Just standing here and watching it happen?’ He hesitated. ‘I’m going to grab the Cloak!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,  <i class=\"calibre4\">no! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione seized the back of Harry’s robes not a moment too soon. Just then, they heard a burst of song. It was Hagrid, making his way up to the castle, singing at the top of his voice, and weaving slightly as he walked. A large bottle was swinging from his hands. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">See? </i>’ Hermione whispered. ‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">See what would have happened? </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">We’ve got to keep out of sight!  <i class=\"calibre4\">No, Buckbeak! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hippogriff was making frantic attempts to get to Hagrid again; Harry seized his rope, too, straining to hold Buckbeak back. They watched Hagrid meander tipsily up to the castle. He was gone. Buckbeak stopped fighting to get away. His head drooped sadly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Barely two minutes later, the castle doors flew open yet again, and Snape had come charging out of them, running towards the Willow. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s fists clenched as they watched Snape skid to a halt next to the tree, looking around. He grabbed the Cloak and held it up. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get your filthy hands off it,’ Harry snarled under his breath. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shh!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 297 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape seized the branch Lupin had used to freeze the tree, prodded the knot, and vanished from view as he put on the Cloak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So that’s it,’ said Hermione quietly. ‘We’re all down there … and now we’ve just got to wait until we come back up again …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She took the end of Buckbeak’s rope and tied it securely around the nearest tree, then sat down on the dry ground, arms around her knees. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, there’s something I don’t understand … why didn’t the Dementors get Sirius? I remember them coming, and then I think I passed out … there were so many of them …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down, too. He explained what he’d seen; how, as the nearest Dementor had lowered its mouth to Harry’s, a large silver something had come galloping across the lake and forced the Dementors to retreat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s mouth was slightly open by the time Harry had finished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But what was it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There’s only one thing it could have been, to make the Dementors go,’ said Harry. ‘A real Patronus. A powerful one.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But who conjured it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry didn’t say anything. He was thinking back to the person he’d seen on the other bank of the lake. He knew who he thought it had been … but how  <i class=\"calibre4\">could</i> it have been? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t you see what they looked like?’ said Hermione eagerly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Was it one of the teachers?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No,’ said Harry. ‘He wasn’t a teacher.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But it must have been a really powerful wizard, to drive all those Dementors away … If the Patronus was shining so brightly, didn’t it light him up? Couldn’t you see –?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I saw him,’ said Harry slowly. ‘But … maybe I imagined it </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… I wasn’t thinking straight … I passed out right afterwards …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Who did you think it was? </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think –’ Harry swallowed, knowing how strange this was going to sound. ‘I think it was my dad.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry glanced up at Hermione and saw that her mouth was fully open now. She was gazing at him with a mixture of alarm and pity. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, your dad’s – well –  <i class=\"calibre4\">dead</i>,’ she said quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know that,’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You think you saw his ghost?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>298 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know … no … he looked solid …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But then – ’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe I was seeing things,’ said Harry. ‘But … from what I could see … it looked like him … I’ve got photos of him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was still looking at him as though worried about his sanity. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know it sounds mad,’ said Harry flatly. He turned to look at Buckbeak, who was digging his beak into the ground, apparently searching for worms. But he wasn’t really watching Buckbeak. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He was thinking about his father, and about his three oldest friends … Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs … Had all four of them been out in the grounds tonight? Wormtail had reappeared this evening when everyone had thought he was dead – was it so impossible his father had done the same? Had he been seeing things across the lake? The figure had been too far away to see distinctly … yet he had felt sure, for a moment, before he’d lost consciousness … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The leaves overhead rustled faintly in the breeze. The moon drifted in and out of sight behind the shifting clouds. Hermione sat with her face turned towards the Willow, waiting. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, at last, after over an hour … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here we come!’ Hermione whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She and Harry got to their feet. Buckbeak raised his head. They saw Lupin, Ron and Pettigrew clambering awkwardly out of the hole in the roots, followed by the unconscious Snape, drifting weirdly upwards. Next came Harry, Hermione and Black. They all began to walk towards the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry’s heart was starting to beat very fast. He glanced up at the sky. Any moment now, that cloud was going to move aside and show the moon … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ Hermione muttered, as though she knew exactly what he was thinking, ‘we’ve got to stay put. We mustn’t be seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There’s nothing we can do …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘So we’re just going to let Pettigrew escape all over again …’ said Harry quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How do you expect to find a rat in the dark?’ snapped Hermione. ‘There’s nothing we can  do!  We  came  back  to  help Sirius. We’re not supposed to be doing anything else!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">All right! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The moon slid out from behind its cloud. They saw the tiny </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 299 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">figures across the grounds stop. Then they saw movement – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘There goes Lupin,’ Hermione whispered. ‘He’s transforming –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione!’ said Harry suddenly. ‘We’ve got to move!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We mustn’t, I keep telling you –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Not to interfere! But Lupin’s going to run into the Forest, right at us!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione gasped. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Quick!’ she moaned, dashing to untie Buckbeak. ‘Quick! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Where are we going to go? Where are we going to hide? The Dementors will be coming any moment –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Back to Hagrid’s!’ Harry said. ‘It’s empty now – come on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They ran, fast as they could, Buckbeak cantering along behind them. They could hear the werewolf howling behind them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The cabin was in sight. Harry skidded to the door, wrenched it open and Hermione and Buckbeak flashed past him; Harry threw himself in after them and bolted the door. Fang the boarhound barked loudly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Shh, Fang, it’s us!’ said Hermione, hurrying over and scratching his ears to quieten him. ‘That was really close!’ she said to Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was looking out of the window. It was much harder to see what was going on from here. Buckbeak seemed very happy to find himself back inside Hagrid’s house. He lay down in front of the fire, folded his wings contentedly and seemed ready for a good nap. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I think I’d better go outside again, you know,’ said Harry slowly. ‘I can’t see what’s going on – we won’t know when it’s time –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione looked up. Her expression was suspicious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m not going to try and interfere,’ said Harry quickly. ‘But if we don’t see what’s going on, how’re we going to know when it’s time to rescue Sirius?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well … OK, then … I’ll wait here with Buckbeak … but Harry, be careful – there’s a werewolf out there – and the Dementors –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stepped outside again and edged around the cabin. He could hear yelping in the distance. That meant the Dementors were closing in on Sirius … he and Hermione would be running to him any moment … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared out towards the lake, his heart doing a kind of drum-roll in his chest. Whoever had sent that Patronus would be </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>300 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">appearing at any moment. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">For a fraction of a second he stood, irresolute, in front of Hagrid’s door.  <i class=\"calibre4\">You must not be seen. </i> But he didn’t want to be seen. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He wanted to do the seeing … he had to know … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And there were the Dementors. They were emerging out of the darkness from every direction, gliding around the edges of the lake  …  they  were  moving  away  from  where  Harry  stood,  to  the opposite bank … he wouldn’t have to get near them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry began to run. He had no thought in his head except his father … If it was him … if it really was him … he had to know, had to find out … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The lake was coming nearer and nearer, but there was no sign of anybody. On the opposite bank, he could see tiny glimmers of silver – his own attempts at a Patronus – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a bush at the very edge of the water. Harry threw himself behind it, peering desperately through the leaves. On the opposite bank, the glimmers of silver were suddenly extinguished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A terrified excitement shot through him – any moment now – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Come on!’ he muttered, staring about. ‘Where are you? Dad, come on –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But no one came. Harry raised his head to look at the circle of Dementors across the lake. One of them was lowering its hood. It was time for the rescuer to appear – but no one was coming to help this time – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then it hit him – he understood. He hadn’t seen his father </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">– he had seen  <i class=\"calibre4\">himself</i> – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry flung himself out from behind the bush and pulled out his wand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘EXPECTO PATRONUM!’ he yelled. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And out of the end of his wand burst, not a shapeless cloud of mist, but a blinding, dazzling, silver animal. He screwed up his eyes, trying to see what it was. It looked like a horse. It was galloping silently away from him, across the black surface of the lake. He saw it lower its head and charge at the swarming Dementors … now it was galloping around and around the black shapes on the ground, and the Dementors were falling back, scattering, retreating into the darkness … they were gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Patronus turned. It was cantering back towards Harry across the still surface of the water. It wasn’t a horse. It wasn’t a unicorn, either. It was a stag. It was shining brightly as the moon </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 301 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">above … it was coming back to him … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It stopped on the bank. Its hooves made no mark on the soft ground as it stared at Harry with its large, silver eyes. Slowly, it bowed its antlered head. And Harry realised … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Prongs, </i>’ he whispered. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But as his trembling fingertips stretched towards the creature, it vanished. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stood there, hand still outstretched. Then, with a great leap of his heart, he heard hooves behind him – he whirled around and saw Hermione dashing towards him, dragging Buckbeak behind her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">What did you do? </i>’ she said fiercely. ‘You said you were only going to keep a lookout!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just saved all our lives …’ said Harry. ‘Get behind here – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">behind this bush – I’ll explain.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione listened to what had just happened with her mouth open yet again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did anyone see you?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, haven’t you been listening?  <i class=\"calibre4\">I</i> saw me but I thought I was my dad! It’s OK!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry, I can’t believe it – you conjured up a Patronus that drove away all those Dementors! That’s very,  <i class=\"calibre4\">very </i> advanced magic …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew I could do it this time,’ said Harry, ‘because I’d already done it … Does that make sense?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t know – Harry, look at Snape!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Together they peered around the bush at the other bank. Snape had regained consciousness. He was conjuring stretchers and lifting the limp forms of Harry, Hermione and Black onto them. A fourth stretcher, no doubt bearing Ron, was already floating at his side. Then, wand held out in front of him, he moved them away towards the castle. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Right, it’s nearly time,’ said Hermione tensely, looking at her watch. ‘We’ve got about forty-five minutes until Dumbledore locks the door to the hospital wing. We’ve got to rescue Sirius and get back into the ward before anybody realises we’re missing …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They waited, watching the moving clouds reflected in the lake, while the bush next to them whispered in the breeze. Buckbeak, bored, was ferreting for worms again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘D’you reckon he’s up there yet?’ said Harry, checking his watch. He looked up at the castle, and began counting the win-</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>302 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">dows to the right of the West Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Look!’ Hermione whispered. ‘Who’s that? Someone’s coming back out of the castle!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry stared through the darkness. The man was hurrying across the grounds, towards one of the entrances. Something shiny glinted in his belt. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Macnair!’ said Harry. ‘The executioner! He’s gone to get the Dementors! This is it, Hermione –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione put her hands on Buckbeak’s back and Harry gave her a leg up. Then he placed his foot on one of the lower branches of the bush and climbed up in front of her. He pulled Buckbeak’s rope back over his neck and tied it to the other side of his collar like reins. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ready?’ he whispered to Hermione. ‘You’d better hold on to me –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He nudged Buckbeak’s sides with his heels. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak soared straight into the dark air. Harry gripped his flanks with his knees, feeling the great wings rising powerfully beneath them. Hermione was holding Harry very tightly around the waist; he could hear her muttering, ‘Oh, no – I don’t like this – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">oh, I  <i class=\"calibre4\">really </i> don’t like this –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry urged Buckbeak forwards. They were gliding quietly towards the upper floors of the castle … Harry pulled hard on the left-hand side of the rope, and Buckbeak turned. Harry was trying to count the windows flashing past – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Whoa!’ he said, pulling backwards as hard as he could. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak slowed down and they found themselves at a stop, unless you counted the fact that they kept rising up and down several feet as he beat his wings to remain airborne. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s there!’ Harry said, spotting Sirius as they rose up beside the window. He reached out, and as Buckbeak’s wings fell, was able to tap sharply on the glass. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black looked up. Harry saw his jaw drop. He leapt from his chair, hurried to the window and tried to open it, but it was locked. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Stand back!’ Hermione called to him, and she took out her wand, still gripping the back of Harry’s robes with her left hand. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Alohomora! </i>’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The window sprang open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How –  <i class=\"calibre4\">how</i> –?’ said Black weakly, staring at the Hippogriff. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Get on – there’s not much time,’ said Harry, gripping Buckbeak </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione’s Secret 303 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">firmly on either side of his sleek neck to hold him steady. ‘You’ve got to get out of here – the Dementors are coming. Macnair’s gone to get them.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black placed a hand on either side of the window-frame and heaved his head and shoulders out of it. It was very lucky he was so thin. In seconds, he had managed to fling one leg over Buckbeak’s back, and pull himself onto the Hippogriff behind Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK, Buckbeak, up!’ said Harry, shaking the rope. ‘Up to the tower – come on!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The Hippogriff gave one sweep of its mighty wings and they were soaring upwards again, high as the top of the West Tower. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak landed with a clatter on the battlements and Harry and Hermione slid off him at once. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius, you’d better go, quick,’ Harry panted. ‘They’ll reach Flitwick’s office any moment, they’ll find out you’ve gone.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Buckbeak pawed the ground, tossing his sharp head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What happened to the other boy? Ron?’ said Sirius urgently. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s going to be OK – he’s still out of it, but Madam Pomfrey says she’ll be able to make him better. Quick – go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But Black was still staring down at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How can I ever thank –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘GO!’ Harry and Hermione shouted together. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Black wheeled Buckbeak around, facing the open sky. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ll see each other again,’ he said. ‘You are – truly your father’s son, Harry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He squeezed Buckbeak’s sides with his heels. Harry and Hermione jumped back as the enormous wings rose once more … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">the Hippogriff took off into the air … he and his rider became smaller and smaller as Harry gazed after them … then a cloud drifted across the moon … they were gone. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><b class=\"calibre3\">— CHAPTER TWENTY-TWO — </b></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Owl Post Again </i></p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Hermione was tugging at his sleeve, staring at her watch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We’ve got exactly ten minutes to get back down to the hospital wing without anybody seeing us – before Dumbledore locks the door –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OK,’ said Harry, wrenching his gaze from the sky, ‘let’s go …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They slipped through the doorway behind them and down a tightly spiralling stone staircase. As they reached the bottom of it, they heard voices. They flattened themselves against the wall and listened. It sounded like Fudge and Snape. They were walking quickly along the corridor at the foot of the staircase. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘… only hope Dumbledore’s not going to make difficulties,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape was saying. ‘The Kiss will be performed immediately?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘As soon as Macnair returns with the Dementors. This whole Black affair has been highly embarrassing. I can’t tell you how much I’m looking forward to informing the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i> that we’ve got him at last … I daresay they’ll want to interview you, Snape … and once young Harry’s back in his right mind, I expect he’ll want to tell the  <i class=\"calibre4\">Prophet</i> exactly how you saved him …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry clenched his teeth. He caught a glimpse of Snape’s smirk as he and Fudge passed Harry and Hermione’s hiding place. Their footsteps died away. Harry and Hermione waited a few moments to make sure they’d really gone, then started to run in the opposite direction. Down one staircase, then another, along a new corridor – then they heard a cackling ahead. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Peeves! </i>’ Harry muttered, grabbing Hermione’s wrist. ‘In here!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They tore into a deserted classroom to their left just in time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Peeves seemed to be bouncing along the corridor in tearing spirits, laughing his head off. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, he’s horrible,’ whispered Hermione, her ear to the door. ‘I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 305 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">bet he’s all excited because the Dementors are going to finish Sirius …’ She checked her watch. ‘Three minutes, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They waited until Peeves’s gloating voice had faded into the distance, then slid back out of the room and broke into a run again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hermione – what’ll happen – if we don’t get back inside – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">before Dumbledore locks the door?’ Harry panted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want to think about it!’ Hermione moaned, checking her watch again. ‘One minute!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They had reached the end of the corridor with the hospital-wing entrance. ‘OK – I can hear Dumbledore,’ said Hermione tensely. ‘Come on, Harry!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">They crept along the corridor. The door opened. Dumbledore’s back appeared. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I am going to lock you in,’ they heard him saying. ‘It is five minutes to midnight. Miss Granger, three turns should do it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Good luck.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore backed out of the room, closed the door and took out his wand to magically lock it. Panicking, Harry and Hermione ran forwards. Dumbledore looked up, and a wide smile appeared under the long silver moustache. ‘Well?’ he said quietly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘We did it!’ said Harry breathlessly. ‘Sirius has gone, on Buckbeak …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore beamed at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well done. I think –’ he listened intently for any sound within the hospital wing. ‘Yes, I think you’ve gone, too. Get inside – I’ll lock you in –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione slipped back inside the dormitory. It was empty except for Ron, who was still lying motionless in the end bed. As the lock clicked behind them, Harry and Hermione crept back to their own beds, Hermione tucking the Time-Turner back under her robes. Next moment, Madam Pomfrey had come striding back out of her office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Did I hear the Headmaster leaving? Am I allowed to look after my patients now?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She was in a very bad mood. Harry and Hermione thought it best to accept their chocolate quietly. Madam Pomfrey stood over them, making sure they ate it. But Harry could hardly swallow. He and Hermione were waiting, listening, their nerves jangling … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And then, as they both took a fourth piece of chocolate from Madam Pomfrey, they heard a distant roar of fury echoing from </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>306 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">somewhere above them … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What was that?’ <i class=\"calibre4\"> </i> said Madam Pomfrey in alarm. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Now they could hear angry voices, growing louder and louder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Madam Pomfrey was staring at the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Really – they’ll wake everybody up! What do they think they’re doing?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry was trying to hear what the voices were saying. They were drawing nearer – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He must have Disapparated, Severus, we should have left somebody in the room with him. When this gets out –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘HE DIDN’T DISAPPARATE!’ Snape roared, now very close at hand. ‘YOU CAN’T APPARATE  <i class=\"calibre4\">OR</i> DISAPPARATE INSIDE THIS </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">CASTLE! THIS – HAS – SOMETHING – TO – DO – WITH – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">POTTER!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Severus – be reasonable – Harry has been locked up –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">BAM. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The door of the hospital wing burst open. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Fudge, Snape and Dumbledore came striding into the ward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore alone looked calm. Indeed, he looked as though he was quite enjoying himself. Fudge appeared angry. But Snape was beside himself. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘OUT WITH IT, POTTER!’ he bellowed. ‘WHAT DID YOU DO?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Snape!’ shrieked Madam Pomfrey. ‘Control yourself!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘See here, Snape, be reasonable,’ said Fudge. ‘This door’s been locked, we just saw –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘THEY HELPED HIM ESCAPE, I KNOW IT!’ Snape howled, pointing at Harry and Hermione. His face was twisted, spit was flying from his mouth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Calm down, man!’ Fudge barked. ‘You’re talking nonsense!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘YOU DON’T KNOW POTTER!’ shrieked Snape. ‘HE DID IT, I KNOW HE DID IT –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That will do, Severus,’ said Dumbledore quietly. ‘Think about what you are saying. This door has been locked since I left the ward ten minutes ago. Madam Pomfrey, have these students left their beds?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Of course not!’ said Madam Pomfrey, bristling. ‘I’ve been with them ever since you left!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well, there you have it, Severus,’ said Dumbledore calmly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Unless you are suggesting that Harry and Hermione are able to be in two places at once, I’m afraid I don’t see any point in troubling them further.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 307 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape stood there, seething, staring from Fudge, who looked thoroughly shocked at his behaviour, to Dumbledore, whose eyes were twinkling behind his glasses. Snape whirled about, robes swishing behind him, and stormed out of the ward. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Fellow seems quite unbalanced,’ said Fudge, staring after him. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’d watch out for him, if I were you, Dumbledore.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, he’s not unbalanced,’ said Dumbledore quietly. ‘He’s just suffered a severe disappointment.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s not the only one!’ puffed Fudge. ‘The  <i class=\"calibre4\">Daily Prophet</i>’s going to have a field day! We had Black cornered and he slipped through our fingers yet again! All it needs now is for the story of that Hippogriff’s escape to get out, and I’ll be a laughing stock! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Well … I’d better go and notify the Ministry …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And the Dementors?’ said Dumbledore. ‘They’ll be removed from the school, I trust?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, yes, they’ll have to go,’ said Fudge, running his fingers distractedly through his hair. ‘Never dreamed they’d attempt to administer the Kiss on an innocent boy … completely out of control … No, I’ll have them packed off back to Azkaban tonight. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Perhaps we should think about dragons at the school entrance …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hagrid would like that,’ said Dumbledore, with a swift smile at Harry and Hermione. As he and Fudge left the dormitory, Madam Pomfrey hurried to the door and locked it again. Muttering angrily to herself, she headed back to her office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a low moan from the other end of the ward. Ron had woken up. They could see him sitting up, rubbing his head, looking around. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What – what happened?’ he groaned. ‘Harry? Why are we in here? Where’s Sirius? Where’s Lupin? What’s going on?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry and Hermione looked at each other. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You explain,’ said Harry, helping himself to some more chocolate. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">When Harry, Ron and Hermione left the hospital wing at noon next day, it was to find an almost deserted castle. The sweltering heat and the end of the exams meant that everyone was taking full advantage of another Hogsmeade visit. Neither Ron nor Hermione felt like going, however, so they and Harry wandered into the grounds, still talking about the extraordinary events of the previous night and wondering where Sirius and Buckbeak were now. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Sitting near the lake, watching the giant squid waving its tentacles </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>308 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">lazily above the water, Harry lost the thread of the conversation as he looked across to the opposite bank. The stag had galloped towards him from there just last night … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">A shadow fell across them and they looked up to see a very bleary-eyed Hagrid, mopping his sweaty face with one of his tablecloth-sized handkerchiefs and beaming down at them. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Know I shouldn’ feel happy, after wha’ happened las’ night,’ he said. ‘I mean, Black escapin’ again, an’ everythin’ – but guess what?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ they said, pretending to look curious. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Beaky! He escaped! He’s free! Bin celebratin’ all night!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s wonderful!’ said Hermione, giving Ron a reproving look because he looked as though he was close to laughing. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah … can’t’ve tied him up properly,’ said Hagrid, gazing happily out over the grounds. ‘I was worried this mornin’, mind … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">thought he mighta met Professor Lupin in the grounds, but Lupin says he never ate anythin’ las’ night …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Harry quickly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Blimey, haven’ yeh heard?’ said Hagrid, his smile fading a little. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He lowered his voice, even though there was nobody in sight. ‘Er – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape told all the Slytherins this mornin’ … thought everyone’d know by now … Professor Lupin’s a werewolf, see. An’ he was loose in the grounds las’ night. He’s packin’ now, o’ course.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘He’s  <i class=\"calibre4\">packing? </i>’ said Harry, alarmed. ‘Why?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Leavin’, isn’ he?’ said Hagrid, looking surprised that Harry had to ask. ‘Resigned firs’ thing this mornin’. Says he can’ risk it happenin’ again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry scrambled to his feet. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m going to see him,’ he said to Ron and Hermione. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if he’s resigned –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘– doesn’t sound like there’s anything we can do –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t care. I still want to see him. I’ll meet you back here.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin’s office door was open. He had already packed most of his things. The Grindylow’s empty tank stood next to his battered old suitcase, which was open and nearly full. Lupin was bending over something on his desk, and only looked up when Harry knocked on the door. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I saw you coming,’ said Lupin, smiling. He pointed to the parchment he had been poring over. It was the Marauder’s Map. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 309 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I just saw Hagrid,’ said Harry. ‘And he said you’d resigned. It’s not true, is it?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m afraid it is,’ said Lupin. He started opening his desk drawers and taking out the contents. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘ <i class=\"calibre4\">Why? </i>’ said Harry. ‘The Ministry of Magic don’t think you were helping Sirius, do they?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin crossed to the door and closed it behind Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘No. Professor Dumbledore managed to convince Fudge that I was trying to save your lives.’ He sighed. ‘That was the final straw for Severus. I think the loss of the Order of Merlin hit him hard. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">So he – er –  <i class=\"calibre4\">accidentally</i> let slip that I am a werewolf this morning at breakfast.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re not leaving just because of that!’ said Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin smiled wryly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This time tomorrow, the owls will start arriving from parents – </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">they will not want a werewolf teaching their children, Harry. And after last night, I see their point. I could have bitten any of you … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">that must never happen again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You’re the best Defence Against the Dark Arts teacher we’ve ever had!’ said Harry. ‘Don’t go!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin shook his head and didn’t speak. He carried on emptying his drawers. Then, while Harry was trying to think of a good argument to make him stay, Lupin said, ‘From what the Headmaster told me this morning, you saved a lot of lives last night, Harry. If I’m proud of anything, it’s how much you’ve learned. Tell me about your Patronus.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘How d’you know about that?’ said Harry, distracted. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What else could have driven the Dementors back?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry told Lupin what had happened. When he’d finished, Lupin was smiling again. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, your father was always a stag when he transformed,’ he said. ‘You guessed right … that’s why we called him Prongs.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin threw his last few books into his case, closed the desk drawers and turned to look at Harry. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Here – I brought this from the Shrieking Shack last night,’ he said,  handing  Harry  back  the  Invisibility  Cloak.  ‘And  …’  he  hesitated, then held out the Marauder’s Map, too. ‘I am no longer your teacher, so I don’t feel guilty about giving you this back as well. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It’s no use to me, and I daresay you, Ron and Hermione will find uses for it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>310 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry took the map and grinned. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You told me Moony, Wormtail, Padfoot and Prongs would’ve wanted to lure me out of school … you said they’d have thought it was funny.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘And so we would have done,’ said Lupin, now reaching down to close his case. ‘I have no hesitation in saying that James would have been highly disappointed if his son had never found any of the secret passages out of the castle.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">There was a knock on the door. Harry hastily stuffed the Marauder’s Map and the Invisibility Cloak into his pocket. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It was Professor Dumbledore. He didn’t look surprised to see Harry there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Your carriage is at the gates, Remus,’ he said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Thank you, Headmaster.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin picked up his old suitcase and the empty Grindylow tank. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Well – goodbye, Harry,’ he said, smiling. ‘It has been a real pleasure teaching you. I feel sure we’ll meet again some time. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Headmaster, there is no need to see me to the gates, I can manage …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry had the impression that Lupin wanted to leave as quickly as possible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Goodbye, then, Remus,’ said Dumbledore soberly. Lupin shifted the Grindylow tank slightly so that he and Dumbledore could shake hands. Then, with a final nod to Harry, and a swift smile, Lupin left the office. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry sat down in his vacated chair, staring glumly at the floor. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He heard the door close and looked up. Dumbledore was still there. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Why so miserable, Harry?’ he said quietly. ‘You should be very proud of yourself after last night.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It didn’t make any difference,’ said Harry bitterly. ‘Pettigrew got away.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Didn’t make any difference?’ said Dumbledore quietly. ‘It made all the difference in the world, Harry. You helped uncover the truth. You saved an innocent man from a terrible fate.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Terrible. </i> Something stirred in Harry’s memory.  <i class=\"calibre4\">Greater and more</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">terrible than ever before </i>… Professor Trelawney’s prediction! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Professor Dumbledore – yesterday, when I was having my Divination exam, Professor Trelawney went very – very strange.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Indeed?’ said Dumbledore. ‘Er – stranger than usual, you mean?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 311 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes … her voice went all deep and her eyes rolled and she said </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">… she said Voldemort’s servant was going to set out to return to him before midnight … she said the servant would help him come back to power.’ Harry stared up at Dumbledore. ‘And then she sort of became normal again, and she couldn’t remember anything she’d said. Was it – was she making a real prediction?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Dumbledore looked mildly impressed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Do you know, Harry, I think she might have been,’ he said thoughtfully. ‘Who’d have thought it? That brings her total of real predictions up to two. I should offer her a pay rise …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But –’ Harry looked at him, aghast. How could Dumbledore take this so calmly? </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But – I stopped Sirius and Professor Lupin killing Pettigrew! </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">That makes it my fault, if Voldemort comes back!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It does not,’ said Dumbledore quietly. ‘Hasn’t your experience with the Time-Turner taught you anything, Harry? The consequences of our actions are always so complicated, so diverse, that predicting the future is a very difficult business indeed … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Professor Trelawney, bless her, is living proof of that. You did a very noble thing, in saving Pettigrew’s life.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But if he helps Voldemort back to power –!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Pettigrew owes his life to you. You have sent Voldemort a deputy who is in your debt. When one wizard saves another wizard’s life, it creates a certain bond between them … and I’m much mistaken if Voldemort wants his servant in the debt of Harry Potter.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I don’t want a bond with Pettigrew!’ said Harry. ‘He betrayed my parents!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘This is magic at its deepest, its most impenetrable, Harry. But trust me … the time may come when you will be very glad you saved Pettigrew’s life.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry couldn’t imagine when that would be. Dumbledore looked as though he knew what Harry was thinking. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I knew your father very well, both at Hogwarts and later, Harry,’ he said gently. ‘He would have saved Pettigrew too, I am sure of it.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked up at him. Dumbledore wouldn’t laugh – he could tell Dumbledore … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Last night … I thought it was my dad who’d conjured my Patronus. I mean, when I saw myself across the lake … I thought I </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>312 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">was seeing him.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘An easy mistake to make,’ said Dumbledore softly. ‘I expect you’re tired of hearing it, but you do look  <i class=\"calibre4\">extraordinarily</i> like James. Except for your eyes … you have your mother’s eyes.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry shook his head. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It was stupid, thinking it was him,’ he muttered. ‘I mean, I knew he was dead.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘You think the dead we have loved ever truly leave us? You think that we don’t recall them more clearly than ever in times of great trouble? Your father is alive in you, Harry, and shows himself most plainly when you have need of him. How else could you produce that  <i class=\"calibre4\">particular</i> Patronus? Prongs rode again last night.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It took a moment for Harry to realise what Dumbledore had said. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Sirius told me all about how they became Animagi last night,’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">said Dumbledore, smiling. ‘An extraordinary achievement – not least, keeping it quiet from me. And then I remembered the most unusual form your Patronus took, when it charged Mr Malfoy down at your Quidditch match against Ravenclaw. So you did see your father last night, Harry … you found him inside yourself.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And Dumbledore left the office, leaving Harry to his very confused thoughts. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Nobody at Hogwarts knew the truth of what had happened the night that Sirius, Buckbeak and Pettigrew had vanished except Harry, Ron, Hermione and Professor Dumbledore. As the end of term approached, Harry heard many different theories about what had really happened, but none of them came close to the truth. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Malfoy was furious about Buckbeak. He was convinced that Hagrid had found a way of smuggling the Hippogriff to safety, and seemed outraged that he and his father had been outwitted by a gamekeeper. Percy Weasley, meanwhile, had much to say on the subject of Sirius’ escape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘If I manage to get into the Ministry, I’ll have a lot of proposals to make about Magical Law Enforcement!’ he told the only person who would listen – his girlfriend, Penelope. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Though the weather was perfect, though the atmosphere was so cheerful, though he knew they had achieved the near impossible in helping Sirius to freedom, Harry had never approached the end of a school year in worse spirits. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He certainly wasn’t the only one who was sorry to see Professor </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 313 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Lupin go. The whole of Harry’s Defence Against the Dark Arts class were miserable about his resignation. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Wonder what they’ll give us next year?’ said Seamus Finnigan gloomily. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Maybe a vampire,’ suggested Dean Thomas hopefully. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">It wasn’t only Professor Lupin’s departure that was weighing on Harry’s mind. He couldn’t help thinking a lot about Professor Trelawney’s prediction. He kept wondering where Pettigrew was now, whether he had sought sanctuary with Voldemort yet. But the thing that was lowering Harry’s spirits most of all was the prospect of returning to the Dursleys. For maybe half an hour, a glorious half hour, he had believed he would be living with Sirius from now on … his parents’ best friend … it would have been the next best thing to having his own father back. And while no news of Sirius was definitely good news, because it meant he had successfully gone into hiding, Harry couldn’t help feeling miserable when he thought of the home he might have had, and the fact that it was now impossible. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The exam results came out on the last day of term. Harry, Ron and Hermione had passed every subject. Harry was amazed that he had got through Potions. He had a shrewd suspicion that Dumbledore had stepped in to stop Snape failing him on purpose. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Snape’s behaviour towards Harry over the past week had been quite alarming. Harry wouldn’t have thought it possible that Snape’s dislike for him could increase, but it certainly had done. A muscle twitched unpleasantly at the corner of Snape’s thin mouth every time he looked at Harry, and he was constantly flexing his fingers, as though itching to place them around Harry’s throat. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Percy had got his top-grade N.E.W.Ts; Fred and George had scraped a handful of O.W.Ls each. Gryffindor house, meanwhile, largely thanks to their spectacular performance in the Quidditch Cup, had won the House Championship for the third year running. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This meant that the end-of-term feast took place amid decorations of scarlet and gold, and that the Gryffindor table was the noisiest of the lot, as everybody celebrated. Even Harry managed to forget about the journey back to the Dursleys next day as he ate, drank, talked and laughed with the rest. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">* </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">As the Hogwarts Express pulled out of the station next morning, Hermione gave Harry and Ron some surprising news. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>314 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I went to see Professor McGonagall this morning, just before breakfast. I’ve decided to drop Muggle Studies.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘But you passed your exam with three hundred and twenty per cent!’ said Ron. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I know,’ sighed Hermione, ‘but I can’t stand another year like this one. That Time-Turner, it was driving me mad. I’ve handed it in. Without Muggle Studies and Divination, I’ll be able to have a normal timetable again.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I still can’t  <i class=\"calibre4\">believe </i> you didn’t tell us about it,’ said Ron grumpily. ‘We’re supposed to be your  <i class=\"calibre4\">friends</i>.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I promised I wouldn’t tell  <i class=\"calibre4\">anyone</i>,’ said Hermione severely. She looked around at Harry, who was watching Hogwarts disappear from view behind a mountain. Two whole months before he’d see it again … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Oh, cheer up, Harry!’ said Hermione sadly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’m OK,’ said Harry quickly. ‘Just thinking about the holidays.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah, I’ve been thinking about them, too,’ said Ron. ‘Harry, you’ve got to come and stay with us. I’ll fix it up with Mum and Dad, then I’ll call you. I know how to use a fellytone now –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘A   <i class=\"calibre4\">telephone</i>, Ron,’ said Hermione. ‘Honestly,  <i class=\"calibre4\">you</i> should take Muggle Studies next year …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron ignored her. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s the Quidditch World Cup this summer! How about it, Harry? Come and stay, and we’ll go and see it! Dad can usually get tickets from work.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">This proposal had the effect of cheering Harry up a great deal. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yeah … I bet the Dursleys’d be pleased to let me come … especially after what I did to Aunt Marge …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Feeling considerably more cheerful, Harry joined Ron and Hermione in several games of Exploding Snap, and when the witch with the tea trolley arrived, he bought himself a very large lunch, though nothing with chocolate in it. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">But it was late in the afternoon before the thing that made him truly happy turned up … </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Harry,’ said Hermione suddenly, peering over his shoulder. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that thing outside your window?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry turned to look outside. Something very small and grey was bobbing in and out of sight beyond the glass. He stood up for a better look and saw that it was a tiny owl, carrying a letter which was much too big for it. The owl was so small, in fact, that </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 315 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">it kept tumbling over in the air, buffeted this way and that in the train’s slipstream. Harry quickly pulled down the window, stretched out his arm and caught it. It felt like a very fluffy Snitch. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">He brought it carefully inside. The owl dropped its letter onto Harry’s seat and began zooming around their compartment, apparently very pleased with itself for accomplishing its task. Hedwig clicked her beak with a sort of dignified disapproval. Crookshanks sat up in his seat, following the owl with his great yellow eyes. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron, noticing this, snatched the owl safely out of harm’s way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry picked up the letter. It was addressed to him. He ripped open the letter and shouted, ‘It’s from Sirius!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What?’ said Ron and Hermione excitedly. ‘Read it aloud!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Dear Harry, </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I hope this finds you before you reach your aunt and uncle. I</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">don’t know whether they’re used to owl post. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Buckbeak and I are in hiding. I won’t tell you where, in case</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">this falls into the wrong hands. I have some doubt about the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">owl’s reliability, but he is the best I could find, and he did seem</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">eager for the job. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I believe the Dementors are still searching for me, but they</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">haven’t a hope of finding me here. I am planning to allow some</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Muggles to glimpse me soon, a long way from Hogwarts, so that</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the security on the castle will be lifted. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">There is something I never got round to telling you during</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">our brief meeting. It was I who sent you the Firebolt –</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Ha!’ said Hermione triumphantly. ‘See! I  <i class=\"calibre4\">told  </i> you it was from him!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, but he hadn’t jinxed it, had he?’ said Ron. ‘Ouch!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The tiny owl, now hooting happily in his hand, had nibbled one of his fingers in what it seemed to think was an affectionate way. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Crookshanks took the order to the Owl Office for me. I used</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">your name but told them to take the gold from Gringotts vault</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">number seven hundred and eleven – my own. Please consider it</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">as thirteen birthdays’ worth of presents from your godfather. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I would also like to apologise for the fright I think I gave</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">you, that night last year when you left your uncle’s house. I had</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>316 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry Potter </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">only hoped to get a glimpse of you before starting my journey</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">north, but I think the sight of me alarmed you. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I am enclosing something else for you, which I think will</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">make your next year at Hogwarts more enjoyable. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">If ever you need me, send word. Your owl will find me. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I’ll write again soon. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">Sirius</i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry looked eagerly inside the envelope. There was another piece of parchment in there. He read it through quickly and felt suddenly as warm and contented as though he’d swallowed a bottle of hot Butterbeer in one go. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I, Sirius Black, Harry Potter’s godfather, hereby give him permission to visit Hogsmeade at weekends. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’ll be good enough for Dumbledore!’ said Harry happily. He looked back at Sirius’ letter. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Hang on, there’s a PS ...’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"> <i class=\"calibre4\">I thought your friend Ron might like to keep this owl, as it’s my</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">fault he no longer has a rat. </i> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Ron’s eyes widened. The minute owl was still hooting excitedly. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Keep him?’ he said uncertainly. He looked closely at the owl for a moment, then, to Harry and Hermione’s great surprise, he held him out for Crookshanks to sniff. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What d’you reckon?’ Ron asked the cat. ‘Definitely an owl?’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Crookshanks purred. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘That’s good enough for me,’ said Ron happily. ‘He’s mine.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Harry read and re-read the letter from Sirius all the way back into King’s Cross station. It was still clutched tightly in his hand as he, Ron and Hermione stepped back through the barrier of platform nine and three-quarters. Harry spotted Uncle Vernon at once. He was standing a good distance from Mr and Mrs Weasley, eyeing them suspiciously, and when Mrs Weasley hugged Harry in greeting, his worst suspicions about them seemed confirmed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘I’ll call about the World Cup!’ Ron yelled after Harry, as Harry bid him and Hermione goodbye, then wheeled the trolley bearing his trunk and Hedwig’s cage towards Uncle Vernon, who greeted </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Owl Post Again 317 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">him in usual fashion. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘What’s that?’ he snarled, staring at the envelope Harry was still clutching in his hand. ‘If it’s another form for me to sign, you’ve got another –’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘It’s not,’ said Harry cheerfully. ‘It’s a letter from my godfather.’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Godfather?’ spluttered Uncle Vernon. ‘You haven’t got a godfather!’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">‘Yes, I have,’ said Harry brightly. ‘He was my mum and dad’s best friend. He’s a convicted murderer, but he’s broken out of wizard prison and he’s on the run. He likes to keep in touch with me, though … keep up with my news … check I’m happy …’ </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">And grinning broadly at the look of horror on Uncle Vernon’s face, Harry set off towards the station exit, Hedwig rattling along in front of him, for what looked like a much better summer than the last. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\"><a></a>\n<a></a> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. (JOANNE KATHLEEN) ROWLING  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">has written fiction since she was a child. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Born in 1965, she grew up in Chepstow and wrote her first ‘book’ at the age of six  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">- a story about a rabbit called Rabbit. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">She studied French and Classics at Exeter University, then moved to London to  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">work at Amnesty International, and then to Portugal to teach English as a foreign language, before settling in Edinburgh. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">The idea for Harry Potter occurred to her on the train from Manchester to London, where she says Harry Potter ‘just strolled into my head fully formed’, and by the time she had arrived at King’s Cross, many of the characters had taken shape. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">During the next five years she outlined the plots for each book and began writing the first in the series,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Philosopher’s Stone, </i> which was first published by Bloomsbury in 1997. The  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">other Harry Potter titles:  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">the Chamber of Secrets, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Prisoner of Azkaban, Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Goblet of Fire, </i> and  <i class=\"calibre4\">Harry Potter and the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Order of the Phoenix, </i> followed. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">J. K. Rowling has also written three other companion books,  <i class=\"calibre4\">Quidditch Through the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Ages, </i>  <i class=\"calibre4\">Fantastic Beasts and Where to</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Find Them</i> and <i class=\"calibre4\"> The Tales of Beedle the</i> <i class=\"calibre4\">Bard, </i> in aid of Comic Relief. </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-2fbf83 twpub-4b86c905eb0f0c7d-9882b5\"><p class=\"calibre1\">Jacket Design: William Webb </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/4b86c905eb0f0c7d/text/000005656",
